INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(1, '<selfname> has accepted these missions.'),
(2, 'What would you like to know,<selfname>?'),
(3, 'Under construction'),
(4, '<selfname> can undertake these missions in training.'),
(5, '<selfname>, click on Save Settings to change your system settings.'),
(6, '<selfname> has accepted these missions.'),
(7, 'What would you like to find out, <selfname>?'),
(8, 'Under construction'),
(9, '<selfname> can undertake these missions in training.'),
(10, '<selfname>, click on Save Settings to change your system settings.'),
(11, 'Your bag is full. You cannot receive the reward.'),
(101, 'How are things in Moradon?|I don`t have anything to ask you yet.'),
(102, 'What mission do you want?'),
(103, 'They say theres a new Moradon Castle. I cant wait to see it!'),
(104, 'They say theres a new Moradon Castle. I cant wait to see it!'),
(105, 'Master! [Kaishan`s Daughter] Menissiah is looking for help.. ..'),
(106, 'You can exchange the Event Item [Voucher for Tears of Karivdis] that you got from purchasing Ultra Premium through me.|Do you want to exchange it now?'),
(107, 'Insufficient space.|You need 4 inventory slots to exchange [Voucher for Tears of Karivdis].'),
(108, 'Insufficient space.|You need 4 inventory slots to exchange [Voucher for Tears of Karivdis].'),
(109, 'Master, Since youre now level 60, why not hit Islante and Ronark Land for more xp and adventure? You should look for Islantes Pablo and Ronark Lands Elrod'),
(110, 'Master. Since youre now level 60, why not hit Islante and Ronark Land for more xp and adventure? You should look for Islantes Agatha and Ronark Lands Della'),
(111, 'Master! [Kaishan`s Daughter] Menissiah is looking for help.. ..'),
(115, 'Looks like you`re a just-arrived new kid on the block. Looks like you didn`t even pay your respects.. Paying respects is as easy as saying hello and presenting a locally produced gift to [Grand Merchant] Kaishan.'),
(116, 'If you bring a fee of 3000 Noah, the [Grand Merchant] Kaishan will give you the first transfer. [Grand Merchant] Kaishan is up in the north from the center of Moradon.'),
(117, ' [Grand Merchant] Kaishan will be pleased to receive a silk spool for making Menissiah Atienne`s dress whom he dotes on.|Then you`ll be able to receive the reward below.'),
(118, 'Dark Forces are coming over the hill...'),
(119, '<selfname>... hmmm~ not a bad name.'),
(120, 'The two faces of the monk. Beware the darkness!|The soulless monks attack from the dark behind your eyes.'),
(121, 'I dont wanna get any closer to you... you dont have time for me anyway. Ah~ what a downer.'),
(122, 'He seems to be a nomad monk of the Esoteric Buddhist order... but at night does he change into a savage mage of the darkness? Here, Im also known as  Paramoon. Cute name, eh? MUAHAHAHA-'),
(123, 'Pablos an odd one for sure... But Im still curious about his identity.'),
(124, 'Careful... Careful... Darkness is falling... The darkness...'),
(125, 'Did you wrestle with Paramun? HAHA- Dont make a face for that! Wasnt it a good experience?'),
(126, 'What?? Youre already over level 70 - too high! Heh.'),
(127, 'Dark Forces are coming over the hill...'),
(128, '<selfname>... hmmm~ not a bad name.'),
(129, 'The two faces of the monk... Beware of the darkness!|The soulless monks attack from the dark behind your eyes...'),
(130, 'I dont wanna get any closer to you... you dont have time for me anyway. Ah~ what a downer.'),
(131, 'You`ve gathered all the Apple of Moradon * Quick, take them to [Grand Merchant`s Daughter] Menissiah'),
(132, 'You`ve gathered all the Apple of Moradon * Quick, take them to [Grand Merchant`s Daughter] Menissiah'),
(133, 'He seems to be a nomad monk of the Esoteric Buddhist order... but at night does he change into a savage mage of the darkness? Here, Im also known as  Paramun. Isnt it a cute name? HAHAHA-'),
(134, 'For some reason Pablo is scary or mentally strange... but Im more curious about Pablos identity.'),
(135, 'Careful... Careful... Darkness is spreading... The darkness.'),
(136, 'Did you wrestle with Paramun? HAHA- Dont make that look. Dont you think it was good experience?'),
(137, 'What?? You are over level 70... too high heh-'),
(138, 'Why so busy? Come here and lets dicuss about how the world is going around.'),
(139, 'He is a nomad monk of the Esoteric Buddhist order... but is his real identity a savage mage of darkness at night? Here Im also called  Brahman. I have a feeling this is the start of a beautiful friendship... KeKe~'),
(140, 'You still haven`t paid your respects to [Grand Merchant] Kaishan? We can`t guarantee your safety if you go around Moradon without having seen him'),
(141, 'Those soulless monks... for some reason I pity them.'),
(142, 'Do you know how it feels to lose your soul? It sure is terrible to become a mindless beast every night.'),
(143, 'Why so busy? Come here and lets shoot the breeze a while.'),
(144, 'He seems to be a nomad monk of the Esoteric Buddhist order... but at night does he change into a savage mage of the darkness? Here, Im also known as  Brahman. I have a feeling this is the start of a beautiful friendship... KeKe~'),
(145, 'Those soulless monks... for some reason I pity them.'),
(146, 'Are you enjoying your trip?'),
(147, 'What mission do you want?'),
(148, 'Do you know how it feels to lose your soul? It sure is terrible to become a mindless beast every night.'),
(149, 'Such an ominous and heavy force...? Its them... It must be them.'),
(150, 'Hello, welcome to Moradon! Have you seen worms in front of the village? The Apple of Moradon that they have are useful for various purposes as they are strong. If it is okay with you.. Can you find and bring the Apple of Moradon to me?'),
(151, 'It was a hard fight, Master-'),
(152, 'The power of their sorcery... As this evil energy melts into your body, it drags your soul down into an endless hell.'),
(153, 'Have I ever told you that I found peace because of you? Hmm...'),
(154, 'Such an ominous and heavy force...? Its them... It must be them.'),
(155, 'Its a Troll Conjurator|Nobody emits evil force like they do! If the evil force is allowed to spread, all Islante will be hell-bound to damnation. But why do I feel such peace as soon as I see you??'),
(156, 'If you find and bring three of them to me so that I can make strong cloth, I will give you a rich reward. Apple of Moradon can be obtained from the worms in front of the castle.'),
(157, 'Oh.. Dear.. Cloth can be made only when three Apple of Moradon are collected..'),
(158, 'I feel good about all of the Apple of Moradon you brought!'),
(159, 'You`re that stranger [Manager] Billbor mentioned? |You have very pleasant silk spools. Are you going to give them to me?'),
(160, 'You`re that stranger [Manager] Billbor mentioned? |You have very pleasant silk spools. Are you going to give them to me?'),
(161, 'It was a hard fight, Master-'),
(162, 'Its the power of their sorcery... As the evil energy melts into your body, it drags your soul down into an endless hell.'),
(163, 'Have I ever told you that I found peace because of you? Hmm...'),
(164, 'Whats it like? When the coldness eats into your bones? Do you know? Thereve been a lot of miserable fellas suffering from the pain lately... Seems someones been provoking the Apostle of Piercing Colds anger... Heh.'),
(165, 'Havent you already got a lot of commitments?  This doesnt feel good. Right now, youve got to deal with the jobs youve been asked to.'),
(166, 'There are too many sentinels around.. Come back some other time..'),
(167, 'What mission are you going to undertake?'),
(168, 'Because of those guys trying to steal the Apostle of Piercing Colds high quality Pet Transformation Scroll, theyre just making the Apostle more fuious. Tut Tut~ Its not even worth trying... itll only end with more souls floating up to heaven.'),
(169, 'Master, you tried hard and fought well. How good is this high quality Pet Transformation Scroll the Apostle of Piercing Cold owns?'),
(170, 'Uh-oh, Master, you`re short on Noahs. You`ll have a hard time making ends meet.. Go see Sentinel Patrick. I heard they`re hiring extra guards.'),
(171, 'If your bones start to freeze under their Glacier Spells... How would you counter it? Well, its not easy~'),
(172, 'Uh-oh, Master, you`re short on Noahs. You`ll have a hard time making ends meet.. Go see Sentinel Patrick. I heard they`re hiring extra guards.'),
(173, 'You haven`t completed the monster hunting mission. Come back after you`ve finished it.'),
(174, 'youre still standing on your own two feet, so obviously it wasnt that bad. You know, youre quite a strange guy. Ha!~'),
(175, 'Moradon maintains peace at all times as we protect it from monsters which were created by the war against Pathos. Incidentally, I`m running low on guards lately. Can you lend a hand?'),
(176, 'If you exit through that gate you`ll spot Worms right outside. They began to breed after the war against Pathos. Go hunt me 5 of those pesky monsters!!'),
(177, 'Whats it like? When the coldness eats into your bones? Do you know? Thereve been a lot of miserable fellas suffering from the pain lately... Seems someones been   provoking the Apostle of Piercing Colds anger... Heh.'),
(178, 'Havent you already got a lot of commitments?  This doesnt feel good. Right now, youve got to deal with the jobs youve been asked to.'),
(179, 'Because of those guys trying to steal the Apostle of Piercing Colds high quality Pet Transformation Scroll, theyre just making the Apostle more fuious. Tut Tut~ Its not even worth trying... itll only end with more souls floating up to heaven.'),
(180, 'Master, you tried hard and fought well. How good is this high quality Pet Transformation Scroll the Apostle of Piercing Cold owns?'),
(181, 'I hunted all 5 Worms. Report it to the guards'),
(182, 'I hunted all 5 Worms. Report it to the guards'),
(183, 'If your bones start to freeze under their Glacier Spells... How would you counter it? Well, its not easy~'),
(184, 'So, what do you think? Was it a good experience? Well youre still standing on your own two feet, so obviously it wasnt that bad. You know, youre quite a strange guy. Ha!~'),
(185, 'Can you see the flames, dancing over the desert? Hmmm~ you can see them quite clearly tonight, its unusually beautiful. KeKe~ Come and look... KeKe~'),
(186, 'Listen, capture all 5. Is that the best you can do?'),
(187, 'You are better than you look. Haha... You say it was a joke? Ive prepared compensation for your trouble. Please kindly accept it.'),
(188, 'Youre always busy. Whats up with that? Are you running away from someone? KeKe~'),
(189, 'What if its the enemy? Youre going to take on the entire Magic Army? Ha Ha- They serve  the Apostle of Flames Theyre usually known as the Red Magic Army. Ho! The hand of help has arrived to crush the cruel Red Army, eh? Well soon see...'),
(190, 'Master, I award you with the title of Supreme Warrior of The Karus, for your amazing victory over the Red Army~ Hee Hee!~'),
(191, 'As the materials have alredy been secured, I have nothing to ask of you for today... I will ask you a favor next time~'),
(192, 'Will you help me?'),
(193, 'Will you help me?'),
(194, 'Those dazzling flames... the Red Magic Army... the Apostle of Flames...'),
(195, 'Wonder what Menissiah`s up to lately. I miss her. Let`s go see her, Master.'),
(196, 'You... will become an... in Karus... I can feel it...'),
(197, 'Wonder what Menissiah`s up to lately. I miss her. Let`s go see her, Master.'),
(198, 'Can you see the flames, dancing over the desert? Hmmm~ you can see them quite clearly tonight, its unusually beautiful. KeKe~ Come and look... KeKe~'),
(199, 'Youre always busy. Whats up with that? Are you running away from someone? KeKe~'),
(200, 'As my father has issued an order, I cant go out of the castle gate on my own authority. So can we be friends with each other? We appear to be of similar age and the foreigner Inisia may have a lot of stories... Oh! This is a secret from my father'),
(201, 'Oh? Nowadays, I am totally preoccupied with the manufacturing of medications learned from my teacher but it is so hard to find the materials for practice. Can you find two Apples of Moradon for me?'),
(202, 'What if its the enemy? Youre going to take on the entire Magic Army? Ha Ha- They serve  the Apostle of Flames Theyre usually known as the Red Magic Army. Ho! The hand of help has arrived to crush the cruel Red Army, eh? Well soon see...'),
(203, 'Master, I award you with the title of Supreme Warrior of El Morad, for your amazing victory over the Red Army~ Hee Hee!~'),
(204, 'Those dazzling flames... the Red Magic Army... the Apostle of Flames...'),
(205, 'You... will become an... in El Morad... I can feel it...'),
(206, 'All the ingredients requested by [Grand Merchant`s Daughter] Menissiah have been collected.'),
(207, 'All the ingredients requested by [Grand Merchant`s Daughter] Menissiah have been collected.'),
(208, 'I have felt their burning gaze... Their bloodthirsty rage is matched only by their incredible stamina... theyre unbearable to be near, let alone fight. Even if you defeat them youll only do so at great loss...'),
(209, 'Just go. Now. Seems like youve already got a lot of commitments.'),
(211, 'In order to make the medication, I need two Apple of Moradon.'),
(212, 'Thanks to you, I will be able to finish the practice safely.'),
(213, 'Its the  Doom SoldierArmy... The resurrection of these guys aint good news right now, what with us fighting the El Morad Army too. If they hit us from behind... Ah~ isnt there anywhere to make a stand for Karus in Ronark Land...'),
(214, 'Well Master, nice job easing Elrods mind a little.'),
(215, 'Ahh, that baleful red gaze, dripping with evil bloodthirtyness... Its the Doom Soldiers alright. Theyre knights too. Darkness Knights...'),
(216, 'Is it you that confounded the Doom Soldier Armies and drove them back? I never wouldve guessed youd become so talented. Youre a real asset ...  Your services are most appreciated.'),
(217, 'Stop, thats fine. More experience at your level is meaningless. Go and find a tougher mission.'),
(218, 'I have felt their burning gaze... Their bloodthirsty rage is matched only by their incredible stamina... theyre unbearable to be near, let alone fight. Even if you defeat them youll only do so at great loss...'),
(219, 'Just go. Now. Seems like youve already got a lot of commitments.'),
(220, 'Patrick`s hiring more guards. Go and apply.'),
(221, 'Its the Doom Soldier Army... The resurrection of these guys aint good news right now, what with us fighting the Karus too. If they hit us from behind... Ah~ isnt there anywhere for El Morad to make a stand in Ronark Land...'),
(222, 'Well Master, nice job easing Dellas mind a little.'),
(223, 'Patrick`s hiring more guards. Go and apply.'),
(224, 'Ahh, that baleful red gaze, dripping with evil bloodthirtyness... Its the Doom Soldiers alright. Theyre knights too. Darkness Knights...'),
(225, 'Have you seen monsters that look like rats in front of Moradon Castle?'),
(226, 'Is it you that confounded the Doom Soldier Armies and drove them back? I never wouldve guessed youd become so talented. Youre a real asset ...  Your services are most appreciated.'),
(227, 'Stop, thats fine. More experience at your level is meaningless. Go and find a tougher mission.'),
(228, 'They`re called Bandicoots. They sometimes venture into the castle and gnaw on the gates and skedaddle. What a major headache. Get rid of 5 of them.'),
(229, 'I learned a different potion production method, and I need Apple of Moradon this time. If you bring me 5 Apple of Moradon, I think I can make antifebrile. Will you help me?'),
(230, 'Darn it! How did this happen? Our base was infiltrated during the night and our supplies set on fire. Luckily a guard survived and saw the culprit at work, so we know who it is. Still, something isnt right here...'),
(231, 'It was a Dark Knight who did it. But why? There mustve had a specific motive. But what, we dont know. Well just have to capture one of the Knights.'),
(232, 'Whoa, Master, you`ve caught all 5 Bandicoots. Bring them to the sentinel and get our reward.'),
(233, 'Whoa, Master, you`ve caught all 5 Bandicoots. Bring them to the sentinel and get our reward.'),
(234, 'Will there be some hidden truth, as Elrod expects?'),
(235, 'No... it doesnt fit. Darkness Knights dont go randomly doing stuff like this. Well capture one and interrogate it.'),
(236, 'Wow, I underestimated you. Here, this is compensation for guarding Moradon.'),
(237, 'You still haven`t caught all 5 Bandicoots?'),
(238, 'Darkness conceals the truth, but it cannot destroy it. Ha, just as expected, El Morad was behind this one. They paid the Darkness Knights to make it look like a random attack. The El Moradians had only recently attacked, so we werent expecting them back again so soon.'),
(239, 'Darn it! How did this happen? Our base was infiltrated during the night and our supplies set on fire. Luckily a guard survived and saw the culprit at work, so we know who it is. Still, something isnt right here...'),
(240, 'It was a  Dark Knight who did it. But why? There mustve had a specific motive. But what, we dont know. Well just have to capture one of the Knights.'),
(241, 'I don`t have time to make your armor right now. I`m researching infusing steel with new magic.'),
(242, 'Which one is tempting?'),
(243, 'Will there be something hidden as Della expected?'),
(244, 'No... it doesnt fit. Darkness Knights dont go randomly doing stuff like this. Well capture one and interrogate it.'),
(245, 'Do you know anything about <font color=@#006699@>weapon upgrade</font> by any chance? The true charm of a knight comes from the weapon. In other words, I mean that strong power can be created [forged?] into the weapon that you have!'),
(246, 'Darkness conceals the truth, but it cannot destroy it. Ha, just as expected, Karus was behind this one. They paid the Dark Knights to make it look like a random attack. Karus had only recently attacked, so we werent expecting them back again so soon.'),
(247, 'Its do or die here! And ¡‹ere is Ronark Land, if you didnt know. The battles against El Morad here rage ever on. Therell be no peace until the day Karus flag is raised over the whole territory.'),
(248, 'Dont think, though, that El Morad is our only enemy here. Eveyone and everything here is our enemy! Remember that, and you might stand a chance. Of all our enemies here, the  Troll Conjuratorhas unrivaled strength and Darkness Spells. Wouldnt you like to give ¡ˆm a kicking? Itd be a good measure of your skills...'),
(249, 'Master, you really gave it some out there! With your skills, you could be the next Outpost Captain! KeKe~'),
(250, '(Feels like hes going to be Top Dog in Karus...)'),
(251, 'Master! [Blacksmith] Heppa, the most famous guy in Moradon, is looking for you.'),
(252, 'Not just anyone could do that. But you managed, and magnificently so. <selfname>!! You are truly one of the finest of Karuss Warriors, stopping at nothing to paint the wind with the blood of your enemies and raise our flag over Ronark Land!!'),
(253, 'No one can match the Troll Conjurators strength and Darkness Spells.'),
(254, 'Its do or die here! And ¡‹ere is Ronark Land, if you didnt know. The battles against Karus here rage ever on. Therell be no peace until the day El Morads flag is raised over the whole territory.'),
(255, 'I know you`re a foreigner, but poise is the lifeblood of knighthood, tsk, tsk... |Haven`t you even heard of [item upgrade]?'),
(256, 'I`ll give you a reward if you take the weapons and scroll I hand you and make a [practice dagger +4] with an anvil'),
(257, 'Dont think, though, that Karus is our only enemy here. Eveyone and everything here is our enemy! Remember that, and you might stand a chance. Of all our enemies here, the  Troll Conjuratorhas unrivaled strength and Darkness Spells. Wouldnt you like to give ¡ˆm a kicking? Itd be a good measure of your skills...'),
(258, 'Master, you really gave it some out there! With your skills, you could be the next Outpost Captain! KeKe~'),
(259, '(Feels like hes going to be Top Dog in El Morad...)'),
(260, 'Not just anyone could do that. But you managed, and magnificently so. <selfname>!! You are truly one of the finest of El Morads Warriors, stopping at nothing to paint the wind with the blood of your enemies and raise our flag over Ronark Land!!'),
(261, 'No one can match the Troll Conjurators strength and Darkness Spells.'),
(262, 'Hey, <selfname>!! Were going against El Morad again shortly. But theres something I want you to take care of first. (Indicating the map) Here, and here... These are important strategic sites, and we need to take and hold them. One is a supply route; the other can be used to hit the enemy from the rear and cut-off their frontal assault.'),
(263, 'No doubt El Morad has the same idea, so its vital that you get on this immediately.  Before you can secure these points fully, youll first have to eliminate  Falcon and the  Crimson Wing'),
(264, 'Brilliant work Master, youve secured both areas. Time to report back to base I think.'),
(265, 'Falcon and Crimson Wing are Harpies. Take ¡ˆm out by using their low intelligence against them.'),
(266, 'Nicely done! Great! We claim these strategic points in the name of Karus!'),
(267, 'Hey, <selfname>!! Were going against Karus again shortly. But theres something I want you to take care of first. (Indicating the map) Here, and here... These are important strategic sites, and we need to take and hold them. One is a supply route; the other can be used to hit the enemy from the rear and cut-off their frontal assault.'),
(268, 'No doubt Karus has the same idea, so its vital that you get on this immediately.  Before you can secure these points fully, youll first have to eliminate  Falcon and the  Crimson Wing'),
(269, 'Brilliant work Master, youve secured both areas. Time to report back to base I think.'),
(270, 'Falcon and Crimson Wing are Harpies. Take ¡ˆm out by using their low intelligence against them.'),
(271, 'Master! The upgrade is successful|Let`s take it to Heppa'),
(272, 'Nicely done! Great! We claim these strategic points in the name of El Morad!'),
(273, 'Blast. Why did I believe him?. Everything was running smoothly... But now were facing the enemy front and back. Biiig trouble.'),
(274, 'Betrayal!!  Apostle of Piercing Cold has betrayed us! He promised to cover our flanks while we took El Morads front lines. But now theyve come around and are attacking our rear!. Were caught like a rat in a trap... damn!!'),
(275, 'Now that the traitors have been dealt with, we must see to the El Moradian scum!'),
(276, 'Blast, my calculations were all wrong. I trusted the Apostles too much. Now they must be stopped, whatever the cost. For Karuusss!!'),
(277, 'Youve made a quite an impression! I cant tell you how inspiring it was having you fighting for us out there. So how did you do it? You brushed them aside like crumbs! You didnt do it all single-handedly, did you?'),
(278, 'You need an item upgrade scroll to upgrade your weapon. If you bring me 5 Apples of Moradon, I will award you low quality item upgrade scroll. Lets talk in detail after you bring me Apples of Moradon.'),
(279, 'Blast. Why did I believe him?. Everything was running smoothly... But now were facing the enemy front and back. Biiig trouble.'),
(280, 'Betrayal!!  Apostle of Piercing Cold has betrayed us! He promised to cover our flanks while we took El Morads front lines. But now theyve come around and are attacking our rear!. Were caught like a rat in a trap... damn!!'),
(281, 'Make a [practice dagger +4] using an anvil'),
(282, 'Now that the traitors have been dealt with, we must see to the Karusian scum!'),
(283, 'Blast, my calculations were all wrong. I trusted the Apostles too much. Now they must be stopped, whatever the cost. For El Morraaadd!!'),
(284, 'Youve made a quite an impression! I cant tell you how inspiring it was having you fighting for us out there. So how did you do it? You brushed them aside like crumbs! You didnt do it all single-handedly, did you?'),
(285, '(From reading the letter, you learn that) the   Apostles of Flames are gathering on the northwest plains. The Apostles of Piercing Cold are joining them! The numbers are only an estimate, but even so... Damn! The news just gets better and better...'),
(286, 'Well at least now we know whats going on, we have an advantage. After all, knowledge is half the battle. We must stop them before they grow too large.'),
(287, 'Thank you for doing me this favor. I will pay you 100 Noahs for each. If something else comes up, you have to help me out again.'),
(288, 'Apples of Moradon are sturdy hence very versatile. Bags made with them are extremely useful across-the-board.'),
(289, 'You`ll find Kecoons to the right of Moradon, where it`s indicated on this map.'),
(290, 'Hey!! I told you to go buy a cheap upgradeable (+1) top from the store! |And don`t wear it. I don`t like taking clothes off people. Haha'),
(291, 'See the increase in your Attack Power and other indicators after the upgrade?? The anvil infuses weaponry or armor with magic powers.. Go to the anvil for upgrades |I`ll give you rewards for upgraded weapons'),
(292, 'Wonder what Menissiah`s up to lately. I miss her. Let`s go see her, Master.'),
(293, 'Wonder what Menissiah`s up to lately. I miss her. Let`s go see her, Master.')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(294, '<selfname>, as a token of my gratitude for your help last time, here`s a special medicine I developed. It`s a special gift just for you.'),
(295, 'It`s called antifebrile and Apple of Moradon is the main ingredient. How about it? Can you get some for me?'),
(296, 'I`m glad you`re not declining my kindness. Thank you in advance.'),
(297, 'Hmm. You`re going to refuse my kindness? That`s too bad.'),
(298, 'Hmm. I need Apple of Moradon to make antifebrile.'),
(299, 'Master, you have the Apple of Moradon. Go to [Grand Merchant`s Daughter] Menissiah and receive antifebriles.'),
(300, 'Master, you have the Apple of Moradon. Go to [Grand Merchant`s Daughter] Menissiah and receive antifebriles.'),
(301, 'You finally brought Apple of Moradon. Here you are. I hope they`ll be of valuable use and I look forward to our next exchange.'),
(302, 'Master, I hear Menissiah is making new a potion.'),
(303, 'Master, I hear Menissiah is making new a potion.'),
(304, 'Oh, you thought of me. Thank you. I`m studying how to move higher and faster than everyone else.'),
(305, 'Just in time. I know it sounds thick-skinned, but I have another favor to ask you. I need Apple of Moradon to make this medicine.'),
(306, 'I`ll be able to make my experiment ingredients and yours as well, <selfname>, if only I had just five Apples of Moradon...'),
(307, 'How about it? Will you get them for me?'),
(308, 'Thank you so much. I will surely to complete it.'),
(309, 'Is that a No? Darn, what am I going to do?'),
(310, 'I need 5 Apples of Moradon.'),
(311, 'Master, you collected all 5 Gavolt scales. Take them to Menissiah.'),
(312, 'Master, you collected all 5 Gavolt scales. Take them to Menissiah.'),
(313, 'I am finally be able to make potion. Please wait .'),
(314, 'Here it is. Potion made with Menissiah`s care.'),
(315, 'I mastered a potion production method which requires Apples of Moradon, but I haven`t been able to obtain the ingredients yet. I will give you the hasten potion if you  bring me Apples of Moradon.'),
(316, 'Everyone knows Menissiah in Moradon.. They all warm to her on first encounter'),
(317, 'Everyone knows Menissiah in Moradon.. They all warm to her on first encounter'),
(318, 'A large load, regardless of weight, can be carried in the magic bag. Its production method is demanding and requires various ingredients one of which is multiple Apples of Moradon. I will give you compensation if you bring me Apples of Moradon.'),
(319, 'Silk spools can be obtained from the Worms in front of the castle. I will compensate you 100 Noahs for each spool.'),
(320, 'Master, you collected all the Apples of Moradon. Menissiah will give you a reward for them.'),
(321, 'Master, you collected all the Apples of Moradon. Menissiah will give you a reward for them.'),
(322, 'Worms dwell in the windbreak forest in front of the castle. You`ll spot them right in front of the castle.'),
(323, 'You`re still short. Can you try a little harder?! Thank you'),
(324, 'Tyons have disappeared to a certain extent, but they`re able to breed exceptional well. Their numbers are sure to increase again.'),
(325, 'Are you going to help me?'),
(326, 'Tyons penetrated the farm and are ruining the crops. There`s even a reward being offered for Tyons.'),
(327, 'Tyons penetrated the farm and are ruining the crops. There`s even a reward being offered for Tyons.'),
(328, 'This year`s harvest will be ruined because of the Tyons. Wish someone would get rid of them.'),
(329, 'I will award you handsomely if you eliminate the Tyons that penetrated the farm and bring me their meat. I`m counting on you.'),
(330, 'Shouldn`t this be enough!? If we hand over the meat to the Farm Manager, we will get a large reward.'),
(331, 'Shouldn`t this be enough!? If we hand over the meat to the Farm Manager, we will get a large reward.'),
(332, 'Tyons are stock monsters spotted in the vicinity of farms. There should be loads of them here.'),
(333, 'Hmm, not bad. But they`ll soon multiply again as their breeding ability`s exceptional. Take a look outside. There`s already more of them lingering outside.'),
(334, 'If you bring Tyon meat to the Farm Manager, he turns them into 10,000 Noahs.'),
(335, 'Who are you supposed to be?'),
(336, 'I thought I smelled something green. It was coming from you.'),
(337, 'Master. There`s rumors circulating that [Archmage] Drake is looking for people to entrust missions.'),
(338, 'Wow, your own mother wouldnt even recognize you! Hee Hee!'),
(339, 'His Royal Highness has personally assigned a mission to me for the first time in a long while. A war against the enemy should ensue shortly...'),
(340, 'If we exert pressure on the enemy there, it will be possible for us to infiltrate their mainland, then we will deposit a spy to hunt Lich who`s taken refuge near Kalluga Valley. As the Lich maintain intricate relations with powerful factions, the sole objective of this mission is to seize the Emblem of Karus and deliver it safely to our mainland.|Emblem of Karus is an essential ingredient for casting a great curse on the enemy nation using an ancient black magic I developed.'),
(341, 'Wow, this is the Emblem of Karus. It might be dangerous for us to remain here. Let`s return to the mainland quickly.'),
(342, 'Didn`t I tell you bring the Emblem of Karus?'),
(343, 'Wow, you have safely collected the Emblem of Karus.. Good work. Your honor will increase accordingly as a result.'),
(344, '10 million EXP are awarded for infiltrating enemy mainland after winning the Lunar War and capturing Lich near Kalluga Valley and securing the Emblem of Karus.'),
(345, 'Master, you also need the Nostrum of Constitution to learn the 70Lv and 75Lv skills. [Warrior Master] Skaki will tell you about that.'),
(346, 'Master, you also need the Nostrum of Constitution to learn the 70Lv and 75Lv skills. [Warrior Master] Skaki will tell you about that.'),
(347, 'Master, you also need the Stamp of Agility to learn the 72Lv and 75Lv skills. [Secret Agent] Clarence will tell you about that.'),
(348, 'Master, you also need the Stamp of Agility to learn the 72Lv and 75Lv skills. [Secret Agent] Clarence will tell you about that.'),
(349, 'The border defending battle is held every day at 10 AM and 1, 3, 5 and 10 PM and 1 AM. And it is held additionally at 8 PM on Tuesday, Friday, Saturday and Sunday when there is no war. When the relevant time comes, the announcement for recruitment will be aired automatically so that application for participation can be made'),
(350, 'The border defending battle is held every day at 10 AM and 1, 3, 5 and 10 PM and 1 AM. And it is held additionally at 8 PM on Tuesday, Friday, Saturday and Sunday when there is no war. When the relevant time comes, the announcement for recruitment will be aired automatically so that application for participation can be made'),
(351, 'The word is that both Enigma and Cruel are in the outskirts of Ronark Land. There is no great danger now as they are quite far from here, but we might have a huge disaster in our hands if even just one of them was to make a move...'),
(352, 'If you could take care of them both, I will give you a weapon made just for you. So what do you think?'),
(353, 'Well.. You seem very busy. Return when you have completed the mission you already have.  Good luck then!'),
(354, 'They were quite strong, werent they, Master? Good job!'),
(355, 'Did you get rid of them? (Perhaps they werent that strong after all... I got scared for nothing...)|Hm~ well done. So, what equipment would you like?'),
(356, 'Getting rid of their followers first could be a way. I heard that some of followers cast HP restoring spells.'),
(357, 'The word is that both Hell Fire and Havoc are in the outskirts of Ronark Land. There is no great danger now as they are quite far from here, but we might have a huge disaster in our hands if even just one of them was to make a move...'),
(358, 'If you could take care of them both, I will give you a weapon made just for you. So what do you think?'),
(359, 'Well.. You seem very busy. Return when you have completed the mission you already have.  Good luck then!'),
(360, 'They were quite strong, werent they, Master? Good job!'),
(361, 'Did you get rid of them? (Perhaps they werent that strong after all... I got scared for nothing...)|Hm~ well done. So, what equipment would you like?'),
(362, 'Getting rid of their followers first could be a way. I heard that some of followers cast HP restoring spells.'),
(363, 'Master, Ronark Land seems to have many enemies posing threat. Lets look for [Outpost Captain] Elrod.'),
(364, 'It feels as if I am sitting on a bed of nails, with all these enemies suddenly appearing from nowhere to threaten Ronark Land and there is not one we can take lightly...'),
(365, 'The biggest threats to Ronark Land are the four Patriarchs, and their followers...'),
(366, 'I think weve more or less completed the expedition mission, with this.'),
(367, 'Have you dealt with all those followers of Patriarchs?! Wow~'),
(368, 'Since we lack the strength to defeat them ourselves, I am thinking of requesting for reinforcements. What do you think? Well..'),
(369, 'Master, Ronark Land seems to have many enemies posing threat. Lets look for [Outpost Captain] Della.'),
(370, 'It feels as if I am sitting on a bed of nails, with all these enemies suddenly appearing from nowhere to threaten Ronark Land and there is not one we can take lightly...'),
(371, 'The biggest threats to Ronark Land are the four Patriarchs, and their followers...'),
(372, 'I think weve more or less completed the expedition mission, with this.'),
(373, 'You need an item called the Armband of Magic to change your job.  You can get the Armband of Magic when you bring 50 Gavolt Wings, 50 Zombie Eyes, and 50 Blood of Glyptodont to [Archmage] Drake.'),
(374, 'Master, now you can learn the Absolute Power. Lets look for [Archmage] Drake.'),
(375, 'Absolute Power... It is an amazing skill that briefly increases magical attack by 30%, so mastering the spell of Absolute Power will boost your magical attack power significantly.'),
(376, 'I will give it to you if you pass my test. Win seven victories at the National Defence Combat at the upper reaches of the Kalluga Valley and bring me the Symbol of Victory.  Would you like to try?'),
(377, 'Master, you have won seven victories at the National Defence Combat.  Lets go and visit [Archmage] Drake to get the Absolute Power scroll that he promised.'),
(378, 'Master, you have won seven victories at the National Defence Combat.  Lets go and visit [Archmage] Drake to get the Absolute Power scroll that he promised.'),
(379, 'Oh, have you won seven times at the combat? You must have worked incredibly hard.  Right then, here is your Absolute Power.'),
(380, 'I will give you the Absolute Power scroll as a reward for your seven victories at the National Defence Combat.'),
(381, 'I hear that the Death Magician has appeared in Ronark Land.. Do you think it is true? Lets go and ask [Outpost Captain] Della about it.'),
(382, 'I told you that you need the Armband of Magic, Cursed Bone, Feather of Harpy Queen and Kekuri Ring to change your job, didnt I?'),
(383, 'Have you dealt with all those followers of Patriarchs?! Wow~'),
(384, 'Since we lack the strength to defeat them ourselves, I am thinking of requesting for reinforcements. What do you think? Well..'),
(385, 'You need the Nostrum of Magic is required to learn the 70Lv and 80Lv skills, master. [Archmage] Drake will tell you about it.'),
(386, 'I see that you will soon reach the level of Archmage and be my equal.  When you reach that final stage of magicians, you get to learn the ultimate magic.  There is no being that can easily take on a magician who has learned the ultimate magic. Not even a god... |You can never complete that ultimate magic with some ordinary skills.  To complete the ultimate magic, you would need the Nostrum of Magic and a Stamp of Magic Power.  Moreover, those two items also require combining several different substances to make them.'),
(387, 'To start off, Nostrum of Magic requires 2 Feathers of Harpy Queen, 5 Venomous Tails of Lesath, and 2 Magic Powders to make.  So, do you feel like bringing them here?'),
(388, 'Master, you have collected all the materials needed for the Nostrum of Magic.  I really wonder what this ultimate magic could be.'),
(389, 'Master. You have collected all the materials for needed for the Nostrum of Magic.  I really wonder what this ultimate magic could be.'),
(390, 'To make the Nostrum of Magic, you need 2 Feathers of Harpy Queen, 5 Venomous Tails of Lesath, and 2 Magic Powders.  You must not miss even one.'),
(391, 'They used to be part of the Death Magicians and were a terror to everyone, but then they disappeared without any trace, as if they vanished into thin air. And now they are back. The ones who made everyone quiver in fear...'),
(392, ' What about you... How good are you?? Ah~am I thinking too recklessly...'),
(393, 'The ingredients are sufficient. This is the Magic Nostrum. Hyahh...|Here, the Magic Nostrum is an important object, but it`s useless in any task other than completing  Ultimate Magic.'),
(394, 'You are able to master Ultimate Magic when you reach the highest mage level(70Lv). Magic Nostrum and the Stamp of Magic Power is required to complete Ultimate Magic. [Archmage] Drake awards the Magic Nostrum for 2 Feather of Harpy Queen, 5 Tail of Lesth and 2 Magic Jewel Power.'),
(395, 'This needs to be a surgical strike - fast and precise.'),
(396, 'We could be facing great numbers, so be prepared. We need to do a good job here. But dont think this will solve all our problems. New threats can appear from anywhere at anytime.'),
(397, '(From reading the letter, you learn that) the   Apostles of Flames are gathering on the northwest plains. The Apostles of Piercing Cold are joining them! The numbers are only an estimate, but even so... Damn! The news just gets better and better...'),
(398, 'Well at least now we know whats going on, we have an advantage. After all, knowledge is half the battle. We must stop them before they grow too large.'),
(399, 'Wow, your own mother wouldnt even recognize you! Hee Hee!'),
(400, 'This needs to be a surgical strike - fast and precise.'),
(401, 'We could be facing great numbers, so be prepared. We need to do a good job here. But dont think this will solve all our problems. New threats can appear from anywhere at anytime.'),
(402, 'Its a  Troll Conjurator|Nobody emits evil force like they do! If the evil force is allowed to spread, all Islante will be hell-bound to damnation. But why do I feel such peace as soon as I see you??'),
(403, '[You found the Linnart Village Notice Board. Would you like to read it?}'),
(404, '[No more new notices.]'),
(405, '[Read the notices.]'),
(406, 'Master, have you seen the village notice board in Linnart Village? Lots of quests... Whatre they all about?'),
(407, 'Master, There are no more new notices. Hee Hee!'),
(408, 'Recently, in the Dark Land west of Linnart Village, large numbers of  Dragon Tooth Soldiers have been sighted. Theyve been attacking and plundering the merchants coming from Moradon. Travellers are advised to avoid the Dark Lands untill the Dragon Teeth Sodlers have been cleared out.||- Sentinel Hassan.'),
(409, 'Master, youve already got a lot of other stuff to deal with.'),
(410, 'Hopefully the Dark Lands will quite-down for awhile. Master, you tried incredibly hard.'),
(411, '(Monologue) Hmmm... are the Dark Lands west from here?'),
(412, '[Recently, many Dragon Tooth Soldiers have been seen west of Linnart Village in the Dark Lands]'),
(413, '[You found the Laiva Village Notice Board. Would you like to read it?}'),
(414, '[No more new notices.]'),
(415, '[Read the notices.]'),
(416, 'Master, have you seen the village notice board in Laiva Village? Lots of quests... Whatre they all about?'),
(417, 'Master, There are no more new notices. Hee Hee!'),
(418, 'Recently, in Blue Feathers Valley, southeast of Laiva Village, large numbers of  Dragon Tooth Solders have been sighted. Theyve been attacking and plundering the merchants coming from Moradon. Travellers are warned to steer clear of Blue Feathers Valley untill the Dragon Tooth Soldiers have been dealt with.||                  - Sentinel Beth.'),
(419, 'Master, youve already got a lot of other stuff to deal with.'),
(420, 'Blue Feathers Valley will become quite for some time? Master, you tried hard.'),
(421, '(Monologue) Hmm... is Blue Feather Valley southeast from here?'),
(422, '[Recently, many Dragon Tooth Soldiers have been appearing southeast of Laiva Village in Blue Feather  Valley]'),
(423, 'Recently, in the Dark Land west of Linnart Village, vast numbers of  Dragon Tooth Soldiers have been sighted. Theyve been attacking and plundering the merchants coming from Moradon. Travellers are advised to avoid the Dark Lands untill the rest of the Dragon Tooth Sodlers have been cleared out.||- Sentinel Hassan.'),
(424, 'Recently, in Blue Feathers Valley, southeast of Laiva Village, vast numbers of  Dragon Tooth Solders have been sighted. Theyve been attacking and plundering the merchants coming from Moradon. Travellers are warned to steer clear of Blue Feathers Valley untill the rest of the Dragon Tooth Soldiers have been dealt with.||                  - Sentinel Beth.'),
(425, '[Recently, more Dragon Tooth Soldiers have been seen west of Linnart Village in the Dark Lands]'),
(426, '[Recently, more Dragon Tooth Soldiers have been appearing southeast of Laiva Village in Blue Feather  Valley]'),
(427, 'Its rumored theyre planning to join a  Dragon Tooth Skeleton Squad Leader to replenish the men they lost plundering the Dark Lands. If they do get together, innocent deaths will sky rocket... Linnart Villages warriors must unite to stop the soldiers and protect the Dark Lands!!||            - Sentinel Hashan.'),
(428, 'Wow, you even creamed the Dragon Knight Squad Leader! Its only a matter of time before the whole lot crumbles!'),
(429, '(Monologue) The Dragon Tooth Skeleton Squad Leaders reinforcements will be going past... round about here. Hmmm... not long now.'),
(430, '[The Dragon Tooth Soldiers who have been plundering the Dark Lands, and  the Dragon Tooth Skeletons Squad Leader, are planning to get together...]'),
(431, 'Its rumored theyre planning to join a  Dragon Tooth Commander to replenish the men they lost plundering the Dark Lands. If they do get together, innocent deaths will sky rocket... Laiva Villages warriors must unite to stop the soldiers and protect the Dark Lands!!||            - Sentinel Hashan.'),
(432, 'Wow, you even creamed the Dragon Knight Squad Leader! Its only a matter of time before the whole lot crumbles!'),
(433, '(Monologue) The Dragon Tooth Commanders reinforcements will be going past... round about here. Hmmm... not long now.'),
(434, '[The Dragon Tooth Soldiers who have been plundering the Blue Feather Valley, and  the Dragon Tooth Skeletons Squad Leader, are planning to get together...]'),
(435, 'I feel it... They are resurrecting... Any true knights of Karus  must go immediately to the Plains of Silence!! And STOP THEM! Their strength will overwhelm Karus if they are not put down. Do so. Now.||                - Archmage Drake.'),
(436, 'Errr~ what happens if they resurrect again?'),
(437, '(Monologue) The Leechs resurrecting in... The Plains of Silence. Its southwest from here.'),
(438, 'I feel it... They are resurrecting... Any true knights of El Morad  must go immediately to the  Ruins of Kalia Village!! And stop their resurrection! Their strength will overwhelm El Morad if they are not put down. Do so. Now.||                - Archmage Drake.'),
(439, 'Errr~ what happens if they resurrect again?'),
(440, '(Monologue) The Leechs resurrecting in... The Ruins of Kalia Village Its northeast from here.'),
(441, '(Monologue)... Must stop their resurrection at the Ruins of Kalia Village!'),
(442, '(Monologue)... Must stop their resurrection in the Ruins of Kalia Village!!'),
(443, 'God is angry with us. Karus legacy, and Linnart Villages precious possession, the  Berubasi Relic Site, has been taken by a sect of Esoteric Buddhist priests. Would someone please drive them out, thus sparing us all from gods wrath. Thankyou. ? Grand Celebrant Murca.'),
(444, 'Were not too late are we?'),
(445, '(Monologue) Were the Esoteric Buddhist priests called Deruvish?'),
(446, '[Karus legacy, Linnart Villages precious possession the Berubasi Relic Site, has been over-run by Esoteric Buddhist priests...'),
(447, 'God is angry with us. El Morads legacy, and Laiva Villages precious possession, the  Relic Site of Temple, has been taken by a sect of Esoteric Buddhist priests. Please, somebody, drive them out and save El Morad from gods wrath. ? Grand Celebrant Helena.'),
(448, 'Were not too late are we?'),
(449, '[El Morads legacy, Laiva Villages precious possession the Relic Site of Temple, is swarming with Esoteric Buddhist priests.'),
(450, '(Monologue) Were the Esoteric Buddhist priests called Apostle?'),
(451, '           - Offical Notice -||I have killed millions of monsters, and Ive never been afraid for my life. But! Those Trolls were a real pants-filler. I nearly died several times fighting them, but next time they wont be so lucky. Thats because Im going to go back there and rip them some new ones! Anyone else who wants a piece, come and meet me at the Waste Land!!'),
(452, 'Well, the Trolls were just as tough as advertised. But, errr~ Master, you killed them all! Ha Ha Ha!'),
(453, '(Monologue) Must get to the Waste Land...'),
(454, '[Whoever wants to, erm, ¡–hare the glory, come to the Waste Land!]'),
(455, '           - Offical Notice -||I have killed millions of monsters, and Ive never been afraid for my life. But! Those Trolls were a real bed-wetter. I nearly died several times fighting them, but next time they wont be so lucky. Thats because Im going to go back there and rip them some new ones! Anyone else who wants a piece, come and meet me at the Revival Hole!!'),
(456, 'Well, the Trolls were just as tough as advertised. But, errr~ Master, you killed them all! Ha Ha Ha!'),
(457, '(Monologue) Must go to the Revival Hole...'),
(458, '[Who want to enjoy the glory together come to the Revival Hole!!]'),
(459, 'Not long ago, in the Valley of Dry Wind, I noticed an incredible increase in the number of Harpy. Everyone knows what Harpies are like... Im concerned that if we dont do something about them, theyll overtake the whole village!||          - Weapon Merchant Mori.'),
(460, 'Huh~ Looks like the Linnart Village folk are quite upset about these feathered dames.'),
(461, '(Monologue) Have to take extra care here not to pull whole bunches of them in one go.'),
(462, 'Not long ago, in Blue Feather Valley, I noticed an incredible increase in the number of Harpy. Everyone knows what Harpies are like... Im concerned that if we dont do something about them, theyll overtake the whole village!||          - Weapon Merchant Falthus.'),
(463, 'Huh~ Looks like the aiva Village folk are quite upset about these feathered dames.'),
(464, 'It is of great concern that the number of Harpies is increasing dramatically in the Valley of Dry Wind.'),
(465, 'It is of great concern that the number of Harpies is increasing dramatically in Blue Feather Valley.'),
(466, 'You have already received a present today. So then, I will see you tomorrow.'),
(467, '<selfname>... Welcome.|How have you been? Its already been a month since Moradon Castle was re-built. I think youre used to the place now... Heh. Anyway, Ive prepared a little present for you this time, I hope you like it.'),
(468, 'This time, I thought a, erm... What was it? umm... I had the list somewhere...(searches~)... ah, here it is. Right, this time Ive prepared an Ascent Scroll, a Spirit of Merchant and a Bridegroom, Bride Transformation Scroll. The important thing to remember here is, that everthing is free!! Do you like it?'),
(469, 'Have a great day! And if youre passing by again, come in and see me for more goodies. Byee!'),
(470, 'Welcome. Whats up?'),
(471, 'This is...  the promise of training. <selfname>, you have already made it to 35, that is amazing. It seems that I just met you just a few days ago, and I cant believe that youve already made it to level 35!'),
(472, 'This is...  the promise of training. <selfname>, could you visit me again after you reach level 35?'),
(473, 'You will be going through many trials while training. I hope my gift will help you.'),
(474, 'Hmm... Your inventory is full.'),
(475, 'If you have a chance, could you take a moment to visit Cougar? You might be able to get the information that you will need during your adventures from <slefname>... well, then, thank you.'),
(476, 'This is the mission I can assign you now...'),
(477, 'This is the mission I can assign you now...'),
(478, 'Hmm... a stranger- It might be your first adventure here in El Morad. Nice to meet you.- Im Jalk, a Sentinel at the El Morad Castle. Im at your service.-If you have time, could you do me a favor?'),
(479, 'Here in the mainland, we have Shadow Seekers, and theyre notorious for their disturbance to our people. Could you give us a hand dealing with them?'),
(480, 'And listen, Sir, you need weapons, this is the place. I got all you need up to Level 35.'),
(481, 'You seem to carry heavy responsibilities.'),
(482, 'You must be still hunting... Dont give up!!'),
(483, 'You must be still hunting... Dont give up!!'),
(484, 'Oh~ you tried very hard. I hope you did not hurt yourself. As a token of our appreciation, I will give you my weapon. Here, youll have an easier time hunting with this weapon. Please pick one item you like among them.'),
(485, 'And listen, Sir, you need weapons, this is the place. I got all you need up to Level 35.'),
(486, 'You seem to carry heavy responsibilities.'),
(487, 'How is your adventure here in the mainland? Isnt it tough? Haha-just like before, I came here to ask you to hunt. The target is Saber Tooth... Theyre pretty tough, but probably a worthy challenge for a stout adventurer like yourself!'),
(488, 'I will give you useful armor if you complete the hunting.'),
(489, 'Well-done. The reward is the armor that is supplied only to the Palace Guard, and Im sure it might be useful for you.'),
(490, 'The Apes around here are acting up...Its actually a serious problem because Rage is out of action.'),
(491, 'Not long ago, I was wounded in battle and I wanted to call you for help, but you already had too many missions, and no one else could help.'),
(492, 'Apes... .'),
(493, 'Youve conquered those oversized and foul smelling Apes?! Thank you very much ? This is a sign of my appreciation, use it well.')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(494, 'Welcome. Nice to meet you. Im Clark. I visit many places around Moradon for trading. I have something to urgently tell you. [Scroll Merchant] Karon lost some materials she needed for making a new scroll. Shes asked me to find some of the items, but Im having difficulty.'),
(495, 'What... How did you know about that? Nobody knows about it... Well, to be honest I dont know too much either. All I know is that Karus offered to secretly trade >Oaths of Darkness nothing more.'),
(496, 'This is the only thing that I learned to do, and that I can do. Haha~'),
(497, 'From what Ive heard, youre the ideal candidate for the quest. Can you do it?'),
(498, 'This is the only thing that I learned to do, and that I can do. Haha~'),
(499, 'From what Ive heard, youre the ideal candidate for the quest. Can you do it?'),
(500, 'Master, you also need the Stamp of Magic Power to learn the 70v, 72Lv and 75Lv skills. [Archmage] Drake will tell you about it.'),
(501, 'Besides the Nostrum of Magic, you also need a Stamp of Magic Power to complete the ultimate magic. What a Stamp of Magic Power does is, that it continuously replenishes the magic power of the caster using the ultimate magic, which consumes magic power infinitely.|Using the ultimate magic is that dangerous. But as someone who has committed himself to the study of magic, dont you think it worth the challenge?'),
(502, 'To make a Stamp of Magic Power, you need 1 Lupus Pendant,  1 Lycaons Pendant, and one Silver Bar. So. Do you feel like bringing them here?'),
(503, 'Master, you`ve collected all the ingredients needed for making the Stamp of Magic Power. I can`t believe this is all it takes to make it.'),
(504, 'Master, you`ve collected all the ingredients needed for making the Stamp of Magic Power. I can`t believe this is all it takes to make it.'),
(505, 'You have safely completed this mission as well, master~.'),
(506, 'How did you manage to defeat those Death Magicians while still fighting in the battles against Karus?? Wow~'),
(507, 'To make a Stamp of Magic Power, you need 1 Lupus Pendant,  1 Lycaons Pendant, and one Silver Bar.'),
(508, 'Here, this is the Stamp of Magic Power. It possesses unlimited magic power but it`s useless in any task other than completing Ultimate Magic.'),
(509, 'You are able to master Ultimate Magic when you reach the highest mage level(70Lv). Magic Nostrum and the Stamp of Magic Power is required to complete Ultimate Magic. [Archmage] Drake awards the Stamp of Magic Power 30 Dragon Teeth Soldier bones, 30 sapphires, and Silver Bar.'),
(510, 'Master, have you heard of the essential collectible for high-ranking knights? I heard [Archmage] Drake knows about it..'),
(511, 'You`ve already reached that position as well. Magic Power is certainly an essential material used by high-ranking knights in mastering skills and magic.'),
(512, 'Heres the deal. You want Magic Powder you got to get me 3 Sapphires, 3 Crystals and 3 Opals.'),
(513, 'Master, all the materials for Magic Powder have been gathered. Hurry and see [Archmage] Drake.'),
(514, 'Master, all the materials for Magic Powder have been gathered. Hurry and see [Archmage] Drake.'),
(515, 'Nuh-uh. I need 3 Sapphires to make Magic Powder.'),
(516, 'Nuh-uh. I need 3 Crystals to make Magic Powder.'),
(517, 'Nuh-uh. I need 3 Opals to make Magic Powder.'),
(518, 'Hmm. You brought all the ingredients I enumerated.|Here you are. You too will soon be able to employ rare and exceptional technique.'),
(519, 'Higher level magic and skills are not granted automatically. Some can only be crafted from items that must be collected. Of these, Magic Powder is the most sought after. It can be obtained from [Archmage] Drake if you bring him 5 Sapphires, 5 Crystals and 5 Opals.'),
(520, 'Master, do you know of Ssohn Magic? I heard Archmage Drake is looking for someone to teach it to.'),
(521, 'Do you know of `Ssohn` magic? The most brutal high-level black magic, it attacks the selected target simultaneously absorbing the opponent`s constitution. Since you`re a figure already making substantial contribution to our nation, I thought it will be all right for me to teach it to you.'),
(522, 'Sun Magic requires 3 Magic Powers and the 1 M Noahs needed to operate the Magic Anvil. So, will you gather the materials needed to learn Sun Magic?'),
(523, 'Master, all the Ssohn Magic ingredients have been collected. Let`s go seek out [Archmage] Drake.'),
(524, 'Master, all the Ssohn Magic ingredients have been collected. Let`s go seek out [Archmage] Drake.'),
(525, 'You`re short on Noahs. Where did you spend them all?'),
(526, '3 Magic Powders are required to complete Sun Magic.'),
(528, 'You will now be able to employ Ssohn magic. Please continue your pursuit of magic studies.'),
(529, 'The Sun Magic Scroll must be crafted in order to learn Sun Magic. You can gain the Sun Magic Scroll from [Archmage] Drake when you bring him 3 Magic Powders and 1 M Noahs.'),
(530, 'Master, I hear [Archmage] Drake is giving a lecture on the Impact Magic Scroll. Let`s go check it out.'),
(531, 'The Impact Magic Scroll is remarkably useful for a Mage. If you wish to learn it, bring me 7 Insignias of Victor as well as 1.5 M Noahs. For your information, the Insignia of Victor is awarded when you prove to be victorious in National Border Defense Battle.'),
(532, 'Nothing worth having is ever easy. 7 Insignias of Victor may be obtained by proving your worth against your enemy in National Border Defense Battle.'),
(533, 'Master, all 7 Insignias of Victor have been gathered!'),
(534, 'Master, all 7 Insignias of Victor have been gathered!'),
(535, 'Listen, didn`t I tell you the 3rd Armor Set(helmet, top, bottom) is needed for the Goblin Armor Formalwear?'),
(536, 'Listen, didn`t I tell you the 3rd Armor Set(helmet, top, bottom) is needed for the Goblin Armor Formalwear?'),
(537, 'Listen, didn`t I tell you the 3rd Armor Set(helmet, top, bottom) is needed for the Goblin Armor Formalwear?'),
(538, 'You brought all the required armor. I`ll be right back.|Here. Isn`t it a nice armor compared to the name?'),
(539, 'Goblin Armor Formalwear can be obtained from [Archmage] Drake. The 3rd Armor Set(helmet, top, bottom) is needed to acquire the Goblin Armor Formalwear.'),
(540, 'Master, I hear that a lot of preparation goes into obtaining Impact Magic Scroll. [Archmage] Drake should know the details.'),
(541, 'In truth, the Goblin Armor Formalwear I made for you plus gauntlet and boots are combined to make a complete Goblin Armor. This is someone`s special request. Can you bring them?'),
(542, 'To make it, I need to combine the Goblin Armor Formalwear you`re wearing and the 3rd Armor Set(gauntlet and boots). Want to give it a try?'),
(543, 'Master, you have acquired the Goblin Armor Formalwear you`re wearing and the 3rd Armor Set. Let`s go back to the Archmage to receive the complete Goblin Armor.'),
(544, 'Master, you have acquired the Goblin Armor Formalwear you`re wearing and the 3rd Armor Set. Let`s go back to the Archmage to receive the complete Goblin Armor.'),
(545, 'I told you the Goblin Armor Formalwear and 3rd Armor Set(gauntlet and boots) are needed to make the complete Goblin Armor!'),
(546, 'I told you the Goblin Armor Formalwear and 3rd Armor Set(gauntlet and boots) are needed to make the complete Goblin Armor!'),
(547, 'I told you the Goblin Armor Formalwear and 3rd Armor Set(gauntlet and boots) are needed to make the complete Goblin Armor!'),
(548, 'Hmm. You have collected all the required objects. I will make the complete Goblin Armor for you soon. |Here it is. This is the ultimate Goblin Armor. Looks good.'),
(549, 'Goblin Armor Formalwear and 3rd Armor Set(gauntlet and boots) are needed to make the complete Goblin Armor. Take the ingredients to [Archmage] Drake for receive it.'),
(550, 'Master, have you heard of Impact, a powerful attack magic? Don`t you think [Archmage] Drake should be able to tell us about it?'),
(551, 'Impact is serious magic. Its rarely taught to even the most able Mage. But I like your look so Im willing to take a chance - IF you can prove youre up to it. So then! Earn 7 Insignias of Victor in Border Defense Battle to prove your worthiness.'),
(552, 'Dont forget to bring me 1.5 M Noahs along with the 7 Insignias of Victor. What? Too expensive? You think I am running a charity here? I already gave you a discount, so move it!'),
(553, 'Gasp! Gasp! Master, all 7 Insignias of Victor have been gathered! Go see [Archmage] Drake now.'),
(554, 'Gasp! Gasp! Master, all 7 Insignias of Victor have been gathered! Go see [Archmage] Drake now.'),
(555, 'Think youre worthy, do you? Not TOO dense, I swear. The cost is 7 Insignias of Victor. 7!'),
(556, 'This look like 1.5 M Noahs to you? Trying to pull a fast one? Better hurry with my money before I triple the price!'),
(557, 'You got it all. Now were talking. Youve got your Impact Magic. Use it well.'),
(558, 'You have to bring 7 Insignias of Victor and 1.5 M Noahs to [Archmage] Drake to learn the powerful offensive magic Impact.'),
(559, 'I finally have some downtime.'),
(560, 'They say that the Spoiler is an avian monster that evolved from one of Pathoss spells.'),
(561, 'Master! Ive heard that Apple of Moradon has a sticky effect. Lets go and find [Mercenary Supply Officer] Osmond and check it out.'),
(562, 'Hello.|My name is Osmond. Im the official Quartermaster for Mercenaries and so on. Youre <selfname>, right? I knew it was you- Ive heard all the stories! So what brings you here?'),
(563, 'Right now were in the middle of repairing the wall of Moradon castle, and need lots of cement. Please bring me any Apple of Moradon you have. I will give you a reasonable price for them.'),
(564, 'Master! Its the Apple of Moradon! You can trade it to  Osmond at a reasonable price.'),
(565, 'Master! Its the Apple of Moradon! You can trade it to  Osmond at a reasonable price.'),
(566, 'Shoot... There isnt enough Apple of Moradon for all the repairs.'),
(567, 'Thank you.|We were worried about our lack of Apple of Moradon, but this really helps. Thanks again!'),
(568, 'We are short of the Apples of Moradon to be used for the repair of the castle wall. I will give you appropriate compensation if you bring two Apples of Moradon.'),
(569, 'Master, theres a strange rumor going around Moradon.'),
(570, 'Our top Merchant is having big trouble since we became infected with a nasty disease on the way to Moradon. In time, everyone will die from this thing. Weve got to get the antidote soon.'),
(571, 'Please fetch some Apples of Moradon.'),
(572, 'Master, Rage will be satisfied with this much.'),
(573, 'Master, Rage will be satisfied with this much.'),
(574, 'You are placing a bet of 5000 Noahs, okay? You have to keep your words, okay? I will not refund your money even if you say your fingers slipped or you didnt know it was going to be like this or whatever after you lose, okay? Then, shall we get started?'),
(575, 'Not TOO weird a hobby. This guys psycho, Im thinking. Repulsive as it is, find me a Rotten Eye.'),
(576, 'Ive heard a rumor that therere ometimes Silver Feathers in amongst the Saber Tooths feathers.'),
(577, 'Master!  <font color=@#990000@>[Mercenary Quartermaster] Mr. Osmond</font> is looking for you, Master, for the preparation of war materials'),
(578, 'What shall we do with this.. Its huge trouble.. Gasp! Oh my! Not even a hint of your approaching. Oh, are you asking me what I am so worried about? Its because of the supply route for the provision of war materials.'),
(579, 'While we were trying to transport war materials for their provisioning, the violence of [Boss] monsters has become more severe. Consequently, the transportation plan is being delayed indefinitely. I wish someone would take care of these guys.. Oh! I think I can ask <selfname> a favor! Fortunately, you dont seem to have anything to do! As for a reward, I will talk to the Commander so that you can be richly rewarded. Please, do me this favor.'),
(580, 'Is this guy the last one? Master! I took care of all the guys on the wanted list!'),
(581, 'Is this guy the last one? Master! I took care of all the guys on the wanted list!'),
(582, 'Um.. Not yet..? Oh.. My heart breaks when I think about the fellow soldiers who are suffering as the materials are not delivered!'),
(583, 'Oh! You took care of them all! Thank you. Now we can start the transporation! Here is your compensation. Do us a favor the next time too!'),
(584, 'Among the goods needed for the war, bezoars of Glyptodont, which are used as explosive material, are in severe shortage. I wish you can secure about five of them for us.'),
(585, 'Master- Theyre preparing the War Supplies over in the Folk Vilage. So Osmond is busy eh? You should go and pay him a visit.'),
(586, 'Karon is my best friend, so I really dont want to let him down. Please, help me out on this one, Ok?'),
(587, 'To save the sickly Merchant, we need Rough Bone Powder. Quick! Quick! We must save them, theyre like family to me. Ill go mad without them!'),
(588, 'Ohhh.. We just have two Apples of Moradon. Master, you also played a part in the preparation for the war!!'),
(589, 'Ohhh.. We just have two Apples of Moradon. Master, you also played a part in the preparation for the war!!'),
(590, 'This opportunity wont come ¡•ound again. I hope you come back in time with the stuff...'),
(591, 'If possible, make them high quality Talismans, Ok?'),
(592, 'Master, they say  Vilbore is giving special gifts to knights who reach 35Lv. And the fact is that you are also close to reaching 35Lv - so cheer up ^^'),
(593, 'Master, I`m bored. Why don`t we go see [Blacksmith] Heppa?'),
(594, 'Master, I`m bored. Why don`t we go see [Blacksmith] Heppa?'),
(595, 'Kecoons are hostile but they like to hide nice objects|What if I give you a reward for bringing me what I ask for?'),
(596, 'Bring 2 Apples of Moradon which can be acquired from Kecoons. How about it? Want to give it a shot?'),
(597, 'Master, all 4 Apples of Moradon [Blacksmith] Heppa asked for have been collected'),
(598, 'Master, all 4 Apples of Moradon [Blacksmith] Heppa asked for have been collected'),
(599, 'Didn`t you remember that I told you I needed at least 2 Apples of Moradon?'),
(600, 'Didn`t you remember that I told you I needed at least 2 Apples of Moradon?'),
(601, 'Haha, you brought them|I will give you a reward in exchange for the Apples of Moradon.'),
(602, '[Blacksmith] Heppa will award a new armor for Apples of Moradon.'),
(603, 'Whew, this is exhausting. Master, we`re low on weapons. Go see [Blacksmith] Heppa. Who knows? Maybe he`ll give you a nice weapon.'),
(604, 'Whew, this is exhausting. Master, we`re low on weapons. Go see [Blacksmith] Heppa. Who knows? Maybe he`ll give you a nice weapon.'),
(605, 'Craftsmen can distinguish high-grade ingredients with a single glance. I discovered something while traversing the Seashore of Hope. With that, I should be able to make you a to-die-for weapon. How about it?'),
(606, 'If you`re tempted, bring me Bulture horns and iron bar and I`ll make you something fabulous.'),
(607, 'Master, all the materials [Blacksmith] Heppa asked for have been collected. All right, it`s time for Weapon Change!'),
(608, 'Master, all the materials [Blacksmith] Heppa asked for have been collected. All right, it`s time for Weapon Change!'),
(609, 'Didn`t I tell you Bulture horns and iron bar are required for weapons? It`s an easy task for me, still I`m charging a fee of 1,000 Noahs.'),
(610, 'Didn`t I tell you Bulture horns and iron bar are required for weapons? It`s an easy task for me, still I`m charging a fee of 1,000 Noahs.'),
(611, 'Didn`t I tell you Bulture horns and iron bar are required for weapons? It`s an easy task for me, still I`m charging a fee of 1,000 Noahs.'),
(612, '[Select the weapon you want to be awarded]
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(695, 'I wanted to thank you for delivering the ring.'),
(696, 'Is there anything you`d like to say to me?'),
(697, 'She was sent to theLunar Gateages ago, and is still stationed there. I want to see her face again...'),
(698, 'I`m sorry, but I`m of no relation to you what-so-ever.'),
(699, 'Ah... you seem to be someone with whom I could share my predicament.'),
(700, 'Um... A ring ... No, never mind.'),
(701, 'This is the right of passage to Lunar Valley. You can go to the front by traversing here.'),
(702, 'The Imperial Palace Chef will give a reward for the Tyon meat he needs and receive the quest which entails delivering BBQ to the Lunar Gate Sentinel.'),
(703, 'EXP are awarded for delivering BBQ to the Lunar Gate Sentinel as well as the Islante Woman Quest.'),
(704, 'A large reward is awarded for delivering the Lunar Gate Sentinel`s ring to the Islante woman.'),
(705, 'Thank you for delivering the ring.'),
(706, 'Theres a lull in the battle at the moment. You dont have to go in.'),
(707, 'Welcome.|Youre here to reinforce the borders of Kalluga Valley, right?'),
(708, 'Master!! Theres trouble on the borders of Kalluga Valley, at the access point! Must be a big battle or something.'),
(709, 'Master, if you need  Middle Class Upgrade Scroll , then you should look for Osmond ^^'),
(710, 'Master, if you need  Middle Class Upgrade Scroll , then you should look for Osmond ^^'),
(711, 'A Middle Class Upgrade Scroll??? Ah~ I heard that it is the scroll that upgrades the level of middle class weapons... Do you need that?'),
(712, 'Hm~ I have kept it somewhere in the supply storage before. I think I will have to look for it.  Since it is one of the supplies, I can not give it to you without Rages permission...'),
(713, 'Will you participate in National Defense Combat?'),
(714, 'This is a guard post, near the national borders. Border disputes occur regularly, so the warriors here are always prepped and ready.'),
(715, 'Master! Theres trouble on the borders of Kalluga Valley, at the access point!  Must be a big battle or something.'),
(716, 'If you want the Magic Scroll, you have to do something for me. See, I lost an Apple of Moradon, right? You get me a replacement, and Ill hand over the Magic Scroll. However, be sure to keep this a secret from Rage.'),
(717, 'Master, you have collected all the Apples of Moradon that Osmond requested.'),
(718, 'You must protect the Training Stone for 30 minutes of the battle.  You will gain EXP for participating in the National Defence Combat. You get 2 million EXP, a Red Box and a EXP scroll when you win... And just 1 million EXP when you lose.'),
(719, 'Master, you have collected all the Apples of Moradon that Osmond requested.'),
(720, 'Please bring them to me before Rage finds out.. Sob.'),
(721, 'This is a guard post, near the national borders. Border disputes occur regularly, so the warriors here are always prepped and ready.'),
(722, 'Phew ~ You have brought them.. I thought you were never coming back.'),
(723, 'Are you ready to sacrifice your life for your nation?|Lead the party to that battlefield and return with 100 lives of our enemy.'),
(724, 'Are you ready to sacrifice your life for your nation?|Lead the party to that battlefield and return with 100 lives of our enemy.'),
(725, 'Master~  The war in Ronark Land doesnt seem to be going so well due to the knights of El Morad.'),
(728, 'Master. Theres trouble on the borders of Kalluga Valley, at the access point!  Must be a big battle or something.'),
(729, 'Its tricky, because the border line is right *in* the valley, so the fighting never stops.  Currently, the whole place is blocked-up with a huge national Training Stone, but its very limited. So theyre recruiting knights here who can protect the Training Stone when its power weakens periodically.'),
(730, 'Youre not really suited to small battles like this. Itd be better to go somewhere like Lunar Valley, where theres more action.'),
(731, 'You must protect the Training Stone for 30 minutes of the battle.  You will gain EXP for participating in the National Defence Combat. You get 7 million EXP, a Red Box and a EXP scroll when you win... And 3.5 million EXP and a EXP scroll when you lose.'),
(732, 'You havent finished the monster hunting mission that you were given before. Come back when you have completed that mission.'),
(733, 'You must protect the Training Stone for 30 minutes of the battle.  You will gain EXP for participating in the National Defence Combat. You get 2 million EXP, a Red Box and a EXP scroll when you win... And just 1 million EXP when you lose.'),
(734, 'This is a guard post, near the national borders. Border disputes occur regularly, so the warriors here are always prepped and ready.'),
(735, 'Master. Theres trouble on the borders of Kalluga Valley, at the access point!  Must be a big battle or something.'),
(736, 'Its tricky, because the border line is right *in* the valley, so the fighting never stops.  Currently, the whole place is blocked-up with a huge national Training Stone, but its very limited. So theyre recruiting knights here who can protect the Training Stone when its power weakens periodically.'),
(737, 'Youre not really suited to small battles like this. Itd be better to go somewhere like Lunar Valley, where theres more action.'),
(738, 'You must protect the Training Stone for 30 minutes of the battle.  You will gain EXP for participating in the National Defence Combat. You get 7 million EXP, a Red Box and a EXP scroll when you win... And 3.5 million EXP and a EXP scroll when you lose.'),
(739, 'The Training Stone still has some strength left in it.'),
(740, 'Will you participate in National Defense Combat?'),
(741, 'This is a guard post, near the national borders. Border disputes occur regularly, so the warriors here are always prepped and ready.'),
(742, 'This is too much for you to deal with. Comeback after youve had a bit more training.'),
(743, 'This is too much for you to deal with. Comeback after youve had a bit more training.'),
(744, 'Welcome.|Youre here to reinforce the borders, right?'),
(745, 'Theres a lull in the battle at the moment. You dont have to go in.'),
(746, 'The enemies are still alive.'),
(747, 'Have you killed all 100?|I will give you a reward in return for those lives.'),
(748, 'Ah, You chose Pathos Glove. The Glove of Pathos comes in two varieties. Aurora of Attack increases your attack power and Aurora of Defense increases your defense power. Which one would you like?'),
(749, 'You need Pathos Glove Certificate to receive Pathos Glove. You can purchase Pathos Glove Certificate from Power Up Store'),
(750, 'Attack Aurora..Glove that increase wrath of Pathos...That is one of Pathos Glove with Attack aurora. 2% attack power increase with a choice of additional attack power option.'),
(751, 'Defense Aurora..Glove with desire to overcome Pathos weakness..That is one of Pathos Glove with Defense Aurora. +10 Defense power increase with a choice of additional defense power option.'),
(752, 'Thank you. Enjoy your adventure'),
(753, 'Attack Aurora...You chose 3% attack damage increse when attacking Warrior class only option. Would you like to exchange?'),
(754, 'Attack Aurora...You chose 3% attack damage increse when attacking Rogue class only option. Would you like to exchange?'),
(755, 'Attack Aurora...You chose 3% attack damage increse when attacking Magician class only option. Would you like to exchange?'),
(756, 'Attack Aurora...You chose 3% attack damage increse when attacking Priest class only option. Would you like to exchange?'),
(757, 'Defense Aurora..You chose 3% defense increase when getting attacked by a Warrior class only option. Would you like to exchange?'),
(758, 'Defense Aurora..You chose 3% defense increase when getting attacked by a Rogue class only option. Would you like to exchange?'),
(759, 'Defense Aurora..You chose 3% defense increase when getting attacked by a Magician class only option. Would you like to exchange?'),
(760, 'Defense Aurora..You chose 3% defense increase when getting attacked by a Priest class only option. Would you like to exchange?'),
(761, 'Hello, Master! How was it today?'),
(762, 'What brings you here? This is the official residence of  <topclanname> Knight Squad, the highest squad. Im Roctar, the Manager.'),
(763, 'This is the official residence that is open to only the highest Knight squad in Karus. The King granted this place as a reward for the labor of the Knight Squad with the highest status in Karus. Owning the place is an honor as the Clan which represents our Nation. Its a special place that only first-class clans are allowed to enter.'),
(764, 'Hello, Master! How was it today?'),
(765, 'What brings you here? This is the official residence of  <topclanname> Knight Squad, the highest squad. Im Elliot, the Manager.'),
(766, 'This is the official residence that is open to only the highest Knight squad in El Morad. The King granted this place as a reward for the labor of the Knight Squad with the highest status in Karus. Owning the place is an honor as the Clan which represents our Nation. 1? ???? ??? ??? ?? ??? ???'),
(767, '(Monologue) Were the Esoteric Buddhist priests called Deruvish?'),
(768, '(Monologue) Were the Esoteric Buddhist priests called Apostle?'),
(769, '(Monologue) Have to take extra care here not to pull whole bunches of them in one go.'),
(770, 'This is the official residence that is open only to  <topclanname>, the highest Knight squad in Karus. The King granted this place as a reward for the labor of the Knight Squad with the highest status in Karus. Owning the place is an honor as a Clan which represents our Nation. Would you like to enter?'),
(771, 'This is the official residence that is open only to  <topclanname>, the highest Knight squad in El Morad. The King granted this place as a reward for the labor of the Knight Squad with the highest status in Karus. Owning the place is an honor as the Clan which represents our Nation. Would you like to enter?'),
(772, 'You already received weapons and armors today. Youd better visit tomorrow to get them.'),
(773, 'Welcome. How have you been? Well, to see you come to me today, you may heard of a news... haha-'),
(774, 'This time, well lend you armor and a weapon especially for you. Hmm~ you <selfname> are a warrior... (looking at the list... )  Glaive and  Chitin Armor Set are ready for you. Would you like to receive it?'),
(775, 'This time, well lend you armor and a weapon especially for you. Hmm~ you <selfname> are Rogue... (looking at the list... )  Mirage Dagger,  Chitin Bow and  Chitin Armor Set are ready for you. Would you like to receive it?'),
(776, 'This time, well lend you armor and a weapon especially for you. Hmm~ you <selfname> are a Wizard... (looking at the list... )  Elemental Staff and  Crimson Armor Set are ready. Would you like to rec'),
(777, 'This time, well lend you armor and a weapon especially for you. Hmm~ you <selfname> are a Wizard... (looking at the list... )  Elemental Staff and  Crimson Armor Set are ready. Would you like to receive it?'),
(778, 'This time, well lend you armor and a weapon especially for you. Hmm~ you <selfname> are warrior... (looking at the list... )  Raptor and  Chitin Shell Armor Set are ready for you. Would you like to receive it?'),
(779, 'This time, well lend you armor and a weapon especially for you. Hmm~ you <selfname> are Rogue... (looking at the list... )  Shard,  Iron Bow and  Chitin Shell Armor Set are ready for you. Would you like to receive it?'),
(780, 'This time, well lend you armor and a weapon especially for you. Hmm~ you <selfname> are a Wizard... (looking at the list... )  Elixir Staff and  Complete Armor Set are ready for you. Would you like to receive it?'),
(781, 'This time, well lend you armor and a weapon especially for you. Hmm~ you <selfname> are a Priest... (looking at the list... )  Lycaon Mace,  Defender of the Lord and  Chitin Shell Armor Set are ready for you. Would you like to receive it?'),
(782, 'Only those of level 47 or higher can participate in this event. Please, visit later after you train yourself more.'),
(783, 'Insufficient inventory space. To receive the item, you should have at least 6 inventory slots.'),
(784, 'Insufficient inventory space. To receive the item, you should have at least 8 inventory slots.'),
(785, 'Insufficient inventory space. To receive the item, you should have at least 7 inventory slots.'),
(786, 'Hello...  Im Slay, I manage the Graveyard. I dont know how many years have passed since I started to watch over this graveyard. Ah- Could you help me?'),
(787, 'What brings you here? Well, excuse me, I have something to do... and you seem pretty busy, too...'),
(788, 'I dont know since when, but  Rotten Eyes have appeared around the tomb, and I cant drive them out by myself. Theyre Zombie Monsters like Undyings, and the problem is they make a terrible mess everywhere, makes the Tomb look awful. Could you try and stop them from coming in and ruining the place?'),
(789, 'You must save this Tomb no matter what happens. Please, do your best.'),
(790, 'Meeting you was possibly the best bit of luck Ive ever had! Thank you very much. Heres a little something for ya. This is what I found while Ive managed this place. This will be quite useful.'),
(791, 'What brings you here?'),
(792, 'Hmm... we seem to have a special guest in the Tomb. Its certainly an uninvited Guest -  people call it Vatalion, and its stronger than both Zombies and Undyings. I cant do anything with them here. Could you help me?'),
(793, 'Well, nothing... I will try to talk to you later as you seem very busy now.'),
(794, 'God, what am I supposed to do?'),
(795, 'What - How - You drove out the Vatalions... Ill never forget this. This is something I dug-up near the Tomb a few days ago. Doesnt look like ordinary stuff. Please, take it as a token of my appreciation.'),
(796, 'Youll get a Weapon out of this if you do [Sentinel] Zalk this favor.'),
(797, 'Youll get some Armor out of this if you do [Graveyard Keeper] Bottom this favor.'),
(798, 'Youll get a Weapon out of this if you do [Sentinel] Cape this favor.'),
(799, 'Youll get some Armor out of this if you do [Graveyard Keeper] Bottom this favor.'),
(800, 'Eh, ham! Whos this? Isnt it <selfname>? Wow, long time no see. What are you doing ¡•ound here? This place is actually a cave that goes all the way down to the underground regions of Jurad Mountain. By Royal decree, I am the gatekeeper! Say what? You want to go in? Right then! Youll be needing my permission!'),
(801, 'Eh, ham! Whos this? Isnt it <selfname>? Wow, long time no see. What are you doing ¡•ound here? This place is actually a cave that goes all the way down to the underground regions of Jurad Mountain. By Royal decree, I am the gatekeeper! Whats that? Say what? You want to go in? Right then! Youll be needing my permission!'),
(802, 'Master! Theres a problem at Islantes Jurad Mountain! Go to Islante quickly!'),
(803, 'They say theres an enormous hole in the side of the Jurad Moutain. Its something to do with a big fight between Karus and some Evil Soldiers. The good news is, because of the power of our Karusian ancestry, weve claimed the entrance! Although, in order to stop chaos setting in, only the best warriors are allowed access, and then only at times chosen by Legure. Sounds good though. You want to go down there? Great! Youre going to wet yourself when you hear this:|Youll get fantastic rewards from down there at the cost of just 1% experience.|Failure doesnt lose you any xp, but it doesnt get you any rewards either.| Right, lets get down there.'),
(804, 'When I let you in, at the appointed time, youll have 50 minutes to poke around in Jurad Mountains Underground Haunt. Be aware that El Moradians may be down there too, and eveyones fair game here. Anyway, theres a bloody big monster down there- the Deva Bird. Kill it and youll receive a Gemstone. Its really precious, something nice.Oh, and when you win in Jurad Mountain, thats when youll see 1% of your xp disappear, and when youll get your fat reward. Ok? And remember this - If you dont defeat the Devabird in time, the outcome will be based on the number of the kills the enemy made.'),
(805, 'So, would you like to enter Jurad Mountains Underground?'),
(806, 'Master! Theres a problem at Islantes Jurad Mountain! Go to Islante quickly!'),
(807, 'They say theres an enormous hole in the side of the Jurad Moutain. Its something to do with a big fight between El Morad and some Evil Soldiers. The good news is, because of the power of our El Moradian ancestry, weve claimed the entrance! Although, in order to stop chaos setting in, only the best warriors are allowed access, and then only at times chosen by Beldan. Do you want to go in? Great! Youre going to wet yourself when you hear this:|Youll get fantastic rewards from down there at the cost of just 1% experience.|Failure doesnt lose you any xp, but it doesnt get you any rewards either.| Right, lets get down there.'),
(808, 'When I let you in, at the appointed time, youll have 50 minutes to poke around in Jurad Mountains Underground Haunt. Be aware that Karusians may be down there too, and eveyones fair game here. Anyway, theres a bloody big monster down there- the Deva Bird. Kill it and youll receive a Gemstone. Its really precious, something nice.Oh, and when you win in Jurad Mountain, thats when youll see 1% of your xp disappear, and when youll get your fat reward. Ok? And remember this - If you dont defeat the Devabird in time, the outcome will be based on the number of the kills the enemy made. Got that?'),
(809, 'So, would you like to enter Jurad Mountains Underground?'),
(810, 'Hey, Hey... Youre totally the wrong level for this place. Go and get yourself some more scars before coming back here!'),
(811, 'Hmm... Well, youve made no contribution to the country. First, get CONT from [Knight Squad Secretary] Delaga in Karus Castle.'),
(812, 'Its not time to enter yet. Come back around 18:40. Sometimes Ill call you, too.'),
(813, 'Geez, youve got a temper! Now you can wait!'),
(814, 'Ahh... You cannot enter unless 8 other people are here too. This place is too dangerous for soloing or messing around. Come back with some friends. Trust me, its better that way. You can not face the enemy alone. Nope. No way. Youre too important to us.'),
(815, 'Hey, Hey... Youre totally the wrong level for this place. Go and get yourself some more scars before coming back here!'),
(816, 'Hmm... Well, youve made no contribution to the country. First, get CONT from [Knight Squad Secretary] Charel in El Morad Castle.'),
(817, 'Its not time to enter yet~ comeback at 1840... Sometimes I call you...'),
(818, 'Geez, youve got a temper! Now you can wait!'),
(819, 'Ahh... You cannot enter unless 8 other people are here too. This place is too dangerous for soloing or messing around. Come back with some friends. Trust me, its better that way. You can not face the enemy alone. Nope. No way. Youre too important to us.'),
(820, 'If you bring a [Voucher], bought from a shop, it can be exchanged for certified National items.'),
(821, 'Menu for testing Familiars.'),
(822, 'You can use it after summoning a Familiar.'),
(823, 'You dont have a [Voucher for Magic Bag].'),
(824, 'You dont have a [Voucher for Automatic Looting].'),
(825, 'Huh. There mustve been some disturbance at Jurad Moutain.'),
(826, 'You cant enter right now. Dont worry, Ill tell you when its time.'),
(827, 'Huh. There mustve been some disturbance at Jurad Moutain.'),
(828, 'You cant enter right now. Dont worry, Ill tell you when its time.'),
(830, 'Thank you, to everyone who participated in the [Era of Knight] test. We are giving out the following supplies for more efficiency testing, so please take them now.'),
(831, 'This is the newly added weapon and armor list for the [Era of Knight].'),
(832, 'Insufficient free Inventory slots.'),
(833, 'This is the newly added accessories list for the [Era of Knight].'),
(834, 'This is the newly added item and Powerup Store item list for [Era of Knight].'),
(835, 'Your skill points and stat points are higher than your level Find somewhere else to grind!'),
(836, 'You carry sins with you. You must cleanse yourself of sins before entering this place.'),
(837, 'Your skill points and stat points are higher than your level. Find somewhere else to grind!'),
(838, 'You carry sins with you. You must cleanse yourself of sins before entering this place.'),
(839, 'Master~  The war in Ronark Land Base isnt seem to be going so well due to the knights of El Morad.'),
(840, 'You havent finished the monster hunting mission that you were given before. Come back when you have completed that mission.'),
(841, 'Youll get some Armor out of this if you do [Graveyard Keeper] Slay this favor.'),
(842, 'Youll get the 5th piece of Armor  out of this if you do [Sentinel] Cape this favor.'),
(843, 'Youll get some Armor out of this if you hunt the Ape and go to [Mercenary] Tales.'),
(844, 'Youll get some Armor out of this if you do the [Mercenary Adjutant] Rage this favor.'),
(845, 'Well...  What can I do for you?'),
(846, 'Hi! Eh? You dont know me? Im Shojin, one of the heroes of the Adonisian Continents past. Hahaha~you recognize me, now? Thats okay. I can put up with that rudeness. Why am I here? Um~I would like to revive the Hero Weapon, so I have been learning blacksmith skills from Heppa. But thats not everything. I want to combine blacksmith skill with the alchemy that I learned from an alchemist in my heroic days. I could develop my alchemy further thanks to the experience. Why? Do you want anything born out of alchemy? Alright, I will do that. However, the rule of equivalent exchange requires you to get some materials.'),
(847, 'Um~Production literally means combining many items. Its a type of alchemy! Well, I have repeatedly failed as my EXP is not high enough. But the weapons and armors made out of it have incredible abilities.  Are you interested? I can try if you want, but as I told you just before, theres a possibility of failure. Just get the materials.'),
(848, ' Are you going to start production? Finally! Lets do it~'),
(849, 'Hey hey~To make the Mattock, I need 100 CONT and 1 million Noah  are needed.'),
(850, 'Well, here it is, If you get this, you wont have hard time obtaining materials. Good luck then!'),
(851, 'Hey hey~To make the Mattock, you should give me a reward. Go to make 1 million Noah...'),
(852, 'Hey hey~ I need reputation to make the Mattock. Kill the enemy to get 100 CONT...'),
(853, 'Hey hey~To make the Mattock, I need 100 CONT and 1 million Noah  are needed.'),
(854, 'Hmm~ Remember you cant get weapons for material if you dont have this~!!'),
(855, 'Hmm... Did Masi ask you to come? You need the Mattock to help Masi.- One Mattock can be used in Moradon, and the other Mattock can be used in Ronark Land. Which one would you like to take?'),
(856, 'Your inventory is full.'),
(857, 'Hmm... Did Masi ask you to come? You need the Mattock to help Masi... The material costs 3000 Noah. Would you like to make Mattock?'),
(858, 'Welcome~ Im Masi, a scholar who studies Ancient Civilizations. Nice to meet you, haha~ These days, historians in each Nation are desperate to study Draki. Im in charge of sending research samples about Draki...But Im very busy with too many orders of research samples... Could you give me a hand?'),
(859, 'Oh~really? Thank you... I really appreciate that you instantly offered help, haha~Then I will tell you what to do. Please, listen and take a memo. You have to collect 10 bones for 5 parts including a head bone, leg bone, backbone, tail bone and foot bone... Take 10 bones for each part to [Heppas Disciple] Shojin to have the bones combined into a research sample. Then, you should bring that to me. Whenever you bring me each sample, I will give you aMonster Sealing Cube as a reward.'),
(860, 'Theres an island away from Moradon, and its said that  Unidentified Fossils are found there. Hm~I heard that you can collect them around Ronark Land where Draki Dragon Fossils are.'),
(861, 'Collecting them is not so easy. You can easily collect them if you have just one Mattock. Go to find [Heppas Disciple] Shojin. You can get the Mattock for Moradon and Mattock for Ronark if you go to Shojin.'),
(862, 'You brought the sample... I will never forget you contributed to the Draki research. I will reward you a Monster Sealing Cube for you to try, haha~'),
(863, 'Oh, what youre holding is...  Hm~it seems like a pretty old mirror...  Dont you want to give me that? Lets make a deal, because it might be any use for you. What about it?'),
(864, 'Thank you. Choose one youd like to have. Red Potion  will increase your hp by 300. Blue Potion increases your Defense  by 60, Yellow Potion will increase your EXP. But keep in mind that the EXP increases are different according to your level.'),
(865, 'Hmm~ that mirror will be useless for you... Well, if you like it, thats fine.'),
(866, 'Good luck. I should keep collecting samples. If youre not busy, bring me samples again, haha~'),
(867, 'Welcomd. <selfname>~ New Weapon Event is going on...  How are you doing?'),
(868, '10 new weapons will be newly introduced. Two-Handed Sword, Two-handed Axe, One-handed Sword, Bow, Knife, Flame Staff, Glacier Staff, Lightning Staff, Priest Club, Shield... 10 weapons were launched. I will give one Si Leveler bar for each person who obtains the 10 weapons and shows me first~!! Arent you interested? Haha~I wonder what kind of weapon it may be. I heard the weapons looks great... believe it or not...'),
(869, 'For your information, the newly launched weapon, if combined with other materials, will be compound into a completed weapon. To learn about the compound, please ask [Heppas Disciple] Shojin.'),
(870, 'Wow~this is the new weapon, the Two-handed Sword. The weapon will reveal a hidden power if upgraded to +7... but I would like to thank you for showing me this. Haha~Good luck.'),
(871, 'Well~youre a bit late. Another Knight already showed me the two-handed sword.'),
(872, 'Wow~this is the new weapon, the Two-handed Axe. The weapon will reveal a hidden power if upgraded to +7... but I would like to thank you for showing me this. Good luck!'),
(873, 'Wow~this is the new weapon, the One-handed Axe. The weapon will reveal a hidden power if upgraded to +7... but I would like to thank you for showing me this. Good luck!'),
(874, 'Wow~this is the new weapon, the bow. The weapon will reveal a hidden power if upgraded to +7... but I would like to thank you for showing me this. Good luck!'),
(875, 'Wow~this is the new weapon, the Flame Staff. The weapon will reveal a hidden power if upgraded to +7... but I would like to thank you for showing me this. Good luck!'),
(876, 'Wow~this is the new weapon, the Glacier Staff. The weapon will reveal a hidden power if upgraded to +7... but I would like to thank you for showing me this. Good luck!'),
(877, 'Wow~this is the new weapon, the Lightning Staff. The weapon will reveal a hidden power if upgraded to +7... but I would like to thank you for showing me this. Good luck!'),
(878, 'Wow~this is the new weapon, the Priest Club. The weapon will reveal a hidden power if upgraded to +7... but I would like to thank you for showing me this. Good luck!'),
(879, 'Wow~this is the new weapon, the Shiled. The weapon will reveal a hidden power if upgraded to +7... but I would like to thank you for showing me this. Good luck!'),
(880, 'Wow~this is the new weapon, the Knife. The weapon will reveal a hidden power if upgraded to +7... but I would like to thank you for showing me this. Good luck!'),
(881, 'Dont you own any new weapons?'),
(882, 'Do you want Mattock for Moradon? Well, collecting is pretty hard in the rough place like Ronark Land... but making a Mattock will cost you 3000 Noah for materials. Would you like to make Mattock?'),
(883, 'Collect 10 bones for 5 parts including head bone, leg bone, backbone, tail bone and foot bone, and then go to [Heppas Disciple] Shojin to select  Production.'),
(884, 'Collect 10 bones for 5 parts including head bone, leg bone, backbone, tail bone and foot bone, and then go to [Heppas Disciple] Shojin to select  Production.'),
(885, 'Well~youre a bit late. Another Knight already showed me the two-handed axe.'),
(886, 'Well~youre a bit late. Another Knight already showed me the one-handed sword.'),
(887, 'Well~youre a bit late. Another Knight already showed me the bow.'),
(888, 'Well~youre a bit late. Another Knight already showed me the Flame Staff.'),
(889, 'Well~youre a bit late. Another Knight already showed me the Glacier Staff.'),
(890, 'Well~youre a bit late. Another Knight already showed me the Lightning Staff.'),
(891, 'Well~youre a bit late. Another Knight already showed me the Priest Club.'),
(892, 'Well~youre a bit late. Another Knight already showed me the Shield.'),
(893, 'Well~youre a bit late. Another Knight already showed me the knife.'),
(894, 'Hmm... material cost for Mattock is 3000 Noah.'),
(895, '[A coffin with unidentified force was found. What would you like to do with it?]'),
(896, 'Master, the Stamp of Strength is required to learn the skill 70 Level and 80 Level. [Warrior Master] Skaki will let you know.'),
(897, 'Master, the Stamp of Strength is required to learn the 70 and 80 level skill. [Warrior Master] Skaki will let you know.')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(898, 'Master, the Nostrum of Speed is required to learn the 70 and 80 level skill. [Secret Agent] Clarence will let you know.'),
(899, 'Master, the Nostrum of Speed is required to learn the 70 and 80 level skill. [Secret Agent] Clarence will let you know.'),
(900, 'Master, the Nostrum of Wisdom is required to learn the 70, 74 and 80 level skill.. [Priest] Minerva will let you know.'),
(901, 'Master, the Nostrum of Wisdom is required to learn the 70, 74 and 80 level skill.. [Priest] Minerva will let you know.'),
(902, 'Hmm... Is the Tyrant of All Means?Marce Krowaz leading the Draki of All Means now? We shouldnt underestimate him...'),
(903, 'On my! Who are you? Do you have any business with me?'),
(904, '...The Draki rejected the God of Logos, but  they were powerless. They were destined to slowly disappear from disasters and diseases. But there were some who appeared to help them. They wore white robes, and their voices were warm and deep like that of the Goddess Akara.  The Draki thought they would save them. So the Draki rejected the God of Logos, and started to worship them.  The Pure White Savior led the Draki to the Eternal Place, just before a meteorite fell in Ronark Land...'),
(905, 'Are you interested in Krowazs Land? The land to which the Gods of All Means took the Draki, which the Tyrant of All Mean Marce Krowa controls. If you have a chance to go there, bring me back some precious Gems. Then, I will make something useful for you.'),
(906, 'Would you like to enter into the Krowazs Land? If the party leader applies for the entrance, all the party members can enter into the same area at one scoop. Otherwise, everybody enters individually.'),
(907, 'Are you leaving Krowazs land?'),
(908, 'Are you leaving Krowazs land?'),
(909, '[You opened the coffin, but there was nothing.]'),
(910, 'Sorry, but only Level 70 players or higher can enter Krowazs Land.'),
(911, 'This door does not open automatically. Its connected to other doors, and opens when others open...'),
(912, 'After the server integration, a new server opened. The opening event for the new?Geronique?server is going on now!'),
(913, 'A star sign for each day of the week is dropped. Whoever collects 10 star signs for that day of the week will be given many presents through a prize draw. The more star signs you give me during the event, the higher your chances for winning the prize becomes!! Haha~ For details, please refer to the event page on our website.'),
(914, '# Event duration August 30~ September 13  # Star sign for each day of week  Monday (Arcas)  Tuesday (Virgo)  Wednesday (Libra)  Thursday (Canes Venatici)  Friday (Leo)  Saturday (Hydra)  Sunday (Corona Borealis)'),
(915, 'You already participated in the event today. Please visit again tomorrow. Thank you.'),
(916, 'You have collected Arcas. Would you like to register for the interview after giving the star signs to me?'),
(917, 'You have collected Virgo. Would you like to register for the interview after giving the star signs to me?'),
(918, 'You have collected Libra. Would you like to register for the interview after giving the star signs to me?'),
(919, 'You have collected Canes Venatici. Would you like to register for the interview after giving the star signs to me?'),
(920, 'You have collected Leo. Would you like to register for the interview after giving the star signs to me?'),
(921, 'You have collected Hydra. Would you like to register for the interview after giving the star signs to me?'),
(922, 'You have collected Corona Borealis. Would you like to register for the interview after giving the star signs to me?'),
(923, 'Thank you. Please visit again tomorrow. Have a nice day!'),
(924, 'Welcome, <selfname>!! Welcome to the ?Geronique? server. We give special gifts to Knights who reach the 60th Level on this server. 2 Vouchers for Pathos Gloves (15-day) will be given. Please go to [Peddler] Hemes. Hope to see you soon.'),
(925, '<selfname>, you have reached the 60th Level. Congratulations! Please, continue to enjoy Geronique server, and we hope to see your character succeed even more!. Have a wonderful day!'),
(926, 'Hmm~ This is a Certificate for Pathoss Gloves, registered with the Geronique server opening event. It can be exchanged with gloves for 15-day use. Would you like to exchange the event gloves certificate?'),
(927, 'Youve already participated in the event before.'),
(928, 'Who are you?'),
(929, 'Who are you?'),
(930, 'It has been over a year since I last visited the continent of Adonis...  I never expected it to prosper like this, haha~ It has changed so much and I dont know where I am~'),
(931, ' No, you dont have to care about it.  That doesnt really matter... Haha ~  I only dropped here to rest in Moradon during this Thanksgiving, so all I want is to have some fun... Haha~ Hey, dont you want a Thanksgiving gift? Bring me  10 Statues of Akarra.  Then although my skills are mediocre, I will cast you a buff that you need.'),
(932, 'Haha~ you have the Statues of Akarra... Wont you give them to me? I will cast you a useful buff in return for 10 of those statues, so what do you think? Haha~'),
(933, 'Good~ Then shall I show off my skills for once? Hey,hey~ Take it easy, you dont have to look so scared~ I used to be really famous for this, you know... (cough~) Just relax~ There wont be any side effect either... Haha~ Now, tell me what you need.'),
(934, 'Huoh~ Dont be so greedy!! You can only receive one buff each time!! Come back when the power of my buff fades away.  Then enjoy your holiday ^^'),
(935, '[Sigh of Relief~]Phew~ It was a success, hehe~ How do you like it? Then drop by again when the buff disappears, haha~'),
(936, 'A monster originally raised in Moradon for security purposes, they are now incorporated in mercenary training due to their violent nature.'),
(937, 'A monster originally raised in Moradon for security purposes, they are now incorporated in mercenary training due to their violent nature.'),
(938, 'You have selected the Monster Summons Stamp.  Would you like to exchange with 5 Monster Summons Stamps?'),
(939, 'Trick or Treat!  Happy Halloween!|I have a special event for you. I hope you enjoy it!|Event: Oct. 25 ? Nov. 8'),
(940, 'Pumpkin Monsters are in the fields. Bring me the event items from the Pumpkin Monsters and I will give you a Halloween Gift!'),
(941, '# Material of Wizard Pumpkin Mask (10 ea) -> Wizard Pumpkin Mask|# Material of Pumpkin Mask (10 ea) -> Pumpkin Mask|# Material of Scream Mask (10 ea) -> Scream Mask|# Material of Devil Mask (10 ea) -> Devil Mask|# Material of Halloween Cane (10 ea) -> Halloween Cane|# Material of Halloween Spear (10 ea) -> Halloween Spear|# Material of Whirlwind Candy (10 ea) -> Whirlwind Candy|# Material of Pumpkin Candy (10 ea) -> Pumpkin Candy'),
(942, 'You select Wizard Pumpkin Mask|Please bring back 10 of [Material of Wizard Pumkin Mask] and I will give you Wizard Pumpkin Mask'),
(943, 'Oh~~ Great work! You brought me back 10 of [Material of Wizard Pumpkin Mask]| Would you like to exchange for Wizard Pumpkin Mask?'),
(944, 'Thank you| Happy Halloween'),
(945, 'You select Pumpkin Mask|Please bring back 10 of [Material of Pumkin Mask] and I will give you Pumpkin Mask'),
(946, 'Trick or treat! You brought me back 10 of [Material of Pumpkin Mak]| Would you like to exchange for Pumpkin Mask?'),
(947, 'You select Scream Pumpkin Mask|Please bring back 10 of [Material of Scream Mask] and I will give you Scream Mask'),
(948, 'Hello Sydney~. You brought me back 10 of [Material of Scream Mask]| Would you like to exchange for Scream Mask?'),
(949, 'You select Devil Mask|Please bring back 10 of [Material of Devil Mask] and I will give you Devil Mask'),
(950, 'Imhotep~ Imhotep~. You brought me back 10 of [Material of Devil Mask]| Would you like to exchange for Devil Mask?'),
(951, 'You select Halloween Cane|Please bring back 10 of [Material of Halloween Cane] and I will give you Halloween Cane'),
(952, 'Trick or treat!. You brought me back 10 of [Material of Halloween Cane]| Would you like to exchange for Halloween Cane?'),
(953, 'You select Halloween Spear|Please bring back 10 of [Material of Halloween Spear] and I will give you Halloween Spear'),
(954, 'Hello Sydney~. You brought me back 10 of [Material of Halloween Spear]| Would you like to exchange for Halloween Spear?'),
(955, 'You select Whirlwind Candy|Please bring back 10 of [Material of Whirlwind Candy] and I will give you Wizard Whirlwind Candy'),
(956, 'Trict or treat! You brought me back 10 of [Material of Whirlwind Candy]| Would you like to exchange for Whirlwind Candy?'),
(957, 'You select Pumpkin Candy|Please bring back 10 of [Material of Pumkin Candy] and I will give you Wizard Pumpkin Candy'),
(958, 'Trict or treat! You brought me back 10 of [Material of Pumpkin Candy]| Would you like to exchange for Pumpkin Candy?'),
(959, 'Do you want to exit from here?'),
(960, 'Master, do you know about the place called Arrdream? You should go to Fargo and ask him about it.'),
(961, 'Master, do you know about the place called Arrdream? You should go to Polkwein and ask him about it.'),
(962, 'Theres no room to put the letter of introduction in.  Empty your inventory and then come back.'),
(963, 'Theres no room to put the letter of introduction in.  Empty your inventory and then come back.'),
(964, 'One caught by madness cannot see beyond ones own nose... And the madness can drag you even deeper into the depth of darkness...'),
(965, 'Those ones seized with madness might be running around and causing trouble somewhere here in Islante right now... Shall we go and have a look? Troll Warriors seized with madness, huh... Kuku~'),
(966, 'Master, nice shot~!!'),
(967, 'Wont you come with me to watch those seized with madness? Kuku~'),
(968, 'I watched you crushing those seized with madness.. But this wind of madness will not be stopped that easily~'),
(969, 'Master, nice shot~!!'),
(970, 'Get rid of your pride.. Or you wont become any stronger.  This would be the end of the road for you if you are intoxicated by how strong you have become. But what you really face on your path to strength may not be the shadow of your pride, but your own hesitation... Will you be able to understand it yourself?'),
(971, 'Break your limit... <selfname>~'),
(972, 'Master, you have done well~.'),
(973, ' So, did I take another step forward?? Haha~'),
(974, 'Master, you have done well~.'),
(975, 'Merry Christmas ^0^//'),
(976, 'what a surprise~ Did you bring me a present? Yes? Ho~ ho~ ho~'),
(977, 'Nice to meet you~ I am a [Sexy Santa] Parfait ho~ho~ Maybe I dont look like Santa because I am wearing Sexy Santa cloth ho ho, but I am Santa Claus~?. You can call me Sexy Santa'),
(978, 'You dont belive me that I am Santa? If you do me a favor, I will give you a nice Christmas present. Hmm..lets see..what kind of favor I should ask you..ho~ho~'),
(979, 'Surprise~ Snowman Transform Scroll~? I only will give you this when you bring me 20 Christmas Trees~ Everytime you bring me 20 Christmas Trees, I will give you one scroll of your choice and I have many different styles~ ho~ho~'),
(980, 'Say good-bye to your sad looking accessories because I have Surprise!! Christmas belt and Christmas Pendant~? I only will give this present when you bring me 100 Christmas Trees. When you bring me 100 Christmas Trees, your present could be a Belt or maybe'),
(981, 'Ah! Found it ho~ho~ Gain additional exprerience with Santas Smile..and..lets see..Increase your defense with Santas Coat..and...Last but not the least~ Increase your HP with Santas Mind! Everytime you bring me 20 Lost Present, I will give you one item o'),
(982, 'Ah! Found it ho~ho~ Gain extra Nation Points with Santas Present..and..lets see..Increase your defense with Santas Coat..and...Last but not the least~ Increase your HP with Santas Mind! Everytime you bring me 20 Lost Present, I will give you one item of'),
(983, 'You will bring me a lost present, wont you??'),
(984, 'You will bring me a Christmas Tree, wont you??'),
(985, 'Joy! Joy! You can exchange 20 Christmas Trees for Snowman Transform Scroll~? Would you like to exchange?'),
(986, 'Thank you so~~ much!! Have a Merry Christmas and please Love Knight Online more~?'),
(987, 'Joy! Joy! You can exchange 100 Christmas Trees for Christmas Accessory~?, Would you like to exchange?'),
(988, 'Hmmm..You dont have enough Christmas Trees to exchange for Christmas Accessory'),
(989, 'Joy! Joy! You can exchange 20 Lost Present for Christmas Scroll of your choice~? Would you like to exchange?'),
(990, 'Your inventory is full. You have so many items'),
(991, 'Oops!!.. You dont have enought X-mas trees to exchange with a Snowman ransformation scroll'),
(992, 'Oops!! ..You dont have enough lost presents to exchange with a X-mas package present'),
(993, 'I cannot let the El Morad take over this base, never!!'),
(994, 'Theres a mission for you, <selfname>...'),
(995, 'I cannot let the El Morad take over this base, never!!'),
(996, 'Theres a mission for you, <selfname>...'),
(997, 'Youre new around here. Its obvious youre a Mage from the power flowing through you. You decide you want to reach a higher level as a Mage, come find me. Ill teach you new magic.'),
(998, 'Searching for Drake, Master? I heard hes in <font color=@#006699@>Linate Village</font>. Look for him there!'),
(999, 'Impressive! You found me. Now for that new magic I promised you.'),
(1000, 'What the..? Who are you?'),
(1001, 'Your magic power will increase accordingly when you reach Level 35. Weve got to increase your skill and these Magic Scrolls should do the trick. Theyll help you gain renown as a Mage.'),
(1002, 'Its not free, though. Magic Scrolls dont make themselves, you follow? You got to get me some materials!'),
(1003, 'You still didnt get enough? Buy Magic Stones at the store. Go on!'),
(1004, 'You havent finished collecting all the materials I told you, yet?'),
(1005, 'You need 5 Pincer Poisons for the Blast Spell.'),
(1006, 'Blast Magic requires 200 Magic Stones. What, you dont know where to buy them? Get them at the store. Hurry it up!'),
(1007, 'Got them? Hand em over and Ill make you a Magic Scroll.'),
(1008, 'When you go to the front of El Morad castle gate, you will see the Pincers.'),
(1009, 'Master, all the materials have been gathered.'),
(1010, 'If you bring Tyon meat to the Farm Manager, he turns them into 10,000 Noahs.'),
(1011, 'Well, everythings ready. Now what type of Magic Scroll do you want? There are Magic Scrolls for Flame, Glacier, and Lightning. Choose one that best suits the magic power flowing through your body.'),
(1012, 'Good. Now youre ready to perform properly as a Mage. Stop by anytime you want another Magic Scroll, but remember nothing is free.'),
(1013, 'Searching for Drake, Master? I heard hes in <font color=@#006699@>Linate Village</font>. Look for him there!'),
(1014, 'His Royal Highness has personally assigned a mission to me for the first time in a long while. A war against the enemy should ensue shortly...'),
(1015, 'If we exert pressure on the enemy there, it will be possible for us to infiltrate their mainland, then we will deposit a spy to hunt Lich who`s taken refuge near Kalluga Valley. As the Lich maintain intricate relations with powerful factions, the sole objective of this mission is to seize the Emblem of Karus and deliver it safely to our mainland.|Emblem of Karus is an essential ingredient for casting a great curse on the enemy nation using an ancient black magic I developed.'),
(1016, 'Wow, this is the Emblem of Karus. It might be dangerous for us to remain here. Let`s return to the mainland quickly.'),
(1017, 'Didn`t I tell you to bring back the Emblem of Karus?'),
(1018, 'Wow, you have safely collected the Emblem of Karus.. Good work. Your honor will increase accordingly as a result.'),
(1019, '10 million EXP are awarded for infiltrating enemy mainland after winning the Lunar War and capturing Lich near Kalluga Valley and collecting the Emblem of Karus.'),
(1020, 'When you go to the front of Karus castle gate, you will see the Pincers.'),
(1021, 'Master, Youve have collected all the materials.'),
(1022, 'I see you brought everything I told you. Yes... From now one I will call you by the title of Elemental Lord, the one who has a thorough knowledge of the universe.  Would you like change your Job now?'),
(1023, 'Hm. Now you are ready.  I appoint you as a Blade Master. Would you like to change your Job now?'),
(1024, 'There enough items here to conduct the ceremony.  You will be conferred the name of Kasar Hood.  Would you like to hold the ceremony right now?'),
(1025, 'You have prepared all the items needed for the 2nd Job change.  You are here to take an oath with the god as a Paladin.  Would you like to hold the ceremony right now?'),
(1026, 'You wasting my time? You dont want it, get out!'),
(1027, 'Your bag seems full.'),
(1028, '[The classified documents box of our force is well kept right now]'),
(1029, '[We havent found anything]'),
(1030, 'Master, your inventory is full and there is no space for the Classified Document.'),
(1031, 'Master, your inventory is full and there is no space for the Classified Document.'),
(1032, '[You have succeeded in seizing the document from the Classified Documents Box]'),
(1033, 'I am analyst Caesar | What kind of mission do you want?||- Spy Rescue Mission :  Available once a day |- Seize the Enemys Classified Document  mission: Available only on Mondays, Wednesdays, Fridays and Sundays |- Searching for the Lost Soul Mission : Available only on Tuesdays, Thursdays, and Saturdays'),
(1034, 'I am analyst Julius | What kind of mission do you want?||- Spy Rescue Mission :  Available once a day |- Seize the Enemys Classified Document  mission: Available only on Mondays, Wednesdays, Fridays and Sundays |- Searching for the Lost Soul Mission : Available only on Tuesdays, Thursdays, and Saturdays'),
(1035, 'I analyze the information I get from the spies who work in various places of Ronark Land.  What do you think.. Would you like to try too?'),
(1036, 'I dont think I can give you a mission since we dont know the location of the soul that is still lingering in this world'),
(1037, 'I am sorry -'),
(1038, 'First of all, you should know the location of El Morad Military HQ in advance.  Return with a classified document from the El Morad Military HQ, but remember that each document has different grade.  The higher grade the classified document is, the higher your reward will be, and one more thing...'),
(1039, 'You will need this potion.  To open that classified document box, you will need the power of this potion.  Not only it makes your body invisible for 1 minute so you can evade the detection by the enemys guard tower, you need the power of this potion to open that document box.  But, remember that you cannot evade the eyes of the enemy rogues and general magic of the magicians.  This potion is extremely difficult to make, so it will cost you 1 million Noahs. What would you like to do?'),
(1040, 'You have already carried out todays mission.  Hey, you know how to have a kick -'),
(1041, 'Master, do you know of [Analyst] Caesar in Ronark Land ?'),
(1042, 'Master, you have seized the enemys classified document.'),
(1043, 'Return with the classified document from the enemys military HQ. And you must never lose the potion I gave to you.'),
(1044, 'Wow.. This mission wasnt easy at all but you managed to complete it successfully.  Hand it over to me now.'),
(1045, 'What??? That document... Didnt you bring it here to give me??'),
(1046, 'Your mission ended as soon as it went past midnight.  Now this document is nothing more than a mere piece of paper.'),
(1047, 'I analyze the information I get from the spies who work in various places of Ronark Land.  What do you think.. Would you like to try too?'),
(1048, 'I dont think I can give you a mission since we dont know the location of the soul yet.'),
(1049, 'I am sorry -'),
(1050, 'First of all, you should know the location of Karus Military HQ in advance.  Return with a classified document from the Karus Military HQ, but remember that each document has different grade.  The higher grade the classified document is, the higher your reward will be, and one more thing...'),
(1051, 'You will need this potion.  To open that classified document box, you will need the power of this potion.  Not only it makes your body invisible for 1 minute so you can evade the detection by the enemys guard tower, you need the power of this potion to open that document box.  But, remember that you cannot evade the eyes of the enemy rogues and general magic of the magicians.  This potion is extremely difficult to make, so it will cost you 1 million Noahs. What would you like to do?'),
(1052, 'You have already carried out todays mission.  Hey, you know how to have a kick -'),
(1053, 'Master, do you know of [Analyst] Julius in Ronark Land ?'),
(1054, 'Master, you have seized the enemys classified document.'),
(1055, 'Return with the classified document from the enemys military HQ. And you must never lose the potion I gave to you.'),
(1056, 'Wow.. This mission wasnt easy at all but you managed to complete it successfully.  Hand it over to me now.'),
(1057, 'What??? That document... Didnt you bring it here to give me??'),
(1058, 'Your mission ended as soon as it went past midnight.  Now this document is nothing more than a mere piece of paper.'),
(1059, 'The location of another sealed soul should be found by tomorrow... Would you like to come back tomorrow?'),
(1060, 'I am still busy analyzing the enemys classified documents collected so far... Im sorry but could you visit again tomorrow?'),
(1061, 'There have been so many battles here in Ronark Land, and many Karus knights were killed in battle.  It is their effort that did not let El Morad to take over this place.'),
(1062, 'According to the information that just came in, an unidentified corpse has been found near the central area of Ronark.  I am guessing that it could be the body of our Karus warrior... I want you to go there and confirm it.'),
(1063, ' But, you will have to hurry as I heard that El Morad is also looking for that corpse.  It will be for naught If they get the body before us.'),
(1064, 'This altar delivers the Kings prayer to the God when the nation is losing in war. But do not expect a response from the God without offering the national treasury.'),
(1065, 'Okay - then go to the central area by this way.  You will have to search the central area very thoroughly.'),
(1066, '        Steal the enemys classified document!|- the potion you are given is for one-use only, and the stealth skill comes into effect for one minute (If you dont have the potion, then you can get it from NPC again)|- Keep it mind that the stealth skill of the potion you received is not effective against the general magic of magicians and the eyes of the enemys rogues.'),
(1067, 'Master, I think this is what Caesar wanted, so lets hurry back and report to him.'),
(1068, 'Do you know that  you are given 10 minutes??'),
(1069, 'Huh!! That.. That is... The dead soul didnt find the right way- Is this what we say we were lucky that this happened. If he was in the hands of El Morad he wouldnt have been able to rest even after his death... Well done, <selfname>...'),
(1070, 'Are you going to look after that soul??'),
(1071, 'The location of another sealed soul should be found by tomorrow... Would you like to come back tomorrow?'),
(1072, 'I am still busy analyzing the enemys classified documents collected so far... Im sorry but could you visit again tomorrow?'),
(1073, 'There have been so many battles here in Ronark Land, and many El Morad knights were killed in battle.  It is their effort that did not let Karus to take over this place.'),
(1074, 'According to the information that just came in, an unidentified corpse has been found near the central area of Ronark.  I am guessing that it could be the body of our Karus warrior... I want you to go there and confirm it.'),
(1075, ' But, you will have to hurry as I heard that Karus is also looking for that corpse.  It will be for naught If they get the body before us.'),
(1076, 'Human power always has its limit. If you are losing, borrow the power from God. But, Gods help always costs you something..'),
(1077, 'Okay - then go to the central area by this way.  You will have to search the central area very thoroughly.'),
(1078, '        Searchng for the Lost Soul.. |- The limit time for the mission is 10 minutes |- You can find the dead body in the central area of Ronark Land |- After accepting the quest, for 10 minutes, you can not use summon skill and the village (But, if you get reward, the ban is canceled).'),
(1079, 'Master, I think this is what Julius wanted, so lets hurry back and report to him.'),
(1080, 'Do you know that  you are given 10 minutes??'),
(1081, 'Huh!! That.. That is... The dead soul didnt find the right way- Is this what we say we were lucky that this happened. If he was in the hands of Karus he wouldnt have been able to rest even after his death... Well done, <selfname>...'),
(1082, 'Are you going to look after that soul??'),
(1083, '[You found the dead body of a Karus warrior who seems to be killed while fighting bravely..]'),
(1084, '[You found the dead body of an El Morad warrior who seems to be killed while fighting bravely..]'),
(1085, '[You didnt find anything new.]'),
(1086, '[You found something in the dead body.]'),
(1087, 'Master, your inventory is full.'),
(1088, 'Master, your inventory is full.'),
(1089, '[The soul who hasnt left the battlefield is staying in the dead body]'),
(1090, 'Master, if you need <font color=@#006666@>Low Level Elemental Magic Scroll</font>, look for Menissiah.'),
(1091, 'Master, if you need <font color=@#006666@>Low Level Elemental Magic Scroll</font>, look for Menissiah.'),
(1092, 'Low Level Elemental Magic Scroll? Did I have that?'),
(1093, 'Ah, here it is! This what you wanted? I havent used it for a while so it slipped my mind. You need it?'),
(1094, 'Make you a deal. I need Apples of Moradon for reasons of my own, see, but I have no clue how to find it. Suppose you get me 5 Apples of Moradon and Ill give YOU this Magic Scroll.'),
(1095, 'Nothing free in this world. Or cant you handle it?'),
(1096, 'Master, all 5 Apples of Moradon have been gathered!'),
(1097, 'Master, all 5 Apples of Moradon have been gathered!')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(1098, 'Still dont have it? Putting me on the spot here...'),
(1099, 'Look at that, got it right away. Youre better than I thought.'),
(1100, 'Doubt you can get them. Thats F-A-N-G O-F W-E-R-E-W-O-L-F, by the way.'),
(1101, 'Hm.. without help of the power of this potion, you wont be able to succeed this mission.'),
(1102, 'Hm.. without help of the power of this potion, you wont be able to succeed this mission.'),
(1103, ' 5000 Noahs might be reasonable for me, dont you think so? Okay, bring me 5000 Noahs and try it!'),
(1104, 'Happy new year, haha~~ I have something good and would you like to see it??'),
(1105, 'This is such a unique scroll that can transform your pet into Etaros.. Haha~~'),
(1106, 'If you want to have this scroll, look for Etaroses that are spread all over this continent, collect 50 pieces in which their souls are kept in and bring them to me.'),
(1107, 'Collecting 50 pieces of Etaros Soul, Great ~~~ Success!!'),
(1108, 'Collecting 50 pieces of Etaros Soul, Great ~~~ Success!!'),
(1109, 'You need 50 pieces of Etaros soul.'),
(1110, 'Haha~~ You did a great job... Happy new year!'),
(1111, 'You chose premium potion. Please select a correct potion type for your voucher'),
(1112, 'You chose 100 premium HP potion. Would you like to receive it?'),
(1113, 'Sorry, you dont have a voucher for 100 premium HP potion'),
(1114, 'Thank you.'),
(1115, 'You chose 300 premium HP potion. Would you like to receive it?'),
(1116, 'Sorry, you dont have a voucher for 300 premium HP potion'),
(1117, 'You chose 100 premium MP potion. Would you like to receive it?'),
(1118, 'Sorry, you dont have a voucher for 100 premium MP potion'),
(1119, 'You chose 300 premium MP potion. Would you like to receive it?'),
(1120, 'Sorry, you dont have a voucher for 300 premium MP potion'),
(1121, 'Hm.. you have grown up too big to go to Arrdream - About the intense battles you had in Ardream, just keep that as a precious memory now.'),
(1122, 'Hm.. you have grown up too big to go to Arrdream - About the intense battles you had in Ardream, just keep that as a precious memory now.'),
(1123, '[You cant open the classified document box]'),
(1124, 'The potion is 1 million Noahs... Would you like to buy it?'),
(1125, 'The potion is 1 million Noahs... Would you like to buy it?'),
(1126, 'You need a [Bahamut Armor Certificate] to get the Bahamut Armor. A [Bahamut Armor Certificate] can be purchased from the Power-up store.'),
(1127, 'You have selected Bahamut Armor HP+200 Would you really like to get it?'),
(1128, 'You have selected Bahamut Armor Defense +30. Would you really like to get it?'),
(1129, 'You have selected Bahamut Armor EXP Gain Rate +4%. Would you really like to get it?'),
(1130, 'You have selected Bahamut Armor Noah Drop Rate +6%. Would you really like to get it?'),
(1131, 'You have selected Bahamut Helmet HP+100. Would you really like to get it?'),
(1132, 'You have selected Bahamut Helmet Defense +20. Would you really like to get it?'),
(1133, 'You have selected Bahamut Helmet EXP Gain Rate +2%. Would you really like to get it?'),
(1134, 'You have selected Bahamut Helmet Noah Drop Rate +3%. Would you really like to get it?'),
(1135, 'Master, do you know Asgaberry?'),
(1136, 'Master, do you know something about Cardinal jewel?'),
(1137, 'Do you know the chocolate that makes you fall into love? I need that chocolate right now so desperately. Would you like to find it for me?'),
(1138, 'Thank you.  [Chocolatier] Cacao who is at the port right now would know something about it.'),
(1139, 'Love Chocolate? I am not selling it now cause it wasnt profitable.  Unless I have  Lavender...'),
(1140, 'Hm..Im sorry but would you please step aside for me? Im really busy trying to adjust to the demand of Valentine chocolates.'),
(1141, 'Collecting 10 Lavender complete!!'),
(1142, 'Collecting 10 Lavender complete!!'),
(1143, 'Wow ~ You have collected the ones with good quality. I will make it for you soon.'),
(1144, 'That is Love Chocolate~~. You should bring that to Menicia~'),
(1145, 'That is Love Chocolate~~. You should bring that to Menicia~'),
(1146, 'Have you met with Cacao?'),
(1147, 'Wow~ Lavender flavor chocolate.. Thank you.  Here, take this.  Its a gift for you since you always comply with my request.'),
(1148, 'Phew~ Im so busy! Hey you! Find some chocolate for me!'),
(1149, 'Phew~ Im so busy!'),
(1150, 'First of all, get special chocolate from  [Chocolatier] Valence  and bring it here.'),
(1151, 'Master, you have received the special chocolate~ you should bring it to Ciders.'),
(1152, 'Master, you have received the special chocolate~ you should bring it to Ciders.'),
(1153, 'Did you see [Chocolatier] Valence?'),
(1154, 'All right~ This is it. Thank you!'),
(1155, 'To make that chocolate, you have to bring the materials for that. The materials are 5 lavenders and 5 rosemaries.'),
(1156, 'Yo ho~!'),
(1157, 'Master, youve collected all the materials for the chocolate~'),
(1158, 'Master, youve collected all the materials for the chocolate~'),
(1159, 'Are you still collecting the materials I requested?'),
(1160, 'Aha~ You have brought them on time! Now you can bring this to Ciders.'),
(1161, 'Hm.. What have I done today~~'),
(1162, 'I havent lost it yet!!!'),
(1163, 'What about my diary?? Huh???'),
(1164, 'Um, ah! Uh?? This is my diary.. Thank you ~ (Hm, but I feel like I will lose it again tomorrow..)'),
(1165, 'Um, ah! Uh?? My diary!! My diary!!! My diary is gone!!!!! Hey~ Have you seen my diary?? I think I lost it somewhere near the  Outskirt of Inside the Moradon Castle..'),
(1166, 'Oh, did you find the diary?? Haha~'),
(1167, 'Oh, did you find the diary?? Haha~'),
(1168, '[You have acquired the diary.]'),
(1169, 'Master, youve already found the diary^^'),
(1170, 'Master, youve already found the diary^^'),
(1171, 'Ah.. I have to prepare a present for my boyfriend...'),
(1172, 'Master, if Moradon has Mercenary Captain Cougar, we have [Captain] Fargo. It wouldn`t hurt to say hello.'),
(1173, 'Not long ago, Recons from Karus infiltrated our country, examined our land and began to draft a map. We planted a spy among them in return. And that spy submitted regular reconnaissance reports. But somehow, the soldier who went to receive the reconnaissance report didn`t come back this time.'),
(1174, 'I need a favor. Go take out the hostiles and establish contact with our spy. Give him this [Orders from Captain] and return with [3 Scouting Maps] and [Reconnaissance Report]. Well, you up to it?'),
(1175, 'Master, all [Reconnaissance Report] and [3 Scouting Maps] have been gathered. Hurry back to [Captain] Fargo.'),
(1176, 'Master, all [Reconnaissance Report] and [3 Scouting Maps] have been gathered. Hurry back to [Captain] Fargo.'),
(1177, 'What about the reconnaissance map? Don`t tell me you dropped it somewhere.'),
(1178, 'Listen, I told you to bring the reconnaissance report. Just what have you done?'),
(1179, 'Good work. You`ve successfully completed your mission.'),
(1180, '(whisper whisper) I`m a bogus Recon who infiltrated this house. You`d better leave before other Recons catch on.'),
(1181, 'I should share my mission with you.'),
(1182, 'This is the reconnaissance report. I hope you will deliver it to the captain safely.'),
(1183, 'You didn`t bring the captain`s written order? Did you come here to fool around?'),
(1184, 'And you must attack the Recons around me now and confiscate the reconnaissance map from them. Without the map, the reconnaissance report is utterly useless. Mark my words.'),
(1185, 'Captain Fargo has planted a spy among the enemy scouts. Find the scouts and establish contact with our spy to receive [Reconnaissance Report]. Also, defeat all enemy scouts and collect all [3 Scouting Maps] you can find. If you return to Captain Fargo with all the required items, you will be rewarded with experience points.'),
(1186, 'There`s no problem with Moradon`s security right now. If one occurs I`ll tell you.'),
(1187, 'I have a mission for you.'),
(1188, 'The mercenary squad haven`t assigned any missions lately. Go see [Mercenary Captain] Kugar. At this rate, we`ll even forget that we`re mercenaries.'),
(1189, 'The mercenary brigade`s haven`t assigned any missions lately. Go see [Mercenary Captain] Kugar. At this rate, we`ll even forget that we`re mercenaries.'),
(1190, 'Just in time. I`ve prepared a special training session as the morale among mercenary ranks seem to be low. The orc Prisoners captured thus far are kept in an underground holding cell in Moradon. I`ve lodged a combat Certificate in each of their clothes. Think of this as a training session.'),
(1191, 'Fight a duel with the Orc prisoners of war at the P.O.W. camp and collect just five certificates of duels which are held by them. How about starting it now?'),
(1192, 'Master all the certificates have been retrieved. Let`s go report to the captain.'),
(1193, 'Master all the certificates have been retrieved. Let`s go report to the captain.'),
(1194, 'What happened? Dont say that you caught Orc but forgot to collect the duel certificates! You should have collected at least five duel certificates.'),
(1195, 'I knew you`d be able to do it with ease. You can train freely until the mission.'),
(1196, '[Mercenary Commander] Couger orders the Mercenary to have duels against the Orc prisoners of war at the dungeon as a special training for mercenaries. If you hunt Orc prisoners of war at the dungeon and collect five cetificates of duel held by them, you can be compensated.'),
(1197, 'Um, Uh.. May I ask you a favor, I prepared a surprise gift for the person right in front of me, but I forgot to bring it, would you please help me?'),
(1198, 'If you go to [Mediator] Ciders, he has the present I asked for, and would you bring it without letting my boyfriend know about that?'),
(1199, 'Master, this seems to be the ordered present.'),
(1200, 'Master, I heard they`re making small body armor for kids like me in front of the blacksmith`s. Go ask [Blacksmith] Heppa.'),
(1201, 'Master, I heard they`re making small body armor for kids like me in front of the blacksmith`s. Go ask [Blacksmith] Heppa.'),
(1202, 'Frankly we aren`t very interested in goblins but we are interested in the armor they`re wearing.| Their technique is terrible but they use ace ingredients. If we just touch it up a little, it becomes a great body armor in no time.| If you bring me Goblin Armor I`ll ask my friends in the Blacksmiths Guild to repair your armor. If you have sub par armor, a new goblin armor wouldn`t hurt.'),
(1203, 'Taking your figure and that of the goblins into account, I`ll need at least 5 pieces of armor of the same body part to make body armor of the same. Will you go find them?'),
(1204, 'Hey! I need 5 Goblin Armor tops to make Goblin Body Armor top. Do I need to have you stand next to each other and size you two up?'),
(1205, 'Still, my pals at the guild are going to repair your armor. You should give them a small fee. They have to make ends meet, too. They will charge 100,000 Noahs to make one Goblin Body Armor top.'),
(1206, 'Here. Here`s a Goblin Body Armor just for you. Doesn`t it look great?'),
(1207, 'Taking your figure and that of the goblins into account, I`ll need at least 5 pieces of armor of the same body part to make body armor of the same. Will you go find them?'),
(1208, 'Hey! I need 5 Goblin Armor bottoms to make Goblin Body Armor bottom. Do I need to have you stand next to each other and size you two up?'),
(1209, 'Still, my pals at the guild are going to repair your armor. You should give them a small fee. They have to make ends meet, too. They will charge 80,000 Noahs to make one Goblin Body Armor top.'),
(1210, 'Here. Here`s a Goblin Body Armor just for you. Doesn`t it look great?'),
(1211, 'Taking your figure and that of the goblins into account, I`ll need at least 5 pieces of armor of the same body part to make body armor of the same. Will you go find them?'),
(1212, 'Hey! I need 5 Goblin Armor helmets to make Goblin Body Armor helmet. Do I need to have you stand next to each other and size you two up?'),
(1213, 'Still, my pals at the guild are going to repair your armor. You should give them a small fee. They have to make ends meet, too. They will charge 50,000 Noahs to make one Goblin Body Armor helmet.'),
(1214, 'Here. Here`s a Goblin Body Armor just for you. Doesn`t it look great?'),
(1215, 'Taking your figure and that of the goblins into account, I`ll need at least 5 pieces of armor of the same body part to make body armor of the same. Will you go find them?'),
(1216, 'Hey! I need 5 Goblin Armor gauntlets to make Goblin Body Armor gauntlet. Do I need to have you stand next to each other and size you two up?'),
(1217, 'Still, my pals at the guild are going to repair your armor. You should give them a small fee. They have to make ends meet, too. They will charge 40,000 Noahs to make one Goblin Body Armor gauntlet.'),
(1218, 'Here. Here`s a Goblin Body Armor just for you. Doesn`t it look great?'),
(1219, 'Taking your figure and that of the goblins into account, I`ll need at least 5 pieces of armor of the same body part to make body armor of the same. Will you go find them?'),
(1220, 'Hey! I need 5 Goblin Armor gauntlets to make Goblin Body Armor boots. Do I need to have you stand next to each other and size you two up?'),
(1221, 'Still, my pals at the guild are going to repair your armor. You should give them a small fee. They have to make ends meet, too. They will charge 30,000 Noahs to make one pair of Goblin Body Armor boots.'),
(1222, 'Here. Here`s a Goblin Body Armor just for you. Doesn`t it look great?'),
(1223, '[Blacksmith Heppa] will make you Goblin Body Armor top for 5 Goblin Armor top and 100,000 Noahs.'),
(1224, '[Blacksmith Heppa] will make you Goblin Body Armor bottom for 5 Goblin Armor bottom and 80,000 Noahs.'),
(1225, '[Blacksmith Heppa] will make you Goblin Body Armor helmet for 5 Goblin Armor helmet and 50,000 Noahs.'),
(1226, '[Blacksmith Heppa] will make you Goblin Body Armor gauntlet for 5 Goblin Armor gauntlet and 40,000 Noahs.'),
(1227, '[Blacksmith Heppa] will make you Goblin Body Armor boots for 5 Goblin Armor boots and 30,000 Noahs.'),
(1228, 'Master! Ive heard that Apple of Moradon has a sticky effect. Lets go and find [Mercenary Supply Officer] Osmond and check it out.'),
(1229, 'Master, theres a strange rumor going around Moradon.'),
(1230, 'Master!  <font color=@#990000@>[Mercenary Quartermaster] Mr. Osmund</font> is looking for you, Master, for the preparation of war materials'),
(1231, 'Note that [Report User] is excluded from National Defense Combat.'),
(1232, 'Uh oh...Problem! Big problem! Where can I get hold of some Blood of Glyptodont?'),
(1233, 'Master, I hear [Archmage] Drake is looking for people to assign a mission.'),
(1234, 'Master, you also need the Stamp of Intelligence to learn the 70v, 72Lv, 75Lv and 78Lv skills. [Priest] Minerva will tell you about it.'),
(1235, 'Master, you also need the Stamp of Intelligence to learn the 70v, 72Lv, 75Lv and 78Lv skills. [Priest] Minerva will tell you about it.'),
(1236, 'The border defending battle is held every day at 10 AM and 1, 3, 5 and 10 PM and 1 AM. And it is held additionally at 8 PM on Tuesday, Friday, Saturday and Sunday when there is no war. When the relevant time comes, the announcement for recruitment will be aired automatically so that application for participation can be made.'),
(1237, ' Master, now you can learn Absolute Power.  Lets look for [Archmage] Drake.'),
(1238, 'You need the Nostrum of Magic is required to learn the 70Lv and 80Lv skills, master. [Archmage] Drake will tell you about it.'),
(1239, 'Master, you also need the Stamp of Magic Power to learn the 70v, 72Lv and 75Lv skills. [Archmage] Drake will tell you about it.'),
(1240, 'Master, I heard there`s a collectible item essential to high-level knights. I heard [Archmage] Drake knows about it.'),
(1241, 'Master, do you know of Ssohn Magic? Archmage Drake is looking for someone to whom he can teach it.'),
(1242, 'Master, [Archmage] Drake is giving an Impact Magic Scroll lecture. Let`s go check it out.'),
(1243, 'Master, you need various objects to obtain the  Impact Magic Scroll. Let`s go find out the details from [Archmage] Drake.'),
(1244, 'Master, have you hear of a powerful attack magic called Impact Magic? Wouldn`t  [Archmage] Drake know about it?'),
(1245, 'Tyons have disappeared to an extent, but they will multiply again as they have superior breeding ability.'),
(1246, 'Will you help me?'),
(1247, 'This year`s harvest will be ruined because of the Tyons. Wish someone would get rid of them for me.'),
(1248, 'I will award you handsomely if you eliminate the Tyons what infiltrated the farm and bring me their meat. I`m counting on you.'),
(1249, 'Tyons are stock monsters around the farm. There will be plenty of them here.'),
(1250, 'Not bad. Look outside. There`s already some of them lurking outside. but they will multiply again as they have superior breeding ability.'),
(1251, 'If you bring the Farm Manager Tyon meat, he will give you 1,000 Noahs in return.'),
(1252, 'Your passion is commendable, but save your strength.'),
(1253, 'You should contribute to your country if you`ve returned home after wandering for so long. I`ve got just the mission for a new recruit like you.'),
(1254, 'Master, this seems to be the ordered present.'),
(1255, 'Are you still working on the thing I asked for??'),
(1256, 'Ah~ thank you. I dont know how I could repay this... Ah, when I was leaving the Island of Fog, I found this ring.  It doesnt fit me or my boyfriend, so please take this.'),
(1257, 'What about the reconnaissance map? Don`t tell me you dropped it somewhere.'),
(1258, 'There`s plenty of cooking ingredients but it`s not time to eat yet so wait.'),
(1259, 'Don`t you think I should make a fabulous dish!?'),
(1260, 'Master, it`s time for the Imperial Palace Chef to start cooking. Go see what he`s up to.'),
(1261, 'Oh, no. I`m going to make BBQ but I`m short on Tyon meat.'),
(1262, 'Can you bring me 2 slabs of Tyon meat from the nearby farm? I will make you great BBQ and a handsome reward in return. How about it?'),
(1263, 'Master, you have collected all slabs of Tyon meat. Let`s go the Imperial Palace Chef.'),
(1264, 'Tyons live near the farm to the right of the castle. They`re a bit savage so be careful.'),
(1265, 'Oh! You brought them? Here`s your reward.'),
(1266, 'Can I ask you one more favor?!'),
(1267, 'Please take this BBQ to the Lunar Gate Sentinel. I`m too busy to take it myself. I`ll give you a nice gift if you do this for me.'),
(1268, 'If you`re craving something delicious, you`ve come to the right place.'),
(1269, 'The Imperial Palace Chef told me he`d bring me BBQ today. Didn`t you run into him on the way?'),
(1270, 'Thank you for bringing me the food..|Um, I`m sorry to ask you a favor but I was wondering if you can take this ring to my love. She`ll be somewhere near the Islante entrance.'),
(1271, 'I`m sorry to ask you a favor but I`m hoping you, <selfname>, would do this for me.'),
(1272, 'I was wondering if you can take this ring to my love. I heard she`s always lingering somewhere near the Islante entrance. You should be able to spot her there.'),
(1273, 'Thank you for delivering the ring.'),
(1274, 'Did you have something to day to me?'),
(1275, 'I heard that my love has been banished to Lunar Gate and is residing there. If only I could see his face just once ...'),
(1276, 'I`m sorry, but I`m of no relation to you what-so-ever.'),
(1277, 'Ah... you seem to be someone with whom I could share my predicament.'),
(1278, 'Um... A ring ... No, never mind.'),
(1279, 'This is the right of passage to Lunar Valley. You can go to the front by traversing here.'),
(1280, 'The Imperial Palace Chef  will give a reward for the Tyon meat he needs and receive the quest which entails delivering BBQ to the Lunar Gate Sentinel.'),
(1281, 'EXP are awarded for delivering BBQ to the Lunar Gate Sentinel as well as the Islante Woman Quest.'),
(1282, 'A large reward is awarded for delivering the Lunar Gate Sentinel`s ring to the Islante woman.'),
(1283, 'Thank you for delivering the ring.'),
(1284, 'Master, I hear Blacksmith Heppa developed a better body armor than the Body Armor of Destruction. Let`s go see what it is.'),
(1285, 'Master, I hear Blacksmith Heppa developed a better body armor than the Body Armor of Destruction. Let`s go see what it is.'),
(1286, 'Talisman of Talia are made from an ancient giant race but they were all looted in the War of Darkness and almost none are left. I heard recently that some Ungas produced them. Talisman of Talia are used to turn the Body Armor of Destruction into Talia Body Armor. Talia Body Armor possesses many traits but it cannot not be repaired yet. If you bring some Talisman of Talia I can try and make some for you. Want to give it a shot?'),
(1287, 'I`ll make it for you if you bring me 5 Talisman of Talia which can be obtained by hunting Ungas and the Body Armor of Destruction top and crystals.'),
(1288, 'You`re short on Talisman of Talia. Body Armor with holes won`t be any good. You need to collect 5.'),
(1289, 'You`re short on Body Armor of Destruction tops. How do you expect me to make body armor with this. If you bring me Body Armor of Destruction ingredients I`ll make it for you.'),
(1290, 'You`re short on crystals. They`re needed as an adhesive.  Without it, the defense ability will fast disappear.'),
(1291, 'Here you go. Good work. I wanted to make this armor, too but I couldn`t get my hands on the ingredients. I should be the one thankful. Hahaha.'),
(1292, 'If you bring Blacksmith Heppa the Body Armor of Destruction top, 5 Talisman of Talia, and 1 crystal, he will make you Talia Body Armor endowed with one trait out of many.'),
(1293, 'The thing?! What was it.. Ah~~~!!! The Special Chocolate! I... Sold it...'),
(1294, '  [Canyon Keeper] Skar  at Python Valley  said that he was going to pay double for the chocolate.  So I just sold it to him, haha~~'),
(1295, 'Did you lose your way??'),
(1296, 'What, chocolate? Thats what I bought, and you are telling me to give it to you, Im quite confused.. This isnt right, dont you think so???'),
(1297, 'Hm... Then bring me something that is worthy of trading with this one.  I think I can accept the handmade chocolate of  [Chocolatier] Valence.')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(1298, 'This is the handmade chocolate, now lets go back to Skar^^'),
(1299, 'This is the handmade chocolate, now lets go back to Skar^^'),
(1300, 'Master, I hear Blacksmith Heppa needs for Apples of Moradon. Let`s go see him.'),
(1301, 'Master, I hear Blacksmith Heppa needs for Apples of Moradon. Let`s go see him.'),
(1302, 'Silan`s bones, concentrated with Silan`s life force, are harder than steel but most blacksmiths don`t touch them as they are hard to melt.  But I discovered a special method to melt Silan bones. I will give you a big reward if you bring me the bones.'),
(1303, 'Can you go find me 2 Apples of Moradon to make a special body armor?'),
(1304, 'You`re short on Apple of Moradon. This is not enough.'),
(1305, 'All 2 Apples of Moradon have been collected.'),
(1306, 'All 2 Apples of Moradon have been collected.'),
(1307, 'Hand me the Apple of Moradon and I`ll give you a reward.'),
(1308, 'If you bring 10 Apples of Moradon, and a fee of 3,000 Noahs he will make you one of the five Silan Body Armor parts.'),
(1309, 'Weve got a spy among the enemy scouts. Find the scouts and establish contact with our spy to receive [Reconnaissance Report]. Also, defeat all enemy scouts and collect all [3 Scouting Maps] you can find.'),
(1310, 'I need more of the Spools of Black Silk for making the War Supplies armor. The Cave Leeches in the Abyss Dungeoun tend to horde those Spools of Black Silk.'),
(1311, 'It might be better you to participate in warfare than in something like this. It`s too trivial a task for someone like you.'),
(1312, 'I finally have some downtime.'),
(1313, 'Incidents never fail to occur.'),
(1314, 'Ok, first of all I should explain about Pincers Scorpions. Pincers Scorpions are monsters evolved from scorpions. Their apple is highly toxic. Many people die from it every year. But, Apple of Moradon is also used as an ingredient in cement for repairing castle walls and bridges here in Moradon, because it has a very strong cohesive effect.'),
(1315, 'Now then, the place Im introducing you to this time is Ardream. You can enter it from levels 45 to 80, and there are often some good PvP fights to be found out there. Ill give you a letter of introduction, so go and introduce yourself to Ardreams [Search Captain] Zamed.'),
(1316, 'Master!! Master, you already have too many other missions to deal with. Come back and help theNameless Warrior later.'),
(1317, 'Master!! Master, you already have too many other missions to deal with. Come back and help theNameless Warrior later.'),
(1318, 'Master, there still seems to be too many bands of Rotten Eyes for the warriors spirits to fall asleep comfortably.'),
(1319, 'Not long ago, our Villages Knight Squad suffered great losses from a Monster attack. So its of no small concern that our citizens morale is falling because its been confirmed that more of our men died than monsters. As such, weve decided to... increase... the number of dead monsters when we officially inform the citizenry.'),
(1320, 'If youre not too busy, could you lend us a hand? We dont have enough hunters because most of them are busy re-building the village.'),
(1321, 'Hmm... I feel this isnt really enough.'),
(1322, 'Thank you so much.|Im ashamed of myself as an Imperial Palace Guard in Folk Village. But I think you did whats best for the citizens and soldiers, and for that I thank you. Heres a little something for ya. Choose the one you like.'),
(1323, 'I should do this for all our citizens and soldiers. Please, help me.'),
(1324, 'Managing Supplies is not suited for everyone.'),
(1325, 'Always be ready, because you never know when war will break out.'),
(1326, 'The best knights dont fight with their tounges... You need endless training and a will of iron!'),
(1327, 'This is Folk Village.|Whats up?'),
(1328, 'Master, there still seems to be too many bands of Rotten Eyes for the warriors spirits to fall asleep comfortably.'),
(1329, 'Ach, so busy, so busy...|Ahh, <selfname>. Welcome. Folk Village is really jumping, preparing the war supplies for our people. If youre not too busy, would you mind lending me a hand?'),
(1330, 'Perhaps youve heard of Apple of Moradon?  Apple of Moradon contains an explosive chemical element so its often used in explosives.'),
(1331, 'I must report back to Rage by tomorrow... Can you speed up a bit, Ok? Thanks.'),
(1332, 'At last, I can relax a bit. Thank you so much. I do appreciate it.'),
(1333, 'Hmm ? if youve not made any contribution to the country, you cant be dispatched. First, charge CONT from [Knight Squad Secretary] Delaga in this castle.'),
(1334, 'Sorry, who are you? Im known as ¡vhe Middle Man, Berret I climb mountains and cross rivers, cross hill and dale, and go wherever I have to to make a little money.'),
(1335, 'Do you have any Apple of Moradon? Fishing Cork made with Apple of Moradon is the best. My goods arent affected by the changing seasons and they can sell for a long time. Whenever you get hold of Apple of Moradon, bring it to me. Ill give you the best price for it, no questions asked.'),
(1336, 'I sell the best products and make the best profit. Simple as that. I need Apples of Moradon to make the best Fishing Cork.'),
(1337, 'Ah~ thats right. This is Apples of Moradon. I will buy 10 Apples of Moradon you have for 70 thousand Noahs.  Would you like to do the trade?'),
(1338, 'Always be ready. You never know when war will break out.'),
(1339, 'It must be the Handmade Chocolate made by Valence.'),
(1340, 'Hmm... you got the right item. Heres what you want.'),
(1341, 'Welcome! What do you need?'),
(1342, 'Then please bring me all the materials for handmade chocolatier. I will make it right away.'),
(1343, 'I collected all the materials for Handmade Chocolate, Master.'),
(1344, 'I collected all the materials for Handmade Chocolate, Master.'),
(1345, '10 rosemary goes into the handmade chocolate.'),
(1346, 'Well, you finally brought that...'),
(1347, 'Have you found the location of the Secret Documents?'),
(1348, 'Have you found the location of the Secret Documents?'),
(1349, '        [ Kaishas Blessing]  Def 20 will increase. Would you like to accept Kaishas Blessing?'),
(1350, 'Do not touch the altar! Only Kings and Leaders can do that!'),
(1351, 'Use your full force before you come! I cant lend my power yet...'),
(1352, 'King of El Morad...  Prepare National treasury first for the offering.'),
(1353, 'Kaishas Blessing shall be with the El Morad Knights...'),
(1354, '        [ Veramuths Blessing]  Def 40 and HP250 will increase. Would you like to accept Veramuths Blessing?'),
(1355, 'Veramuths Blessing shall be with the El Morad Knights...'),
(1356, '        [ Aress Blessing ] In the National Treasury,  1 million Noah is used as an offering, and with  Def +60, HP +500,  Prison Gate is open every 40 seconds. Would you like to accept Aress Blessing?'),
(1357, 'Aress Blessing shall be with the El Morad Knights...'),
(1358, '        [ Aress Blessing ] In the National Treasury,   2 million Noah is used as an offering, and with  Def+80, HP +750,  Prison Gate is open every 40 seconds. Would you like to accept Diazs Blessing?'),
(1359, 'Diazs Blessing shall be with the El Morad Knights...'),
(1360, '        [ Logoss Blessing ] In the National Treasury,   3 million Noah is used as an offering, and with  Def+80, HP +1000,  Prison Gate is open every 40 seconds. Would you like to accept Logoss Blessing?'),
(1361, 'Logoss Blessing shall be with the El Morad Knights...'),
(1362, 'This Altar delivers the Kings prayer to God when the Nation is losing a war. But do not expect the response of God without making offerings to the National Treasury.'),
(1363, 'Human power has its limits. If youre losing, borrow some power from God. But Gods help always costs you something...'),
(1364, '        [ Kaishas Blessing]  Def 20 will increase. Would you like to accept Kaishas Blessing?'),
(1365, 'Do not touch the altar! Only Kings and Leaders can do that!'),
(1366, 'Use your full force before you come! I cant lend my power yet...'),
(1367, 'King of Karus...  Prepare National treasury for the offering first.'),
(1368, 'Kaishas Blessing shall be with the Karus Knights...'),
(1369, '        [ Veramuths Blessing]  Def 40 and HP250 will increase. Would you like to accept Veramuths Blessing?'),
(1370, 'Veramuths Blessing shall be with the Karus Knights...'),
(1371, '        [ Aress Blessing ] In the National Treasury,  1 million Noah is used as an offering, and with  Def +60, HP +500,  Prison Gate is open every 40 seconds. Would you like to accept Aress Blessing?'),
(1372, 'Aress Blessing shall be with the Karus Knights...'),
(1373, '        [ Aress Blessing ] In the National Treasury,   2 million Noah is used as an offering, and with  Def+80, HP +750,  Prison Gate is open every 40 seconds. Would you like to accept Diazs Blessing?'),
(1374, 'Diazs Blessing shall be with the Karus Knights...'),
(1375, '        [ Logoss Blessing ] In the National Treasury,   3 million Noah is used as an offering, and with  Def+80, HP +1000,  Prison Gate is open every 40 seconds. Would you like to accept Logoss Blessing?'),
(1376, 'Logoss Blessing shall be with the Karus Knights...'),
(1377, '[3 National notices were found.]'),
(1378, '[3 National notices were found.]'),
(1379, 'Only El Morad citizens can participate.'),
(1380, 'Only Karus citizens can participate.'),
(1381, 'I shall confess my love to her with love candies'),
(1382, 'I do want to confess my love to her with my own candies. Please help me to pratice for making my own candies.  Bring me ordinary candies, then I can make white day candies to my love. Help me ~~~'),
(1383, 'Hmm~~. Please bring me 15 ordinary candies,then I shall make my own lovely candy.'),
(1384, 'Hmm~~ I need 15 ordinary candies for this new candy'),
(1385, 'Wow~~ You brought me 15 candies. I will thank you if I get my love this time.'),
(1386, 'Great! You have all materials.'),
(1387, 'Great! You have all materials.'),
(1388, 'Hmm~~ I need 25 ordinary candies for a new white day candy.'),
(1389, 'Wow~~ You brought me 25 candies. I will thank you if I get my love this time.'),
(1390, 'Hmm~~ Bring me 25 ordinary candies, then I shall make my own lovely candy. Please~~~'),
(1391, 'Hmm~~ I need 100 ordinary candies for this new candy.'),
(1392, 'Good work!  You brought me 100 ordinary candies. I will thank you if I get my love.'),
(1393, 'Hmm~ Bring me 100 ordinary candies, then I shall make my own lovely candy. Please~~~'),
(1394, 'Ah~~ I wish I receive candies at this white day.'),
(1395, 'I need more information about Karus...'),
(1396, 'I need more information about El Morad...'),
(1397, 'Sorry, Im not in the mood to talk to you.'),
(1398, 'Master, what about hunting in Islante?'),
(1399, 'Welcome! Its been quite a while since I saw you here. Did you come here to loosen up? Haha~'),
(1400, 'Your current responsibilities seem too heavy to carry out another quest...'),
(1401, 'Troll Berserker! Its one of the targets which many hunters and questers want to hunt. Do you accept the challenge? The quest target is 250...'),
(1402, 'Whooa...! Its not just not to loosen up!'),
(1403, 'Isnt your quest just a tad bit too difficult for you? Haha!'),
(1404, 'What about your quest this time?... Was it bearable?'),
(1405, 'Master, what about hunting in Islante?'),
(1406, 'Welcome! Its been quite a while since I saw you here. Did you come here to loosen yourself up? Haha~'),
(1407, 'Your responsibilities seem too heavy to carry out another mission...'),
(1408, 'Troll Berserker! Its one of the targets which many hunters and questers want to hunt. Do you accept the challenge? The quest target is 250...'),
(1409, 'Whooa...! Its not just not to loosen up!'),
(1410, 'Isnt your quest just a tad bit too difficult for you? Haha!'),
(1411, 'What about your quest this time?... Was it bearable?'),
(1412, 'Master, what about another quest in Islante?'),
(1413, 'Are you looking for another quest? I like this attitude of ceaseless effort! Find the Troll Captain.'),
(1414, 'Given all the quests you have done so far, this quest may not be unreasonable...'),
(1415, 'Master, you completed another quest!'),
(1416, 'What about your quest?'),
(1417, 'Another quest is completed. Well-done!'),
(1418, 'Master, what about another quest in Islante?'),
(1419, 'Are you looking for another quest? I like this attitude of ceaseless effort! Find the Troll Captain.'),
(1420, 'Given all the quests you have done so far, this quest may not be unreasonable...'),
(1421, 'Master, you completed another quest!'),
(1422, 'What about your quest?'),
(1423, 'Another quest is completed. Well-done!'),
(1424, 'Master, Its said that something strange is going on in Islante. Please go to [Ascetic] Veda and ask.'),
(1425, 'Nights here in Islante are getting more and more fearful. Citizens here are suffering from a monster in their dreams every night...'),
(1426, 'Hmm... Before I hear the strange rumor, I think youd better finish your quest first.'),
(1427, 'Given the shape of the monster, I suspect its a Buro, a monster living in the northeastern part of the forest. Theyre said to be capable of real magic, but who knows? If theyre the real cause of the nightmares, they should be removed...'),
(1428, 'Islante is not suffering from nightmares any more, is it?'),
(1429, 'Wheres the end of the nightmares...'),
(1430, 'After you got rid of the Buro, no one is suffering from nightmares any more. Thank you!'),
(1431, 'Master, its said that something strange is going on in Islante. Please go to [Ascetic] Taved and ask.'),
(1432, 'Nights here in Islante are getting more and more fearful. Citizens here are suffering from a monster in their dreams every night...'),
(1433, 'Hmm... Before I hear the strange rumor, I think youd better finish your quest first.'),
(1434, 'Given the shape of the monster, I suspect its a Buro, a monster living in the northeastern part of the forest. Theyre said to be capable of real magic, but who knows? If theyre the real cause of the nightmares, they should be removed...'),
(1435, 'Islante is not suffering from nightmares any more, is it?'),
(1436, 'Wheres the end of the nightmares...'),
(1437, 'After you got rid of Buro, no one is suffering from nightmares any more. Thank you!'),
(1438, 'Master, its said that theres a monster whos gone berserk in Islante. Please ask [Ascetic] Veda for details.'),
(1439, 'Hm~they were no more than rocks. The ancient Priest gave life to them, and employed them as servants. Theyre Stone Golems. After the war against Pathos, the Priests lost control of them, and they staged an attack against anything living.'),
(1440, 'Well, the carelessness of the ancient Priests may have caused the current problem, but everybody makes mistakes. But the power of Dark Stones is the strongest, and theyre ruthless. The outcome of one mistake seems too severe...'),
(1441, 'Dark Stones which lost control, rest in peace... ha~'),
(1442, 'Dark Stone is one of the strongest Stone Golems.'),
(1443, 'Youre still very good. If we have a way to regain control over them, we wont need to be engaged in tough fights like this...'),
(1444, 'Master, its said that theres a monster whos gone berserk in Islante. Please ask [Ascetic] Taved for details.'),
(1445, 'Hm~they were no more than rocks. The ancient Priest gave life to them, and employed them as servants. Theyre Stone Golems. After the war against Pathos, the Priests lost control of them, and they staged an attack agasint anything living.'),
(1446, 'Well, the carelessness of the ancient Priests may have caused the current problem, but everybody makes mistakes. But the power of Dark Stones is the strongest, and theyre ruthless. The outcome of one mistake seems too severe...'),
(1447, 'Dark Stones which lost control, rest in peace... ha~'),
(1448, 'Dark Stone is one of the strongest Stone Golems.'),
(1449, 'Youre still very good. If we have a way to regain control over them, we wont need to be engaged in tough fights like this...'),
(1450, 'Master, its said that therere creatures that were created from the changes of Spirit of Flame... Please meet [Ascetic] Veda and check it out.'),
(1451, 'Fallen Spirit of Flame...  They seem like huge burning men with manes and whips of flames with many leather strings... If you see how horrible they look once, youll never want to see them again.'),
(1452, 'Its called Balog. Theyre already notorious in this region. You may be the one who can get rid of them. Dont you think so?'),
(1453, 'Even Balog dropped their knees before you, Master~'),
(1454, 'Theyre already notorious in this region. We need your help.'),
(1455, 'You did it again... well~now that you caught Balog, where do you want to go?? Haha~'),
(1456, 'Master, its said that there are creatures that were created from the changes of Spirit of Flame... Please meet [Ascetic] Veda and check it out.'),
(1457, 'Fallen Spirit of Flame...  They seem like huge burning men with manes and whips of flames with many leather strings... If you see how horrible they look once, youll never want to see them again.'),
(1458, 'Its called Balog. Theyre already notorious in this region. You may be the one who can get rid of them. Dont you think so?'),
(1459, 'Even Balog dropped their knees before you, Master~'),
(1460, 'Theyre already notorious in this region. We need your help.'),
(1461, 'You did it again... well~now that you caught Balog, where do you want to go?? Haha~'),
(1462, 'Master, have you ever heard about ambilaterality of the Guard Tower in Ronark Land? Ask [Magician] Casielo for details.'),
(1463, 'The Guard Tower in the base here may do good... or harm on us. It has ambilaterality.'),
(1464, 'You already got rid of the guardian Ibexs today. May the power of Guard Tower be with you...'),
(1465, 'Literally, if we take up the Guard Tower, well be blessed, but at the same time we will make the Guard Tower angry. So the Protector of Guard Tower will appear.'),
(1466, 'Ibexs, guardian of Guard Tower (Ibexs). To concentrate on combat with Karus in the base, wed better get rid of the guardian Ibexs first. If the Guard Tower falls into the hands of El Morad, the guardians that we should attack will disappear. Remember that.'),
(1467, 'Protector of Guard Tower - The guardians appear only when the central Guard Tower is occupied. - If your enemy occupies the Guard Tower, the guardians will disappear. - You have only 20 minutes. - If you cant get reward within 20 minutes, you fail.'),
(1468, 'Master, I have accomplished the quest I got from Casielo!'),
(1469, 'What about the quest I assigned to you?'),
(1470, '<selfname>,...  You finished the quest I assigned you pefectly! Youll be blessed by Karus...'),
(1471, 'The fight with the Protectors of Guard Tower starts now... <selfname>, come and visit me again tomorrow, and I will assign you a new mission.'),
(1472, 'Master, have you ever heard about ambilaterality of the Guard Tower in Ronark Land? Ask [Magician] Aragona for details.'),
(1473, 'The Guard Tower in the base here may do good... or harm on us. It has ambilaterality.'),
(1474, 'You already got rid of the guardian Crisis today. May the power of Guard Tower be with you...'),
(1475, 'Literally, if we take up the Guard Tower, well be blessed, but at the same time we will make the Guard Tower angry. So the Protector of Guard Tower will appear.'),
(1476, 'Crisis, guardian of Guard Tower (Crisis). To concentrate on the combat with Karus in the base, wed better get rid of the guardian Crisis first. If the Guard Tower falls into the hands of Karus, the guardians that we should attack will disappear. Remember that.'),
(1477, 'Master, I have accomplished the quest I got from Aragona!'),
(1478, 'What about the quest I assigned to you?'),
(1479, '<selfname>,...  You did a perfect quest for what Id assigned to you. Youll be blessed by El Morad...'),
(1480, 'The fight with the Protectors of Guard Tower starts now... <selfname>, come and visit me again tomorrow, and I will assign you a new mission.'),
(1481, '<selfname>,...  Youd better train more and come back again, as you seem incapable to know the truth about the Guardian Tower...'),
(1482, '<selfname>,...  Youd better train more and come back again, as you seem incapable to know the truth about the Guardian Tower...'),
(1483, 'Spies are mainly active at the back of Karus Military HQ.'),
(1484, 'Spies are mainly active at the back of El Mora Military HQ.'),
(1485, 'The spies you rescued are now recuperating. You will be assigned to another mission soon. But anyway, well-done.'),
(1486, 'Hmm... There are spies I planted to see El Morads movement. But I have lost my contact with them for a few days. I have no idea if theyre alive or dead... or if they were caught by El Morad...'),
(1487, 'Really?? Well, then, please. The spies that Id previously assigned used to quest at the back of El Morad Military HQ. Could you search the area? Please take the spies, and collect the Intelligence Report they recorded.'),
(1488, '       Find the spy! - You can rescue 4 spies. (Reward offered differs depending on the number of Intelligence Reports you get from the spies you rescue) - If youre killed by an enemy Nations player, your count of rescued spies and Intelligence Reports is reset. - During the quest, Summon skills are disabled. [ /town ] can be used, but your count of rescued spies and Intelligence Reports will be reset.'),
(1489, 'Master, I recovered some spies and Intelligence Reports. Are you going back? Or... are you continuing the rescue quest???'),
(1490, 'Hmm... Its taking too long to complete the mission... Its already past midnight.'),
(1491, 'Dont you have any news related to spies??? Hmm... I expect good news.'),
(1492, 'Oh~Did you come back? You found 1 out of 4. Well done, the other 3 will be searched for by another group...'),
(1493, 'Oh~Did you come back? You found 2 out of 4. Well done, the other 2 will be searched for by another group...'),
(1494, 'Wow~You found 3 out of 4... Im impressed by your searching skills. Thank you very much.'),
(1495, 'Gosh... you rescued all 4? And 4 intelligence reports?? Youre excellent, well-done!!'),
(1496, 'The spies you rescued are now recovering. You will be assigned to another mission soon. But first and foremost, well-done.'),
(1497, 'Hmm... There are spies I put into place to see Karuss movement. But I have lost contact with them for a few days. I have no idea if theyre dead or alive... or if they were caught by Karus...')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(1498, 'Really?? Well, then, please. The spies that Id previously assigned used to quest at the back of Karus Military HQ. Could you search the area? Please find the spies, and recover the Intelligence Report they recorded.'),
(1499, 'Master, I found the spies and the Intelligence Report. Are you going back? Or... are you continuing the rescue mission???'),
(1500, 'Hmm... Its taking too long to complete the mission... Its already past midnight.'),
(1501, 'Dont you have any news on the spies??? Hmm... I expect good news.'),
(1502, 'Oh~Did you come back? You found 1 out of 4. Well done, the other 3 will be searched for by another group...'),
(1503, 'Oh~Did you come back? You found 2 out of 4. Well done, the other 2 will be searched for by another group...'),
(1504, 'Wow~You found 3 out of 4... Im impressed by your skills. Thank you very much.'),
(1505, 'Gosh... you rescued all 4? And 4 intelligence reports?? Youre excellent, well-done!!'),
(1506, 'Oh my... I didnt expect to meet the Karus here... What are you doing here???'),
(1507, 'Oh my... Wait a second!! Who are you?! Why are you with our spies??'),
(1508, 'Oh my... Wait a second!! Who are you?! Why are you with our spies??'),
(1509, 'Who are you!! Get out of my way and get out of my sight!! Youre interfering with my mission!!'),
(1510, 'Hmm~ Im doing my mission assigned by Caesar. Im a spy who is watching the El Morad and researching geographical traits!'),
(1511, 'Really?? Hmm..Actually, I couldnt even think about going back, because the security was tightened. I need to deliver the Intelligence Report to Caesar, but the deadline has already passed... (Caesar wont like this... ) Could you do me a favor? Could you deliver this to him?'),
(1512, 'Ugh... I cant help it if its Caesars order. Then I will trust you and follow. Protect me, okay? I wont let you get away if you try to run from me!! Well~lets go!!'),
(1513, 'A strange fellow...'),
(1514, 'Oh my... I didnt expect to meet the El Morad... What are you doing here???'),
(1515, 'Oh my... Wait a second!! Who are you?! Why are you with our spies??'),
(1516, 'Oh my... Wait a second!! Who are you?! Why are you with our spies??'),
(1517, 'Who are you!! Get out of my sight!! Youre interfering with my mission!!'),
(1518, 'Hmm~ Im doing my mission, as assigned by Julius. Im a spy, watching the Karus and researching geographical features! Hmm~'),
(1519, 'Really?? Hmm..Actually, I couldnt even think about going back, because Karus security has been tightened. Ive need to deliver the Intelligence Report to Julius, but the deadline has already passed. (Julius wont like this... ) Could you do me a favor? Could you deliver this to him?'),
(1520, 'Ugh... I cant help it if its Juliuss order. Then I will trust you and follow. Protect me, okay? I wont let you get away if you try to run from me!! Well~lets go!!'),
(1521, 'A strange fellow...'),
(1522, 'Well, I was looking for migrants, too! To win the next Lunar War, theyre recruiting many soldiers. Are you ready for migration?'),
(1523, 'Well... to transfer your Nation, you should bring the  Nation Transfer Certificate needed for a Nation transfer. You can buy the Nation Transfer Certificate at the PowerUP Store.'),
(1524, 'Change your character to the nation you want, and click OK to transfer your Nation. Dont be surprised if the game automatically disconnects.'),
(1525, 'You can enter Krowazs Land only if you have Country CONT. Please go back to the castle to charge CONT, and come back.'),
(1526, 'Oh, applying for the entire clan to transfer, eh. The camp they are transferring to will have their strength boosted significantly! Are you ready to move?'),
(1527, 'You are trying to move to El Morad. We provide the item which enables you to preserve the clan at the same grade considering all the deeds you have done, so I will first check the grade of your clan and then give you the item.   Are you ready?'),
(1528, 'You are trying to move to Karus. We provide the item which enables you to preserve the clan at the same grade considering all the deeds you have done, so I will first check the grade of your clan and then give you the item.   Are you ready?'),
(1529, 'The grade of your clan is Formal Knight Squad. Would you like to receive the [Certificate of Formal Knight] and the item?'),
(1530, 'The grade of your clan is Royal Knight Squad. Would you like to receive the [Certificate of Royal Knight] and the item?'),
(1531, 'The grade of your clan is Training Knight Squad. Would you like to receive the [Certificate of Training Knight] and the item?'),
(1532, 'Well... To transfer your nation, you should bring the  Nation Transfer Certificate. You can buy the  Exile Application Form  at the Power-up store.'),
(1533, 'This definitely is an  Exile Application Form.'),
(1534, 'Then I will change the  Exile Application Form to the items you need for migration and give them to you, are you ready?'),
(1535, 'Your clan havent made any great contribution yet, Im sorry but I can not give you the certificate, but dont feel too sad as your CONT recovers when you move.'),
(1536, 'You are the leader of the transferred clan, and you are here to reestablish the prestige of your clan as it was in the previous nation, right?!'),
(1537, 'Hm? It is only available for the clan leaders.  Im sorry but you are not qualified.'),
(1538, 'Firstly, I will check the current grade of the present clan as per procedure, and wait for a moment as the promotion is determined by the confirmed grade.'),
(1539, 'Oh! You are [Formal Knight Squad] right now! Would you like to be promoted to the next grade, [Royal Knight Squad]!?'),
(1540, 'You are already [Royal Knight Squd], arent you!? Haha, there is no more place for you to go up!'),
(1541, 'Um, you are [Training Knight Squad], you can promote to the next grade [Formal Knight Squad]. Would you like to be promoted?'),
(1542, 'Your clan has never been promoted. Would you like to be promoted to [Training Knight Squad]?'),
(1543, 'You have been promoted! I expect your clan to contribute even more from now on!'),
(1544, 'To promote the clan, you have to bring the certificate of the relevant degree. You either dont have the certificate or you got it but havent transferred yet, so return when you have the certificate or complete the transfer!'),
(1545, 'You have Nation Transfer Certificate, you can make national transfer right now.  And   for the clan leaders who are transferring right now, we are providing the item which enables them to recover the clan, so if you are a clan leader, dont forget to take it.'),
(1546, 'Before using the Nation Transfer item, remember that you can get the Clan Recovery Item here if you are the leader of your clan, you can use the item after you transfer.'),
(1547, 'You already got it! Dont be too greedy!'),
(1548, 'You are the leader of a clan! Right now we provide   the item which recovers the grade of clan after the transfer, and are you sure that you have it?'),
(1549, '       Nation Transfer System|- If you win more than   8 victories  in the Lunar War Status on the website, you can transfer to the other country.  |- When transferring, all the characters within the account must withdraw from the clan |- When transferring, when you submit  the  [Exile Application Form] you can exchange it with a  [National Transfer Certificate]. Accumulation starts from this point of time.'),
(1550, 'To become [Royal Knight Squad], you have to be [Formal Knight Squad]  1st Class. So come back when you are [Formal Knight Squad]  1st Class.'),
(1551, 'Only clans with more than  25000 Knight Squad Saving Points, so return after youve accumulated more CONT.'),
(1552, 'Master! You have successfully seized the classified document! Hurry back to [Councilor] Herga!'),
(1553, 'Hm? You have done todays mission already.  Arent you absent-minded... Come back tomorrow!'),
(1554, 'You came on time, good. El Morad is showing some suspicious activities, and I want to know what is happening there but I have no one to spare as all the spies are doing their mission in Ronark Land. So would you sneak into the El Morad castle and return with the classified document?'),
(1555, 'Are you taking this mission!? Great, then I will give you the [Enemy State Moving Scroll] and the [Scroll] which you can copy the information on. You just need to copy the information in the enemys classified document box on this [Scroll].'),
(1556, '        Disturbing the Enemy|- You have to make the [Scroll] into [Copy of Information Paper] from the classified document box in the El Morad Castle.  |- You have to sneak into the castle when the enemys defense is loose, and when you get killed by users of the enemy nation then your quest becomes initialized.  |-During the quest, the summon related skills are not available and when you acquire [Copy of Information Paper] you can escape to the entrance of Lunar Gate with [/Village] command. |-[Infiltration Scroll] can be place in the skill shortcut window for use.'),
(1557, 'To get the item needed for the mission, you have to have two empty spaces in your inventory. Return after you have checked it.'),
(1558, 'You still havent left yet? Infiltrate the El Morad castle and make [Scroll] into [Copy of Information Paper] and then come back.'),
(1559, 'Oh, this is definitely a [Copy of Information Paper], let me see... Right! So they were planning something like this! You will have to take the next mission, too!'),
(1560, 'You lost the [Scroll]? What a clumsy fellow you are. I will give you another one, so complete the mission without making any mistake this time.'),
(1561, 'I gave you the [Enemy Nation Moving Scroll] and [Scroll], so dont lose them and return safely!'),
(1562, 'Master! You have successfully seized the classified document! Hurry back to [Councilor] Nez!'),
(1563, 'Hm? You have done todays mission already.  You must have forgotten that. Please come back tomorrow.'),
(1564, 'Karus is showing some suspicious activities. I want to know what is happening there but I have no one to spare as all the spies are doing their mission in Ronark Land.  So could you sneak into the Luferson Castle instead and return with the classified document?'),
(1565, 'Are you taking the mission!? Great, then I will give you this [Enemy Nation Moving Scroll] and the [Scroll] on which you can copy the information. You can copy the information in the enemys classified document box on this [Scroll].'),
(1566, '        Disturbing the Enemy|- You have to make the [Scroll] into [Copy of Information Paper] from the classified document box in the El Morad Castle.  |- You have to sneak into the castle when the enemys defense is loose, and when you get killed by users of the enemy nation then your quest becomes initialized.  |-During the quest, the summon related skills are not available and when you acquire [Copy of Information Paper] you can escape to the entrance of Lunar Gate with [/Village] command. |-[Infiltration Scroll] can be place in the skill shortcut window for use.'),
(1567, 'To get the item needed for the mission, you have to have two empty spaces in your inventory. Please check it and come back.'),
(1568, 'Is there any misunderstanding? Hurry and infiltrate the Luferson Castle, and make the [Scroll] into [Copy of Information Paper] and then come back.'),
(1569, 'Oh, this is definitely a [Copy of Information Paper]! Um,um, I see! So they were planning something like this! Could you take the next mission, too?'),
(1570, 'You lost the [Scroll]? I will give you another scroll, so dont lose it again.'),
(1571, 'I definitely gave you the[Enemy Moving Scroll] and [Scroll]. Please dont lose it. Then, good luck.'),
(1572, 'According to the [Copy of Information Paper] you brought, the enemy is planning to confuse our force in each of the war bases. So we decided to take the initiative this time and disrupt their information instead. Now, take this [Fake Information Paper] and go to the person in charge of each base.  We already got in touch with them, so you have to go to each base and help the person in charge to disrupt the enemys plan.'),
(1573, 'Accordnig to the [Copy of Information Paper] you brought, the enemy is planning to confuse our force at each of the war bases. So those above as decided to take the initiative this time and disrupt their information instead.  Take the [Fake Information Paper] to the person in charge of each base. We already got in touch with them, so you have to go to each base and help the person in charge to disrupt the enemys plan.'),
(1574, '       Disrupting the Enemy Base|- You have to receive Disrupt the Enemy Information mission from the people in charge of  [Arrdream], [Ronark Base], and [Ronark Land].|- People in charge of each mission area are as follows. |- [Arrdream] - [Search Captain] Zamed |- [Ronark Base] - [Base Spearhead] Cruzed |- [Ronark Land] - [Analyst] Caesar'),
(1575, '       Disrupting the Enemy Base|- You have to receive Disrupt the Enemy Information mission from the people in charge of  [Arrdream], [Ronark Base], and [Ronark Land].|- People in charge of each mission area are as follows. |- [Arrdream] - [Search Captain] Laek |- [Ronark Base] - [Base Spearhead] Krable |- [Ronark Land] - [Analyst] Julius'),
(1576, 'Did [Councilor] Herga send you? Since the situation is urgent, you should hurry.  Take the [Fake Information Paper], infiltrate the enemys base and switch it with the [Arrdream Information Paper].  Will you carry out the mission?'),
(1577, 'You can do the mission after you complete the mission of [Councilor] Herga and bring the [Fake Information Paper].'),
(1578, 'This is the mission objective.  You must switch the [Fake Information Paper] with [Arrdream Information paper]. Have you verified it?'),
(1579, 'This is definitely the [Arrdream Information Paper], and the fact that it is here means that you have succeeded in switching it! This is the reward for the success of the mission.'),
(1580, 'Master! It was a clean switch! Lets hurry back to the base!'),
