(1649, 'We are giving the mission of rescuing the spies who are currently operating in Arrdream region... We are giving different rewards according to ones ability, so please take the mission that is appropriate for your level.'),
(1650, 'We are giving the mission of rescuing the spies who are currently operating in Arrdream region... We are giving different rewards according to ones ability, so please take the mission that is appropriate for your level.'),
(1651, 'Hmph~ I am on a mission given by Tikta. I am a spy who is watching the activities of El Morad and investigating geographical features here! Heh~'),
(1652, 'Re..Really?? Hm~ To tell you the truth I coudnt even think about going back lately because the El Morad have tightened their security. I have to deliver the Intelligence Report to Caesar, but I couldnt meet the deadline. So could you do me a favor? Could you deliver this Intelligence Report on behalf of me? I dont think I can get out of here..Hm~'),
(1653, 'Ugh..I cant help it if its Tiktas order. Then I will trust you and follow you, so you have to protect me, okay? I wont let you get away if you run without me!! Well~ lets go!!'),
(1654, 'Hmph~ I am on a mission given by Aimo. I am a spy who is watching the activities of Karus and investigating geographical features here! Heh~'),
(1655, 'Re... Really??  To tell you the truth I coudnt even think about going back lately because the Karus have tightened their security I have to deliver the Intelligence Report to Julius, but I couldnt meet the deadline. So could you do me a favor? Could you deliver this Intelligence Report on behalf of me? I dont think I can get out of here..Hm~'),
(1656, 'Ugh..I cant help it if its Aimos order. Then I will trust you and follow you, so you have to protect me, okay? I wont let you get away if you run without me!! Well~ lets go!!'),
(1657, 'To become [Training Knight Squad], you have to be more than [Normal Clan]   3rd Class, so come back when you are  [Normal Clan]  3rd Class.'),
(1658, 'To become [Formal Knight Squad], you have to be [Training Knight Squad]  1st Class, come back when you are [Training Knight Squad]  1st Class.'),
(1659, 'Hello. Isnt the weather lovely today?'),
(1660, 'Hi, they call me jewel. Why am I here you ask? Its a bit of a long story ... but I will tell you, <selfname>. I have been taught to craft magical jewelry as a part of my familys business, but greed has corrupted my family and I ran away. I travelled around the world before ending up here in Moradon. Now I use my jeweling skills here to combine old accessories to help people. My skills have yet to be perfected, but sometimes I get lucky!'),
(1661, 'Combining three old accessories into a new accessory is the greatest skill a jewel crafter can possess. These old accessories now can have a new life and make their owner feel reborn in the process! Oh how wonderful! Bring me 3 identical Old Accesory, Nest Scrap (5), Scrap of Steel (50) and Soft Stone (1), and I will make you a new accessory. Be aware that my skills are not perfected yet, so I cannot guarantee results. I have a higher probability to fail than succeed. Haha!'),
(1662, 'Are you ready to try crafting?'),
(1663, 'Hmm.. This is pretty rare stuff ... Well, <selfname> you know not everything in life is free! But I will let you have it for only 1 million Noah. How can I make it cheaper?'),
(1664, 'Lets see ... 998, 999, 1 million ... Perfect. No need for change I guess ... Here you go. Gread deal, huh? Do not tell anyone else! OK?'),
(1665, '<selfname>? Are you short on Noah?'),
(1666, 'Your bag is full, Please create more space.'),
(1667, 'You still have the [Fake infosheet], go perform the confusion tactic please'),
(1668, 'You chose 5000 premium HP potion. Would you like to receive it?'),
