(1671, 'Sorry, you dont have a voucher for 5000 premium MP potion'),
(3000, 'Kill the Undyings around here and bring me their Apples of Moradon.'),
(3001, 'The Nameless Warrior will perform a ritual to praise the souls of the dead warriors. Go and meet him, check him out. ^^'),
(3002, 'The Nameless Warrior will perform a ritual to praise the souls of the dead warriors. Go and meet him, check him out. ^^'),
(3003, 'There is nothing I can do now... Blast.'),
(3004, 'Not long ago, our Villages Knight Squad suffered great losses from a Monster attack. Since then, our morale has been badly shaken.'),
(3005, 'This is an Apple of Moradon, isnt it? Uh ? These guys look scary so they make my blood run cold, arent they?'),
(3006, 'This is an Apple of Moradon, isnt it? Uh ? These guys look scary so they make my blood run cold, arent they?'),
(3007, 'Not long ago, our Villages Knight Squad suffered great losses from a Monster attack. Since then, our morale has been badly shaken.'),
(3008, 'Master- Theyre preparing the War Supplies over in the Folk Village. So Osmond is busy eh? You should go and pay him a visit.'),
(3009, 'Do you know about an object called the horn of comprehension?'),
(3010, 'The horn of comprehension is the most precious object to us priests.'),
(3011, 'A prospective priest who went out training a while ago had lost it to the Fallen Angels on the lowest level of the Abyss Dungeon.  Right now, that prospective priest is going through a period of repentance for his mistake, so we need someone to go there and bring it back.'),
(3012, 'If it goes into someones hand, worse yet into the hand of the enemy, then it could be a big problem for us.  Could you bring the back Horn of Comprehension from the lowest level of the Abyss Dungeon?'),
(3013, 'Master, do you know the skill called Scream? You should visit [Warrior Master] Skaki and ask him about it.'),
(3014, 'Master, do you know the skill called Scream? You should visit [Warrior Master] Skaki and ask him about it.'),
(3015, 'Master, I hear that there are enemies who threatening Ronark Land.  Lets look for [Outpost Captain] Della.'),
(3016, 'Master, I hear that there are enemies who threatening Ronark Land.  Lets look for [Outpost Captain] Elrod.'),
(3017, 'I`ll be waiting. May the gods bless you...'),
(3018, 'May the gods bless you...'),
(3019, 'horn of comprehension can be retrieved from Fallen Angels in the nether Abyss Dungeon.'),
(3020, 'Master, you retrieved the horn of comprehension. Hurry back to [Priest] Minerva.'),
(3021, 'Master, you retrieved the horn of comprehension. Hurry back to [Priest] Minerva.'),
(3022, 'Thank you. This completes the retrieval of all the horn of comprehension in the mainland. May the gods shower you with blessings.'),
(3023, 'Master, they`re none other than Fallen Angels. They`re powerful monsters so be careful.'),
(3024, 'Master, they`re none other than Fallen Angels. They`re powerful monsters so be careful.'),
(3025, 'Master, you retrieved the horn of comprehension. Hurry back to [Priest] Minerva.')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(3026, 'Master, Minvera is looking for something. Go see what it is.'),
(3027, 'Master, Minvera is looking for something. Go see what it is.'),
(3028, 'Master, have you heard of an attack technique called Judgment?'),
(3029, 'There`s talk about physical attack being as important an attack technique to a priest as is magic.'),
(3030, 'You know who to see if you want to know more about Judgment, don`t you?'),
(3031, 'The border defending battle is held every day at 10 AM and 1, 3, 5 and 10 PM and 1 AM. And it is held additionally at 8 PM on Tuesday, Friday, Saturday and Sunday when there is no war. When the relevant time comes, the announcement for recruitment will be aired automatically so that application for participation can be made'),
(3032, 'Master, have you heard of an attack technique called Judgment?'),
(3033, 'There`s talk about physical attack being as important an attack technique to a priest as is magic.'),
(3034, 'You know who to see if you want to know more about Judgment, don`t you?'),
(3035, 'Come on, Master. [Priest] Minerva`s an expert in this field.'),
(3036, 'Judgment, which priests can learn with the 2nd job change is a technique which employs powerful attack power.'),
(3037, 'The border defending battle is held every day at 10 AM and 1, 3, 5 and 10 PM and 1 AM. And it is held additionally at 8 PM on Tuesday, Friday, Saturday and Sunday when there is no war. When the relevant time comes, the announcement for recruitment will be aired automatically so that application for participation can be made'),
(3038, 'You will first have to prove to me that you are capable enough to handle Judgment Scroll.  Win seven victories at National Defence Combat at the upper reaches of the kalluga valley and then bring me the Symbol of Vctory to me, and I will give you this scroll.'),
(3039, 'The gods will bless your journey with light.'),
(3040, 'May the gods bless you...'),
(3041, 'Sorry, Im not in the mood to talk to you.'),
(3042, 'Master, all the ingredients have been collected. Go to complete the Judgment Scroll.'),
(3043, 'You are ready. Please wait.'),
(3044, 'This is the Judgment Scroll. As it is a dangerous technique, please use it to protect justice under the name of the gods.'),
(3045, 'Master, all the ingredients have been collected. Go to complete the Judgment Scroll.'),
(3046, 'You are ready. Please wait.'),
(3047, 'This is the Judgment Scroll. As it is a dangerous technique, please use it to protect justice under the name of the gods.'),
(3048, 'Whoa... You are beginning to emit the aura of the gods. That indicates that you have reached the final stage of priest training.'),
(3049, 'The priest who completes the final training earns the right to receive the pure ability that the god grants directly to the priests.  But. To be endowed with the ability, there are two things that you need.  They are the Nostrum of Wisdom and Stamp of Intelligence.  I will make the Nostrum of Wisdom for you if you bring me 5 Holy Water of Temple, 5 Venomous Tails of Lesath, and 2 Magic Powders. Do you want to do it?'),
(3050, 'You will be the most celebrated priest in the continent if the gods personally award you with infinite ability.'),
(3051, 'Do you believe that you still need more training? You are modest. May the gods be with you...'),
(3052, 'Making a Nostrum of Wisdom requires ,5 Holy Water of Life, 5 Venomous Tails of Lesath, and 2 Magic Powders.'),
(3053, 'Master, all the materials needed for making the Nostrum of Wisdom have been collected. My heart`s going ballistic to think that you will be conferred infinite ability by the gods.'),
(3054, 'Master, all the materials needed for making the Nostrum of Wisdom have been collected. My heart`s going ballistic to think that you will be conferred infinite ability by the gods.'),
(3055, 'You have accumulated all the ingredients required for making Nostrum of Wisdom. Please wait. Here`s the Nostrum of Wisdom. I hope you will be bestowed with the ability of the gods and realize your dream.'),
(3056, 'Priest, you who will undertake the final stage of training, you will need two objects to practice the ability which the gods will confer on you should you complete the final stage of your training.'),
(3057, 'They are the Nostrum of Wisdom and Stamp of Intelligence.  The gods ability will not be endowed on you even if one of them is insufficient.  Stamp of Intelligence can be made with 1 Lycaons Pendant, 1 Robos Pendant, and 1 Silver Bar.  Can you find them?'),
(3058, 'The gods will be moved by your devotion.'),
(3059, 'But the gods will not be disappointed in you.'),
(3060, 'To make a Stamp of Intelligence, you need 1 Lycaons Pendant,  1 Robos Pendant, and one Silver Bar. What you brought isnt enough.'),
(3061, 'Master, you have collected 1 Lycaons Pendant, 1 Robos Pendant, and one Silver Bar. Now you can make the stamp of intelligence with these.'),
(3062, 'Master, you have collected 1 Lycaons Pendant, 1 Robos Pendant, and one Silver Bar. Now you can make the stamp of intelligence with these.'),
(3063, 'The ingredients for making the Stamp of Intelligence have all been collected. This is the Stamp of Intelligence. It is an essential item for the final stage of your training.'),
(3064, 'It is now time for me to teach you the most powerful secret weapon. The name of that secret weapon is Scream...'),
(3065, ' It has such a name because it makes an enormous sound like the scream of Lucifer when you use the skill.  Show me whether you are qualified to deal with the secret scroll of this skill.  Win seven victories at the National Defence Combat at the upper reaches of the Kalluga Valley and bring me the Symbol of Victory. Then I will acknowledge your ability and give you this secret scroll.'),
(3066, 'Come back after you have collected all the items I enumerated.'),
(3067, 'Don`t you want to learn the Scream? I guess you`re already sufficiently strong as is.'),
(3068, 'The border defending battle is held every day at 10 AM and 1, 3, 5 and 10 PM and 1 AM. And it is held additionally at 8 PM on Tuesday, Friday, Saturday and Sunday when there is no war. When the relevant time comes, the announcement for recruitment will be aired automatically so that application for participation can be made'),
(3069, 'Master, all the objects needed for obtaining the Scream Secret Scroll have been collected. Go see [Warrior Master] Skaki.'),
(3070, 'Master, all the objects needed for obtaining the Scream Secret Scroll have been collected. Go see [Warrior Master] Skaki.'),
(3071, 'Um~ Youve won seven victories as I told you.  Great job, here~ I will hand this scream secret scroll to you.  Make good use of this.'),
(3072, 'You are now fast approaching the ultimate warrior level.'),
(3073, ' We warriors have been thinking for a long time on the limit of our abilities. And as a result, we discovered the special skill filled with the last of our spirit and strength, and we recognized it as our final limit. And it is time for you to be handed down with that last secret skill. Since it is the last secret skill, the process of making it is also very complex. First, you need a Stamp of Strength and Nostrum of Constitution.  But these two items cannot be obtained from somewhere straightaway.  Such'),
(3074, 'I truly want to witness you practicing the culmination of all skills.'),
(3075, 'It shouldn`t matter too much. You are sufficiently strong as it is.'),
(3076, 'To make a Stamp of Strength, you need  1 Fangs of Bakirra, 1 Venomous Tails of Shaula, 2 Magic Powders and you cant afford to miss any one of them.'),
(3077, 'Master, all the ingredients needed to make the Stamp of Power have been amassed. The ultimate secret weapon of the warrior... I can`t wait to witness it.'),
(3078, 'Master, all the ingredients needed to make the Stamp of Power have been amassed. The ultimate secret weapon of the warrior... I can`t wait to witness it.'),
(3079, 'Wow... every single ingredient is here. The Stamp of Power will soon be completed. Please wait. This is the Stamp of Power. It is an essential object for completing the ultimate skill of the warrior.'),
(3080, 'The skill practiced in the ultimate warrior level not only requires ultimate power but also ultimate constitution.'),
(3081, ' For that reason, you need an item called the Nostrum of Constitution along with the Stamp of Strength.  To make Nostrum of Constitution, you need 1 Lupus Pendant, 1 Robos Pendant, and one Silver Bar. If you have the Stamp of Strength, then you can complete the final skill of warriors with the Nostrum of Constitution.  What do you say, are you going to bring those?'),
(3082, 'I truly want to teach you the final skill as well.'),
(3083, 'I was hoping you`d be the one mastering the final skill...'),
(3084, 'To make the Nostrum of Constitution, you must have all of 1 Lupus Pendant, 1 Robos Pendant, and 1 Silver Bar.'),
(3085, 'Master, all the Nostrum of Constitution ingredients have been gathered. I want to witness the final secret weapon of the warrior.'),
(3086, 'Master, all the Nostrum of Constitution ingredients have been gathered. I want to witness the final secret weapon of the warrior.'),
(3087, 'You`ve gathered all the Nostrum of Constitution ingredients. I will make it for you right away. This is Nostrum of Constitution. It isn`t long till you complete the final skill now.'),
(3088, 'For me to make the Scroll of Magic Shield, you must prove your ability at the National Combat.  And that can also prove whether you are qualified to use the Magic Shield.'),
(3089, 'Win seven victories at the National Defence Combat at upper reaches of the kalluga valley and bring me the Symbol of Victory, and I will  make the Scroll of Magic Shield for you. Do you want to do it?'),
(3090, 'I`ll be waiting.'),
(3091, 'That might be a wise choice.'),
(3092, 'I hear that the Death Magician has appeared in Ronark Land.. Do you think it is true? Lets go and ask [Outpost Captain] Elrod about it.'),
(3093, 'Master, you have won seven victories.  Lets return to [Secret Agent] Clarence.'),
(3094, 'Master, you have finally won all seven victories.  Lets return to [Secret Agent] Clarence.'),
(3095, 'You have moved me with your drive. Here is the Magic Shield Scroll. Please don`t lose that rogue`s passion of yours.'),
(3096, 'What do you think is the most important thing for rogues?'),
(3097, ' The most important things for us Rogues would obviously be speed and agility.  And when these elements reach the maximum, that rogue can be called to have reached the highest status.  The highest status... Of course it is easy to speak about it, but it requires great persistence and effort to reach that status, of course.  To respond to your such great effort, I will hand you down  the last secret art of us Rogues.  To complete the last secret art of Rogues, as I said before, the Rogue'),
(3098, 'Come back if you have all the ingredients.'),
(3099, 'That might be a wise choice.'),
(3100, 'To make the Nostrum of Speed, you need 5 Bracelets of Orc Bandit, 5 Venomous Tails of Shaula, and 2 Magic Powders, and you dont have all of them yet.'),
(3101, 'Master, the Nostrum of Speed ingredients have all been acquired. You are now one step closer to being the greatest rogue.'),
(3102, 'Master, the Nostrum of Speed ingredients have all been acquired. You are now one step closer to being the greatest rogue.'),
(3103, 'You have collected all the ingredients needed to make the Nostrum of Speed. This is the Nostrum of Speed. It is one of the items you will need to unleash your latent ultimate ability.'),
(3104, 'The two most important rogue traits speed and dexterity... The Stamp of Dexterity is the symbol of the most accomplished dexterity.'),
(3105, ' You need this along with the Nostrum of Speed to learn the ultimate secret art, and it also requires several special ingredients to make.  To complete the Stamp of Agility, you need 1 Lupus Pendant, 1 Robos Pendant, and one Silver Bar. Are you going to bring those?'),
(3106, 'Come back when you have all the ingredients.'),
(3107, 'That might be a wise choice.'),
(3108, 'I already told you that to make the Stamp of Agility, you need 1 Lupus Pendant, 1 Robos Pendant, and 1 Slver Bar.'),
(3109, 'Master, you`ve collected all the Stamp of Dexterity ingredients. Now it`s just a matter of time till you learn the ultimate secret technique.'),
(3110, 'Master, you`ve collected all the Stamp of Dexterity ingredients. Now it`s just a matter of time till you learn the ultimate secret technique.'),
(3111, 'You`ve collected all the Stamp of Dexterity ingredients. This is the Stamp of Dexterity, an object needed to master the final secret technique of the rogue.'),
(3112, 'Master, I heard that [Secret Agent] Clarence knows of an assistant magic that increases all resistance of the body during combat.'),
(3113, 'Master, I heard that [Secret Agent] Clarence knows of an assistant magic that increases all resistance of the body during combat.'),
(3114, 'The border defending battle is held every day at 10 AM and 1, 3, 5 and 10 PM and 1 AM. And it is held additionally at 8 PM on Tuesday, Friday, Saturday and Sunday when there is no war. When the relevant time comes, the announcement for recruitment will be aired automatically so that application for participation can be made'),
(3115, 'The border defending battle is held every day at 10 AM and 1, 3, 5 and 10 PM and 1 AM. And it is held additionally at 8 PM on Tuesday, Friday, Saturday and Sunday when there is no war. When the relevant time comes, the announcement for recruitment will be aired automatically so that application for participation can be made'),
(3116, 'I guess you came to me after hearing some stories, but I dont carelessly make it for just anyone.'),
(3117, 'You have safely completed this mission as well, master~.'),
(3118, 'Please bring every single item I enumerated then.'),
(3119, 'That might be a wise choice.'),
(3120, 'They used to be part of the Death Magicians and were a terror to everyone, but then they disappeared without any trace, as if they vanished into thin air. And now they are back. The ones who made everyone quiver in fear...'),
(3121, ' What about you... How good are you?? Ah~am I thinking too recklessly...'),
(3122, 'How did you manage to defeat those Death Magicians while still fighting in the battles against El Morad?? Wow~'),
(3123, 'You have brought all the materials. I will keep my word and produce the Holy Water of Poison.'),
(3124, 'For a long time, us rogues have been offering the valuable berries to the Imperial Family.'),
(3125, 'But cardinals living in the vicinity stole all the Asga berries and there`s nothing to present to the Imperial Family. Please help us and retrieve the berries.'),
(3126, 'We`re counting on you.'),
(3127, 'Are you still oblivious to the value of the berries?'),
(3128, 'Asga berries can be obtained by hunting cardinals.'),
(3129, 'Master, the Asga berries have been retrieved. Go back to [Secret Proxy] Clarence now.'),
(3130, 'You brought Asga berries? I will give you a small gift for them.'),
(3131, 'Belua`s peal is immensely beautiful but it is sacred enough to resurrect a dying plant.'),
(3132, 'We were waiting for a true knight who will give us a chance to hear it. Please defeat the cardinals which are threatening this village and seize their jewels and show it in front of the Belua Bell. The bell will toll then.'),
(3133, 'Belua Bell will certainly toll in front of you.'),
(3134, 'You don`t deserve to ring the Belua Bell.'),
(3135, 'Cardinal`s jewels can be obtained by hunting cardinals.'),
(3136, 'Master, Cardinal`s jewels have been gathered. Now we can hear the peal of the Belua Bell.'),
(3137, 'Thanks to you, we are able to listen to the beautiful peal. Thank you.'),
(3138, 'Master, aren`t you hungry suddenly?  Something smells good...'),
(3139, 'Hey, it`s coming from there. I bet he`s the Imperial Palace Chef. Go see him, Master.'),
(3140, 'The Imperial Palace is always replete with guests, from passersby to knights...'),
(3141, 'It is our duty to provide them with food and study methods to cook more delicious and nutritious dishes. But we`ve been inundated with guests today, short on help, and even the pig to be barbecued ran away. If you catch the pig for us I will make you delicious BBQ.'),
(3142, 'Tyon meat can be obtained by catching Tyons in the farm. Please help us.'),
(3143, 'Guess you`re not really hungry.'),
(3144, 'Hmm... How much longer till we see the Tyon meat?'),
(3145, 'Master, you obtained Tyon meat. We`re finally having delicious BBQ, heh heh.'),
(3146, 'Thank you. Delicious BBQ is now complete.'),
(3147, 'Master, aren`t you hungry suddenly?  Something smells good...'),
(3148, 'Hey, it`s coming from there. I bet he`s the Imperial Palace Chef. Go see him, Master.'),
(3149, 'Master, you obtained Tyon meat. We`re finally having delicious BBQ, heh heh.'),
(3150, 'Master, [Sentinel] Patrick looks preoccupied again.'),
(3151, 'Master, [Sentinel] Patrick looks preoccupied again.'),
(3152, 'For the protection of Moradon... What is it you wanted to say to me?'),
(3153, 'Peddlers that have arrived recently say they were attacked by Kecoons en route to the castle. Kecoons are malicious monsters who attack humans and take their belongings. Say, do you mind venturing to the outskirts of Moradon and teaching them a lesson?'),
(3154, 'You never let me down. Thank you in advance.'),
(3155, 'You seem to be tied up right now. I`ll ask you later.'),
(3156, 'Your ability is wasted. Dont you need to catch this much at least?'),
(3157, 'Master, I caught all of the Kecoons as promised. Lets go back to [Sentinel] Patrick.'),
(3158, 'Master, I caught all of the Kecoons as promised. Lets go back to [Sentinel] Patrick.'),
(3159, 'Thanks to you the number of Kecoons dwelling in the village outskirts have been reduced significantly. Thank you. I`ll ask for your help again next time.'),
(3160, 'Another day in thriving Moradon! What do you want?'),
(3161, 'I received word that peddlers are having a hard time traveling due to Bulcans lurking in the sand plains. Moradon is a quasi-desert with 80% of the terrain covered with sand. Their numbers are sure to grow if they go unchecked. Do you think it`s possible for you to wipe out the Bulcans inhabiting the sand?'),
(3162, 'Thank you. I`m counting on you.'),
(3163, 'That`s too bad. See you later.'),
(3164, 'In order to guarantee the safety of the peddlers, at least five Bulcans must be caught.'),
(3165, 'I caught all of 5 Bulcans. Lets go back to [Guard] Patrick.'),
(3166, 'I caught all of 5 Bulcans. Lets go back to [Guard] Patrick.'),
(3167, 'Excellent. Thanks to you the number of Bulcans have declined markedly. Thank you.'),
(3168, 'I`m Moradon`s Guardian, no, still just Sentinel Patrick. What did you want?'),
(3169, 'This time Bulcan creatures have appeared, but they are more powerful. The creatures called Wild Bulcan look similar to regular Bulcan in appearance, but these creatures are more ferocious. Several mercenaries and peddlers have already been vicitimized by these Wild Bulcans. I think you can solve this matter for us this time too. Please hunt five Wild Bulcans, which are similar to but fiercer than Bulcan, and come back.'),
(3170, 'I knew you would accept this mission as well. Thank you.'),
(3171, 'Are you rejecting it? You have grown a lot.'),
(3172, 'Hey, you must hunt at least five Wild Bulcans. Dont even think about going easy.'),
(3173, 'Master, you`ve hunted down the Bulcans again. Hurry back to [Sentinel] Patrick.'),
(3174, 'Master, you`ve hunted down the Bulcans again. Hurry back to [Sentinel] Patrick.'),
(3175, 'I should`ve asked you from the beginning. Thank you for taking care of it for me.'),
(3176, 'Master, I hear that Kecoons are running rampant again lately in the Moradon outskirts.'),
(3177, 'Master, I hear that Kecoons are running rampant again lately in the Moradon outskirts.'),
(3178, 'Wonder why there`s no word from [Sentinel] Patrick. It`s about time he asked you to get rid of them.'),
(3179, 'Wonder why there`s no word from [Sentinel] Patrick. It`s about time he asked you to get rid of them.'),
(3180, 'Master, what if we go ahead and hunt down Kecoon Warriors which are at the root of the commotion and pleasantly surprise [Sentinel] Patrick?'),
(3181, 'Master, what if we go ahead and hunt down Kecoon Warriors which are at the root of the commotion and pleasantly surprise [Sentinel] Patrick?'),
(3182, 'Knew you`d be up to it, Master. Let`s move to Moradon outskirts where Kecoon Warriors primarily breed.'),
(3183, 'Knew you`d be up to it, Master. Let`s move to Moradon outskirts where Kecoon Warriors primarily breed.'),
(3184, 'Jeez, Master, you`re more passive than you look.'),
(3185, 'Jeez, Master, you`re more passive than you look.'),
(3186, '..........'),
(3187, 'Master, you caught 10 Kecoon Warriors. This should be enough to surprise [Sentinel] Patrick.'),
(3188, 'Master, you caught 10 Kecoon Warriors. This should be enough to surprise [Sentinel] Patrick.'),
(3189, 'No way. I didn`t ask you because I felt so guilty enlisting your help all the time. And you went ahead and resolved it without my asking.'),
(3190, 'Thank you so much. I`ll never forget what you did for me today. Wish you can be a true colleague of mine.'),
(3191, 'Master, we have to first finish the hunt we started!'),
(3192, 'Master, we have to first finish the hunt we started!'),
(3193, 'Phew...'),
(3194, 'Kecoons seem to be running rampant again lately in the Moradon outskirts.'),
(3195, 'Lately... No, never mind, I can`t ask you. Goodbye!'),
(3196, 'You`re declining my request? What an upstart.'),
(3197, 'What are you doing?'),
(3200, 'Dying and killing, dying and killing... There is nothing left for me anymore.'),
(3201, 'Thanks to you, I think we will have a ceremony to commemorate the spirits of the warriors who have been freed. As there were troubles up to now because of these Zombie creatures, I think well use Apples of Moradon as a sacrifice. What do you think? Isnt it a good idea?'),
(3202, 'So can you obtain their apples for me? Even though I am in such a situation, I intend to perform the grave site ceremonies so that the spirits of the dead warriors can sleep peacefully. Apples of Moradon can be obtained from all kinds of zombies.'),
(3203, 'As soon as Apple of Moradon is secured, I am going to hold the ceremony immediately. Please note that Apple of Moradon can be obtained from all kinds of zombies.'),
(3204, 'We are eternally grateful.|Now the dead warriors can finally rest after their ancient wanderings.'),
(3205, 'The war on the continent of Adonis is doing great injustice to the warriors who have turned into casualties of war.'),
(3206, 'With the ceremony delayed, Rotten Eyes have seized this place and turned it into a situation which the warriors spirits cant reside peacefully. I feel like I am turning into the dead being surrounded by this. If we do nothing, Rotten Eyes will take over the warriors spirits soon.'),
(3207, 'As long as these Rotten Eyes exist, their spirits may not be able to sleep peacefully. I feel pathetic that there is nothing I can do.'),
(3208, 'Master, they say  Vilbore is giving special gifts to knights who reach 35Lv. And the fact is that you are also close to reaching 35Lv - so cheer up ^^'),
(3209, 'Congratulations~ Master, you have finally reached 35Lv.  If you show  Promise of Training to Vilbore, he will give you special present.'),
(3210, 'Dont block me any more.'),
(3211, 'I heard that someone wiped out Rotten Eyes.. Was it you? I think I probably was a little rude to you. I am sorry. Their spirits can rest comfortably now, cant they? Oh, thank you very much.'),
(3212, 'Congratulations~ Master, you have finally reached 35Lv.  If you show  Promise of Training to Vilbore, he will give you special present.'),
(3213, 'Do you like the new Moradon?|Weve organized a small event to celebrate the birth of New Moradon. The First Event!'),
(3214, 'Master, according to rumors the [Warrior Master] is teaching the ultimate skill to those warriors who have reached the apex as a warrior. Go for it.'),
(3215, 'Master, according to rumors the [Warrior Master] is teaching the ultimate skill to those warriors who have reached the apex as a warrior. Go for it.'),
(3216, 'You are well qualified to advance to the ultimate warrior level.'),
(3217, 'To master the ultimate skill of the ultimate warrior, you need 1 Stamp of Strength, 1 Nostrum of Constitution, and 7 million Noahs.  Will you return after you satisfy all the requirements?'),
(3218, 'Preliminary'),
(3219, 'Preliminary'),
(3220, 'To master the ultimate skill of the ultimate warrior, you need 1 Stamp of Strength, 1 Nostrum of Constitution, and 7 million Noahs.'),
(3221, 'Master, all the items needed to master ultimate warrior skills have been acquired. Let`s hurry back to [Warrior Master] Skaki.'),
(3222, 'Master, all the items needed to master ultimate warrior skills have been acquired. Let`s hurry back to [Warrior Master] Skaki.'),
(3223, 'This is Howling Sword and Iron Skin, the ultimate level skills. You will triumph in the war by your own powers.'),
(3224, 'Master, according to rumors the [Secret Proxy] is teaching the ultimate skill to those rogues who have reached the apex as a rogue. Go for it.'),
(3225, 'Master, according to rumors the [Secret Proxy] is teaching the ultimate skill to those rogues who have reached the apex as a rogue. Go for it.'),
(3226, 'Children of wind and shadow, that is us rogues. You, who have reached the final rogue training stage, are qualified to learn and employ the final skill.'),
(3227, 'If you want to learn the final skill of rogue, you have to have one stamp of agility, one nostrum of speed and 7 million noah.  Will you come back after collecting all the preparations for the final skill?')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(3228, 'Let me know when you have equipped all of them.'),
(3229, 'Do not lose your pride as a descendant of the wind and shadow.'),
(3230, 'To learn the final skill of Rogue, you have to have 1 Stamp of Agility, 1 Nostrum of Speed and 7 million Noahs.'),
(3231, 'Master, all the items needed to learn the rogue final skill has been collected. Let`s hurry back to [Secret Proxy] Clarence.'),
(3232, 'Master, all the items needed to learn the rogue final skill has been collected. Let`s hurry back to [Secret Proxy] Clarence.'),
(3233, 'This is the final secret technique, Dark Pursuer and Bloody Beast. Your ability will be a hope to us rogues.'),
(3234, 'Master, according to rumors the [Archmage] is teaching the ultimate skill to those mages who have reached the apex as a mage. Go for it.'),
(3235, 'Master, according to rumors the [Archmage] is teaching the ultimate skill to those mages who have reached the apex as a mage. Go for it.'),
(3236, 'Magic is the greatest ability created by man. You are well qualified to employ the ultimate magic. Is it time for another archmage to come on board...'),
(3237, 'To learn the ultimate magic, you have to have with 1 Stamp of Magic Power, 1 Nostrum of Magic and 7 million Noahs.  Are you going to get ready to learn the ultimate magic?'),
(3238, 'Come back when you are equipped with all of them.'),
(3239, 'Even if you do master the magic, it`s up to you whether you practice it or not! Why are you faltering?'),
(3240, 'To complete the ultimate magic, you have to have with 1 Stamp of Magic Power, 1 Nostrum of Magic and 7 million Noahs.'),
(3241, 'Master, all the items needed to complete ultimate magic employed by archmages have been acquired. Let`s hurry back to [Archmage] Drake.'),
(3242, 'Master, all the items needed to complete ultimate magic employed by archmages have been acquired. Let`s hurry back to [Archmage] Drake.'),
(3243, 'You now possess ultimate magic. With two different magic for each element, your powers will be incomparable and unprecedented. You have nothing more to wish for as a mage.'),
(3244, 'Master, according to rumors [Priest] Minerva is teaching the ultimate skill to those priests who have reached the pinnacle as a priest . Go for it.'),
(3245, 'Master, according to rumors [Priest] Minerva is teaching the ultimate skill to those priests who have reached the pinnacle as a priest . Go for it.'),
(3246, 'Priests save the world in the name of the gods. You are qualified to undergo the final training of the priesthood. In the final training the gods will confer the greatest ability available to a priest upon you.'),
(3247, 'To learn the ability of god of final training, you have to have 1 Stamp of Intelligence, 1 Nostrum of Wisdom and 7 million Noahs.  Will you satisfy these conditions and be granted with the ability of god?'),
(3248, 'Let me know when you are equipped all of the elements needed to be bestowed with the ability of the gods.'),
(3249, 'Even if you do not undergo the final training, you must not neglect the duty of the priesthood.'),
(3250, 'To learn the ability of god of final training, you have to have 1 Stamp of Intelligence, 1 Nostrum of Wisdom and 7 million Noahs.'),
(3251, 'Master, you have collected all the items needed to be bestowed with the ability of the gods. Let`s hurry back to [Priest] Minerva.'),
(3252, 'Master, you have collected all the items needed to be bestowed with the ability of the gods. Let`s hurry back to [Priest] Minerva.'),
(3253, 'The gods have heeded your will. Please continue to work to save the world.'),
(3798, 'Master, wonder what`s going on with the food rationing. [Sentinel] Patrick should know about it. Go ask him.'),
(3799, 'Master, wonder what`s going on with the food rationing. [Sentinel] Patrick should know about it. Go ask him.'),
(3800, 'Moradon is in my hands. What do you want?'),
(3801, 'Wheat bread, Moradon`s special local product, has killer taste. But since not too long ago, Gavolts raided the harvested mill and as a result, the food supply is running low and the number of citizens suffering from malnutrition rising. Can you wipe those monsters out and help the farmers of Moradon?'),
(3802, 'Thanks. If you do this for me, I`ll buy drinks.'),
(3803, 'That`s too bad. I`ll ask someone else.'),
(3804, 'In order for the farmers to be relieved, at least five of them may have to be caught.'),
(3805, 'Master, you`ve done a decent job at wiping out Gavolts. Go back to [Sentinel] Patrick .'),
(3806, 'Master, you`ve done a decent job at wiping out Gavolts. Go back to [Sentinel] Patrick .'),
(3807, 'Good work. The wheat supply has been normalized again. Let`s indulge in plenty of bread and wine tonight.'),
(3808, 'For the protection of Moradon... What did you want to say to me?'),
(3809, 'Do you know of monsters called Bultures? They belong to the Bulcan species, but 3 times as large. Even the most accomplished warriors are rendered helpless in front of them, but they should be no match for you. Their numbers have increased markedly lately. Nothing trumps Bultures in the Moradon monster food chain so we can`t just sit by the sidelines. Can you please hunt them and rein them in?'),
(3810, 'You never let me down.'),
(3811, 'You don`t look too well. Come back when you`re feeling better.'),
(3812, 'I commend you for accepting my request but you should have kept your word.'),
(3813, 'Wow, you`re incredible, Master, getting rid of so many of these giant monsters. Let`s hurry back to [Sentinel] Patrick and brag.'),
(3814, 'Wow, you`re incredible, Master, getting rid of so many of these giant monsters. Let`s hurry back to [Sentinel] Patrick and brag.'),
(3815, 'You succeeded again? Amazing!'),
(3816, 'Another day in thriving Moradon! What do you want?'),
(3817, 'You`ve arrived again without fail. Bulcan-type monsters are really tenacious. The giant Bultures seem to be the most powerful of them all, but that`s not true. Across the creek outside of Moradon in the farthest outskirts dwell human-sized Silans. They are normal  sized, but their muscle strength and physical power are incomparable since they primarily feed on underground iron bars. With their numbers continuously escalating, we need to wipe them out for the safety of the residents. Those shoddy mercenaries were no match for them. That is why I`m asking you.'),
(3818, 'It should be a boon to your ability enhancement. Thank you.'),
(3819, 'Maybe Silans are still too dangerous for you. Come back after you`ve enhanced your power.'),
(3820, 'Listen, it`s nothing novel. Did it slip your mind? Get at least 10 Silans, right?'),
(3821, 'Master, you`ve caught all 5 Silans. Your ability is growing everyday. Hurry back to [Sentinel] Patrick.'),
(3822, 'Master, you`ve caught all 5 Silans. Your ability is growing everyday. Hurry back to [Sentinel] Patrick.'),
(3823, 'I knew you`d be able to pull it off this time as well. You`ll soon catch up to me.'),
(3824, 'I`m Warrior Master Skaki. Do you have anything to say to me?'),
(3825, 'Why did you come to me?'),
(3826, 'The power of evil in the Adonis continent is gaining stock. What did you want?'),
(3827, 'Master, have you heard of a monster called the werewolf?'),
(3828, 'Master, have you heard of a monster called the werewolf?'),
(3829, 'They`re nocturnal but I heard they grew increasingly violent of late.'),
(3830, 'They`re nocturnal but I heard they grew increasingly violent of late.'),
(3831, 'You know who to go see about this time as well, don`t you?'),
(3832, 'You know who to go see about this time as well, don`t you?'),
(3833, 'Jeez, [Sentinel] Patrick`s just the person who`d be in the know on something like this, right?'),
(3834, 'Jeez, [Sentinel] Patrick`s just the person who`d be in the know on something like this, right?'),
(3835, 'Moradon`s Guardian, no still just Sentinel Patrick. What is it?'),
(3836, 'You appear just in time like an apparition. I don`t know if you`ve heard but the werewolves are funning rampant recently. They`re powerful enough that not many mercenaries in Moradon can take them down.  Maybe they`re no match for you, either. And what`s more, their habitat is teeming with all kinds of fierce monsters. You still want to have a go at them?'),
(3837, 'You still want to have a go at them? Seriously?'),
(3838, 'I`m telling you this because I`m worried for your safety. Just come back whenever you feel endangered.'),
(3839, 'Even you`re no match for them this time. It might be a wise decision...'),
(3840, 'Your resolve was commendable but looks like you failed to reduce the number of werewolves.'),
(3841, 'Incredible, Master. Werewolves are one of the strongest monsters in Moradon. I bet [Sentinel] Patrick will be pleasantly surprised as well.'),
(3842, 'Incredible, Master. Werewolves are one of the strongest monsters in Moradon. I bet [Sentinel] Patrick will be pleasantly surprised as well.'),
(3843, 'You`re amazing. I would like to express my admiration as a fellow guard. I`m being totally sincere.'),
(3844, 'This is a token of my gratitude. I think you`re ready to venture out to a bigger world. Thanks for everything. (He may have already surpassed me...)'),
(3845, 'Information is key. We do know that theres a strange movement in El Morad, but we need you to recover the Classified Document from the spy.'),
(3846, 'Information is key. We do know that theres a strange movement in Karus, but we need you to recover the Classified Document from the spy.'),
(3847, 'This is a guard post, near the national borders. Border disputes occur regularly, so the warriors here are always prepped and ready.'),
(3848, 'This is a guard post, near the national borders. Border disputes occur regularly, so the warriors here are always prepped and ready.'),
(3849, 'Are you kidding me? Heres where the El Moradian Knights are  dispatched from.'),
(3850, 'The enemies are still alive.'),
(3851, 'Master! If it ends like this, then yes, the warriors under our feet may sleep in peace.'),
(3852, 'Master! If it ends like this, then yes, the warriors under our feet may sleep in peace.'),
(3853, 'The Training Stone still has some strength left in it.'),
