(4017, 'If you learn about the upgrade for strengthening weapon from Blacksmith Hepa, he will give you a weapon suitable for your job as a reward.'),
(4018, 'Master Blacksmith Hepa is about to talk about the strengthening of weapon! Go there quickly!'),
(4019, 'Master Blacksmith Hepa is about to talk about the strengthening of weapon! Go there quickly!'),
(4020, 'The strengthening of weapon is a fundamental basis! First as practice, go up the stairs with me, purchase a dagger (+1) from the [Arms Dealer] Gargameth, and then purchase the [Upgrade Scroll (Low Class Item)] from the [Scroll Merchant] Charon and strengthen the dagger (+2)! And then I will exchange it with a weapon that is suitable for your job!'),
(4022, 'I say this one more time. The dagger (+1) can be purchased from the [Arms Dealer] Gargameth and the [Upgrade Scroll (Low Class Item)] from the [Scroll Merchant] Charon.'),
(4023, 'Come on, go there and come back. Weapon is not acquired for free!'),
(4024, 'Well, you dont like it? This is a  good opportunity.... If you like it, come back to me'),
(4025, 'Havent you had the strengthening yet? You have to strengthen the dagger (+2) and come back!'),
(4026, 'I succeeded in the refining! Hurry up and bring this to [Blacksmith] Hepa.'),
(4027, 'I succeeded in the refining! Hurry up and bring this to [Blacksmith] Hepa.'),
