(4051, 'bandit suppression squad has begun again. Hurry, Master.'),
(4052, 'I hear the number of bandits who raid merchants converging near Moradon are on the rise. Accordingly, the Grand Merchant has asked us to suppress the bandits and eliminate their monsters.  I will give you directions once your squad has accumulated 4-8 members. Don`t worry about gathering members. If you accept my suggestion, I`ll gather them for you.'),
(4053, 'Member gathering is complete.'),
(4054, 'Member gathering is complete.'),
(4055, 'I will relay it to you when the next suppression squad is dispatched. No other requests have come in.'),
