(4470, 'Winning nation can enter Bifrost. It will open to both nations after 30 minutes.|If there is no winning nation, both nations cannot enter the Bifrost. Entrance fee is 2,000,000 Noah.'),
(4471, 'Bifrost will only open when one nation is victorious over the other.|Bifrost opens for 2 hours and nations can fight against each other after 30 minutes from opening time.|(Nation Point loss will occur when a player is killed by enemy nation.)'),
