(4643, 'Do you remember that day? The war against Pathos which turned the land crimson... After that day the only compensation the heroes who survived received were Pathos`s curse and a frigid blade |Let`s show those El Moradians who drove us to these cutting Iskan mountain range that the we are the true descendants of the heroes!'),
