(4822, 'Karus great hero Xigenon is known to have had the characteristics of a Leo. One of his great enemies was Kaisha, the God of War, who hated him deeply. After numerous attempts to assassinate him, Xigenon had to kill the Cannibal Lion that was sent against him, and he utterly destroyed it in a brutal battle.|Kaisha sent the defeated lion to heaven and made it a Star-sign in its honor.'),
