(4828, 'Half man and half serpent with 9 heads, Hydra inhabits the swamp near the Arimone Spring threatening the people of Argos. Ziegnon killed it and stopped it from growing more heads. | Kaisha sent the sacrificed Hydra to the sky to pay respects.'),
