(4833, 'To change Familiar names, you need the [Familiar Name Change Certificate].'),
(4834, 'Im [Trainer] Kate. Im in charge of all things related to Familiar| You can hatch Familiar eggs or change names with the [Familiar Name Change Certificate]. Would you like to try it?'),
(4846, 'Long ago... when the Karusians infiltrated our village, I saw it, that blue-faced charisma... Why do we keep fighting? Its so sad... I want to see him again. I keep thinking about him.'),
(4847, 'I know its an act of treason, but warrior, cant you accept my request? Please find him deliver this letter to him. I will compensate you for it. And dont forget to bring back his reply.'),
(4848, 'Master! I have Klasrass reply. Lets take it to Nusram.'),
(4849, 'You will get a reply if you deliver the letter of my affection to Klasras in Karus.'),
(4850, 'Oh! Youve delivered my letter! |  Thank you so much. This is your compensation.'),
(4851, 'Everyone looks thrilled with the spring festival |  Hope you enjoy it as well.'),
(4852, 'What can I do for you...'),
(4853, 'Everyone looks thrilled with the spring festival |  Hope you enjoy it as well.'),
(4854, 'What can I do for you...'),
(4855, 'Go to El Morad and bring back the letter of affection from Nusram.'),
(4856, 'Oh... Ive seen her. She was a true beauty... I couldnt brandish my sword against her although shes the enemy... What? Shes looking for me? Shes my destiny! This is my reply. Please relay my affection to her.'),
(4857, 'Please deliver my reply to Nusram in El Morad.'),
(4858, 'Long ago... when we infiltrated El Morad, I saw her...| Her incredible beauty... How can I tell her how I feel about her? | I want to send this letter to her.'),
(4859, 'Master! I have Nusrams reply. Lets take it to Klasras.'),
(4860, 'You will get a reply if you deliver the letter of my affection to Nusram in El Morad.'),
