(4864, 'You must deliver this reply to Klasras in Karus.'),
(4865, 'But... I have a concern... Would you like to hear it?'),
(4866, 'In fact... After reading his reply, I think even enemies could fall in love... But thats not possible anymore, is it? Thats why I made a ring for him.'),
(4867, 'But the trolls stole it... reproducing it requires too many ingredients. But I want to make it for him again! Will you heed my request?'),
(4868, 'Master! Ive collected all the ingredients. Take it to Nusram.'),
(4869, 'Thank you. If you hand me the ingredients I will make the ring.'),
