(4924, 'Errrm... Right, yeah, erm, Ok, so I made a mistake!! Im extremely busy now, well have to talk some other time.'),
(4925, 'Errrm... Right, yeah, erm, OK, so I made a mistake!! What should I do?! Our war preparations are almost over. We just need to hold the ¡–afety ritual. But, uh, I forgot to prepare the materials for it. So... You know, if Rage finds out...'),
(4926, 'Are you sure? You see! We only have <selfname>!! If you can resolve this matter, I will treat you as my benefactor for the rest of my life. All you have to do is to collect two Apples of Moradon needed for the ceremony. Please look for them quickly before Rage finds out.'),
(4927, 'The collection has been completed!!'),
(4928, 'Ugh! If you <selfname> move that slowly, my life..'),
(4929, 'Ah, my life is safe now. You <selfname> saved my life!!'),
(4930, 'Master! Master, Folk Village is preparing some kind of weird ritual in preparation for the war. Would you like to look around?'),
(4931, 'You need some Shadow Seekers blood and some Blood of Beasts for Karon to use as Scroll material.'),
(4932, 'An Oath of Darkness can be earned from the zombie people call ¡dattalion. But whats it for? What?! Ah~ I want to know!'),
(4933, 'Itd be great if Silver Feathers were in greater supply... Ha, the Hunters say that Meganterions are really brutal. Take care of yourself.'),
(4934, 'The collection has been completed!!'),
(4935, 'If you are looking for Cougar, you will find him near the entrance of Moradon castle.'),
(4936, 'If you are looking for Cougar, you will find him near the entrance of Moradon castle.'),
(4937, 'As the trade capital of the continent, Moradon is heaving with precious goods.'),
(4938, 'Call me ¡derret.|I climb mountains and cross seas just to trade and make a little profit.'),
(4939, 'Call me ¡derret.|I climb mountains and cross seas just to trade and make a little profit.'),
(4940, 'Its said that the Lycan is a cursed man; a man evolved into a Wolfman after the war against Pathos.'),
(4941, 'Master! Middle man Berret from Moradon is here. Go and introduce yourself.'),
(4942, 'Damn... Big trouble...|KNIGHT!! Can you please, please help me? Im in dire straits here.'),
(4943, 'You need Apple of Moradon to make the antidote. Hunt the Pincers Scorpion and collect the poison in its tail.'),
(4944, 'Master, Ok, youve got enough Apple of Moradon for Berret. Lets get it back to him.'),
(4945, 'Eh? Armor? <selfname>, youve got a talent for confusing people. Heh, Id give it to you free, but Im obliged to protect the supplies.'),
(4946, 'Hmm. There is some armor that would suit you,  <selfname>. Unless  Rageallows it, Im afraid its not possible.'),
(4947, 'Master! Middle man Berret from Moradon is here. Go and introduce yourself.'),
(4948, 'Well well, look who it is.|Seems like it was just yesterday when I first met you and now look at you. Youre doing me proud. Ach, Moradon is too small for your talents now, <selfname>...ha, ha'),
(4949, 'Time to leave Moradons embrace and say ¡‹ello to the wider world. You ought to get out there, look around and learn and feel some new things. Listen, Im not a fortune teller, but I know youre going to do great things for your country, <selfname>. It was <selfname> who inspired me all along..'),
(4950, 'Master, Ok, youve got enough Pincer Poison for Berret, lets get it back to him.'),
(4951, 'To save them all, we need at least <font color=@#660066@>three Apples of Moradon</font>. Please take courage and find them for me'),
(4952, 'Thanks. Thank you so much. Really, you saved everyone. We really are thankful.'),
(4953, 'Berret is looking for something special, right?'),
(4954, 'Welcome, <selfname>| Apple of Moradon is just what Ive been looking for. Apples of Moradon sell really well around the Luferson Castle area in Karus because its so cold around there. It profits you to profit from it. Heh heh heh!'),
(4955, 'Karus Luferson Castle area makes special Apples of Moradon, and trades it out to all sorts of places.'),
(4956, 'Master! Youve got a hold of a Apple of Moradon. Now you just need to trade ¡ˆm with Berret.'),
(4957, 'I really want a Apple of Moradon. Youll get a Apple of Moradon from an Any Wolf and Lycan, no problems.'),
(4958, 'Oh, great, you got all the right stuff and just enough of it too. Thanks. You helped our chief make a big profit there. Well done.'),
(4959, 'Berret is looking for something special, right?'),
(4960, '[Ok, Ok you can have the Boots of War ? Folk Village Mercenary Adjutant Rage]|Ha! You got your permission then, eh? Grats! Ok, so, Ill supply you with the boots as per this docket.'),
(4961, 'Thats the Wolfmans Claw. Whats it like? You want to trade with me? <selfname> wont be harmed by this. Mwuahahaha!'),
(4962, 'Master! Youve got hold of a Apple of Moradon. Now you just need to trade ¡ˆm with Berret.'),
(4963, 'Although its only a boot, its not bad collecting ¡ˆm one by one. Heh.'),
(4964, 'Although its only a boot, its not bad collecting ¡ˆm one by one. Heh.'),
(4965, 'Have you ever eaten Apple of Moradon before? They say it tastes amazing...(Gulping) Berret sells it doesnt he?'),
(4966, 'Apple of Moradon? Heh heh, how could you still not know how it tastes? Apple of Moradon is the best fruit. However, there arent enough supplies of it in Moradon! Words cant do the melting taste justice. You just gotta try it!'),
(4967, 'Well, unfortunately we dont have any at the moment. The hunter used to trade a certain amount of meat with me at the end of each day. But he seems to have disappeared... This is going to cost me. Ach, trouble. Nothing but trouble.'),
(4968, 'Hmm, so this is Apple of Moradon eh? Tastes awesome doesnt it? So juicy!'),
(4969, 'Ach...How much is lost! Agrrr, Im so stupid!'),
(4970, 'Well then! This is the Apple of Moradon then? Well thank you very much indeed. I dont really know how to repay your continual help. Hey! How about this- Heres Apple of Moradon for yourselves. Enjoy!'),
(4971, 'Have you ever eaten Apple of Moradon? They say it tastes amazing...(Gulping) Berret sells it doesnt he?'),
(4972, 'Let me write a letter of introduction for you. Go and see Luferson Castles [Captain] Fargo with this.'),
(4973, 'Let me write a letter of introduction for you. Go and see El Morad Castles [Captain] Polkwein with this.'),
(4974, 'Hmm, so this is Apple of Moradon eh? Tastes awesome doesnt it? So juicy!'),
(4975, 'Master, do you know about the place called Ronark Land? You should go to Fargo and ask him about it.'),
(4976, 'Hello new face. Who are you then?'),
(4977, 'There must be something wrong with Berrets guild?'),
(4978, 'Why is it so hard to run a simple business? This is really getting me down... Why is that we dont have enough  Apple of Moradon at the height of the fashion season?'),
(4979, 'Apple of Moradon has a reputation for juiciness so its often used in smoothies and foods. Thing is, its so good theres never enough of it. Excuse me, Im kind of busy~ Hey, Secretary~~!! Hunters... Call the hunters quickly~!!'),
(4980, 'Wow, thats tough! Just like we heard it was.'),
(4981, 'Oh my god, I cant even scrape a tiny piece off!'),
(4982, 'This is Smirdon Hide!? Thank you sooo much, this is great. Would you like to work for our boss? HA HA HA!'),
(4983, 'There must be something wrong with Berrets guild?'),
(4984, 'Erm... Well, if Cougar recommended you, then thats fine with me. This is a small token of your formal entry to Karus Castle. Let me briefly explain some stuff about the Karus.'),
(4985, 'You ought to get out there, look around and learn and feel some new things.'),
(4986, 'Wow, thats tough! Just like we heard it was.'),
(4987, 'Master, do you know about the place called Ronark Land? You should go to Polkwein and ask him about it.'),
(4988, 'Hello new face. Who are you then?'),
(4989, 'Master! Shaimer is looking for you urgently, Master!'),
(4990, 'Welcome. Nice to meet you. I am Shaimer, and I visit many places around Moradon to do trade. I have something urgent to tell you. [Scroll Merchant] Karon lost some materials she need for making a new scroll, and she has asked me to find some of the them, but Im having difficulty finding them.'),
(4991, 'I can find most of them, but I just cant get the  Shadow Seekers blood or the Blood of Beast. Youd have to hunt Shadow Seekers to get it, but thats easy enough for you, isnt it <selfname>? Heh Heh.'),
(4992, 'You have gathered all the Animal Blood Shymer has asked for. Sigh!'),
(4993, 'Seems Ive only <selfname> to trust. Take care out there eh? Heh.'),
(4994, 'I knew you could do it, <selfname>. Thanks~ thanks~ and Thank you again. Hee hee!'),
(4995, 'Master! Clark is looking for you urgently, Master!'),
(4996, 'Erm... Well, if Cougar recommended you, then thats fine with me. This is a small token of your formal entry to El Morad Castle. Let me briefly explain some stuff about El Morad.'),
(4997, 'Cougar? Hes an old friend. Weve seen a few wars together.')
