(5242, 'You now possess the Superilaist skill. I trust you will continue to work toward saving the world.'),
(5243, 'Master, let`s go see [Priest] Minerva to try out for the Level 80 skill.'),
(5244, 'Master, let`s go see [Priest] Minerva to try out for the Level 80 skill.'),
(5245, 'You still haven`t undergone the 2nd job change?|Come back after you`ve completed it.'),
(5246, 'Priests save the world in the name of the gods. You are qualified to undergo the final training of the priesthood.'),
(5247, 'You must have the Nostrum of Wisdom, 3 Magic Jewel Powder, and 10 million Noahs  to master Level 80 skills. Will you be equipped with all the elements in order to be endowed with the ability of the gods?'),
(5248, 'Let me know when you are fully prepared  to be endowed with the ability of the gods.'),
(5249, 'Even if you don`t learn Level 80 skills, I hope you will not neglect the duties of the priesthood.'),
(5250, 'You must have the Nostrum of Wisdom, 3 Magic Jewel Powder, and 10 million Noahs to be endowed with Level 80 skills.'),
(5251, 'Master, you have collected all items needed to be conferred Level 80 skills. Hurry back to [Priest] Minerva.'),
(5252, 'Master, you have collected all items needed to be conferred Level 80 skills. Hurry back to [Priest] Minerva.'),
(5253, 'You now possess Fast Restore, Counter Curse, and Discount Curse, Level 80 skills. I trust you will continue to work toward saving the world.'),
(5254, 'This is the Discipline Dungeon. You have been charged of using a hack tool.'),
(6000, 'Master, I hear the mercenary captain is looking for men to join the bandit suppression squad. Let`s go check it out.'),
(6001, 'Master, I hear the mercenary captain is looking for men to join the bandit suppression squad. Let`s go check it out.'),
(6002, 'As bandits are increasingly emerging In the mountain behind Moradon, I`m forming a suppression squad. Would you like to join?'),
(6003, 'Infiltrate the bandit base, eliminate their leader, and bring back the proof. Simple enough, no?'),
(6004, 'The bandit suppression squad`s been already dispatched. Apply again later.'),
(6005, 'Do you want to form a bandit suppression squad?'),
(6006, 'Rock Mountain - Be careful of the Rock Giant who attacks from above the rock.'),
(6007, 'Picket fence barricade - Be wary of orc bandit archers who attack from behind the picket fences.'),
(6008, 'Bandit hideout - Destroy the boss monster inside the hideout.'),
(6009, 'Master, this must be the proof. Let`s go see the mercenary captain now.'),
(6010, 'Master, this must be the proof. Let`s go see the mercenary captain now.'),
(6011, 'You don`t have the proof. Proof of the bandit leader is necklace worn by their boss Labuma. Kill him and bring me his necklace.'),
(6012, 'The proof is authentic. Here, it should come into good use.'),
(6013, 'After wiping out the bandits and their boss Labuma, take his proof to Mercenary Captain Cougar for a reward.'),
(6014, 'Master, I heard the mercenary captain is preparing a training evaluation. Let`s go see him.'),
(6015, 'Master, I heard the mercenary captain is preparing a training evaluation. Let`s go see him.'),
(6016, 'I think the time has come to test how much you`ve grown.'),
(6017, 'Don`t feel obligated. It`s not a difficult exam. Catch the Smirdon inside the stadium and bring back 10 Dragon Jewels. Isn`t it a piece of cake?'),
(6018, 'You came back after eliminating all 100, didnt you?|If you give me their lives, I will give you a reward in return.'),
(6019, 'Master, all the Dragon Jewels have been collected. Let`s talk to the stadium manager and get out of here.'),
(6020, 'Master, all the Dragon Jewels have been collected. Let`s talk to the stadium manager and get out of here.'),
(6021, 'You`re short on Dragon Jewels. Are you going to go back to the stadium?'),
(6022, 'Good. You`re all right. I should give you an appropriate award for passing the test.'),
(6023, 'You will pass the test if you catch the Smirdon in the arena where Mercenary Captain Cougar sends you and bring back 10 Dragon Jewels to him.'),
(6024, 'That gate in the front is the first right of passage to the bandit hideout. If you want to leave, click on[Withdraw from bandit suppression squad].')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(6025, 'Please keep this in mind if you want to proceed. The monsters here are not a mob of bandits. Their attack is methodical enough to have demolished the previous suppression squad.'),
(6026, 'To enter the bandit hideout, you must pass the first right of passage at front and pass through the land of the Rock Giants. Be careful as Rock Giants attack from above the rocks there.'),
(6027, 'If you cross the river in the center, you will approach the bandit hideout. Orcs and archers will surface from that point. If you kill the archers and advance, you will find Bandit Boss Labuma.'),
(6028, 'Killing Bandit Boss Labuma awards proof of the bandit leader. Take the proof to Mercenary Captain Cougar and he will give you a big reward.'),
(6029, 'Sorry, you can`t leave.'),
(6030, 'Master, Mercenary Captain Cougar is performing training assessment. Let`s go take the test.'),
(6031, 'Master, Mercenary Captain Cougar is performing training assessment. Let`s go take the test.'),
(6032, 'You want to provide proof of your training? Let`s see. Here it is, <selfname>.'),
(6033, 'You need more training. How do I know that? Not just anyone becomes mercenary captain, you know. You have be at least Level 40 to prove yourself.'),
(6034, 'It`s time for you to prove your training. I will send to a place teeming with goblins I raised just for warrior training purposes. They`re not just your stock goblins so they`ll be a formidable opponent. If your power increases in there you can leave.'),
(6035, 'You don`t need to prove your training. Goodbye.'),
(6036, 'Your ability has been enhanced, Master. I think we can leave now.'),
(6037, 'Your ability has been enhanced, Master. I think we can leave now.'),
(6038, 'Catch the goblin at the spot where Captain Cougar sends you and upgrade your ability. The test is completed by upgrading your ability and talking to the stadium manager.'),
(6039, 'Master, I hear monsters are raiding people in herds. Captain Polkwein seems to be forming a monster suppression squad. Let`s go check it out.'),
(6040, 'Master, I hear monsters are raiding people in herds. Captain Polkwein seems to be forming a monster suppression squad. Let`s go check it out.'),
(6041, 'Monsters have grown brave and are increasingly attacking merchants and civilian residents so we`re trying to locate their hide out and wipe them out. I can only send you as a party no matter how strong you are. It`s for your own good. Don`t object.'),
(6042, 'The task is too trivial for someone of your ability. I`ll summon you if something more important comes up.'),
(6043, 'I hear the monsters have taken refuge in the Delok Creek in Kartia Desert. If you kill Ripper, their leader, and bring me the proof, you don`t have to worry about going. I`ve already pulled some strings.'),
(6044, 'You won`t be able to pull it off on your own. Not even our best and brightest could get rid of them. I`ll send you if you come back in a party.'),
(6045, 'Are you joining the monster suppression squad?'),
(6046, 'This is the proof. If we take this to Fargo, he will give a reward.'),
(6047, 'This is the proof. If we take this to Polkwein, he will give a reward.'),
(6048, 'You have to kill Monster Leader Ripper and bring back proof. Don`t tell me you still haven`t even gone near him.'),
(6049, 'All right. Here`s the reward. Knew you could do it.'),
(6050, 'Get Captain Polkwein`s monster suppression squad request, join the squad, kill their leader Ripper and bring the captain the proof.'),
(6051, 'How odd. The monster raids have decreased but plagues and famine are breaking out in its place. We formed a suppression squad to assess the reason.'),
(6052, 'The task is too small for someone of your ability. I`ll summon you if something more important comes up.'),
(6053, 'We lost contact with the suppression squad which traveled far and wide to discover the reason but we lost contact with them in the Pizarre Snowfield. We dispatched search parties 3 times and found out why. Ferocious monsters are guarding something there and a powerful curse energy has been detected as well. There must be a link to the events in the mainland. Kill the monsters and investigate the curse energy. Monster power is stronger than anywhere else there. If you die, your weapons and armor will incur extensive damage.'),
(6054, 'You won`t be able to pull it off on your own. Not even our best and brightest could get rid of them. I`ll send you if you come back in a party.'),
(6055, 'Do you want to join the Devil`s Army suppression squad?'),
(6056, 'Did you even approach the recesses of the curse energy? Don`t tell me you lost how to get there.'),
(6057, 'So that`s what happened. Thank you anyhow. Here`s your reward.'),
(6058, 'Kill the monsters who were former members of the Devil`s Army, investigate the curse energy and go to Captain Polkwein.'),
(6059, 'Passionate Warrior`s Desert - Lose the monsters who are chasing you.'),
(6060, 'Abandoned Relic Site - Be careful of the scouters hiding out in the relic site.'),
(6061, 'Abandoned Temple - Eliminate Ripper, the monster leader, and take the proof to the captain.'),
(6062, 'Ice Hill - Be careful of the monsters who attack from to the hilltop'),
(6063, 'Frigid pond - Be wary of the monsters who attack from inside the seemingly lifeless pond.'),
(6064, 'Altar of Ice - Pathos`s subordinates who are casting curse at mainland must be killed.'),
(6065, 'Monsters have grown brave and are increasingly attacking merchants and civilian residents so we`re trying to locate their hide out and wipe them out. I can only send you as a party no matter how strong you are. It`s for your own good. Don`t object.'),
(6066, 'The task is too trivial for someone of your ability. I`ll summon you if something more important comes up.'),
(6067, 'I hear the monsters have taken refuge in the Delok Creek in Kartia Desert. If you kill Ripper, their leader, and bring me the proof, you don`t have to worry about going. I`ve already pulled some strings.'),
(6068, 'You won`t be able to pull it off on your own. Not even our best and brightest could get rid of them. I`ll send you if you come back in a party.'),
(6069, 'You have to kill Monster Leader Ripper and bring back proof. Don`t tell me you still haven`t even gone near him.'),
(6070, 'Great. Here`s your reward. Knew you`d be able to do it.'),
(6071, 'Get Captain Fargo`s monster suppression squad request, join the squad, kill their leader Ripper and bring the captain the proof.'),
(6072, 'How odd. The monster raids have decreased but plagues and famine are breaking out in its place. We formed a suppression squad to assess the reason.'),
(6073, 'The task is too trivial for someone of your ability. I`ll summon you if something more important comes up.'),
(6074, 'We lost contact with the suppression squad which traveled far and wide to discover the reason but we lost contact with them in the Pizarre Snowfield. We dispatched search parties 3 times and found out why. Ferocious monsters are guarding something there and a powerful curse energy has been detected as well. There must be a link to the events in the mainland. Kill the monsters and investigate the curse energy. Monster power is stronger than anywhere else there. If you die, your weapons and armor will incur extensive damage.'),
(6075, 'You won`t be able to pull it off on your own. Not even our best and brightest could get rid of them. I`ll send you if you come back in a party.'),
(6076, 'Do you want to join the Devil`s Army suppression squad?'),
(6077, 'Did you even approach the recesses of the curse energy? Don`t tell me you lost how to get there.'),
(6078, 'So that`s what happened. Thank you anyhow. Here`s your reward.'),
(6079, 'Kill the monsters who were former members of the Devil`s Army, investigate the curse energy and go to Captain Fargo.'),
(6080, 'Master, I hear the plagues circulating. Something feels ominous. Let`s go ask Captain Polkwein.'),
(6081, 'Master, I hear the plagues circulating. Something feels ominous. Let`s go ask Captain Polkwein.'),
(6082, 'This is the certificate. Fargo will give you a reward for it.'),
(6083, 'This is the certificate. Fargo will give you a reward for it.'),
(6084, 'Caution - Your CONT will drop if you die. Take caution.'),
(6100, 'Who are you then?|New face, you could die wandering around here. Hide yourself, quickly.'),
(6101, 'Master! Moradon Merchant Shaimer is looking for you. Hmm~ He is becoming a bother for my master!!'),
(6102, 'Ahhh~ My savior, <selfname>! Listen up. One of the nobles in Moradon is collecting eyes. Funny guy, but anyway. Hes collected almost every monster eye around, except for the  Eyes of Rotten Eye... And guess who hes asked to find it for him? Hes always coming by doing business with the boss, so I couldnt refuse him...'),
(6103, 'Well, theres not much I can do because as you know,  even the hunters stay away from those zombies. So you can see my dilemma. You up for a bit of eye collection then?'),
(6104, 'Master, youve collected enough Rotten Eyes. Lets get out of here as soon as possible.'),
(6105, 'Thats some weird hobby hes got there. Blurgh~ It makes me feel sick.'),
(6106, 'Ill... Yuk|Good effort though. I was worried you wouldnt make it back from this one. Thank you so much. Ill... Yuk~ Yuk~'),
(6107, 'Master! Moradon Merchant Clark is looking for you. Hmm~ He is becoming a bother for my master!!'),
(6108, 'Hmm... Well, Fargo seems to hold your skills in high esteem. But I still need to see for myself just how good you are. As Fargo introduced you to me, I will give you the fund needed for the adventure. Grab your gear and follow me. Ill explain on the way'),
(6109, 'I might be able to see him when I resign. Ha Ha!'),
(6110, 'Master, youve collected enough Rotten Eyes. Lets get out of here as soon as possible.'),
(6111, 'I dont know how many years its been living with all this tension. Itll be so good just to relax and have a drink with  Cougar today...'),
(6112, 'Who are you then?|New face, you could die wandering around here. Hide yourself, quickly.'),
(6113, 'These days, Silver Feather is very popular with the society crowd.'),
(6114, 'Erm, Silver Feather? Silver Feather shines, even at night~ just wear it once, and youll feel like a god~~ Heh, Its the one material thats never left out of a noble womans dress. But, being so valuable, its a bugger to get hold of.'),
(6115, 'I heard that some of the  Saber Tooths have Silver Feathers... But Im not sure if this is entirely true. Anyway, can you please hunt me down some Silver Feather? Ill make some profit selling it, and youll get some decent EXP. Everyones a winner! Hee Hee!'),
(6116, 'Weelll.... Not every Saber Tooth has Silver Feather. Anyway Master, you tried hard.'),
(6117, 'I need at least  <font color=@#660066@>3 Silver Hairs</font> to make a profit. Yes, indeed.'),
(6118, 'Wow! The shine! It must be Silver Feather~!!'),
(6119, 'These days, Silver Feather is very popular with the society crowd.'),
(6120, 'Hmm... Well, Polkwein seems to hold your skills in high esteem. But I still need to see for myself just how good you are. As Polkwein introduced you to me, I will give you the fund needed for the adventure. Grab your gear and follow me. Ill explain on the way'),
(6121, 'I might be able to see him when I resign. Ha Ha!'),
(6122, 'Weelll.... Not every Saber Tooth has Silver Feather. Anyway Master, you tried hard.'),
(6123, 'Ach, the enemys too bloody strong. At least  Cougar is by my side. To the death!'),
(6124, 'Are you new here?|Dont relax in Ronark Land. Its far too dangerous. If you dont wish to die, that is...'),
(6125, 'Master! Shaimer is once again looking for some material...'),
(6126, 'Wow, the grapevines smoking today!|So, you remember Karon that you helped out before? She said that Blood of Beast you brought her was really quality stuff. So now she wants you to get her some  Skeletons!'),
(6127, 'You might already know, but anyway I want to ask you for those Skeletons. A friend told me you can easily get the Apple of Moradon from  Skeleton Warriors. Makes sense I suppose!'),
(6128, 'One, two, and three Apples of Moradon! Success!'),
(6129, 'My trust in you knows no bounds, <selfname>!! Heh!'),
(6130, 'WoW, theres nothing you cant get!'),
(6131, 'Master! Clark is once again looking for some material...'),
(6132, 'Hmm... Rage is not someone who would do that... I dont know how good you are, but youve done a lot of good deeds for the country. Here, use this for purchasing goods for war. And, let me explain about ¡‹ere briefly.'),
(6133, 'Rage! My good, old friend...'),
(6134, 'One, two, and three Apples of Moradon! Success!'),
(6135, 'Ach, the enemys too bloody strong. At least  Cougar is by my side. To the death!'),
(6136, 'Are you new here?|Dont relax in Ronark Land. Its far too dangerous. If you dont wish to die, that is...'),
(6137, 'Master! Shaimers merchant caravan has been attacked by someone while on the move. You should go and see if they need assistance.'),
(6138, 'Phew... We were on the way to Moradon with all the stuff you found for us. Somewhere along the way though, bandits ambushed us, gave us a real good beating. weve patched ourselves up as best as we can, but... There are still some serious injuries, broken bones and so on...'),
(6139, 'Maybe its true, maybe not, but I heard if you grind <font color=@#660066@>Coarse Bone Powder</font> into a potion, it heals broken bones. Three men are wounded, so 3 portions would do it. Please help us.'),
(6140, '3 Coarse Bone Powders have been gathered. Hope its not too late.'),
(6141, 'Can you please hurry up? There isnt much time left before these injuries become fatal.'),
(6142, 'I dont know what to say... Im constantly in your debt. My staff are like my family to me. Thank you so, so much.'),
(6143, 'Master! Clarks merchant caravan has been attacked by someone while on the move. You should go and see if they need assistance.'),
(6144, 'Hmm... Rage is not someone who would do that... I dont know how good you are, but youve done a lot of good deeds for the country. Here, use this for purchasing goods for war. And, let me explain about ¡‹ere briefly.'),
(6145, 'Rage! My good, old friend...'),
(6146, '3 Coarse Bone Powders have been gathered. Hope its not too late.'),
(6147, 'I recommend you return to Karus and really get to know it. Youll be able to increase your strength fighting tougher monsters, and theres a lot of good adventures to be had around Karus heart, Luferson Castle. Would you like to go there?'),
(6148, 'Supply goods cannot just be given away unless theyre already personal property. Until the approval comes down from Rage...'),
(6149, 'Master! Merchant Shaimer seems to have good news, so lets go and find out^^'),
(6150, 'Theres a memorial service being held at Moradon Castle to give thanks for the peace, and theyre buying all the Memorial Goods from our boss. Great news, eh?'),
(6151, 'There is one small problem, though. A couple of Apples of Moradon were in route to Moradon for the memorial service, but heavy sand storms have seriously delayed their arrival. I cant just give up now, supplying these Memorial Goods is a huge honor for my family. Im really up against it this time...'),
(6152, 'Really, there isnt much time left. Please rush to deliver them to Shaimer.'),
(6153, 'Yikes, what am I going to do, there isnt much time to prepare for the Memorial service!'),
(6154, 'Nice~ Timing~~!! Thank you so much. Im going to tell everyone how <selfname> saved the service! Heh.'),
(6155, 'Master! Merchant Clark seems to have good news, so lets go and find out^^'),
(6156, 'Master, Do you know the village known as  Folk Village? Its a small village just outside Moradon Castle... Why not pay ¡ˆm a visit?'),
(6157, 'Master, Do you know the village known as  Folk Village? Its a small village just outside Moradon Castle... Why not pay ¡ˆm a visit?'),
(6158, 'Really, there isnt much time left. Please rush to deliver them to Clark.'),
(6159, 'You want me to just let you run around in the Armor supply?|You know the stuff in there is state property, right? Its forbidden to use any of it for personal use.'),
(6160, 'I dont know whats going, on but Im in a hurry here, so go talk with Quartermaster Osmond about it.'),
(6161, 'Master! Did you know that these days Orc Talismans are used for making weapons? Whys that? Would Shaimer know why?'),
(6162, 'Ah~ an Orc Talisman?|Ive heard that Moradons [Blacksmith] Heppa is always interested in making special weapons. He and I have traded a lot of stuff, and Orc Talismans have always been the most popular.'),
(6163, 'Phew... <selfname> knows too much about me!  Its really quite simple - Orc Talismans are found on Lard Orcs armor. One more thing - Lard Orcs are really ugly.'),
(6164, 'Is this an Orc Talisman? Looks like scrap to me...'),
(6165, 'Heppa wants 1,000 of em this month, and Im... hmm... exactly 7 short. Not bad.'),
(6166, 'Ah, so this months trade with Heppa was a success. Thanks.'),
(6167, 'Master! Did you know that these days Orc Talismans are used for making weapons? Whys that? Would Clark know why?'),
(6168, '<selfname>, youre quite a persevering soul, arent you? Okay, lets do this then. As I said before, I cannot supply goods unless theyre personally owned. But itd be different if you did something for Moradon.'),
(6169, 'Should I trust you? Ok, Im putting you in charge of the Folk Villages security. Occasionally, the  Spoiler attacks traveling merchants near the village. Ill give you the supply docket that you want, if you take care of the Spoilers.'),
(6170, 'Is this Orc Talisman? Looks like scrap to me...'),
(6171, '<selfname>, comeback after youve finished the current mission. You must be getting lazy, pilling up all the missions and not finishing them.'),
(6172, 'These are good talismans! [Blacksmith] Heppa will be pleased.|So Ill reward you well if you bring me an [Orc Talisman].'),
(6173, 'Master! I hear that Shaimer is secretly trading with El Morad... Thats no good! What does he think hes doing?'),
(6174, 'What... How did you know about that?|Nobody knows about it... Well, to be honest I dont know too much either. All I know is that sometime ago El Morad offered me to trade  Oaths of Darkness quietly so Ive been doing so, and nothing more than that.'),
(6175, 'I was going to make this trade the last one. I dont want to get in too deep with those people, its bad for business. Trading with them is just too much for my nerves to take, no matter how good the money is. And, I cant seem to fill the quantity for this last trade. Perhaps you could help me out here?'),
(6176, 'Youve got enough Oaths of Darkness now, Master. Lets skedaddle. It so creepy here, I get frightened every time.'),
(6177, 'By the way, what do these Oaths of Darkness do?'),
(6178, 'Ahh, great, thank you.|Ive lost weight worrying about this business. Im not going to get involved in this part, its too much for me.'),
(6179, 'Master! I hear that Clark is secretly trading with Karus... Thats no good! What does he think hes doing?'),
(6180, 'Im happy to report that the Spoiler-clearing mission is complete! Hee Hee!'),
(6181, 'Im happy to report that the Spoiler-clearing mission is complete! Hee Hee!'),
(6182, 'Youve got enough Oaths of Darkness now, Master. Lets skedaddle. It so creepy here. I get frightened every time.'),
(6183, 'So, how goes it?'),
(6184, 'You clearly defeated them. Nice work. I was afraid that I would regret giving you that mission,  but it looks like I was wrong on that one. Anyway, well done. Here, its the Boots of War Voucher I promised you. Show it to [Mercenary Supply Officer] Osmond.'),
(6185, 'Master. I think I hear the sound of Shaimer hitting jackpot even from here! Heh heh!'),
(6186, 'Ha Ha, fortune eh? Ive still got a long way to go yet! Ahh, Silver Feather-based clothes have become this seasons must-have items for our Noble women. If youre not wearing  Silver Feather clothes, youre nobody!  The feathers are well known for their amazing color and incredible softness.'),
(6187, 'But, as always, supply is being outstripping by demand. Ive hired some renowned Moradon hunters to gather the feathers for me, but it aint easy because the  Meganterions are really brutal beasts. Ahem... <selfname>, perhaps you might have better luck in this endeavor? Heh Heh.'),
(6188, 'Phew! Master, you really tried hard. Looks like they really are hard to get.'),
(6189, 'I need about 10 of ¡ˆm. Keep up the good work <selfname>! Hee Hee!'),
(6190, 'Great work <selfname>, thanks to your effort, Moradons ladies are still the best-dressed! Infinite thanks!'),
(6191, 'Master. I think I hear the sound of Clark hitting jackpot even from here! Heh heh!'),
(6192, 'Just wearing the Boots of War on their own without the rest of the War set doesnt look so good, Master. Couldnt you get the other parts too?'),
(6193, 'Just wearing the Boots of War on their own without the rest of the War set doesnt look so good, Master. Couldnt you get the other parts too?'),
(6194, 'Phew! Master, you really tried hard. Looks like they really are hard to get.'),
(6195, 'Cougar? Hes an old friend. Weve seen a few wars together.'),
(6196, 'Thanks to you, <selfname>, I can provide the textiles in time again.|If you hand me the [Silver Feather] I will give you a reward.'),
(6197, 'Dead characters cannot enter.'),
(6198, '[Name Change Scroll]You must retrieve all of items in your mail box before changing character name.'),
(6199, 'The stars come out and the moon shines like never before. All signs of a fresh start and a new beginning. Come, I will bless the people with my sword and theyll be united in their strength and resolve. And when they are united so, the world will look on in wonder at the might of their souls.'),
(6200, 'When 10,000 Statues of Akarra have been gathered, a blessing of EXP will fall upon all Karus.'),
(6201, 'When 10,000 Statues of Akarra have been gathered, a blessing of EXP will fall upon all El Morad.'),
(6202, 'Recently, someones been pilfering the military funds. I suspect my personal slave, but I want you to find out who it is for sure.'),
(6203, 'Move aside please, little one. Youll have to be much stronger if you want to talk to me.'),
(6204, 'Hey! Arent you the famous <selfname>? Im El Morad Castles resident Nobleman, Alpuer Kane the 4th. I heard you were the ¡oessenger of Love between Karuss Warrior and the beautiful Nusram. Like many of our people, Ive quite an interest in their sad love story.'),
(6205, 'Listen, I want to help you. If you give me 10 [Will of War] Ill give the matter my full attention.'),
(6206, 'Listen, I want to help you. If you bring me 10 [Will of War] Ill give the matter my full attention.'),
(6207, 'First of all, find my slave. I suspect he might know about the missing military funds. See what you can find out. Ill reward you with a Red Treasure Chest! By the way, my slaves name is Triger.'),
(6208, '<selfname>, what kind of person is this Sentinel that Alpuers talking about?'),
(6209, 'Back so soon? Thats good then. Anyway, thank you for your all your effort, its most appreciated. Here, by way of saying ¡—hanks to you... Right now, theres a suspicious Sentinel in Moradon. Im  off to check him out. Perhaps I will see you later? Until then.'),
(6210, 'Havent you find him yet?'),
(6211, 'Say what? Is my master looking for me? Bugger. What did I do wrong this time then? He accused me of stealing 4 gold bars last time. But, this is my fate, so off  I go. I¡l go and attend to him now. See you around. Perhaps..'),
(6212, 'See you around. Perhaps..'),
(6213, 'Where am I?'),
(6214, 'You shouldnt trust the nobles too much. They look elegant and benign on the outside, but inside theyre rotten to the core.'),
(6215, '(Surprise~!) Holly~ You scared me! Have you heard the rumor? The Nobles are at war... ah~ never mind. Just pretend you didnt hear anything.'),
(6216, 'Yeah, I know. I heard the nobles pretend to work for peace, but in fact are only trying to prolong the violence. Gods know why theyd do that... But I hate them for it because Im the one who actually has to go out there and fight, when Im recruited.'),
(6217, 'I also heard that Alpuer Kane the 4th is involved in some fishy business. He looks like he stinks anyway. Ha. Thats about all I know. You should meet Alpuer Kane the 4th yourself if you want more details.'),
(6218, 'Who says talk is cheap!'),
(6219, 'Give this to the Karus warrior, Klasras.'),
(6220, 'Give this to El Morads Lady Nusram.'),
(6221, 'Eh? So, <selfname>, we meet again! Do you think our destinies might be meeting briefly? (Smirk)~ Do me a favor would you-'),
(6222, 'Im disturbed by the fact that even though we strive for peace, the enemy continues to slowly invade our land. So I was wondering. Wouldnt peace fall on the Adonisian Continent if Klasras and Nusrams love were to be given full bloom?'),
(6223, 'So, let us first gather 20 [Will of War]. Well talk about the rest later.'),
(6224, 'Will you give this to Klasras? Tell her its a small present in the name of El Morad. Ill give you 3 Fragments of Sloth if you deliver it safely.'),
(6225, 'Good job <selfname>, well done!'),
(6226, 'Ah~ You delivered it? Excellent, herere the Fragments as promised. It wont be long now before their love unites them in time and place... Im so glad...'),
(6227, 'Deliver it safely please.'),
(6228, 'Send word of the good news to my brother!'),
(6229, 'Send word of the good news to my brother!'),
(6230, 'WoW! This is... precious... Thank you. Thank you so much for caring about the two of us.'),
(6231, 'Master, You should return to that Alpuer Kane the 4th now and give him the message.'),
(6232, 'Master, How about sharing the good news with Nusram? Ohhh, itd be good if you could take 20 [Will of War] with you, too.'),
(6233, 'Is that what the nobility said? Really? Im delighted to hear it. Ahh, the sky is so clear, they must be celebrating for us. I must tell my brother the good news...'),
(6234, 'You dont have any [Will of War] with you though. Show me your Will. Show me 20, that should be enough.'),
(6235, 'My brother is the Nameless Warrior. You should have seen him around the Tomb. Hell be delighted when he hears about this. You will help me, wont you?'),
(6236, 'What...Is that really true? Finally, there might be an end to this ancestral war. Peace will come and blanket us, and I will even be able to close my eyes and rest. The most amazing thing is that the nobles are encouraging and blessing this peace. I still cant believe it...'),
(6237, 'Anyway, thank you so much. I dont have much to give, but please accept this. Please, send my appreciation to Alpuer Kane the 4th when you see him.'),
(6238, 'Master, How about telling ol Alpuer Kane the 4th about all this good stuff? Just checking, but you do have 20 [Will of War], right?'),
(6239, 'Ahh, how is my sister Nusram doing these days.')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(6240, 'Welcome. Ive just received some Holy Water directly from El Morads own King, and Id like you to personally give it to them as a symbol of the peace.'),
(6241, 'Long time no see. If you want to talk to me, youll need 20 [Will of War].'),
(6242, 'When you give the Holy Water to Klasras, youll be helping the people of his nation to receive the Worship of Peace. Ill pay you 2 Fragments of Jealousy. Will you do it?'),
(6243, 'You must give this Holy Water to Klasras.'),
(6244, 'You must give this Holy Water to Nusram.'),
(6245, 'Heh Heh Heh... Yes, yes. You did just as I asked, well done. Peace! What bloody peace? History is written in war and blood. Ha ha ha ha!! Those who do not write history, die in it instead!! Well done anyway. Heres your cut. Mwuahahahahaha!!!'),
(6246, 'You must deliver this!'),
(6247, 'When you give the Holy Water to Klasras, youll be helping the people of his nation to receive the Worship of Peace. I will pay you 2 Fragments of Jealousy, or 25 million EXP. Will you do this?'),
(6248, 'Whats that? You should see the look on your face! Youre no match for me yet! Mwuahahaha~ Finally, the war has begun!!'),
(6249, 'Huh! Did Alpuer really give this to you? How nice... Well then, I accept it with gratitude.'),
(6250, '(~worried~) Errr What... What is this? How... How could you... rr...Errr..argh...err...'),
(6251, 'Why wont you give it to me?'),
(6252, 'No, something is wrong... Oh gods... I feel the war is almost upon us... Aieeee! Where... Wheres my weapon? My weapon is missing! Gone! It was a +8 Dagger!'),
(6253, 'What am I going to do? I was wearing a Dagger (+8) a moment ago, and now... Blast!'),
(6254, 'Phew! Thank you so much! Please, for finding my Dagger, choose whatever you want.'),
(6256, 'Im busy because I havent found my dagger yet. Hmm...'),
(6257, 'Eh? Isnt that short sword actually a Dagger (+8)? You going to give it to me or what?'),
(6258, 'Recently, someones been pilfering the military funds. I suspect my personal slave, but I want you to find out who it is for sure.'),
(6259, 'Move aside please, little one. Youll have to be much stronger if you want to talk to me.'),
(6260, 'Hey! Arent you the famous <selfname>? Im Lufersons resident Nobility, Chronoris Shes. I heard you were the ¡oessenger of Love between Karuss Warrior and the beautiful Nusram. Like many of our people, Ive quite an interest in their sad love story.'),
(6261, 'Listen, I want to help you. If you give me 10 [Will of War] Ill give the matter my full attention.'),
(6262, 'I want to help you. If you bring me 10 [Will of War] I will consider it.'),
(6263, 'First, find my slave. I suspect he might know about the missing military funds. See what you can find out. Ill reward you with a Red Treasure Chest! By the way, my slaves name is Takatu.'),
(6264, '<selfname>, what kind of person is this Sentinel that Chronoriss talking about?'),
(6265, 'Back so soon? Thats good then. Anyway, thank you for your all your effort, its most appreciated. Here, by way of saying ¡—hanks to you... Right now, theres a suspicious Sentinel in Moradon. Im  off to check him out. Perhaps I will see you later? Until then.'),
(6266, 'Havent you find him yet?'),
(6267, 'What? Is my master looking for me? Phew... What did I do wrong this time... He accused me of stealing 4 gold bars last time... But, this is my fate so I must go. I must go to my master now. Then I will see you next time.'),
(6268, 'Then I will see you next time'),
(6269, 'Where am I?'),
(6270, 'I also heard that Chronoris Shes is involved in some fishy business. He looks like he stinks anyway. Ha. Thats about all I know. You should meet Chronoris Shes yourself for more detail...'),
(6271, 'Eh? So, <selfname>, we meet again! Do you think our destinies might be meeting briefly? (Smirk)~ Do me a favor would you-'),
(6272, 'Im disturbed by the fact that even though we strive for peace, the enemy continues to slowly invade our land. So I was wondering. Wouldnt peace fall on the Adonisian Continent if Klasras and Nusrams love were to be given full bloom?'),
(6273, 'So, let us first gather 20 [Will of War]. Well talk about the rest later.'),
(6274, 'Will you give this to Nusram? Tell her its a small present in the name of Karus. I will give you 3 Fragments of Sloth if you deliver it safely.'),
(6275, 'Good job <selfname>, well done!'),
(6276, 'Ah~ You delivered it? Excellent, herere the Fragments as promised. It wont be long now before their love unites them in time and place... Im so glad...'),
(6277, 'Deliver it safely please.'),
(6278, 'WoW! This is... precious... Thank you. Thank you so much for caring about the two of us.'),
(6279, 'Master, You should go see Chronoris Shes now and give him the message.'),
(6280, 'Master, How about sharing the good news with Klasras? Ohhh, itd be good if you could take 20 [Will of War] with you, too.'),
(6281, 'Is that what the nobility said? Really? Im delighted to hear it. Ahh, the sky is so clear, they must be celebrating for us. I must tell my brother the good news...'),
(6282, 'You dont have any [Will of War] with you though. Show me your Will. Show me 20, that should be enough.'),
