(6299, 'Choose one. Its a choice of two. Mwuahahaha!!'),
(6300, 'The 12th Warrior Red Devil uniform is a reward for a KO World Cup victory.|Be ware that you can only wear it for a week. Its then removed after the 13th of July.'),
(6301, 'You need a [Certificate of Red Devil uniform top] to receive the Red Devil top. A [Certificate of Red Devil uniform] can be found during World Cup events, such as in treasure chests.'),
(6302, 'Choose the one you want.'),
(6303, 'First, tell Alpuer that I found the slave.'),
(6304, 'First, tell Choronis that I found the slave.'),
(6305, 'Gah! I think you were deceived by Alpuer, <selfname>!'),
(6306, 'Gah! I think you were deceived by Chronoris, <selfname>!!'),
(6307, 'Choose one. Its a choice of two. Mwuahahaha!!'),
(6308, 'Choose the one you want.'),
(6309, 'I want peace to come quickly.'),
(6310, 'I want the peace to come quick.'),
(6311, 'What...Is that really true? Finally, there might be an end to this ancestral war. Peace will come and blanket us, and I will even be able to close my eyes and rest. The most amazing thing is that the nobles are encouraging and blessing this peace. I still cant believe it...'),
(6312, '(~smirk~) My name is Chard... People call me ¡gnchanter Chard. Do you understand the meaning of these drums?'),
(6313, 'War. The drums announce the outbreak of war. Every nation busies its self preparing their war supplies,  calling softly under their breath for blood. Will you join them?'),
(6314, 'If you had the true blood of a knight flowing in you, I dont think you would just sit by and watch. Tell me, whats it like? Show me you have the will to protect this nation by standing at the front lines, and I will awaken your sleeping potential with each Talisman you bring me.'),
(6315, 'I will always help you if you need it. See you then...'),
(6316, 'For me to help you each time, I will need 15 [Will of War].'),
(6317, 'First, bring the 15 [Will of War].'),
(6318, 'Select the ability you wish to unlock.'),
(6319, 'In the Lunar war, CONT cannot be charged.'),
(6320, 'In the Lunar war, CONT cannot be charged.'),
(6321, 'Hmm... Your inventory is full.'),
(6322, 'Hmm... Your inventory is full.'),
(6323, 'Hmm... Your inventory is full.'),
(6324, 'Hmm... Your inventory is full.'),
(6325, 'Apologies for any inconvenience caused by the ¡Œtem disappearing bug.|Please keep the Power-Up items until the 27th of July if you have suffered from the bug.'),
(6326, 'You are not on the compensation list.|You have already been compensated or you are not registered. Please contact our Client Center via the website.'),
(6327, 'You do not have enough space in the inventory.|You need 3 empty shelves in the inventory to receive compensation.'),
(6328, 'Enjoy Knight Online!'),
(6329, 'Sorry, but this mission can only support 40 players at one time. Come back in a little while.'),
(6330, 'Youve already accomplished your mission.|See you tomorrow.'),
(6331, 'Welcome.|The most important thing now is intelligence. War with El Morad is unavoidable, so we must be ready. Our first priority is to clarify the status of El Morads military forces, their strategy and any preparations theyre making.'),
(6332, 'In order to undertake this mission youll need 30 [Will of War]. You need to give me 15 of them before the infiltration can begin.|Are you in?'),
(6333, 'Retrieve the Classified Document from the Secret Locker in El Morad Castle. I will make a separate payment to you for this.'),
(6334, 'You havent enough Wills of War. You need to show me 30 [Will of War] to engage the mission.'),
(6335, 'One more thing!|Ill increase your reward, if you can also bring me the keys from El Morads Asga Village, Laiva Village and Doda camp. Got that? The keys are kept in each villages communal Locker. Good luck.'),
(6336, 'Your mission is up to here|See you tomorrow.'),
(6337, 'Well done!|The Goddess of Victory must be on our side! Ha Ha, heres your reward.'),
(6338, 'Well done!|The Goddess of Victory must be on our side! Shame, you earned the Classified Document only after you were killed. Youve got to get it whilst alive! Then Ill increase your award.'),
(6339, 'Good, you brought the key.|Select your reward. In return, youll have to give me 3 keys for the [Green Treasure Chest], 2 keys for the [Red Treasure Chest] and 1 key for a [Lottery Ticket]. Got it?'),
(6340, 'Im disappointed tbh.|You didnt get the Classified Document or the keys. Nub. Try again tomorrow.'),
(6341, 'Your inventory is bursting. Come back after youve cleared some space.'),
