(6372, 'Im sorry, the Lunar War is starting soon, and I cant give out any missions in the hour before it begins.'),
(6373, 'Im sorry, the Lunar War is starting soon, and I cant give out any missions in the hour before it begins.'),
(6374, 'Sorry, but salary and booty cant be handed out between 6:15pm and 7pm. Please rememeber.'),
(6375, 'Sorry, but salary and booty cant be handed out between 6:15pm and 7pm. Please rememeber.'),
