(6435, 'There are many trials in the Cave of the Red Dragon. As soon as you enter for your Knight Squad test,  everyone else in your clan will be summoned to your side. There is no distinction down there between enemy and ally. Anyone can attack anyone else, friend or foe. This is what makes it so challenging. Only the best and strongest combatant will earn the [Emblem Royal].'),
(6436, 'Consequences include the loss of EXP, becoming trapped temporarily, or losing the contest to another Knight Squad, in which case the [Emblem Royal] goes with them, of course.'),
(6437, 'Despite all of this, you must focus on one thing-|You,  <selfname>, Knight Squad Leader, must physically get  the [Emblem Royal] yourself! By which I mean, your allies can help you to defeat Red Dragon in combat, but they wont be able to loot the emblem. Thats up to you. Bear it in mind, anyway. I wish you luck.'),
(6438, 'Did you bring everything required for promotion to Royal Knight Squad?'),
(6439, 'Hmm, you have insufficient Noah. You need 100 million Noah for your Formal Night Squad registration fee.'),
(6440, 'You need the [Emblem Royal] from Red Dragon to be promoted to Royal Knight Squad.')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(6441, 'Congratulations on your promotion to Royal Knight Squad! Show us youre worthy of the title!'),
(6442, 'Sorry, but this test can only be attempted by a 1st  Class training Knight Squad. Its a useless test to you, <selfname>.'),
(6443, 'Sorry, but this test can only be attempted by a 1st  Class Formal Knight Squad. Its a useless test to you, <selfname>.'),
(6444, 'You need 3rd Clan qualifications as a proof of national service to become a training Knight Squad. Also, you must prove your courage and ability. Right now, Caitharos is waiting to test you in the Coliseum. You have to fight Isiloon and retrieve the [Key of Glory], as well as your training Knight Squad dues of 10 million Noah.'),
(6445, 'Congratulations! <selfname>s squad is now an approved National Combat Unit. I hope you achieve many honorable things trying for the Formal Knight Squad position in the future.'),
(6446, 'Sorry, but to get your Knight Squad to the next class, you must undergo the Royal Knight Squad promotion test. Would you like to give it a shot?'),
(6447, 'Sorry, try applying for promotion after youve been made a Formal Knight Squad.'),
(6448, 'You are already the highest-class Knight Squad.'),
(6449, 'Would you like to raise your Knight Squads class?|You need 45,000 Knight Squad saving points to be promoted to 1st Class Royal Knight Squad.'),
(6450, 'Congratulations!|Your Knight Squad class has been raised a level. Well done indeed!'),
(6451, 'Sorry, but your Knight Squads saving points are insufficient. You need 45,000 points to rise to the next class.'),
(6452, 'Sorry, but your Knight Squads saving points are insufficient. You need 40,000 points to rise to the next class.'),
(6453, 'Sorry, but your Knight Squads saving points are insufficient. You need 35,000 points to rise to the next class.'),
(6454, 'Sorry, but your Knight Squads saving points are insufficient. You need 30,000 points to rise to the next class.'),
(6455, 'Sorry, but your Knight Squads saving points are insufficient. You need 20,000 points to rise to the next class.'),
(6456, 'Sorry, but your Knight Squads saving points are insufficient. You need 15,000 points to rise to the next class.'),
(6457, 'Sorry, but your Knight Squads saving points are insufficient. You need 10,000 points to rise to the next class.'),
(6458, 'Sorry, but your Knight Squads saving points are insufficient. You need 7,000 points to rise to the next class.'),
(6459, 'Sorry, but class applications can only be made by the Squad Leader or Co-Leader.'),
(6460, 'Sorry, but class applications can only be made by the Squad Leader or Co-Leader.'),
(6461, 'Sorry, but your Knight Squads saving points are insufficient. You need 25,000 points to be promoted to Royal Knight Squad.'),
(6462, 'Sorry, but the saving points in the Knight Squad is insufficient. You need 25,000 points to be promoted to Royal Knight Squad.'),
(6463, 'Would you like to be ported out after the promotion test?'),
(6464, 'Would you like to raise your Knight Squads class?|You need 40,000 Knight Squad saving points to be promoted to 2nd Class Royal Knight Squad.'),
(6465, 'Would you like to raise your Knight Squads class?|You need 35,000 Knight Squad saving points to be promoted to 3rd Class Royal Knight Squad.'),
(6466, 'Would you like to raise your Knight Squads class?|You need 30,000 Knight Squad saving points to be promoted to 4th Class Royal Knight Squad.'),
(6467, 'Would you like to raise your Knight Squads class?|You need 20,000 Knight Squad saving points to be promoted to 1st Class Formal Knight Squad.'),
(6468, 'Would you like to raise your Knight Squads class?|You need 15,000 Knight Squad saving points to be promoted to 2nd Class Formal Knight Squad.'),
(6469, 'Would you like to raise your Knight Squads class?|You need 10,000 Knight Squad saving points to be promoted to 3rd Class Formal Knight Squad.'),
(6470, 'Would you like to raise your Knight Squads class?|You need 7,000 Knight Squad saving points to be promoted to 4th Class Formal Knight Squad.'),
(6471, 'Would you like to raise your Knight Squads class?|You need 40,000 Knight Squad saving points to be promoted to 2nd Class Royal Knight Squad.'),
(6472, 'Would you like to raise your Knight Squads class?|You need 35,000 Knight Squad saving points to be promoted to 3rd Class Royal Knight Squad.'),
(6473, 'Would you like to raise your Knight Squads class?|You need 30,000 Knight Squad saving points to be promoted to 4th Class Royal Knight Squad.'),
(6474, 'Would you like to raise your Knight Squads class?|You need 20,000 Knight Squad saving points to be promoted to 1st Class Formal Knight Squad.'),
(6475, 'Would you like to raise your Knight Squads class?|You need 15,000 Knight Squad saving points to be promoted to 2nd Class Formal Knight Squad.'),
(6476, 'Would you like to raise your Knight Squads class?|You need 10,000 Knight Squad saving points to be promoted to 3rd Class Formal Knight Squad.'),
(6477, 'Would you like to raise your Knight Squads class?|You need 7,000 Knight Squad saving points to be promoted to 4th Class Formal Knight Squad.'),
(6478, 'Finally, the war against Karus has begun. I wonder if the Karus are ready for us. El Morad is already fully prepared and ready to go. HA!!~'),
(6479, 'In the war against Karus, <selfname>, I want to see some serious results from you. Youll bring me [Will of Victory] as proof of your deeds, and I will reward you for every 10 I see from you. Just so you know, [Will of War] is earned for enemy player kills. You got that? Good, now get out there and kick some!'),
(6480, 'Ah~ [War of Will], great. Thats great, good work <selfname>. Heres a little something for you. But remember, the war against Karus has only just begun. Keep bringing me those Wills, for the greater glory of El Morad!'),
(6481, 'Erm, Your inventory appears to be full. Show some initiative and clear out the junk eh?'),
(6482, 'Finally, the war against El Morad has begun. I wonder if El Morad is ready for us. Karus is already fully prepared and ready to go. HA!!~'),
(6483, 'In the war against El Morad, <selfname>, I want to see some serious results from you. Youll bring me [Will of Victory] as proof of your deeds, and I will reward you for every 10 I see from you. Just so you know, [Will of War] is earned for enemy player kills. You got that? Good, now get out there and kick some!'),
(6484, 'Ah~ [War of Will], great. Thats great, good work <selfname>. Heres a little something for you. But remember, the war against El Morad has only just begun. Keep bringing me those Wills, for the greater glory of Karus!'),
(6485, 'Erm, Your inventory appears to be full. Show some initiative and clear out the junk eh?'),
(6486, 'This is the Forgotten Temple. Its a very holy place. I cant allow you to enter, all covered in sin like that. Go and wash it all off and then come back.'),
(6487, 'Sorry. This is an examination period. Please wait a moment.'),
(6488, 'You need a [Gryphons Armor Voucher] to get the Gryphon Armor. A [Gryphons Armor Voucher] can be purchased from the Power-up store.'),
(6489, 'You have selected Gryphon Armor HP+200 Nice isnt it? Do you really want it?'),
(6490, 'You have selected Gryphon Armor Defense +30. Nice isnt it? Do you really want it?'),
(6491, 'You have selected Gryphon Armor EXP Gain Rate +4%. Nice isnt it? Do you really want it?'),
(6492, 'You have selected Gryphon Armor Noah Drop Rate +6%. Nice isnt it? Do you really want it?'),
(6493, 'You have selected Gryphon Armor HP+100 Nice isnt it? Do you really want it?'),
(6494, 'You have selected Gryphon Armor Defense +20. Nice isnt it? Do you really want it?'),
(6495, 'You have selected Gryphon Armor EXP Gain Rate +2%. Nice isnt it? Do you really want it?'),
(6496, 'You have selected Gryphon Armor Noah Drop Rate +3%. Nice isnt it? Do you really want it?'),
(6497, 'You need a [Gryphons Helmet Voucher] to get the Gryphon Helmet. A [Gryphons Helmet Voucher] can be purchased from the Power-up store.'),
(6498, 'Theres an SAT event going on now.|If you bring me the SAT item, Ill give you something good.|#Event Date: 16th of November to the 23rd of November, before  examination time.'),
(6499, 'If you bring me 10 each of the [S], [A] and [T] Talismans, for a total of 30 in one go, Ill trade ¡ˆm for a [Pass Notice].|# Pass Notice: Increases EXP gain by 20% for an hour.'),
(6500, 'Ah, one more thing! The [S], [A] and [T] talismans are dropped by all monsters.'),
(6501, 'Well done. Best of luck to everyone sitting the SAT test today.'),
(6502, 'Yes, its 10 each, total of 30.|Do you want to trade them for a [Pass Notice]?'),
(6503, 'Hmm... Im sure I said 5 Kekoon Gallbladders...'),
(6504, 'Good, good, just as I expected.|Now Ill tell you about the Upgrade Scroll (Low Class). Open your ears.'),
(6505, 'To buff extra strength into a weapon, you need the right Upgrade Scroll.'),
(6506, 'Go to the Magic Anvil and upgrade your weapon.'),
(6507, 'Have you done your homework yet?'),
(6508, 'The Enhancement Scroll (Low Class) that I gave you is the spell you use to upgrade the weapon with. For the record, weapons are divided into three classes -  Low Class, Medium Class and High Class.'),
(6509, 'Now, go and do the Iron bar Mission(Quest)again.'),
(6511, 'I dont know if youve noticed yet, but  when you do an upgrade, you have to use the appropriate spell for each class of weapon. i.e. Low Class Scrolls for Low Class Weapons, Medium Scrolls for Medium Weapons, and so on.'),
(6512, 'Well, come back with that weapon I gave you and upgrade it with an Enhancement Scroll (Low Class). As I said before, the upgrade must be done at the Magic anvil. Youll find it over by the Scroll Merchant Charon.'),
(6513, 'Master! Youve successfully upgraded the weapon and earned a Magical Enhancement Rock in the process. Lets go back to Heppa and see what he says.'),
(6514, 'Master! Youve successfully upgraded the weapon and earned a Magical Enhancement Rock in the process. Lets go back to Heppa and see what he says.'),
(6515, 'So youve done a Weapon Enhancement Upgrade eh? How was it? Well, youll have many opportunities to buff your weapons, so better get a grip on the process. So,  shall we take it to the next level?|Are you ready?'),
(6516, 'Im going to tell you about the weapon  Attack Power attribute. The Attack Power attribute covers   additional damage beyond your weapons normal Attack Power. What do you think so far? Opened your ears up already eh? Ha Ha!'),
(6517, 'Do me a favor, if you want to know more. Im making a new thing here, but I dont have enough Iron bar. Bring me   3 Iron bar and 3,000 Noah. Ill tell you the rest after that.'),
(6518, 'Master! Right, the Iron bar and Noah is in hand, lets hump it back to Blacksmith Heppa.'),
(6519, 'Master! Right, the Iron bar and Noah is in hand, lets hump it back to Blacksmith Heppa.'),
(6520, 'Oh, right. Well done. Ok, I can stick to the weapon production schedule now. Humm... First, take this Elemental Scroll (Low Class item).'),
(6521, 'Hmm... You dont want to help me? Disappointing, isnt it?'),
(6522, 'Master! [Blacksmith] Hepa is looking for you again! They said they were going to practice how to attach the attributes! Anyway, lets go there!'),
(6523, 'Master! [Blacksmith] Hepa is looking for you again! They said they were going to practice how to attach the attributes! Anyway, lets go there!'),
(6524, 'In addition to the strengthening of weapon, it is the provision of weapon attributes which can make the weapons strong! Then shall we provide the weapon with attributes as a practice? Purchase dagger (+1) from the [Arms Dealer] Gargameth and the [Elemental Scroll (Low Class Item)] from the [Scroll Merchant] Charon and try to attach the attributes!'),
(6525, 'The dagger (+1) can be purchased from the [Arms Dealer] Gargameth and the [Elemental Scroll (Low Class Item)] from the [Elemental Scroll (Low Class Item)] Charon! Be sure to remember that it is the [Elemental Scroll (Low Class Item)]'),
(6526, 'Master! I was successful in strengthening the attributes! Hurry up and go to [Blacksmith] Hepa!'),
(6527, 'Master! I was successful in strengthening the attributes! Hurry up and go to [Blacksmith] Hepa!'),
(6528, 'Oh, Ok, youve done it. Right, lets wrap this up. I said that theres a way to reveal the attribute effect on (+7) Normal Upgrade items, remember? Well, you can do that with a Reverse Scroll. Using a Reverse Scroll on a weapon will tell you what it could do,   saving you from having to upgrade it until (+8).'),
(6529, 'Youve done a fine job so far.|I know it sounds complicated, but once youve done it a few times, itll all come clear and be a great asset to you. Here, its nothing great, but take it anyway. Perhaps itll help you somewhere along the way. Think of it as an investment? HAHAHAHA!!!'),
(6530, 'Oh, whilst youre out and about, could you bring me the  Magical Enhancement Rock from Menissiah? Thanks. Sorry to keep bothering you.'),
(6531, 'Bring me the weapon I gave you after the step  one enhancement.'),
(6532, 'Bring me 3 Iron bar and 3,000 Noah.|Well talk about the rest later.'),
(6533, 'Bring me the weapon I gave you after you did the Attack Power attribute upgrade. Use the Elemental Scroll (Low Class) with the  Magic anvil and then upgrade. I trust you can handle that.'),
(6534, 'You were successful, werent you! Let me see.'),
(6535, 'Come to me if you need more Armor. Keep helping me, and Ill keep supplying the Armor. Anyway, do you know about Armor Upgrades?'),
(6536, 'Come to me if you need more Armor. If <selfname> continues to help me, Ill always supply em with Armor.'),
(6637, 'Theres nobody who knows more than [Blacksmith] Heppa about upgrading stuff. Go see him in Moradon.'),
(6638, ' Do you know anything about <font color=@#990000@>armor upgrade</font> by any chance?'),
(6639, 'Come to me if you need more Armor. If <selfname> continues to help me, Ill always supply em with Armor.'),
(6640, 'Theres nobody who knows more than [Blacksmith] Heppa about upgrading stuff. Go see him in Moradon.'),
(6641, 'Master! Remember about Armor Upgrades from Moradons [Blacksmith] Heppa.'),
(6642, 'Master! Remember about Armor Upgrades from Moradons [Blacksmith] Heppa.'),
(6643, 'Its been while Ive seen you.|Guess you want to hear about Armor Upgrades then? Armor Upgrades arent much different from Weapon Upgrades. Whilst weapons have upgrades for their Attack Power attribute, armor has  Enchant Upgrades for their  Ability attribute.'),
(6644, 'Before we go any further, I want to check your understanding of the armor Enhancement Upgrades. Bring me your  Full Plate Boots after youve done a +5 Enhancement Upgrade on ¡ˆm.'),
(6645, 'Before we go any further, I want to check your understanding of the armor Enhancement Upgrades. Bring me your  Rogue Full Plate Boots after youve done a +5 Enhancement Upgrade on ¡ˆm.'),
(6646, 'Before we go any further, I want to check your understanding of the armor Enhancement Upgrades. Bring me your  Crystal Plate Boots after youve done a +5 Enhancement Upgrade on ¡ˆm.'),
(6647, 'Before we go any further, I want to check your understanding of the armor Enhancement Upgrades. Bring me your  Priest Full Plate Boots after youve done a +5 Enhancement Upgrade on ¡ˆm.'),
(6648, 'Fair enough, you seem to have the hang of it.|I like you, youre good. Heh. Now then, let me explain Enchant Upgrades.'),
(6649, 'Youre familiar with the upgrade process, right? Right.'),
(6650, 'The Enchant Upgrade is only for Armor Upgrades. Im thinkin of armors Ability attribute here... Enhancement Upgrades   give your armor a bonus ability by unlocking an extra Strength, Agility, Health, Intelligence or Magic attribute.'),
(6651, 'As usual, the Scroll has to be in the same Class as the armor, and again, you can only upgrade a piece of armor once per scroll. One cool thing is that you can choose which ability attribute to unlock, but once youve done that you can never change it. Ok?'),
(6652, 'Okay, bring me  10 Fang of Wolfman. Do that, and Ill give you an Enchant Scroll. I need the fangs for a weapon Im making right now. Deal?'),
(6653, 'Sorry, Im a little tired at the moment. Lets give it a rest eh?'),
(6654, 'Master! Youve got all the teeth now. Lets head back to Heppa and exchange them for the Enchant Scroll.'),
(6655, 'Master! Youve got all the teeth now. Lets head back to Heppa and exchange them for the Enchant Scroll.'),
(6656, 'Thanks. Choose the scroll you want...'),
(6657, 'Hmm... I actually asked for 10 Fangs.'),
(6658, 'The weather today is incredible isnt it? I really need some major downtime. Well talk about it next time.'),
(6659, 'As I said before, once an Enchant Upgrade ability is unlocked on the Armor, it cant be changed or taken back. So think carefully before you go wasting scrolls and putting useless enchantments on things.'),
(6660, 'Okay, how about giving the ol Enchant Upgrade scroll a whirl? Bring me your  Full Plate Boots (+5) after youve done an Enchant Upgrade.'),
(6661, 'Okay, how about giving the ol Enchant Upgrade scroll a whirl? Bring me your  Rogue Plate Boots (+5) after youve done an Enchant Upgrade.'),
(6662, 'Okay, how about giving the ol Enchant Upgrade scroll a whirl? Bring me your  Crystal Plate Boots (+5) after youve done an Enchant Upgrade.'),
(6663, 'Okay, how about giving the ol Enchant Upgrade scroll a whirl? Bring me your  Priest Plate Boots (+5) after youve done an Enchant Upgrade.'),
(6664, 'You done the Enchant Upgrade yet?'),
(6665, 'Great, you did it. Ha Ha! Cant you feel the armor giving you an extra edge with its new Ability attribute? Anyway, I think at last Ive told you everything I know. Here, have this on me. Consider it a ¡Šraduation present from the School of Heppa! Ha Ha Ha!'),
(6666, 'Bring me your Full Plate Boots after youve done a +4 Enhancement Upgrade on ¡ˆm.'),
(6667, 'Bring me your Rogue Plate Boots after youve done a +4 Enhancement Upgrade on ¡ˆm.'),
(6668, 'Bring me your Crystal Robe Boots after youve done a +4 Enhancement Upgrade on ¡ˆm.'),
(6669, 'Bring me your Priest Full Plate Boots after youve done a +4 Enhancement Upgrade on ¡ˆm.'),
(6670, 'Can you get me those 10 Fang of Wolfman for the weapon Im working on? Thanks.'),
(6671, 'Okay, this time youre going to do an Enchant Upgrade!'),
(6672, 'Huh, long time no see. Whats up?'),
(6673, 'Oh, really? I thought Heppa would come himself... Magical Enhancement Rock!! This is what Heppa is looking for, right? Very well, its his again.'),
(6674, 'What kind of fun will today bring us?'),
(6675, 'Yeah, Id love to hear about your Weapon Upgrade.I*First, though, you need to hear about the  Scroll (Low Class) creation Quest.'),
(6676, 'Plus, I have a favor to ask. I need a   Magical Enhancement Rock, a rare thing indeed. Its for this weapon Im making.'),
(6677, 'I know that  [Merchants Daughter] Menissiah has a Magical Enhancement Rock. Ive already contacted her about it after hearing that she had one in her collection. Id go over and talk to her myself, but this knee is killing me (~whimper~)'),
(6678, 'Anyway, first do the Weapon Upgrade, then you can bring me the  Magical Enhancement Rock. Menissiah will hand it over to ya.'),
(6679, 'And on your way back, grab that  Magical Enhancement Rock for me will ya?. Tell Menissiah you came on my behalf.'),
(6680, 'Armor Upgrade... Sort out some armor that you like. Ill explain everything later.'),
(6681, 'Master, as I recall, youll get the boots from Castles [Mercenary Adjutant] Rage after completing the Full Plate Armor (Boots) Quest. Remember?'),
(6682, 'Master, as I recall, youll get the boots from Castles [Mercenary Adjutant] Rage after completing the Full Plate Armor (Boots) Quest. Remember?'),
(6683, 'Gj master, the upgrade was successful. Lets go back to ol Heppa now.'),
(6684, 'Gj master, the upgrade was successful. Lets go back to ol Heppa now.'),
(6685, 'Master, you didnt lose the boots did you? If you want another pair, youll have to go back to Castles [Mercenary Adjutant] Rage and complete the Full Plate Armor (Boots) Quest. Again.'),
(6686, 'Master, you didnt lose the boots did you? If you want another pair, youll have to go back to Castles [Mercenary Adjutant] Rage and complete the Full Plate Armor (Boots) Quest. Again.'),
(6687, 'Master, if you want to hear about Enchant Upgrades from Heppa, you must complete the Armor Enhancement Quest.'),
(6688, 'Master, if you want to hear about Enchant Upgrades from Heppa, you must complete the Armor Enhancement Quest.'),
(6689, 'Merry Christmas!! | I have a special Christmas Quest Event for you!! | * Oh! Christmas Tree Event: 12/19 - 12/28'),
(6690, 'We need help decorating the Christmas Trees!  We are missing the ornaments.  Please go hunt the Christmas Trees and bring the ornaments back to me.'),
(6691, 'Oh! Christmas Tree Event Rewards | * 10 Golden Star Ornaments -> Christmas Cross| * 10 Red Bow Ornaments -> Candy Cane Belt| * 10 Tinsel Ornaments -> Snowman Transformation Scroll| * 5 Golden Stars, 1 Red Bows, 5 Tinsels -> Christmas Present'),
(6692, 'Oh~ you tried very hard. Did you hurt yourself anywhere? As a token of appreciation, I will give you my weapon. I believe you will hunt easier in the future with this weapon.'),
(6693, 'Oh~ you tried very hard. Did you hurt yourself anywhere? As a token of appreciation, I will give you my weapon. I believe you will hunt easier in the future with this weapon.'),
(6694, 'I recommend you go back to El Morad, eh? Youll be able to increase your strength fighting tougher monsters, and theres a lot of good adventures to be had around El Morads heart, the El Morad Castle. Would you like to go there?'),
(6695, 'Howd the hunting go? Yaaah, well, anyway. Well done.'),
(6696, 'Howd the hunting go? Yaaah, well, anyway. Well done.'),
(6697, 'Thanks a lot. As a token of our appreciation, wed like to give you the treasure of our village.|It wont be a great boon to you, but please accept it anyway.'),
(6698, 'Thank you so much. As a token of our appreciation, wed like to give you the treasure of our village.|It wont be a great boon to you, but please accept it anyway.'),
(6699, 'You are amazing!'),
(6700, 'You chose a Christmas Cross| I will give you a Christmas Cross if you bring me 10 Golden Star Ornaments'),
(6701, 'Oh~~ I am so glad you brought me 10 Golden Star Ornaments| Would you like to exchange for a Christmas Cross?'),
(6702, 'Thank you | Merry X-Mas ~~'),
(6703, 'You chose a Candy Cane Belt| I will give you a Candy Cane Belt if you bring me 10 Red Bow Ornaments'),
(6704, 'Oh~~ I am so glad you brought me 10 Red Bow Ornaments| Would you like to exchange for Candy Cane Belt?'),
(6705, 'You chose a Snowman Transformation Scroll| I will give you a Snowman Transformation Scroll if you bring me 10 Tinsel Ornaments'),
(6706, 'Oh~~ I am so glad you brought me 10 Tinsel Ornaments| Would you like to exchange for Snowman Transformation Scroll?'),
(6707, 'You chose Chrismas Present| I will give you chrismas Gift card if you bring me 5 Golden Star, 5 Tinsel, and 1 Red Bow Ornament'),
(6708, 'Oh~~ I am so glad you brought me 5 Golden Star, 5 Tinsels, and 1 Red Bow Ornament| Would you like to exchange for a Chrismas Present?'),
(6709, 'You havent upgraded it yet.|You didnt lose the weapon did you?'),
(6710, 'Master, you should upgrade the thing first.'),
(6711, 'Master, you should upgrade the thing first.'),
(6712, 'You successfully upgraded it. That was a lesson worth learning then. So, did you get the Magical Enhancement Rock?'),
(6713, 'Your inventory is full, nub.|Make some space and Ill give you a present.'),
(6714, 'Master! Imperial Palace Chef Veros is the best. You should go and ask Veros for some BBQ cuisine.'),
(6715, 'Master! Imperial Palace Chef Veros is the best. You should go and ask Jakata for some BBQ cuisine.'),
(6716, 'Master, the lover must be near the Lunar Gate. Help their love to blossom eh? Ah, its so sad...'),
(6717, 'Master, the lover must be near the Lunar Gate. Help their love to blossom eh? Ah, its so sad...'),
(7000, 'Master! [Kaishan`s Daughter] Menissiah wants to see you quick.'),
(7001, 'Master! [Kaishan`s Daughter] Menissiah wants to see you quick.'),
(7002, 'Oh. I thought you`d be willing to do me the favor.'),
(7003, 'Can you hunt Gavolts this time and bring me Apple of Moradon? I will compensate you with Speed Potion.'),
(7004, 'Thank you very much. I vow to succeed.'),
(7005, 'Master, you`ve collected all 5 Apple of Moradon. Let`s go take it Menissiah.'),
(7006, 'I told you I need  Apple of Moradon.'),
(7007, 'I`ll finally be able to make the potion. Please wait. Here. It is made with Menissiah`s care.'),
(7008, 'You don`t think you can? Darn, what am I going to do.'),
(7009, 'I mastered a potion production method which requires Apple of Moradon, but I haven`t been able to obtain the ingredients yet. I will give you the hasten potion if you  bring me  Apple of Moradon.'),
(8000, 'Master, [Mercenary] Russel is looking for you.'),
(8001, 'What took you so long?  I have a favor to ask you. Dragon Tooth soldiers and knights have been killing and looting the village of late. I need your help as there`s too many of them to handle alone.'),
(8002, 'The first Dragon Tooth soldiers to hunt is a far from the previous skeleton-class monsters. Brace yourself!'),
(8003, 'Master, the hunt was demanding but you gained a lot of experience.'),
(8004, 'Thank you. We will depart for Dragon Tooth Skeleton hunting soon. Rest up.'),
(8005, 'Master, [Mercenary] Tales is looking for you.'),
(8006, 'What took you so long?  I have a favor to ask you. Dragon Tooth soldiers and knights have been killing and looting the village of late. I need your help as there`s too many of them to handle alone.'),
(8007, 'The first Dragon Teeth soldier to hunt is a far from the previous skeleton-class monsters. Brace yourself!'),
(8008, 'Master, the hunt was demanding but you gained a lot of experience.'),
(8009, 'If you do a favor for [Mercenary] Tales, you will be rewarded with experience points.'),
(8010, 'Indern`s triumph'),
(8011, 'Indern`s defeat'),
(8012, 'Thank you. We will depart for Dragon Tooth Skeleton hunting soon. Rest up.'),
(8013, 'No time to kill. Get ready to go hunting right away. It`s Dragon Tooth Skeletons this time so repair your equipment and be well prepared.')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(8014, 'You should be able to do this alone. Are you scared?'),
(8015, 'No time to kill. Get ready to go hunting right away. It`s Dragon Tooth Skeletons this time so repair your equipment and be well prepared.'),
(8016, 'You should be able to do this alone. Are you scared?'),
(8018, 'If you do a favor for [Mercenary] Russell, you will be rewarded with experience points.'),
(8019, 'Master, I hear [Sentinel] Zalk is giving out top-notch treasure... Let`s go see if it`s true.'),
(8020, 'Hooray~!! That treasure`s yours now, Master.'),
(8021, 'Arrdream?? That place is a battle zone accessible to 60Lv and below. The place where clashes with the Karus occur frequently!! Ill give you a separate letter of introduction, so go to [Search Captain] Laekand listen about the situation in detail.'),
(8022, 'Ronark Land... Its an exploration territory like Arrdream, and we are fighting intense battles against the enemy to gain control of the area. Ill give you a letter of introduction, so go and introduce yourself to [Search Captain] Della.'),
(8023, 'Ronark Land... Its an exploration territory like Arrdream, and we are fighting intense battles against the enemy to gain control of the area. Ill give you a letter of introduction, so go and introduce yourself to [Defense Captain] Elrod.'),
(8024, 'Have you purchased Ultra Premium? Then youve found the right person. You can exchange the Event Item that you received from purchasing Ultra Premium to one that you really want. Select the item you wish to trade.'),
(8026, 'I think Ive said this before, but unless Rage gives his permission, I cant hand out the supplies.'),
(8027, 'Master, theres a rumor going about that Rage is handing out great treasure... Lets go and check if its true or not.'),
(8028, 'Yes!! Now the treasure is all ours- I mean yours, master!'),
(8029, 'Ha ha, so you heard the rumor? Well, I found some armor and a weapon and Im going to give ¡ˆm away. But not for free, as a reward for some hard work. So Im giving a nice pair of boots to the one who hunts 10 Spoilers in the shortest time.'),
(8030, 'Want to give it a shot? You should be able to pull it off.'),
(8031, 'I told you to bring me 10!'),
(8032, 'My intuition never fails.. You are well qualified to wear the boots. Hope they will come to good use.'),
(8034, 'If you heed [Mercenary Adjutant] Rages request you can obtain craft items as a reward.'),
(8035, 'Master... How about Scorpion Hunting this time?'),
(8036, 'Now all that`s left to do is get our reward!'),
(8037, 'You have not enough Noah.'),
(8038, 'You have not enough Noah.'),
(8039, 'This is one battle field you cant relax on -  This is Ardream!'),
(8040, 'This is a place where only the strong survive. This is Ronark Land!!'),
(8041, 'Master.. What about scorpion hunt this time?'),
(8042, 'Now all that`s left to do is get our reward!'),
(8043, 'Hey! Can you help me with scorpion hunting this time? Please catch just ten of them.'),
(8044, 'I will give you my gauntlet as reward. How does that sound?'),
(8045, 'Nothing in this world is free.'),
(8046, 'Haha~ You`re more talented than I thought. Here`s the gauntlet I promised.'),
(8047, 'Master, [Sentinel] Zalk is giving a helmet as the reward this time..'),
(8048, 'Good work, Master..'),
(8049, 'This is the heart of Karus - Luferson Castle.'),
(8050, 'This is the heart of El Morad - Luferson Castle.'),
(8051, 'This is one battle field you cant relax on -  This is Ardream!'),
(8052, 'This is a place where only the strong survive. This is Ronark Land!!'),
(8055, 'Master, Rage is giving you the helmet this time.'),
(8056, 'Master, you did try hard, I know.'),
(8057, 'It`s Lycan monsters this time. They`re wolfmen and you`ll be able to find them right outside the castle gate. Want to give it a shot?'),
(8058, 'Hunt me 20 Lycans'),
(8059, 'Listen, I`m not in the mood to joke around.'),
(8060, 'You`re amazing. I`ll be sure to remember your name.'),
(8061, 'Master, [Sentinel] Zalk is giving body armor bottom as reward this time. Wonder which monster it is...'),
(8062, 'Im Dueller, I manage the Clan Stadium. If you have any questions, just ask me, any time.'),
(8063, 'As soon as you enter this place, its a total free-for-all. No allies, just enemies all around.  Can you handle that?'),
(8064, 'This is a place where you can fight your allies with enemies in your party! Speaking of parties, teamwork will keep you alive out there. Think about it.'),
(8065, 'Theres always something kicking off in here.'),
(8066, 'Master, [Sentinel] Zalk is giving body armor bottom as reward this time. Wonder which monster it is...'),
(8067, 'Welcome. Will you help with the Loup-garou Hunt? I only need you to hunt 10 of them.'),
(8068, 'I will give you my body armor bottom this time.'),
(8069, 'If it sounds too demanding, it`s not too late to give up'),
(8070, 'You`re truly reliable. Good work!'),
(8071, 'Master, [Sentinel] Zalk called again. Ready to go hunting?'),
(8072, 'Ahhh, bugger it.|Ive been all over the place buying things to trade in Moradon, and tired myself out before I even got there. This stuff is bloody useless anyway (~grumble grumble~).'),
(8073, 'I need to reduce the load a bit.|Hey, would you take this off me? Itd be a shame to throw it away and who knows, it might be useful to you one day.'),
(8074, 'Youre greedier than I am!|Look at all the crap youre carrying around, almost as much as me! You should throw some stuff away mate! Ha Ha Ha!'),
(8075, 'Are you.. <selfname>?|A dark shadow follows you.. Im curious what fate has in store for you.'),
(8076, 'Master, [Sentinel] Melverick called again. Ready to go hunting?'),
(8077, 'Knew you`d show up again. Haha. Hunt me 20 Dark Eyes this time.'),
(8078, 'Want to give it a try?'),
(8079, 'Haha~ Take it slow. Theyre not as docile as you think.'),
(8080, 'Good work. Don`t be too rough on my body armor now.'),
(8081, 'Mr. Patrick is looking for you Master!'),
(8082, 'Its not hard to divine your fate. And anyway, its about time for a break. I was getting kind of hungry. In fact, it could be fate that we met! Listen, for 10,000 Noah Ill show you a little of your own future.'),
(8083, 'Okay, great. Shall we begin?'),
(8084, 'Yeah, well, we could start, but you dont seem to have the 10,000 Noah...'),
(8085, 'From the 15th of February, the Goddess Akarras (patron of life and peace) trust has fallen upon us for 2 weeks.'),
(8086, 'Mr. Patrick is looking for you Master!'),
(8087, 'Long time no see. I called you for no ther reason than to ask a favor of you. Nowadays, they say Orcs are stationed on the outskirts of Folk Village. The timing is not good. If they invade us during these troubled times, we will certainly lose as there are only new recruits available to defend...'),
(8088, 'How is it? If you take care of Orc Watchers, I will give a corresponding reward'),
(8089, '[In reserve]'),
(8090, 'If you fulfill a [Guard] Patricks request, you can receive an experience value as a reward.'),
(8091, 'Master, do you know Telson in charge of imperial palace security? Why don`t you pay him a visit?'),
(8092, 'Youll receive an Event Item Voucher if you purchase Ultra Premium. First, bring me the voucher.'),
(8093, 'Youve selected Trinas Piece. Would you like to exchange it for Trinas Piece?'),
(8094, 'The exchange was successful. Thanks.'),
(8095, 'You have selected Karibedis Piece Would you like to exchange it for 4 Karibedis Pieces?'),
(8096, 'Master, do you know Verca in charge of imperial palace security? Why don`t you pay him a visit?'),
(8097, 'Nice to meet you. I`m the [Mercenary Adjutant] Rage. I`d like to ask you a favor if you don`t mind.'),
(8098, 'Theres these Skeleton monsters. Undead, undying, you know the drill. So will you protect our village and hunt them down for us?'),
(8099, 'When are you going to finish your mission?'),
(8100, 'Thank you very much. The toughest is behind us. I will give you my body armor as compensation.'),
(8101, 'Master, the imperial palace guard wants to see you quick.'),
(8102, 'You have selected the Redistribution Item. Would you like to exchange it for one Redistribution Item?'),
(8103, 'Moradon has changed a lot. 10 years has even changed the river and the mountains... Never thought Moradon would develop this much. What do you reckon? Do you like the new Moradon? Tut Tut.'),
(8104, '¡cllo. Im Norman.|I may look old and weak, but Im still a Magician. Tut Tut. Shall I join Moradons birthday festivities?'),
(8105, 'Oi oi - dont look at me like that... If you dont believe me, Ill prove it. Hmm, so, what if I improve one of your abilities? Youd believe it then wouldnt you?'),
(8106, 'Master, the imperial palace sentinel wants to see you quick.'),
(8107, 'I looked everywhere for you.  If you`re not too busy I could use your help. I received word that Paralyzer monsters surfaced around the castle. I`ve got a hunch something`s up their sleeve.'),
(8108, 'They should be eliminated just in case. Eliminate 20 of them. Will you take on the task?'),
(8109, 'Oh~ you tried very hard. Did you hurt yourself anywhere? As a token of appreciation, I will give you my weapon. Here, youll have an easier time hunting with this weapon. Please pick one that you like from here.'),
(8110, 'You`re already finished? I`ll give you my body armor as reward. They`re supplied exclusively to us imperial palace guards but they`re more useful than they look. Haha...'),
(8111, 'Master, the imperial palace guard sent an urgent message. Why don`t you go see him?'),
(8112, 'Now, in return, would you bring me  15 Morandon Invitations? Got it now then?'),
(8113, 'Now, in return, would you bring me  15 Morandon Invitations? It wont be so hard to get together. Tut Tut-'),
(8114, 'Finally! Now, choose an ability for me to buff. Tut Tut.'),
(8115, 'Master, the imperial palace guard sent an urgent message. Why don`t you go see him?'),
(8116, 'Oh, you`re here. I wanted to see you urgently as there was no one else with whom I could entrust this mission. We`ve just organized the list of monsters who pose a potential threat.'),
(8117, 'We`re short on knights who can take on this mission. We need your help. The first monster to be eliminated is the Dire Wolf.'),
(8118, 'Thank you. I hope you`ll continue to help me in the future.'),
(8119, 'Master, you`re going to help out the imperial palace sentinel again, aren`t you? That means now!! Heh heh...'),
(8120, 'Dont you think youre being a bit greedy? Tut Tut.'),
(8121, 'If you hunt outside Moradon Castle, youll easily get enough   Morandon Invitations. Whoever collects 30 invitations will be given many presents through a prize draw. Presents include NDS, Happy Money Vouchers and Mgame Present Cash Vouchers. For more details, please check the event page on the website.'),
(8122, '<selfname> is either already in the event draw list or hasnt got enough Invitations to register on it.'),
(8123, 'Master, you`re going to help out the imperial palace guard again, aren`t you? That means now!! Heh heh...'),
(8124, 'The monster to be hunted this time is the Smilodon. They`re the local carnivore of the Adonis continent whose bodies are covered by a hard shell. Be careful as they are capable of waging a rapid attack.'),
(8125, 'The reward will be the same as last time, imperial palace guard body armor. Thank you in advance.'),
(8126, 'Thank you so much. We`ll meet again when there`s another mission.'),
(8127, 'Master, we have a message from Zalk. He would surely give us a hunting mission, right?'),
(8128, 'You dont have enough Invitations.|You need 30 Invitations to get on the Event Draw List.'),
(8129, '<selfname> is registered as your name. Please note that winners will be announced on the 22nd of February on the website.'),
(8130, 'Master, This Moradon place is quite unfamiliar, eh? Go find Mercenary Captain Cougar, hell explain all about Moradon.'),
(8131, 'Master, we have a message from Melverick. He would surely give us a hunting mission, right?'),
(8132, 'The third target is Wild Smilodon. Their defense ability is higher than ordinary Smirdons.'),
(8133, 'Your objective is to capture 10 of them. It shouldn`t be too difficult.'),
(8134, 'Thank you. Things are progressing faster than planned.'),
(8135, 'Master, do you know [Sentinel] Zalk in the El Morad Castle?'),
(8136, 'Master, This Moradon place is quite unfamiliar, eh? Go find Mercenary Captain Cougar, hell explain all about Moradon.'),
(8137, 'You must be new to Moradon.|This is a neutral area where citizens of both Karus and El Morad may mix freely. Its the only place on the continent where the two peoples coexist peacefully. Follow me, theres more to tell.'),
(8138, 'Moradon is also the center of Commerce on the Adonisian Continent, and again, the only neutral city not belonging solely to either Karus or El Morad.'),
(8139, 'Master, do you know [Sentinel] Melverick in the Luferson Castle?'),
(8140, 'Hm... A stranger- It might be your first adventure here in Karus. Nice to meet you.- I am Melverick, a Sentinel at the Luferson Castle. I am at your service.-If you have time, could you do me a favor?'),
(8141, 'Here in the mainland, we have creatures called  Shadow Seekers that are notorious for causing troubles everywhere. Even now they are rampaging about at various places, so could you please help us with them?'),
(8142, 'Oh, you can always come and see me when you need new weapons. I can keep supporting you with weapons until you reach 35Lv.'),
(8143, 'Don`t strain yourself. You won`t be able to handle them alone.'),
(8144, 'Don`t strain yourself. You won`t be able to handle them alone.'),
(8145, 'Thanks a lot! I will ask a favor of you next time too.'),
(8146, 'Dont like your fate today? Heh, come and see me tomorrow then.'),
(8147, 'Master, [Mercenary] Russel is looking for you urgently.'),
(8148, 'Master, [Mercenary] Russel is looking for you urgently.'),
(8149, 'Arent you tired of traveling alone, master? Why not get yourself one of the Familiars that  [Trainer] Kate breeds?'),
(8150, 'Don`t strain yourself. Come back after you`ve completed the last monster hunt.'),
(8151, 'Undertake [Mercenary Adjutant] Rage`s request and you`ll receive weaponry as compensation.'),
(8152, 'Undertake [Mercenary Adjutant] Rage`s request and you`ll receive weaponry as compensation.'),
(8153, 'Heed [Mercenary] Russel`s request and you`ll receive 5th armor as compensation.'),
(8154, 'Heed [Mercenary] Tales`s request and you`ll receive 5th armor as compensation.'),
(8155, 'Hey. I`m going on a hunt. Have you heard of Ash Knights? If this comes through we`ll make a bundle. Lend me a hand.'),
(8156, 'Hey. I`m going on a hunt. Have you heard of Ash Knights? If this comes through we`ll make a bundle. Lend me a hand.'),
(8157, 'If you do a favor for [Imperial Guard] Bekar, you will be rewarded with experience points.'),
