(8171, 'Howd the hunting go? Select the weapon you want.'),
(8172, 'Howd the hunting go? Select the weapon you want.'),
(8173, 'A chance to put some experience under your belt like this doesn`t come by often.'),
(8174, 'A chance to put some experience under your belt like this doesn`t come by often.'),
