(8219, 'Were going after 40 Haungas! Isnt that great! Ha-ha-ha!'),
(8220, 'Your ability`s growing by leaps and bounds. You know that`s all on my account, don`t you? Haha...'),
(8221, '[Mercenary] Tales sent word. Must be about another hunting mission.'),
