(8223, 'Were going after 40 Haungas! Isnt that great! Ha-ha-ha!'),
(8224, 'Your ability`s growing by leaps and bounds. You know that`s all on my account, don`t you? Haha...'),
(8225, 'Master, maybe we should swing by Belua Village. Wonder if everything`s all right.'),
(8226, 'Eh, eh, I was about to contact you. Its just that the villagers cant freely go out of the village because of the monsters lurking nearby.'),
(8227, 'As you know, we are barely protecting the village and dont have the strength to take care of them. Would you please help us?'),
(8228, 'Master, maybe we should swing by Asga Village. Wonder if everything`s all right.'),
(8229, 'Eh, eh, I was about to contact you. Its just that the villagers cant freely go out of the village because of the monsters lurking nearby.'),
(8230, 'As you`re well aware, we`re short on men just for village security and we have no means of confronting them. Can you help us?'),
(8231, 'Master, Linnart Village is recruiting knights due to heightened monster attacks. I think you should go talk to [Sentinel] Hashan.'),
(8232, 'Nice to meet you. I am Hashan, in charge of village security. I`ve heard so much about you. Meeting you in person like this finally affords hope to our village.'),
(8233, 'The monster attacks have jumped markedly and the resulting damage dire. At this rate, it`s just a matter of time till our village disappears. Please save our village.'),
(8234, 'Master. [Imperial Palace Guard] Verca is about to go on a hunt, so how about joining him?'),
(8235, 'Ha ha~ I guess it reached your ears as well. Yes, it is true. This time I am going to hunt the Hornets, so do you want to join me?'),
(8236, 'You may be able to gain valuable experience from this hunt. Why don`t you and your colleagues come join us?'),
(8237, 'Haha... how is it going? Good work.'),
(8238, 'Master, [Imperial Palace Guard] Verca is recruiting warriors for a massive Haunga hunt. Why don`t you go join him?'),
(8239, 'This time its hunting the Haunga Warriors, so do you want to be on it? By the way, a Haunga Warrior isnt easy to hunt as it is strong and has high defense power as well as resistances.'),
(8240, 'However, this should be a simple task for someone of your skill level, <selfname>.'),
(8241, 'Good work. You`ve gained valuable experience from this hunt.'),
(8242, 'Master, Laiva Village is recruiting knights due to heightened monster attacks. I think you should go talk to [Sentinel] Beth.'),
