(8311, 'Master, here in the mainland there is a graveyard... How about meeting Bottom who is the keeper of the place?'),
(8312, 'Hello... Im Bottom, and I manage the Graveyard. I dont know how many years have passed since I started to keep this graveyard. Ah- Could you help me, by the way?'),
(8313, 'What brings you here? Well, excuse me, I have something to do... And you seem pretty busy, too..'),
(8314, 'I dont know since when, but  Rotten Eyes have begun to appear at the graveyard and I cannot drive them out by myself. Theyre zombie monsters like Undyings, and the problem is that they come and make a terrible mess in the place. Could you try and protect the graveyard from them?'),
(8315, 'Well done master, well done.'),
(8316, 'The graveyard must be protected no matter what happens. Please, do your best.'),
(8317, 'Meeting you is possibly the best bit of luck Ive ever had! Thank you, thank you so much. Heres a little something for ya. This is what I found while Ive been keeping this place, and should be quite useful.'),
(8318, 'There must be something wrong down in the Tomb, master.'),
(8319, 'What brings you here?'),
(8320, 'Well, its nothing... I will try to talk to you later as you seem very busy now.'),
(8321, 'What - How - You drove out all those Vatalions..Ill never forget this. And this is something I picked up near the graveyard a few days ago, and it doesnt look like something ordinary... Please, take it as a token of my appreciation.'),
(8322, 'Master, the mainland has its own Gravesite. Slay defends the site. How about you meet him?'),
(8323, 'As it has already been reported to [Mercenary Adjutant] Rage that I would stand guard until tomorrow, I am worried since they are still short of Apples. As I dont have anybody else that I can turn to in this situation, can you secure the Apples of Moradon for me? Five or more will be alright.'),
(8324, 'Oops, seems like you already have too many other missions. Come back when youve taken care of some of them.'),
(8325, 'Oops, seems like you already have too many other missions. Come back when youve taken care of some of them.'),
(8326, 'Well done master, well done.'),
(8327, 'You are still doing yesterdays mission. Sorry, but that mission isnt valid any more.'),
(8328, 'You are still doing yesterdays mission. Sorry, but that mission isnt valid any more.'),
(8329, 'There must be something wrong down in the Tomb, master.'),
(8330, 'Thanksgiving Day, the biggest holiday in 2008! We have prepared a special event for the occasion!'),
(8331, 'It is the duel in a game of Yut!! Erm? Are you asking what the difference is from the New Year Holiday? Hu hu, if you beat me, I will give you not just 10,000 Noahs but also a premium coupon, which you can exchange with a [Special Pet Transformation Scroll] when you collect 50 coupons. Now, how about betting 5,000 Noahs for a match?'),
(8332, 'You are engaging in National Defence Combat.'),
(8333, 'If you take on too many missions, it will produce calamitous results. Please finish your current hunting mission first.'),
(8334, 'If you take on too many missions, it will produce calamitous results. Please finish your current hunting mission first.'),
(8335, 'A hunt of this intensity is a piece of cake, right? Heh heh...'),
(8336, 'A hunt of this intensity is a piece of cake, right? Heh heh...'),
(8337, 'Master, how`re you feeling? The imperial palace guard is looking for you...'),
(8338, 'Did you just get here? How are you feeling? We`re hunting Saber Tooth this time, a Smirdon like monster. I feel a little guilty always enlisting your help.'),
(8339, 'In return, I`ll give you knight-class body armor as reward beginning with this mission. It`s incomparable to the previous ones.'),
(8340, 'Thank you. This is the imperial knight body armor.'),
(8341, 'Master, how`re you feeling? The imperial palace guard is looking for you...'),
(8342, 'How is your adventure here in the mainland? Isnt it tough? Haha- just like before, I came here to ask you for a hunt. The targets are the Saber Tooths.. They are pretty ferocious, but would you like to hunt them?'),
(8343, 'I will give you a very useful armor when you complete this hunt.'),
(8344, 'Well done. The reward is the armor suppied only to the Palace Guards, so I am sure youll find it handy.'),
(8345, 'Hum...The targets of this hunt are Skeletons of the Warrior class. It might be a difficult hunt as it is said that they never stop attacking until the last drop of the magic of life that sustains them is left in them.'),
(8346, 'I know you will succeed.'),
(8347, 'As I expected... Well done. Ill contact you when there is another assignment, then.'),
