(8390, 'I have yet another favor to ask you. Monsters named Scolars dwell in our village outskirts. It`s a magic organism Pathos spurned out of casting a curse on scarecrows. They attack all humans who approach them with curse magic.'),
(8391, 'I know it`s no easy task but I don`t have anyone else to ask. Please help us.'),
(8392, 'Thank you. Peace has been restored to the village once again. This is all I can give you now in compensation but I promise to reward you handsomely next time.'),
