(8486, 'Did you obtain the bottom? Now all I have left is the top. The prey for this hunt is Stone Golem. Ancient priests infused stones with life and employed them as servants. But they`ve lost self-control and have turned into savage monsters now...'),
(8487, 'I wish you success in this hunt as well.'),
(8488, 'Thank you. Here`s the top, as promised.'),
