(8496, 'Youll get some Armor out of this when you hunt all the Apes and go to [Mercenary] Russel.'),
(8497, 'Hmm... we seem to have some unexpected guests at the graveyard. They are certainly uninvited guests - they are called  Vatalions, which are much tougher than the Undyings or Rotten Eyes. I cant do any work because of them. Could you help me?'),
(8498, 'What`s all that you`re lugging around... Please put them away and come back.'),
(8499, 'What`s all that you`re lugging around... Please put them away and come back.'),
(8500, 'Have you seen the Kecoon Captains around the castle? Its alarming how their numbers have suddenly shot up.'),
(8501, 'Yaaah... hunting about 5 of them would do the trick. Ill pay you loads.'),
(8502, 'Yahoo! Well done. Now lets go and get that reward from Patrick.'),
(8503, 'Yahoo! Well done. Now lets go and get that reward from Patrick.'),
(8504, 'Good job. It was clever of me to ask you to do that. Heh! Heres the reward I promised.'),
(8505, 'Hey! Is the mission over yet?'),
(8506, 'Master, do you know a monster called the Giant Bulcan? No? Lets go and ask [Sentinel Patrick] about it.'),
(8507, 'Master, do you know a monster called the Giant Bulcan? No? Lets go and ask [Sentinel Patrick] about it.'),
(8508, 'The Giant Bulcan? Yeah, hes an enormous bugger, even by Bulcan standards. Bulcans have no eyes so they hate it when you go up close and mess with them.'),
(8509, 'Heres a thought... Go out and catch 10 Bulcans to start.'),
(8510, 'Nail the Giant Bulcan after youve taken care of all the others.'),
(8511, 'Phew! Well done master. Did the world of good for your abilities and experience eh? Ha ha!'),
(8512, 'Phew! Well done master. Did the world of good for your abilities and experience eh? Ha ha!'),
(8513, 'Obviously, the harder the hunt, the more EXP youll get from it.'),
(8514, 'Good job. Your skills got a good workout there eh master?.'),
(8515, 'Ah~ Welcome. I thought you would come. Have you seen a monster called Giant Gavolt?'),
(8516, 'It is called that way as its body is big even among Gavolts.  Anyway, those with big bodies are strong so be careful. Ha ha... your goal is 25 of them! Will you give it a try?'),
(8517, 'Master, They say that [Sentinel] Patrick is collecting  Apple of Moradon. Lets go and see if we can profit from this.'),
(8518, 'Master, They say that [Sentinel] Patrick is collecting  Apple of Moradon. Lets go and see if we can profit from this.'),
(8519, 'r'),
(8520, 'Please bring me Apple of Moradon. You already know that you can get apples if you catch werewolves even if I dont explain it to you, dont you? Ha ha...'),
(8521, 'Youve collected all the Apple of Moradon. Lets go back and see Patrick now.'),
(8522, 'Youve collected all the Apple of Moradon. Lets go back and see Patrick now.'),
