(8524, 'Good job. Heres a little something for you.'),
(8525, 'Master, Do you know a monster called the Glyptodont? Lets go and ask [Sentinel Patrick] about it.'),
(8526, 'Master, Do you know a monster called the Glyptodont? Lets go and ask [Sentinel Patrick] about it.'),
(8527, 'The Glyptodont? Youre talking about that big, ugly-looking bugger?'),
(8528, 'Well, the Glyptodont is a giant omnivore that can be found pretty much anywhere on the Adonisian Continent. Its slow, but hits hard. How about going out and thinning their numbers a bit? Itll go much easier if you form a party.'),
(8529, 'Phew! Well done master. It looks stupid, but its pretty powerful. Hee Hee!'),
(8530, 'Phew! Well done master. It looks stupid, but its pretty powerful. Hee Hee!'),
(8531, 'Itll be hard to deal with on your own. Better to form a party before tackling it.'),
(8532, 'So, whats it like hunting Glyptodont? Ha Ha! Anyway, Well done.'),
(8533, 'Welcome. There should be a monster called Gloomwing outside the Castle there. Gloomwing is a Gavolt with extra hard scales. Gloomwings scale is a popular material in armor and weapons.'),
(8534, 'Id like you to hunt 10 Gloomwings... Sound good?'),
(8535, 'Master, [Mercenary Adjutant] Rage is urgently looking for you!'),
(8536, 'Master, [Mercenary Adjutant] Rage is urgently looking for you!'),
(8537, 'As I see <selfname>, now I am relieved. I just want to let you know that Keilans are gathering near the outskirts of Folk Village and their numbers are growing.'),
(8538, 'As their numbers are growing rapidly, we are in big trouble. Can you help me take care of these of Keilans?'),
(8539, 'Master, you did a good job. Now Rages worry will completely disappear.'),
(8540, 'Master, you did a good job. Now Rages worry will completely disappear.'),
(8541, 'I just believe in you <selfname>.'),
(8542, 'Ah! The Adonisian Continents best holiday - the Creation of Logos! It chills everyone out for a little while, regardless of their origins or beliefs.'),
(8543, 'I want everyone to be together on this holiday. Thats the gods wish too.'),
(8544, 'Thank you very much! This is a small token of my appreciation.'),
(8545, 'Will you participate in National Defence Combat?'),
(8546, 'There arent enough soldiers to carry the battle. Be aware that taking on too many enemies by yourself is pretty damn reckless.'),
(8547, 'Note that [Report User] is excluded from National Defence Combat.'),
(8548, 'Hmm ? if youve not made any contribution to the country, you cant be dispatched. First, charge CONT from [Knight Squad Secretary] Charel in this castle.'),
(8549, 'Master, Shall we go some hunting and get some more experience? Hee Hee!'),
(8550, 'Master, Shall we go some hunting and get some more experience? Hee Hee!'),
(8551, 'Are you going out to hunt? Hmm... How about hunting Hell Hounds?'),
(8552, 'Are you going out to hunt? Hmm... How about hunting Hell Hounds?'),
(8553, 'Hell Hounds are meat-eating beasts that have their breeding grounds behind the Goblin Village. Its has a characteristically fast attack speed and is popular among hunters because it drops Talismans of Destruction. This hunt will be a great experience for you.'),
(8554, 'Hell Hounds are meat-eating beasts that have their breeding grounds behind the Goblin Village. Its has a characteristically fast attack speed and is popular among hunters because it drops Talismans of Destruction. This hunt will be a great experience for you.'),
(8555, 'Well done! Should I give you a massage now? Hee Hee!'),
(8556, 'Well done! Should I give you a massage now? Hee Hee!'),
(8557, 'Hows the hunt going? Experience doesnt always come easy. Cheer up!'),
(8558, 'Hows the hunt going? Experience doesnt always come easy. Cheer up!'),
(8559, 'Hahahahaha!! You got wasted! Well done. I think.'),
(8560, 'Hahahahaha!! You got wasted! Well done. I think.'),
(8561, 'Master, do you know anything about Manticore? You should ask Keife for more information.'),
(8562, 'Master, do you know anything about Manticore? You should ask Keife for more information.'),
(8563, 'A Manticore is a fearsome winged beast that has the body of a lion and the tail of a scorpion. Youll understand better if you see it for yourself.'),
(8564, 'A Manticore is a fearsome winged beast that has the body of a lion and the tail of a scorpion. Youll understand better if you see it for yourself.'),
(8565, 'I recently heard that a Manticore has been seen somewhere near Karus.'),
(8566, 'I recently heard that a Manticore has been seen somewhere near El Morad.'),
(8567, 'How you feeling today?'),
(8568, 'How you feeling today?'),
(8569, 'Well done. Was it as hard as they say?'),
(8570, 'Well done. Was it as hard as they say?'),
(8571, 'Bekar is gathering knights who will participate in the Phantom Hunt. Master, you should sign up as well!'),
(8572, 'Bekar is gathering knights who will participate in the Phantom Hunt. Master, you should sign up as well!'),
(8573, 'Would you like to join the Phantom Hunt?'),
(8574, 'Would you like to join the Phantom Hunt?'),
(8575, 'The Phantom is in the Hell Abyss of Delos Abyss Dungeon. Return from the hunt and the Transformation Magic Scroll is yours.'),
(8576, 'The Phantom is in the Hell Abyss of Delos Abyss Dungeon. Return from the hunt and the Transformation Magic Scroll is yours.'),
(8577, 'Phew~ Its done. Lets get out of here. I dont like this eerie feeling...'),
(8578, 'Phew~ Its done. Lets get out of here. I dont like this eerie feeling...'),
(8579, 'I heard the Phantom can be found in Hell Abyss of Delos Abyss Dungeon.'),
(8580, 'I heard the Phantom can be found in Hell Abyss of Delos Abyss Dungeon.'),
(8581, 'Well done. Heres the Transformation Scroll, as promised.'),
(8582, 'Well done. Heres the Transformation Scroll, as promised.'),
(8583, 'Master, do you about a Monster named Groom Hound? Perhaps Verca would know about it?'),
(8584, 'Master, do you about a Monster named Groom Hound? Perhaps Telson would know about it?'),
(8585, 'Groom Hound? Hum...I dont know exactly, but I heard that its a Smirdon type monster residing in the Abyss of Hell.'),
(8586, 'Groom Hound? Hum...I dont know exactly, but I heard that its a Smirdon type monster residing in the Abyss of Hell.'),
(8587, 'The hunt is over so lets get out quickly~ Feels so gloomy every time I come here...'),
(8588, 'The hunt is over so lets get out quickly~ Feels so gloomy every time I come here...'),
(8589, 'How did you feel about hunting the Groom Hounds? Dont you just feel like hunting them over and over again? Haha~ it was just a joke.'),
(8590, 'How did you feel about hunting the Groom Hounds? Dont you just feel like hunting them over and over again? Haha~ it was just a joke.'),
(8591, 'Master, Zamed the Search Captain is looking for you... I wonder why?'),
(8592, 'Master, Laek the Search Captain is looking for you... I wonder why?'),
(8593, 'Ah, I was looking for you. Your reputation is known even here in Ardream. I contacted you because I have a special favor to ask.'),
(8594, 'Ah, I was looking for you. Your reputation is known even here in Ardream. I contacted you because I have a special favor to ask.'),
(8595, 'Hmm...I dont want to interrupt your hunting. Ill see you later.'),
(8596, 'Hmm...I dont want to interrupt your hunting. Ill see you later.'),
(8597, 'There are two particular monsters here in Ardream, Atros and Lyot. Atros was active in Pathos Darkness Armys Raiders unit. Recently, these two monsters joined forces and now present an overwhelming threat that must be dealt with immediately and violently. From what Ive heard, youre the ideal candidate for the job. Can you do it?'),
(8598, 'There are two particular monsters here in Ardream, Atros and Lyot. Atros was active in Pathos Darkness Armys Raiders unit. Recently, these two monsters joined forces and now present an overwhelming threat that must be dealt with immediately and violently. From what Ive heard, youre the ideal candidate for the job. Can you do it?'),
(8599, 'Phew! Atros is strong enough, eh? The upside is, your skills got a great workout there!'),
(8600, 'Phew! Atros is strong enough, eh? The upside is, your skills got a great workout there!'),
(8601, 'Hmm ? Are you still hunting? I doubt your reputation is exaggerated.'),
(8602, 'Hmm ? Are you still hunting? I doubt your reputation is exaggerated.'),
(8603, 'Youre every bit as good as they say you are. Thank you so much.'),
(8604, 'Youre every bit as good as they say you are. Thank you so much.'),
(8605, 'Veda is looking for you, master. But who is Veda??'),
(8606, 'Veda is looking for you, master. But who is Veda??'),
(8607, 'Welcome to Islante. I appreciate your interest in our corner of the world. My name is Veda, I train in aesthetic practices here in Islante.'),
(8608, 'Welcome to Islante. I appreciate your interest in our corner of the world. My name is Tabeth, I train in aesthetic practices here in Islante.'),
(8609, 'Hmm.. You still have unfinished hunt training.'),
(8610, 'Hmm.. You still have unfinished hunt training.'),
(8611, 'I called for you because with your reputation and ability, Islante is the perfect place for you to improve your skills. Youll understand if you start hunting Doom Soldiers.'),
(8612, 'I called for you because with your reputation and ability, Islante is the perfect place for you to improve your skills. Youll understand if you start hunting Doom Soldiers.'),
(8613, 'Well done~ The work here in Islante is better than I expected.'),
(8614, 'Well done~ The work here in Islante is better than I expected.'),
(8615, 'The road of practice must be walked with patience.'),
(8616, 'The road of practice must be walked with patience.'),
(8617, 'Good job. Are you satisfied with that?'),
(8618, 'Good job. Are you satisfied with that?')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(8619, 'You were with Veda a long time. How about paying him a little visit?'),
(8620, 'You were with Veda a long time. How about paying him a little visit?'),
(8621, 'We meet again. How goes the training?'),
(8622, 'We meet again. How goes the training?'),
(8623, 'I saw some Harpy type Monsters - Crimson Wings I think theyre called - a few days ago while I was training. Big wings, Sharp claws... its said that hundreds of people have died from their poisons in even little scratches. But, for you, theyd make for great training.'),
(8624, 'I saw some Harpy type Monsters - Crimson Wings I think theyre called - a few days ago while I was training. Big wings, Sharp claws... its said that hundreds of people have died from their poisons in even little scratches. But, for you, theyd make for great training.'),
(8625, 'Well done. Was it a hard hunt? But I can see the results of your training already. Well done. Heh.'),
(8626, 'Well done. Was it a hard hunt? But I can see the results of your training already. Well done. Heh.'),
(8627, 'Master, Theres a monster with a devils shape! Ill bet Veda knows about it.'),
(8628, 'Master, Theres a monster with a devils shape! Ill bet Veda knows about it.'),
(8629, 'The devil-shaped monster is actually a Gargoyle.'),
(8630, 'Yeah, the devil monster is really a Gargoyle.'),
(8631, 'Its a stony monster with the devils visage that owes its life to an ancient spell. After the war against Pathos, the seals were permanently removed and its been stuck here threatening humans ever since. I think itd be good to ¡—rain on these beasts next. Heh.'),
(8632, 'Its a stony monster with the devils visage that owes its life to an ancient spell. After the war against Pathos, the seals were permanently removed and its been stuck here threatening humans ever since. I think itd be good to ¡—rain on these beasts next. Heh.'),
(8633, 'Its a terrible monster to be sure. Wasnt it? I dont want to mess with them again. Anyway, we were fortunate to finish all that without any troubles.'),
(8634, 'Its a terrible monster to be sure. Wasnt it? I dont want to mess with them again. Anyway, we were fortunate to finish all that without any troubles.'),
(8635, 'Master, How about we go and ask Veda for another training mission?'),
(8636, 'Master, How about we go and ask Taved for another training mission?'),
(8637, 'You want to keep training? You look strong enough already... How much stronger do you want to be?? Heh.'),
(8638, 'You want to keep training? You look strong enough already... How much stronger do you want to be?? Heh.'),
(8639, 'Right then, I think its time you met the Apostle of Piercing Cold. You should be able to dispatch him easily enough. Just watch out for that meddling monks Glacier Spell of Darkness. It can freeze your bones solid.'),
(8640, 'Right then, I think its time you met the Apostle of Piercing Cold. You should be able to dispatch him easily enough. Just watch out for that meddling monks Glacier Spell of Darkness. It can freeze your bones solid.'),
(8641, 'Phew- Good effort. It was a hard fight, wasnt it?'),
(8642, 'Phew- Good effort. It was a hard fight, wasnt it?'),
(8643, 'Their seems to be no end to your skill! Simply amazing.'),
(8644, 'Their seems to be no end to your skill! Simply amazing.'),
(8645, 'Master, Are you ready for more training?'),
(8646, 'Master, Are you ready for more training?'),
(8647, 'Hmm... Did you have anything in particular in mind?'),
(8648, 'Hmm... Did you have anything in particular in mind?'),
(8649, 'What? What are you going to do with that worm? Itll just decrease your ability. Ha Ha! This time, lets make the Apostle of Flames the target of the training. His Flame Spell of Darkness attack cannot be explained in words. So please, be careful. And wear asbestos underwear for this one!.'),
(8650, 'What? What are you going to do with that worm? Itll just decrease your ability. Ha Ha! This time, lets make the Apostle of Flames the target of the training. His Flame Spell of Darkness attack cannot be explained in words. So please, be careful. And wear asbestos underwear for this one!.'),
(8651, 'There are many knights gathering in Ronark Land to hunt cursed monsters.  Would you like to go and join them, master?'),
