(8656, 'But I want you to finish the hunts you were already on. Im kind of busy right now, so see you later...'),
(8657, 'Bishop, Bach and Duke... These monsters are the cursed monsters youve been hearing about. Theyre magical life forms brought to life when Pathos himself cursed some tailors dummies. Theyre a rewarding hunt to engage in since you can earn special strength by defeating them.'),
(8658, 'Bishop, Bach and Duke... These monsters are the cursed monsters youve been hearing about. Theyre magical life forms brought to life when Pathos himself cursed some tailors dummies. Theyre a rewarding hunt to engage in since you can earn special strength by defeating them.'),
