(8700, 'Hmm. I have 2 Legendary Accessories. I will reward you with the first of 2 rings when you complete the Machirodus hunt.'),
(8701, 'Hmm. I have 2 Legendary Accessories. I will reward you with the first of 2 rings when you complete the Machirodus hunt.'),
(8702, 'Your current mission log must be quite stuffed! We can discuss some other stuff when you come back from this hunt.'),
(8703, 'Your current mission log must be quite stuffed! We can discuss some other stuff when you come back from this hunt.'),
(8704, 'The Machirodus is a kind of  Smirdon. Remember them? Hes got hard skin and a quick attack, so dont treat him lightly. Would you like to try?'),
(8705, 'The Machirodus is a kind of  Smirdon. Remember them? Hes got hard skin and a quick attack, so dont treat him lightly. Would you like to try?'),
(8706, 'This hunt is over! Woo, now youre going to be the proud owner of a Ring of Legend!'),
