(8714, 'Do you want the Belt of Legend? Okay, you can have it if you can complete the mission Im about to give you.'),
(8715, 'Do you want the Belt of Legend? Okay, you can have it if you can complete the mission Im about to give you.'),
(8716, 'Blood Don is a type of Smirdon monster. I will reward you with this belt when you complete the Blood Don hunt. Would you like to give it a shot?'),
(8717, 'Blood Don is a type of Smirdon monster. I will reward you with this belt when you complete the Blood Don hunt. Would you like to give it a shot?'),
(8718, 'Phew~ Good effort master. Go and find Cape now~'),
(8719, 'Phew~ Good effort master. Go and find Cheina now~'),
(8720, 'I knew you could do it. Heres the Belt of Legend, as promised.'),
(8721, 'I knew you could do it. Heres the Belt of Legend, as promised.'),
(8722, 'Master, Finding the last Earring of Legend would be a good experience. I reckon Russel would know where to start.'),
(8723, 'Master, Finding the last Earring of Legend would be a good experience. I reckon Russel would know where to start.'),
(8724, 'What? Yeah? You wanted to see me? What about this Earring that holds the strength of Legend?'),
(8725, 'What? Yeah? You wanted to see me? What about this Earring that holds the strength of Legend?'),
(8726, 'Ah. Finish the hunts youre already on first. I have to catch more monsters than most in order to make a living.'),
(8727, 'Ah. Finish the hunts youre already on first. I have to catch more monsters than most in order to make a living.'),
(8728, 'Hmm. This is no ordinary earring. The earring will only shine with true power for those worthy to wear it. I have it but cant wear it myself. Ill give it to you if youll hunt the Sheriff. What do you say?'),
(8729, 'Hmm. This is no ordinary earring. The earring will only shine with true power for those worthy to wear it. I have it but cant wear it myself. Ill give it to you if youll hunt the Sheriff. What do you say?'),
(8730, 'Well, well. The last Strength of Legends ring is yours now, master. Congratulations!'),
(8731, 'Well, well. The last Strength of Legends ring is yours now, master. Congratulations!'),
(8732, 'Stop wandering around and just go and hunt quickly!'),
(8733, 'Stop wandering around and just go and hunt quickly!'),
(8734, 'Hmm... Did you catch them all, already? Well, a promise is a promise, here you go. I hope you are the true owner of this earring.'),
(8735, 'Hmm... Did you catch them all, already? Well, a promise is a promise, here you go. I hope you are the true owner of this earring.'),
(8736, 'Master, Found it~! The Pendant that holds the Strength of Legend!! Russel is rumored to have it. Please, let it be true...'),
(8737, 'Master, Found it~! The Pendant that holds the Strength of Legend!! Russel is rumored to have it. Please, let it be true...'),
(8738, '...... How did you know I have the Pendant of Legend? This is the last little treasure I have.'),
(8739, '...... How did you know I have the Pendant of Legend? This is the last little treasure I have.'),
(8740, 'What? You think people are earning money by digging-up the ground? Youre so shameless as to say you want this precious thing - for nothing! Bloody well go and do something amazing, then I might consider giving it up. Cheek!'),
(8741, 'What? You think people are earning money by digging-up the ground? Youre so shameless as to say you want this precious thing - for nothing! Bloody well go and do something amazing, then I might consider giving it up. Cheek!'),
(8742, '(~grin~) Russel would give it to me if he sees the amount of hunting Ive done, wouldnt he?'),
(8743, '(~grin~) Tales would give it to me if he sees the amount of hunting Ive done, wouldnt he?'),
(8744, 'What? Did you really hunt them? I really should know the extent of your stubbornness by now. Still, my mouth never seems to learn. Oh well, here it is then. Its yours now too.'),
(8745, 'What? Did you really hunt them? I really should know the extent of your stubbornness by now. Still, my mouth never seems to learn. Oh well, here it is then. Its yours now too.'),
(8746, 'Master, by my calculations, theres still another ring to find. One last Ring of Legend... Emm... I think Vercas the one we need to tap for this piece.'),
(8747, 'Master, by my calculations, theres still another ring to find. One last Ring of Legend... Emm... I think Telsons the one we need to tap for this piece.'),
(8748, 'Are you looking for the ring that holds the Strength of Legend? To be honest, Ive already sent Searchers out to find it. Theyll find it soon, Im sure. But the Strength of Legend  only grants itself to the owner it approves of. So who knows?'),
