(8750, 'Hmm... If its about the Ring of Legend, lets talk about it next time. Looks like youre already busy hunting?'),
(8751, 'Hmm... If its about the Ring of Legend, lets talk about it next time. Looks like youre already busy hunting...'),
(8752, 'You want to trade with me? If you defeat the Gray Oozy monsters on the way to the farm, then Ill give you the treasure. The chaos on the farm is made even worse by all the poison they gush out.'),
(8753, 'You want to trade with me? If you defeat the Gray Oozy monsters on the way to the farm, then Ill give you the treasure. The chaos on the farm is made even worse by all the poison they gush out.'),
