(8775, 'Master, The [Farm Manager] has found a great treasure! Im curious, lets go and see it.'),
(8776, 'Treasure? Ahh, well, I was plowing the fields when I saw something shining in the dirt. So I picked it up, and it turned out to be an earring. It looks expensive, but it doesnt seem right to sell it.'),
