(8789, 'Master, Veda is going to start you on the second training. Go and see him~'),
(8790, 'Are you ready for the second round of training?'),
(8791, 'Are you ready for the second round of training?'),
(8792, 'The second training target is our friend, the Brahman. Brahman are in a completely different class to the Esoteric Buddhist Monks. His nonstop attacks wont give you any breathing time. Its a tougher opponent than perhaps what youre used to, but for training, this can only be a good thing. What do you think?'),
(8793, 'The second training target is our friend, the Brahman. Brahman are in a completely different class to the Esoteric Buddhist Monks. His nonstop attacks wont give you any breathing time. Its a tougher opponent than perhaps what youre used to, but for training, this can only be a good thing. What do you think?'),
(8794, 'Groom Hounds are said to be in the Abyss of Hell... Is there really anyone who would fight monsters like that? What would you do?'),
(8795, 'Groom Hounds are said to be in the Abyss of Hell... Is there really anyone who would fight monsters like that? What would you do?'),
(8796, 'If you bring a [Exchange National Flag] item, your National flag will be exchanged with the one youd like.'),
(8797, 'First, you should bring the [Exchange National Flag] item.'),
(8798, 'Would you like to exchange to the [Turkish National Flag]?'),
(8799, 'Would you like to exchange to the [U.S National Flag]?'),
(8800, 'Would you like to exchange to the [Canadian National Flag]?'),
(8801, 'Would you like to exchange to the [German National Flag]?'),
(8802, 'Would you like to exchange to the [Danish National Flag]?'),
(8803, 'Would you like to exchange to the [Polish National Flag]?'),
(8804, 'Would you like to exchange to the [Korean National Flag]?'),
(8805, 'Would you like to exchange to the [Chinese National Flag]?'),
(8806, 'Would you like to exchange to the [Japanese National Flag]?'),
(8807, 'Youve collected 10 [Seeds of All Means]. I will offer you one reward item. Which one would you like?'),
(8808, 'If you bring 10 [Seeds of All Means], the proper reward will be offered.'),
(8809, 'You do not have enough [Seeds of All Means]. Reward can be offered only if you bring 10 items.'),
(8810, 'Master! Youve collected 10 [Seeds of All Means]. Go to [Manager] Vilbore right away! If you bring 10 [Seeds of All Means], a reward will be given.'),
(8811, 'Master! Youve collected 10 [Seeds of All Means]. Go to [Manager] Vilbore right away! If you bring 10 [Seeds of All Means], a reward will be given.'),
(8812, 'Master, go to [White Shadow] Scout leader Valencia. He is giving away great items to those who complete new missions!'),
(8813, 'Master, go to [White Shadow] Scout leader Valencia. He is giving away great items to those who complete new missions!'),
(8814, 'I cant assign you a mission. Please, come see me again some other time.'),
(8815, 'I have been offering [Imirus Pray] to those who help out with the mission. You can complete your mission only once a day. Would you like to accept this mission?'),
(8816, 'Currently, [Scouts] are dispatched throughout the land. I have to collect their [Reconnaissance Diary] once a day, but I cant do that firsthand as I have too many missions. I will give you the [Collect Reconnaissance Diary Order]. Could you collect the diary?'),
(8817, 'You lost your [Collect Reconnaissance Diary Order]? I will rewrite it for you.'),
(8818, 'You havent collected a [Reconnaissance Diary] yet. Get moving!')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(8819, 'You collected all [Reconnaissance Diary]. Could you hand them over to me?'),
(8820, 'Did you come here to collect Reconnaissance Diaries? Im sorry, but I cant give you my [Reconnaissance Diary] if you dont have the [Collect Reconnaissance Diary Order].'),
(8821, 'Did you come here to collect Reconnaissance Diary? Please, show me your [Collect Reconnaissance Diary Order].'),
(8822, 'I confirm that this is the [Collect Reconnaissance Diary Order] of [Valencia]. Here is my [Reconnaissance Diary]. Take this and go to [Scout Marvin] to receive the next [Reconnaissance Diary].'),
(8823, 'I can give you the next Reconnaissance Diary, only after you collect [Reconnaissance Diary] from [Scout Merlin]. Collect [Reconnaissance Diary] from [Scout Merlin], and then come see me.'),
(8824, 'I confirmed [Reconnaissance Diary] and signature of [Collect Reconnaissance Diary Order]. Here is [2nd Reconnaissance Diary]. Take this and go to Marble to receive [3rd Reconnaissance Diary]. Do you want to collect that?'),
(8825, 'You didnt collect other [Reconnaissance Diary], did you? Though you have [Collect Reconnaissance Diary Order], I cant give you mine if you dont go in order. Im sorry.'),
(8826, 'Well, lets see. Yes, that is the real [Collect Reconnaissance Diary Order]! It has the signature of Scout leader [Valencia], and [Reconnaissance Diary] from [Scout Merlin] and [Scout Marvin].'),
(8827, 'You have done well collecting [Reconnaissance Diary] so far! Hopefully [3rd Reconnaissance Diary] is the last, but you have two more diaries to collect from to scouts. Here is [3rd Reconnaissance Diary]. Do you want to collect that?'),
(8828, 'You have collected the previous three [Reconnaissance Diary]. It must have been hard to deal with [Scout Marble]...  Anyway, could you show me your [Collect Reconnaissance Diary Order]?'),
(8829, 'Yes, I confirm this is the signature of [Valencia]. I will give you the [4th Reconnaissance Diary]. Do you want to collect that?'),
(8830, 'Please show me your [Collect Reconnaissance Diary Order] and the [Reconnaissance Diary] you have collected so far.'),
(8831, 'Well...  All of them are real, Scout Leader [Valencia], [Scout Merlin], [Scout Marvin]... [Scout Marble]... You, troublemaker! Hmm... And I confirmed the signature of [Scout Mark]. Well, then would you like to collect [5th Reconnaissance Diary]?'),
(8832, 'You have collected all the [Reconnaissance Diary]. Your mission complete when you deliver them with [Collect Reconnaissance Diary Order] to [Valencia]. Good job on your mission!'),
(8833, 'Your inventory is full. You should empty your inventory so you can carry more items.'),
(8834, 'Master, heres the [Seed of All Means]! [Manager] Vilbore said he would offer a reward if you collect 10 [Seeds of All Means]. Pay visit to him once you have collected 10!'),
(8835, 'Master, heres the [Seed of All Means]! [Manager] Vilbore said he would offer a reward if you collect 10 [Seeds of All Means]. Pay visit to him once you have collected 10!'),
(8836, 'You already have the [Collect Reconnaissance Diary Order].'),
(8837, 'Youve just collected [Reconnaissance Diary]. You cant collect another one.'),
(8838, 'You completed your mission. You can do your scout mission again tomorrow.'),
(8839, 'When you bring the Leaders Ornament to [Mercenary] Russel, he will convert it to the 2nd Job Change item.'),
(8840, 'When you bring the Dim Essence to [Mercenary] Russel, he will convert it to the Leaders Essence of the respective monster.'),
(8841, 'When you bring the Leaders Ornament to [Mercenary] Tales, he will convert it to the 2nd Job Change item.'),
(8842, 'When you bring the Dim Essence to [Mercenary] Tales, he will convert it to the Leaders Essence of the respective monster.'),
(8843, 'Currently, if you bring me [Urkthrons necklace], [Colmicolas ring], [GaruKongas belt], [Trethonzs earrings], and [Alkeradeuas belt], I will reward you with the respective [Leaders Essence]. I dont care about ability of the accessories themselves, so just bring them to me. But, you better hurry as the deadline is June 5th.'),
(8844, 'Did you bring [Urkthrons necklace]?'),
(8845, 'Did you bring [Colmicolas Ring]?'),
(8846, 'Did you bring [GaruKongas belt]?'),
(8847, 'Did you bring [Trethonzs earrings]?'),
(8848, 'Did you bring [Alkeradeuas belt]?'),
(8849, 'What the hell is this?! Are you playing around with me?! Bring me another one right now!'),
(8850, 'Oh, you brought the correct one. So do you want to exchange it?'),
(8851, 'Here you are, well done. It is good to see you smiling, and see you next time.'),
(8852, 'Currently, if you bring me [Urkthrons necklace], [Colmicolas ring], [GaruKongas belt], [Trethonzs earrings], and [Alkeradeuas belt], I will reward you with the respective [Leaders Essence]. I dont care about ability of the accessories themselves, so just bring them to me. But, you better hurry as the deadline is June 5th.'),
