(8877, 'You can get a mission to disturb the enemy nation when you go to [Search Captain] Zamed in Arrdream Karus Base with the [False Information Paper].'),
(8878, 'You can get a mission to disturb the enemy nation when you go to [Search Captain] Laek in Arrdream El Morad Base with the [False Information Paper].'),
(8879, 'You can get a mission to disturb the enemy nation when you go to [Base Spearhead] Zamed in Karus Base of Ronark Base with the [False Information Paper].'),
