(8883, 'You already rented weapons and armor for today, so return tomorrow for more.'),
(8884, 'Welcome. Our mercenary band rents the weapons for [Spirit Alseides] Of mounting at set Confirmation.'),
(8885, '<selfname> are a warrior, so (looking at the list...) Glaive and  Chitin Armor Set are ready for you. Do you want to rent?'),
(8886, '<selfname> are a rogue, so (looking at the list...) Mirage Dagger,  Chitin Bow and  Chitin Armor Set are ready for you. Do you want to rent?'),
(8887, '<selfname> are a magician, so (looking at the list...) <Elemental Staff and  Crimson Armor Set are ready for you. Do you want to rent?'),
(8888, '<selfname> are a priest, so (looking at the list...) Lycaon Mace,  Defender of the Lord and  Chitin Armor Set are ready for you. Do you want to rent?'),
(8889, '<selfname> are a warrior, so (looking at the list...) Raptor and  Chitin Shell Armor Set are ready for you. Do you want to rent?'),
(8890, '<selfname> are a rogue, so (looking at the list...) Shard,  Iron Bow and  Chitin Shell Armor Set are ready for you. Do you want to rent?'),
(8891, '<selfname> are a magician, so (looking at the list...) Elixir Staff and  Complete Armor Set are ready for you. Do you want to rent?'),
(8892, '<selfname>, since you are a Priest, (checks the log) <font color=@#660066@>Homely Animal</font>, <font color=@#660066@>Defender of Piana Knights</font>, and <font color=@#660066@>Chitin Shell Armor Set</font> has been prepared for you. Will you proceed?'),
(8893, '<selfname> are a warrior, so (looking at the list...) Beginners Sword of Mercenary and  Beginners Armor Set of Mercenary are ready for you. Do you want to rent?'),
(8894, '<selfname> are a rogue, so (looking at the list...) Beginners Dagger of Assassin and  Beginners Bow of Assassin,  Beginners Armor Set of Assassin are ready for you. Do you want to rent?'),
(8895, '<selfname> are a magician, so (looking at the list...) Staff of a rudimentary Magic Scholar and  Armor Set of a rudimentary Magic Scholar are ready for you. Do you want to rent?'),
(8896, '<selfname> are a priest, so (looking at the list...) Mace of a rudimentary Paladin and  Armor Set of a rudimentary Paladin are ready for you.  Do you want to rent?'),
(8897, 'Only users who are 30Lv or higher can participate in this event. Please return after you have trained a little more.'),
(8898, 'There is not enough space in the Inventory. To receive the item, you should have at least 6 inventory slots available.'),
(8899, 'There is not enough space in the Inventory. To receive the item, you should have at least 8 inventory slots available.'),
(8900, 'There is not enough space in the Inventory. To receive the item, you should have at least 7 inventory slots available.'),
(8901, 'What! Why did you put the Intelligence Report in the magic bag? Come again after youve put it correctly in the basic bag!'),
(8902, 'What! Why did you put the Intelligence Report in the magic bag? Come again after youve put it correctly in the basic bag!'),
(8903, 'How are you? Currently, our mercenary band is renting equipments that can be used once a day for 6 hours and are suitable for the users level. Just come to me if you are looking to rent something.'),
(8904, 'Please keep in mind that the equipment disappears after exactly 6 hours. Then, have a nice day.'),
(8905, 'Magnificent power will be given to those who want power!'),
(8906, 'Greed brings harm, so come again once you have spent your current power.'),
(8907, 'Power of protection shall be given to those who wish to protect!'),
(8908, 'Greed brings harm, so come again once you have spent your current power.'),
(8909, 'Return once you have prepared additional space.'),
(8910, 'There is no space in your bag, so please make some space available.'),
(8911, 'You already have [Poison Knife]. You can only purchase [Poison Knife] after you have used all you currently have.'),
(8912, 'We are selling [Poison Knife]. You can use it for an hour from the time of purchase regardless of how many you have. And once you have purchased [Poison Knife], you cannot buy them again until you have used all you have. Prices are as follows. Do you want to buy? 10 : 20,000 Noahs|30 : 60,000 Noahs|50 : 100,000 Noahs|100 : 200,000 Noahs'),
(8913, 'You have purchased 10 [Poison Knife].| You can buy it again when you have used all ten.'),
(8914, 'You have purchased 30 [Poison Knife].| You can buy it again when you have used all 30.'),
(8915, 'You have purchased 50 [Poison Knife].| You can buy it again when you have used all 50.'),
(8916, 'You have purchased 100 [Poison Knife].| You can buy it again when you have used all 100.'),
(8917, 'We can exchange only if you bring the [War Trophy Chest] rewarded by the person in charge of each region for the completion of Disturbing the Enemy Nation mission.'),
(8918, 'Its the War Trophy Chest of [Outpost Captain]! Incredible! Let me see... Right! You will have a nice reward!'),
(8919, 'Its the War Trophy Chest of the [Base Spearhead]! Well done, I know it must have been a difficult mission. Hmm~then, the reward is... To this side!'),
(8920, 'Its the War Trophy Chest of [Search Captain]. You did a good job. I hope you do even better next time! Now then, I ought to give you a reward...'),
(8921, 'Not all the letters are collected yet, and I can only reward you when you collect all the letters of K. N. I. G. H. T.'),
(8922, 'You brought me the complete word! Now, choose the reward that you want to have. You can apply for only one, either a game item or Premium application.  Consider it carefully as all the collected letters will disappear automatically once you make your choice.'),
(8923, 'You have chosen Item Reward. Rewardable items are as follows. You apply several times as you collect the letters. The reward items can be used for 30 minutes, and any unused items disappear automatically when the Event period ends.'),
(8924, 'You have chosen the Premium application. There are plenty of prizes available in the draw. You can apply several times as you collect the letters, and the collected letters disappear when you apply for the draw. Are you sure you want to apply?'),
(8925, 'Your application has been confirmed. The winner of the draw will be announced on the homepage later. Thanks for your application.'),
(8926, 'Your reward item has been issued. Have a pleasant day.'),
(8927, 'Gosh! Did you come to have something made? But its just that the tool I was using broke just a short while ago... I need to fix it first if I want to make a living, right? Sorry, but please wait till the tool is fixed. Im Terribly sorry.'),
(8928, 'You are not suitable for the mission, as we only accept those who are Lv.66~69.'),
(8929, 'You are not suitable for the mission, as we only accept those who are Lv.66~69.'),
(8930, 'We are selling [Poison Knife] and [Ability Up Item]. Move to each menu to purchase the respective items.'),
(8931, 'We are selling the [Ability Up Item]. You can use it for an hour from the time of purchase regardless of how many you have. And once you have purchased [Ability Up Item], you cannot buy them again until you have used all you have. The purchase price is 1 million Noahs. Do you want to buy it?'),
(8932, 'You already have this item. You can buy it again only after you have used all you currently have.'),
(8933, 'You have purchased [Scroll of Atk Up].|You can buy it again only after you have used all you currently have.'),
(8934, 'You have purchased [Scroll of 350 Atk Up].|ou can buy it again only after you have used all you currently have.'),
(8935, 'You have purchased [Speed Up Potion].|ou can buy it again only after you have used all you currently have.'),
(8936, '[2000 HP Increase Scroll] has been purchased. It has to be used completely to purchase again.'),
(8937, 'I heard that [Mercenary Quartermaster] has opened up the Arsenal and renting the equipments inside!'),
(8938, 'I heard that [Mercenary Quartermaster] has opened up the Arsenal and renting the equipments inside!'),
(8939, 'We are currently receiving applications for the upcoming  4th World Championship.  Anybody who wants to make the Entry Application can do it by paying an  Entry Application Fee of 100,000 Noahs. But, 100,000 Noahs will not be refunded even if you do not get selected in the draw. Do you want to receive the entry guide?'),
(8940, '    The 4th World IChampionship Guide|- Application to be made to [World Championship Dispatcher] from Aug. 7th ~Aug. 11th |- Prize winner confirmation : Homepage Pop-up on Aug. 18th.|- Application Fee : 100,000 Noahs|- Once applied, the entry application fee isnt refundable even if you are not selected in the draw.'),
(8941, '    The 4th World Championship Guide II|- when applying to enter, 100% entry User | - July Top 20 Clans by Server and Clan leaders of Top 20 Clans by nation (40 person) :  Total 280 person from Servers| - Top 50 ranked on the ladder ranking per nation and per server (100 person) : Total 1400 person from Servers| - King of each Server : Total 14 person from Servers|- 100% of all users who applied and satisfy the above conditions will be selected, but without an application the eligible users will not be able to participate.'),
(8942, 'If you choose [Participate], your entry application and payment of 100,000 Noahs will be processed immediately, and if you click [Apply later], application will be cancelled. For more information, choose [Read Guide Again].'),
(8943, 'Your entry application has been processed. |For the announcement of the winners, can check the Pop-up of our homepage on Aug.18th.|Thanks.'),
(8944, 'Your entry application has already been processed. The date of the winner announcement is Aug. 18th. Thank you.'),
(8945, 'We are currently receiving applications for the upcoming  4th World Championship.  Anybody who wants to make the Entry Application can do it by paying an  Entry Application Fee of 100,000 Noahs. But, 100,000 Noahs will not be refunded even if you do not get selected in the draw. Do you want to receive the entry guide?'),
(8946, '    The 4th World IChampionship Guide|- Application to be made to [World Championship Dispatcher] from Aug. 7th ~Aug. 11th |- Prize winner confirmation : Homepage Pop-up on Aug. 18th.|- Application Fee : 100,000 Noahs|- Once applied, the entry application fee isnt refundable even if you are not selected in the draw.'),
(8947, '    The 4th World Championship Guide II|- when applying to enter, 100% entry User | - July Top 20 Clans by Server and Clan leaders of Top 20 Clans by nation (40 person) :  Total 280 person from Servers| - Top 50 ranked on the ladder ranking per nation and per server (100 person) : Total 1400 person from Servers| - King of each Server : Total 14 person from Servers|- 100% of all users who applied and satisfy the above conditions will be selected, but without an application the eligible users will not be able to participate.'),
(8948, 'If you choose [Participate], your entry application and payment of 100,000 Noahs will be processed immediately, and if you click [Apply later], application will be cancelled. For more information, choose [Read Guide Again].'),
(8949, 'Your entry application has been processed. |For the announcement of the winners, can check the Pop-up of our homepage on Aug.18th.|Thanks.'),
(8950, 'Your entry application has already been processed. The date of the winner announcement is Aug. 18th. Thank you.'),
(8951, 'Due to a system error, equipments of Lv. 30~46 cannot be rented right now. The service will be restored as quickly as possible. We are sorry.'),
(8952, 'You dont have enough Noah. You need 100,000 Noahs for the entry application.'),
(8953, 'You dont have enough Noah. You need 100,000 Noahs for the entry application.'),
(8954, 'You can acquire the Blue Treasure Chest of the Forgotten Temple by completing [Commissarial] Parrents mission.'),
(8955, 'You can acquire the Blue Treasure Chest of the Forgotten Temple by completing [Commissarial] Baelertzs mission.'),
(8956, 'Master! You have completed all the missions! As expected, El Morad wasnt your match!'),
(8957, 'A new war zone has been created. Those wicked El Morad provoked us first! Its an important strategical point, we, Karus, must take it to have an edge in the upcoming battles!'),
(8958, 'New war needs a new hero! Return after you have defeated 40 wicked El Morads!'),
(8959, 'Good! Smashing! Right, depart now! My fingers are crossed! Death to anyone who dares to stand in your way!'),
(8960, 'What is it? Its still not enough! Hurry and get back quickly!'),
(8961, 'You have returned with your mission completed! A hero should get the war trophy deserving of his prowess!'),
(8962, 'Finishing one mission isnt the end! Youd better keep challenging for more missions, as more you complete the better war trophy you will get at the end of the war!'),
(8963, 'As expected of the Master! You defeated those brutal Karus! Lets hurry back and report the competion of your mission!'),
(8964, 'Well.. We discovered a new war zone, this time. We realized that it was a strategically important point, and launched the first attack but were stopped by the soldiers of Karus who noticed what we were doing.'),
(8965, 'By occupying this region we can drive out the brutal Karus and continue the glory of El Morad. Please return once you have defeated 40 Karus on the battlefield.'),
(8966, 'Good. Then, just leave for the battle zone right now. Glory to you sword!'),
(8967, 'What happened to you? You still havet left?'),
(8968, 'You have performed excellently. I have prepared a war trophy for you.'),
(8969, 'Finishing one mission isnt the end. More missions you complete, the better war trophy you will get at the end of the war. So please keep on challenging.'),
(8970, 'It isnt yet the time to use this power.'),
(8971, 'We are sorry. You cannot access the Royal Promotion Dungeon due to an error. We will try to fix the problem as quickly as possible.'),
(8972, 'We are sorry. You cannot access the Royal Promotion Dungeon due to an error. We will try to fix the problem as quickly as possible.'),
(8973, 'To exchange the Minerva clothings you need the [Minerva Armor Certificate] or the [Minerva Hemlet Certificate] issued at a Power-up store.|There are two types of certificate where one is for 2 months use while the other is for 30 days, and please select the [Individual Voucher] if you made your purchase prior to the integration.'),
(8974, 'Special Event for Thanksgiving Holiday! It is the Transformation Scroll Event! Now, we are giving special Pet Transformation Scrolls to those who collected 50 Runes of Conversion.  It is a great chance to evolve your pet into a special Pet! There are also chances of getting Krowaz, Giaga Hammer, or Cuff Binder Pet Transformation Scrolls!'),
(8975, 'Would you like to exchange it?'),
(8976, 'Insufficient space in the inventory. Please check again.'),
(8977, 'You have chosen the [Cuff Binder Pet Transformation Scroll]. Would you like to exchange it?'),
(8978, 'There are not enough Runes of Conversion. You need 50 for the exchange.|You can get the Rune of Conversion when you win a match against [Doge Girl] in Yut game.'),
(8979, 'It has been exchanged with a [Giga Hammer Transformation Scroll]. Thank you.'),
(8980, 'It has been exchanged with a [Krowaz Transformation Scroll]. Thank you.'),
(8981, 'It has been exchanged with a [Krowaz Transformation Scroll]. Thank you.'),
(8982, 'It requires either a [Minerva Helmet Certificate (30 days)] or [Minerva Armor Certificate (30 days)]. Please check again.'),
(8983, 'It requires either a [Minerva Helmet Certificate (2 months)] or a [Minerva Armor Certificate (2 months)]. Please check again.'),
(8984, 'It requires a [Minerva Armor Certificate]. Please check again.'),
(8985, 'It requires a [Minerva Helmet Certificate]. Please check again.'),
(8986, 'A monk with two faces.. Be careful of the darkness! In the darkness, a monk who lost his spirit can stare at you from behind you.'),
(8987, 'Master, now that you have become 60 level, it will be better for you to try more adventures at the Ronarkland stronghold. Please go see <font color=@#990000@>Cruzed at the Ronarkland stronghold</font>'),
(8988, 'Mmh?? It went over 74 level..it is too high. Huh-'),
(8989, 'I dont want to get near to...a person like you who doesnt have any composure. Ah...I feel bad'),
(8990, 'He is a wandering monk of Esoteric Buddhism..but his true identity is an outrageous wizard of darkness? Here it is also called <font color=@#660066@>Paramun</font>. Isnt the name cute? Haha..'),
(8991, 'I dont know why but I am afraiod of Cruzed even more.'),
(8992, 'Be careful..Darkness is spreading.. Darkness..'),
(8993, 'Did you have a fight with Paramun? Haha.. Dont make a face like that. Dont you think that you had good experiences to some extent?'),
(8996, 'A monk with two faces.. Be careful of the darkness! In the darkenss, a monk who lost his spirit can stare at you from behind you.'),
(8997, 'Master, now that you have become 60 level, it will be better for you to try more adventures at the Ronarkland stronghold. Please go to see <font color=@#990000@>Krable at the Ronarkland stronghold</font>'),
(8998, 'Mmh?? It went over 74 level..it is too high. Huh-'),
(8999, 'I dont want to get near to...a person like you who doesnt have any composure. Ah...I feel bad'),
(9000, 'He is a wandering monk of Esoteric Buddhism..but his true identity is an outrageous wizard of darkness. Here it is also called <font color=@#660066@>Para Moon</font>. Isnt the name cute? Haha..'),
(9001, 'I dont why but I am afraiod of Krable even more.'),
(9002, 'Be careful..Darkness is spreading.. Darkness..'),
(9003, 'Did you have a fight with Paramun? Haha.. Dont make a face like that. Dont you think that you had good experiences to some extent?'),
