(9051, 'I was waiting for you. The superiors are expecting a lot of <selfname> who has distinguished himself in war many times so far. It is a guerilla warfare this time too. Of course, you have to carry out the task by yourself in the same way as you did with the previous tasks. Are you ready?'),
