(9054, 'Please catch 60 Haungas. Ill tell you once more. You have to perform the task by yourself.|# When the party play is performed with the [Repeat Quest] which can perform this Quest up to Lv. 60 to 65, the monster counter doesnt go up but the counter goes up only when solo play is performed.'),
(9055, 'Oh, you completed the task! Thanks a lot. For your information, please note that this Quest can be performed repeatedly up to 65 levels.'),
(9056, 'You have already passed the level that you can perform.'),
(9057, 'You have already passed the level that you can perform.'),
(9058, 'You selected the Transparent Minerbas armor HP+200. Do you really want to receive this?'),
(9059, 'You selected the Transparent Minerbas armor defensive power +30. Do you really want to receive this?'),
(9060, 'You selected the Transparent Minerbas armor experience value acquisition rate +4%. Do you really want to receive this?'),
(9061, 'You selected the Transparent Minerbas armor Noah drop rate +6%. Do you really want to receive this?'),
(9062, 'You selected the Transparent Minerbas helmet HP+100. Do you really want to receive this?'),
(9063, 'You selected the Transparent Minerbas helment defensive power +20. Do you really want to receive this?'),
(9064, 'You selected the Transparent Minerbas helmet experience value acquisition rate +2%. Do you really want to receive this?'),
(9065, 'You selected the Transparent Minerbas helmet Noah drop rate +3%. Do you really want to receive this?'),
(9066, 'Long time no see! Are you asking me why I stand here? I am here to provide the exchange to the people who bring [war supplies]!| It looks like a lot of pretty good stuff are coming out! Do you want to challenge it? [War supplies] are sold at the power up store!'),
(9067, 'Oh! <selfname>! You brought war supplies! And then lets see what you have inside? Expectedly, it looks like the goods have exceed our expectations.'),
(9068, 'There is no room in the bag! You empty it first and then I can give it to you!'),
(9069, 'Well, we did the exchange! I hope the stuff you like has arrived!'),
(9070, 'Mmh? There isnt any item that I can exchange for, is there? Confirm again and come back.'),
(9071, 'How are you doing?  Im back once again to give you your presents!  What are they?  I could tell you, but youll get a BIGGER surprise if you find out for yourself!  Youll have to work hard to figure it out though!'),
(9072, 'Oh no, all the presents are gone!  I somehow managed to lose all the presents and Christmas Trees while I was coming here!  Tell you what:  Bring me 10 [Lost present]s and 10 [Christmas Tree]s and Ill make a nice present just for you!'),
(9073, 'Youve found the lost [Christmas Tree]s and [Lost present]s!  Here you go!'),
(9074, 'Great Scott!  Youve managed to create me!'),
(9075, 'What did one snowman say to the other snowman?  Give up?  DO YOU SMELL CARROTS?  GET IT?  BAHAHAHAHA!  Since Im in a jolly mood, Ill give you one present.'),
(9076, 'You do not recognize me? How dare you! I am [Happy Snowman]! Someone said I am the messenger of Love! MUHAHAHA! For that, I will give you a present! Well, Take your pick. It will give you a blessing!'),
(9077, 'Hey, dont be greedy, one at a time ONE AT A TIME! If you keep bothering me, Ill fill your stocking full of coal!'),
(9078, 'Well then, have a Merry Christmas! You should spend Christmas with family, ok?'),
(9079, 'The Christmas Event is currently underway.  So what am I doing this for even though Santa is here?  Im getting paid a fortune!'),
(9080, '[Sexy Santa] Parpe asked me a favor. She asked me to give out the following items to whoever brings me [Lost Present] and [Christmas Tree]. How much shes paying me to do this? That is secret. |#Santas Coat : Defense increse by 30 for 30 minutes|#Santas Mind : Raise HP by 250 for 30 minutes|#Santas Smile : Extra 10% EXP gain for 30 minutes|#Santas Present :  Extra 2 NP points gain for 30 minutes'),
(9081, 'Did you bring me the items? Five [Lost Present]s?  Lets see... one, two...five, yes, all here. Nice work! Well then, pick a reward you like.'),
(9082, 'You must bring me 5 [Lost Present] and 5 [Christmas Tree]'),
(9083, 'Do you want a Transformation scroll? Besides items obtained by combininations, I can give you snowman transformation scroll for exchange. If you get lucky you could transform into me -- but theres a low chance of that happening.'),
(9084, 'Here you go! Did you get the one you wanted?'),
(9085, 'Right now, the [high level border defense compensation ascent scroll] and [low level border defense compensation ascent scroll] which have been obtained at the border defending battle are exchanged with a class that you want to have respectively. Those people who cant use them, as they are not appropriate for the current level, are allowed to exchange them so that they can use them. # Exchange period: December 18 to December 22'),
(9086, 'It is an exchange of the [high level border defense compensation ascent scroll] with the [low level border defense compensation ascent scroll]. Do you want to have the exchange?'),
(9087, 'It is an exchange of the [low level border defense compensation ascent scroll] with the [high level border defense compensation ascent scroll]. Do you want to have the exchange?'),
(9088, 'They have been exchanged normally.'),
(9089, 'Thanks a lot. Have a Merry Christmas!'),
(9090, 'You dont have a scroll. Only one who has a scroll can have the exchange.'),
(9091, ' Information on the provision of the materials for supporting Karus people|- The materials to be provided here are the materials which the King of Karus will use ¡‰or the people of Karus.|- The materials for supporting the people shall be provided from December 31, 2008 to January 29, 2009.|- The materials can be received by the King and the room of 16 or more compartments is needed in 5 inventories.|- If you received the last provision on the same day of the previous week, you cant receive the provision. |- Please be sure to confirm whether the provision was received on the same day of the previous week|- Example) If the material was received on Monday of the first week and then it has not been received at all until Monday of the second week, the material cant be provided.'),
(9092, 'How are you? My name is Bell. I am the secretary of His Royal Highness, the King. His Royal Highness, the King is currently helping the people of Karus so that they can receive the produced materials once a day. |#Period of provision: December 31, 2008 to January 29, 2009'),
(9093, 'You have already received the materials. Materials provided only once a day!!! You can receive them only once. Do you understand? His Royal Highness, the King? Please keep this in your mind.'),
(9094, 'The list of materials which are provided now is as follows and in order to receive them normally, you need to have an inventory space of 16 or more compartments.|#Period of provision: December 31, 2008 to January 29, 2009|# Pledge of allegiance: Experience value went up by 30%|# Pledge of honor: Contribution+3 added|# Epic of Chevalier: Movement velocity went up by 150%|# Valor of Chevalier: Striking power went up by 20%|# Shelter of Chevalier: Defensive power went up by 350|# Guard of Chevalier: Defensive power went up by 300|# Spirit of Chevalier: Maximum HP2000 increase|# Soul of Chevalier: Maximum HP1500 increase'),
(9095, 'His Majesty, you dont have enough space in the inventory. You need to empty the space and be ready to receive.'),
(9096, 'You are not His Royal Highness, the King. Can you go back?'),
(9097, 'All of the materials have been provided just as listed without any problems. Please use them for all of the people of Karus.'),
(9098, ' Information on the provision of the materials for supporting El Morad people|- The materials to be provided here are the materials which the King of El Morad will use ¡‰or the people of El Morad.|- The materials for supporting the people shall be provided from December 31, 2008 to January 29, 2009.|- The materials can be received by the King and the room of 16 or more compartments is needed in the inventory.|- If you received the last provision on the same day of the previous week, you cant receive the provision. |- Please be sure to confirm whether the provision was received on the same day of the previous week|- Example) If the material was received on Monday of the first week and then it has not been received at all until Monday of the second week, the material cant be provided.'),
(9099, 'How are you? My name is Leed. I am the secretary of His Royal Highness, the King. His Royal Highness, the King is currently helping the people of El Morad so that they can receive the produced materials once a day. |#Period of provision: December 31, 2008 to January 29, 2009'),
(9100, 'There seems to be a mistake. You have already received them. I never doubt the integrity of His Royal Highness, the King but let me be bold enough to ask you, You didnt come here in an expectation that you could receive them again, did you?'),
(9101, 'This is the list of the materials which can be provided now. Please confirm it. Please note that in order to receive the materials now, you need to have a space of about 16 compartments in the inventory.|# Period of provision: December 31, 2008 to January 29, 2009|# Pledge of allegiance: Experience value went up by 30%|# Pledge of honor: Contribution+3 added|# Epic of Chevalier: Movement velocity went up by 150%|# Valor of Chevalier: Striking power went up by 20%|# Shelter of Chevalier: Defensive power went up by 350|# Guard of Chevalier: Defensive power went up by 300|# Spirit of Chevalier: Maximum HP2000 increase|# Soul of Chevalier: Maximum HP1500 increase'),
(9102, 'You dont have enough space in the inventory. Your Majesty, even I cant put them in unless the space is emptied.'),
(9103, 'Unless my eyes are in trouble now, you, who is in front of me, are not the His Royal Highness, the King, are you?'),
(9104, 'All of the materials have been provided for completely. I will not doubt that all of the materials will be used for the people of El Morad according to the wise judgment of His Royal Highness.'),
(9105, 'Happy New Year!'),
(9106, 'Our big holiday, New Years Day, has come! And I have come too! Are you asking me what this is? Of course, this is for the distribution of presents. However, you think there is no such thing as free stuff in this world, dont you? Hoho, if you go to the island over there to which I will send you, there will be Etaroths. These guys swallowed the [lucky bag]. It is unfortunate but please take the [lucky bag] back from those guys. I will combine them as a present! Uhm.. If you have 20 [lucky bags], the combination will be possible! Now it occurs me that a kid called [Parfait] also asked to do this kind of stuff some time ago. However! My present is better!'),
(9107, 'Did you bring all of the [lucky bags]!? Then lets start the combination right now!'),
(9108, 'If you go to the island, you can obtain the lucky bag by catching Etaroth!! Are you going to move now?'),
(9109, 'You appear to have brought the NPC exchange coupon. Depending on the exchange coupon, it can be exchanged with the following order sheet. What do you want to exchange?'),
(9110, 'Exchange has been successful! Have a happy new years day!'),
(9111, 'There is no exchange coupon to be exchanged. In order to get an exchange coupon, you have to bring a lucky bag and carry out the combination.'),
(9112, 'How are you? I am the Enchanter dispatched to Luferson Castle. I offer buffs to help you on your journey. The are three types of buffs that you can receive: attack power, defensive power and enhancement of physical strength, and they can be stacked! Possible payment means are Noah, and for those people between level 36 and 60, can pay with the [sign of victory] too.'),
(9113, 'Knights between levels 1 and 35 can use it free of charge. The list of  buffs which a user can receive is as follows: |#Shout for charge: Attack power 10%|# Firm will: Defensive power 100|# Endless patience: Enhancement of physical strength by 500 |The price is 30000 Noah per buff. It can also be paid by one [sign of victory].'),
(9114, 'This is the list of buffs which a user between levels 36 and 60 can receive: |#Shout for charge: Attack power 10%|# Unbeatable will: Defensive power 150|# Unlimited patience: Enhancement of physical strength by 800|The price is 30000 Noah per buff. It can also be paid by two [signs of victory].'),
(9115, 'This is the list of buffs which a user between levels 61 and 83 can receive:|# Shout for charge: Attack power 10%|# Unyielding will: Defensive power 200|# Extreme patience: Enhancement of physical strength by 1000|The price is 50000 Noah per buff.'),
(9116, 'Information on the NPC buff payment|- It is free for a customer who is at the level between Lv. 1 and 35..|- The three types of buffs, enhancement of striking power, enhancement of defensive power and enhancement of physical strength, are provided for 30 minutes.|- The buff provided varies depending on the degree of level and the money to be paid also varies.|- The three types of buffs can be overlaid with each other and as for the buff that has already been received, it cant be received again unless the time has expired or cancelled.'),
(9117, 'Please select your method of payment. Buffs are free for a customer between the levels of 1 and 35.|#Lv.1~35: Free |# Noah : 10000 Noah consumed |# sign of victory : One used'),
(9118, 'The payment means are not enough. Please confirm it again.'),
(9119, 'Please select the buff you would like to receive.|# Shout for charge : Attack power 10%|# Firm will: Defensive power 100|# Endless patience: Enhancement of physical strength by 500'),
(9120, 'Please select the buff you would like to receive.|# Shout for charge : Attack power 10%|# Unbeatable will: Defensive power 150|# Unlimited patience: Enhancement of physical strength by 800'),
(9121, 'Please select the buff you would like to receive.|# Shout for charge : Attack power 10%|# Unyielding will: Defensive power 200|# Extreme patience: Enhancement of physical strength by 1000'),
(9122, 'Please select your method of payment. |#Noah : 30000 Noah consumed |# sign of victory : Two used'),
(9123, 'Please select your method of payment. |#Noah : 50000 Noah consumed'),
(9124, 'It has been completed. Have a good time.'),
(9125, 'How are you? I am the Enchanter dispatched to El Morad Castle.  I offer buffs to help you on your journey. The are three types of buffs that you can receive: attack power, defensive power and enhancement of physical strength, and they can be stacked! Possible payment means are Noah, and for those people between level 36 and 60, can pay with the [sign of victory] too.'),
(9126, 'Knights between levels 1 and 35 can use it free of charge. The list of  buffs which a user can receive is as follows: |#Shout for charge: Attack power 10%|# Firm will: Defensive power 100|# Endless patience: Enhancement of physical strength by 500 |The price is 30000 Noah per buff. It can also be paid by one [sign of victory].'),
