(9130, 'Please select your method of payment. Buffs are free for a customer between the levels of 1 and 35.|#Lv.1~35: Free |# Noah : 10000 Noah consumed |# sign of victory : One used'),
(9131, 'The payment means are not enough. Please confirm it again.'),
(9132, 'Please select the buff you would like to receive.|# Shout for charge : Attack power 10%|# Firm will: Defensive power 100|# Endless patience: Enhancement of physical strength by 500'),
(9133, 'Please select the buff you would like to receive.|# Shout for charge : Attack power 10%|# Unbeatable will: Defensive power 150|# Unlimited patience: Enhancement of physical strength by 800'),
(9134, 'Please select the buff you would like to receive.|# Shout for charge : Attack power 10%|# Unyielding will: Defensive power 200|# Extreme patience: Enhancement of physical strength by 1000'),
(9135, 'Please select your method of payment. |#Noah : 30000 Noah consumed |# sign of victory : Two used'),
(9136, 'Please select your method of payment. |#Noah : 50000 Noah consumed'),
(9137, 'It has been completed. Have a good time.'),
(9138, 'How are you? I am the Enchanter dispatched to Moradon Castle.  I offer buffs to help you on your journey. The are three types of buffs that you can receive: attack power, defensive power and enhancement of physical strength, and they can be stacked! Possible payment means are Noah, and for those people between level 36 and 60, can pay with the [sign of victory] too.'),
(9139, 'This buff is already in use. You cant receive the same type of buff repeatedly.'),
(9140, 'This buff is already in use. You cant receive the same type of buff repeatedly.'),
(9141, 'I am standing here for those people who want to go back to Moradon. Are you going back to Moradon?'),
(9144, 'You do not possess the right item.'),
(9145, 'You have brought the event item voucher. Would you like to trade in the voucher?'),
(9146, 'The [NPC change scroll voucher] received from [Daily check event] is being changed to your matching nations scrolls. You may use this menu to trade in the voucher.'),
(9147, 'See you next time!'),
(9148, 'Hello!'),
(9149, '??, ??? ????... ?? ?????? ? ??...?? ???? ??? ????! ?? ?????? ??? ?? ?? ?? ???? ?? ?? ??? ???. ??? ?? ??? ??? ??? ????? ??? ?? ???. ?? ????... ? ??? ??? ? ?? ?? ?? ???? ?????. ???? ???? ??? ? ??? ?? ???????? ???? ?????. ?? ???? ?? ???? ????.'),
(9150, 'Hello! I am luxury chocolate maker [Chocolatier]Cacao. My chocolates have a history of over 300 years and have an exquisite.. Hm.. Hm.. What are you looking for?'),
(9151, 'You have brought the chocolates! Its covered in dirt but.. Damn.. Oops. I should kill that son of a.. Oops.. We should teach him a lesson. Tee hee hee.. Anyways would you like to trade the item you brought?'),
(9152, 'You have received the pickaxe already huh? Since Im not supporting <selfname> because I can, Ill have to charge you from now on. How much? Its just 1 million Noah.'),
(9153, 'Its you first time right? Its free for the first time. But after long period of use it will wear out and you will have to purchase a new one!'),
(9154, 'Its yours! Hope you can bring me as much chocolate as possible.'),
(9155, 'You dont have enough space in your bag. Make some room and come again.'),
(9156, 'Its has been traded. Have a happy Valentines day.'),
(9157, 'You dont have a voucher. Please check again.'),
(9158, 'You have a voucher? May I take a look at it?'),
(9159, 'You have brought a wedding voucher. With this you can receive a free groom or bride enchantment. Which one would you like?'),
(9160, 'Bouquet and flower shield vouchers may be traded in here. Which one would you like?'),
(9161, 'You do not have enough Noah. To buy a pickaxe you need 1 million Noah.'),
(9162, 'Hi! Im [Camouflage Master] Serena. I came to Adonis to help you get transformed!'),
(9163, 'Price? Its not free. Pay 450,000 and youll get a random scroll out of 7 possible. Nothings free!'),
(9164, 'Sorry pal, but youre running low on funds. Come back after pay day.'),
(9165, 'Thanks, and heres your scroll.  Take care!'),
(9166, 'Info of Random Transformation Scroll|- 450000 coins required.| - 1 scroll in 7 scrolls in random.| - Scroll Information| #Snowman Nunu|#Snowman Titi|#Snowman Teo| #Snowman Porum|#Magpie |#Sexy Santa| #Dream Girl'),
(9167, 'I will look forward to our next encounter.'),
(9168, 'How do you do? What brings you to me today?'),
(9169, 'Why am I standing here? Is it not obvious? I am standing here because I am a miner! Why is a miner standing here? So I can mine ores! You sure ask silly questions! Then why am I not mining any ores? It is bothersome, that is why, you smirk bastard! Actually, this is great. Go over there and start mining some ores for me. You do not know how to? Here, I will give you a Mattock, so hold this and press [Sparce Bar] near the ore veins. Then you will automatically start mining. Go on now! If you mine up some [Mysterious Ore], I will purify it and then craft it into a useful item for you! Run along now!'),
(9170, 'The weather sure is great today. Who are you? What do you want?'),
(9171, 'Oh, you actually managed to find [Mysterious Ore] and [Mysterious Gold Ore]. Well, do you want me to purify it and turn it into an item?'),
(9172, 'What? You want a Mattock? You took one before. I cannot just keep giving away Mattock for free, so I will give you a Mattock for 1 M Noah.'),
(9173, 'Mattock? Heres a spare one. No need to pay for it. Just go mine up some ores already. For your information, it has to be repaired when it runs out of durability, or else you will have to purchase it from me again.'),
(9174, 'Here, take it.'),
(9175, 'Did you check your bag space? How packed is it if you cannot even accept this? Come back after you free up some space!'),
(9176, 'Here, take it. Hopefully it is something you wanted.'),
(9177, 'You do not have the [Exchange Coupon]. Check again!'),
(9178, 'Which [Exchange Coupon] did you bring?'),
(9179, 'Bring me [Mysterious Ore] and [Mysterious Gold Ore! Hurry and go mine it up!'),
(9181, 'That will be 1 M Noah. 1 M Noah, I tell you. You have to bring me 1 M Noah!'),
(9182, '   Information on Lunar Spy & Dark Lunar Spy|- This quest must be done on the War Map during the Lunar War on Monday and Thursday or during the Dark Lunar War on Wednesday. |- Please note that this quest cannot be completed except on the designated War days listed above.'),
(9183, '   Information on Lunar Spy & Dark Lunar Spy|- This quest must be done on the War Map during the Lunar War on Monday and Thursday or during the Dark Lunar War on Wednesday. |- Please note that this quest cannot be completed except on the designated War days listed above.'),
(9184, '       What you need to know during Mission Quest|- This quest is rather difficult relative to its level requirement. Users who are unfamiliar with Knights Online should be aware of this.|- Users should also note that during this mission, Contribution Points and Experience Points can be lost.'),
(9185, '       What you need to know during Mission Quest|- This quest is rather difficult relative to its level requirement. Users who are unfamiliar with Knights Online should be aware of this.|- Users should also note that during this mission, Contribution Points and Experience Points can be lost.'),
(9186, 'Master! [Mercenary] Russell urgently requires your help! He must be struggling against strong enemies!'),
(9187, 'Greetings! How about hunting the Boss of each region this time?  Each Boss is well known among its own kind.'),
(9188, 'Your mission is not complete. I can only advise you when your missions are complete.'),
(9189, 'Master! [Mercenary] Talesl urgently requires your help! He must be struggling against strong enemies!'),
(9190, 'Greetings! How about hunting the Boss of each region this time? Each Boss is well known among its own kind.'),
(9191, 'Your mission is not complete. I can only advise you when your missions are complete.'),
(9192, 'Troll Armor can be crafted and acquired by paying 100 K Noahs during Level 50  to Level 59. The available accessories are [Gloves], [Boots], [Helmet], [Lower Garment], and [Upper Garment]. These items can be purchased only after all the required quests have been completed.'),
(9193, 'The fee is 100 K Noahs. Well, which part do you want?'),
(9194, 'You dont have 100 K Noahs? No money, no goods, so youd better get some.'),
(9195, 'You do not have enough inventory space. Come back after you have secured some free space.'),
(9196, '[Lamia Hunt] quest must be completed before you can buy this.|- Karus: [Guard] Hashan from Linate Village|- El Morad: [Guard] Beth from Raiba Village.'),
(9197, '[Uruk Hai Hunt] quest must be completed before you can buy this.|- Karus: [Guard] Hashan from Linate Village|- El Morad: [Guard] Beth from Raiba Village.'),
(9198, '[Haunga Warrior Hunt] quest must be completed before you can buy this.|- Karus: [Imperial Guard] Bekar from Luferson Castle|- [Imperial Guard] Telson from El Morad Castle'),
(9199, '[Dragon Tooth Soldier Hunt] quest must be completed before you can buy this.|- Karus: [Mercenary] Russell from Raon Camp|- El Morad : [Mercenary] Tales from Doda Camp'),
(9200, '[Ancient Hunt] quest must be completed before you can buy this.|- Karus: [Guard] Hashan from Linate Village|- El Morad: [Guard] Beth from Raiba Village.'),
(9201, 'The Troll Armor that has been provided for you can be purchased from [Blacksmith] Hepa from Moradon Castle for 100 K Noahs. However, the armor can be purchased only after all the required quests have been completed.'),
(9202, 'The Troll Armor that has been provided for you can be purchased from [Blacksmith] Hepa from Moradon Castle for 100 K Noahs. However, the armor can be purchased only after all the required quests have been completed.'),
(9203, '           WARNING!!!|- This quest can only be completed during [Lunar War].|- To carry out the quest, your faction must win in [Lunar War] and infiltrate a hostile nation.|- [Crest] can be acquired by hunting [Leech] during your infiltration in the hostile nation.'),
(9204, 'Please select which effect you would like to receive. |#Cry for Charge: 150% Increment of Magic Power|#Firm Will : Defense 100|#Endless Patience : HP Increased by 500'),
(9205, 'Greetings! I am an Enchanter from Moradon Castle. I am currently charging a regular fee for casting desired Buffs. The 3 Buffs I service are Attack Power, Defense Power, and HP Increment. They may overlap. I accept payments in Noah but I also accept [Insignia of Victor] from those who are between Level 20 to Level 60.'),
(9206, 'Please select which effect you would like to receive. |#Cry for Charge: 150% Increment of Magic Power|#Firm Will : Defense 100|#Endless Patience : HP Increased by 500'),
(9207, 'Please select which effect you would like to receive. |#Cry for Charge: 150% Increment of Magic Power|#Firm Will : Defense 150|#Endless Patience : HP Increased by 800'),
(9208, 'Back, are you? Seeing as you already borrowed once today, you can borrow them again for twice the fee. The individual fees are as follows:| Lv.30~46 : 200 K Noah|Lv.47~59 : 600 K Noah|Lv.60~83 : 1 M Noah|'),
(9209, '<selfname>, since you are a Warrior, (checks the log? <font color=@#660066@>Glaive</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Chitin Armor Set</font> have been prepared for you. The rental cost will be 600 K Noahs. Proceed?'),
(9210, '<selfname>, since you are a Rogue, (checks the log) <font color=@#660066@>Mirage Dagger</font>, <font color=@#660066@>Chitin Bow</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Chitin Armor Set</font> have been prepared for you. The rental cost will be 600 K Noah. Proceed?'),
(9211, '<selfname>, since you are a Mage, (checks the log) <font color=@#660066@>Elemental Staff</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Crimson Armor Set</font> have been prepared for you. The rental cost will be 600 K Noah. Proceed?'),
(9212, '<selfname>, since you are a Priest, (checks the log) <font color=@#660066@>Recaon Mace</font>, <font color=@#660066@>Defender of the Road</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Chitin Armor Set</font> have been prepared for you. The rental cost will be 600 K Noah. Proceed?'),
(9213, '<selfname>, since you are a Warrior, (checks the log) <font color=@#660066@>Raptor</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Chitin Shell Armor Set</font> have been prepared for you. The rental cost will be 1 M Noah. Proceed?'),
(9214, '<selfname>, since you are a Rogue, (checks the log) <font color=@#660066@>Shard</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Iron Bow</font>, <font color=@#660066@>Chitin Shell Armor Set</font> have been prepared for you. The rental cost will be 1 M Noah. Proceed?'),
(9215, '<selfname>, since you are a Mage, (checks the log) <font color=@#660066@>Elixir Staff</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Complete Armor Set</font> have been prepared for you. The rental cost will be 1 M Noah. Will you proceed?'),
(9216, '<selfname>, since you are a Priest, (checks the log) <font color=@#660066@>Homely Animal</font>, <font color=@#660066@>Defender of Piana Knights</font>and <font color=@#660066@>Chitin Shell Armor Set</font> have been prepared for you. The rental cost will be 1 M Noah. Proceed?'),
(9217, '<selfname>, since you are a Warrior, (checks the log) <font color=@#660066@>Novice Mercenary Sword</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Novice Mercenary Armor Set</font> have been prepared for you. The rental cost will be 200 K Noah. Will you proceed?'),
(9218, '<selfname>, since you are a Rogue, (checks the log) <font color=@#660066@>Novice Assassin Short Knife</font>, <font color=@#660066@>Novice Assassin Bow</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Novice Assassin Armor Set</font> have been prepared for you. The rental cost will be 200 K Noah. Will you proceed?'),
(9219, '<selfname>, since you are a Mage, (checks the log) <font color=@#660066@>Novice Wicked Scholar Staff</font>and <font color=@#660066@>Novice Wicked Scholar Armor Set</font> have been prepared for you. The rental cost will be 200 K Noah. Proceed?'),
(9220, '<selfname>, since you are a Priest, (checks the log) <font color=@#660066@>Novice Paladin Mace</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Novice Paladin Armor Set</font> have been prepared for you. The rental cost will be 200 K Noah. Will you proceed?'),
(9221, '[Mercenary] Russell has commissioned you to hunt [Boss].|# You can locate the [Boss] Monster with ease if you click Full Map (Shortcut Key::M) and then use the [NPC&MOB Search] option.'),
(9222, '[Mercenary] Tales has commissioned you to hunt [Boss].|# You can locate the [Boss] Monster with ease if you click Full Map (Shortcut Key::M) and then use the [NPC&MOB Search] option.'),
(9223, 'Do you know what a Cardinal is?')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(9224, 'A Cardinal is a magical lifeform created when Pathos cast a curse on a Scarecrow. No one knows how these monsters managed to wander onto the Adonis continent, but lately weve had a few show up on the outskirts of our village.'),
(9225, 'It was only yesterday. A Guard out on a patrol discovered a bunch of these monsters. It wasnt a big deal with only one or two of them around, but they increase in number every day.'),
(9226, 'At this rate, the monsters will overwhelm not only our village, but all of Adonis itself. We are currently working with other [Secret Agents] to eradicate them but were shorthanded. <selfname>, please help us.'),
(9227, 'I entrust this matter to you. Time is ticking so you should be on the move.'),
(9228, 'Quite a few Cardinals have been found in places other than the outskirts of the village.'),
(9229, 'Those monsters were multiplying fast, but you put a stop to THAT! Please go see [Secret Agent] Clarence!'),
(9230, 'Those monsters were multiplying fast, but you put a stop to THAT! Please go see [Secret Agent] Clarence!'),
(9231, 'Thank you! You did better than I expected. Youve made our job much easier.'),
(9232, 'Master, those must be what [Secret Agent] Clarence mentioned!'),
(9233, 'Master, those must be what [Secret Agent] Clarence mentioned!'),
(9234, 'Master! They have been annihilated! A Scarecrow cursed by Pathos is a nasty piece of work!'),
(9235, 'Master! They  have been annihilated! A Scarecrow cursed by Pathos is a nasty piece of work!'),
(9236, 'Master, [Secret Agent] Clarence seems troubled. We should go visit him.'),
(9237, 'You have a lot of hunts yet to be completed. Come back once you have completed your present quests.'),
(9238, 'You must attend Border Defense War and bring [High Level Border Defense Compensation Ascent Scroll].'),
(9239, 'You must attend Border Defense War and bring [High Level Border Defense Compensation Ascent Scroll].'),
(9240, 'Master, it looks like [Captain] Fargo would like to assign you a new mission. Hurry and see him.'),
(9241, 'You finally made it, <selfname>! I wanted to ask a favor in private.'),
(9242, 'A soldier who recently returned from the border wars reported that were short on manpower. Report for duty at the border at once!'),
(9243, 'It is extremely urgent. Will you join the battle at the border?'),
(9244, '#Information on Border Defense War#|- Border Defense War begins each day at the following times. |  - AM : 1AM, 10AM|  - PM : 1PM, 3PM, 5PM, 8PM, 10PM|- Please note that during Lunar and Dark Lunar War on Monday, Wednesday and Thursday, the 8PM Border Defense War will not occur.|- Border Defense War automatically starts gathering forces at the appointed time and the battle commences after 10 minutes.|- Good equipment is essential to victory.|- Equipment Support Information: Equipment can be rented from the Moradon Equipment Quartermaster with Noah payments. Fees are set according to user level.'),
(9245, 'Master! We have the scroll. You can use this to boost your Experience Points for a limited period. But taking it directly to [Captain] Fargo will give you a lot of experience all at once!'),
(9246, 'Is it time?  Border Defense Battle commences automatically at these appointed times. |  - AM : 1AM, 10AM|  - PM : 1PM, 3PM, 5PM, 8PM, 10PM|#  Please note that during Lunar and Dark Lunar War on Monday, Wednesday and Thursday, the 8PM Border Defense Battle will not occur.'),
(9247, 'You brought it! How did it go? Wait, doesnt matter! I look forward to your action as a member of the Border Defense!'),
(9248, 'Master, it looks like [Captain] Folkwine would like to assign you a new mission. Hurry and see him.'),
(9249, 'You finally made it, <selfname>! I wanted to ask a favor in private.'),
(9250, 'A soldier who recently returned from the border wars reported that were short on manpower. Report for duty at the border at once!'),
(9251, 'It is extremely urgent. Will you join the battle at the border?'),
(9252, '#Information on Border Defense Battle#|- Border Defense Battle begins each day at the following times. |  - AM : 1AM, 10AM|  - PM : 1PM, 3PM, 5PM, 8PM, 10PM|- Please note that during Lunar and Dark Lunar War on Monday, Wednesday and Thursday, the 8PM Border Defense Battle will not occur.|- Border Defense Battle automatically starts gathering forces at the appointed time and the battle commences after 10 minutes.|- Good equipment is essential to victory.|- Equipment Support Information: Equipment can be rented from the Moradon Equipment Quartermaster with Noah payments. Fees are set according to user level.'),
(9253, 'Master! We have the scroll. You can use this to boost your Experience Points for a limited period. But taking it directly to [Captain] Fargo will give you a lot of experience all at once!'),
(9254, 'Is it time? Border Defense Battle commences automatically at these appointed times. | - AM : 1AM, 10AM| - PM : 1PM, 3PM, 5PM, 8PM, 10PM|# Please note that during Lunar and Dark Lunar War on Monday, Wednesday and Thursday, the 8PM Border Defense Battle will not occur.'),
(9255, 'You brought it! How did it go? Wait, doesnt matter! I look forward to your action as a member of the Border Defense!'),
(9256, 'Please select which effect you would like to receive. |#Cry for Charge: 80% Increment of Magic Power|#Firm Will : Defense 100|#Endless Patience : HP Increased by 500'),
(9257, 'Greetings! I am an Enchanter from Moradon Castle. I am currently charging a regular fee for casting desired Buffs. The 3 Buffs I service are Attack Power, Defense Power, and HP Increment. They may overlap. I accept payments in Noah but I also accept [Insignia of Victor] from those who are between Level 20 to Level 60.'),
(9258, 'Please select which effect you would like to receive. |#Cry for Charge: 80% Increment of Magic Power|#Firm Will : Defense 100|#Endless Patience : HP Increased by 500'),
(9259, 'Please select which effect you would like to receive. |#Cry for Charge: 80% Increment of Magic Power|#Firm Will : Defense 150|#Endless Patience : HP Increased by 800'),
(9260, 'Cant even do this much on your own? Disband the party and do it alone!'),
(9261, 'Cant even do this much on your own? Disband the party and do it alone!'),
(9262, 'Not so easy alone, this one... Better you find some folks to help.'),
(9263, 'Not so easy alone, this one... Better you find some folks to help.'),
(9264, 'Greetings! Im Sirin, a [White Shadow Commander]. I am responsible for the Chaos Battle. I change the Wings of heroes into items. Please make a selection from the menu.'),
(9265, 'I offer the [Map of Chaos] needed to enter the Chaos War to those who have purchased a [Map of Chaos Exchange Coupon]. If you wish to exchange your coupon for a [Map of Chaos], please press [Commence Exchange].'),
(9266, 'You do not have a [Map of Chaos Exchange Coupon]. Please be advised that a [Map of Chaos Exchange Coupon] is available for purchase at the [Power Up Store].'),
(9267, 'You have chosen to make a trade. Once you proceed with this exchange, you cannot trade the item with any other users or NPC. Would you like to continue?'),
(9268, 'You have received the requested item. Good luck in your coming battles!'),
(9269, 'You have gained a [Voucher of Oracle] after a victorious Chaos Battle. The voucher can be exchanged into a Wing by adding either [Ancient Text] or [Noah]. |# Using [Ancient Text] will not cost any [Noah]. It also increases the likelihood of acquiring a high level Wing that will have better attributes. |# If you make the exchange with [Noah], a Wing will be randomly selected regardless of high or low level attributes.'),
(9270, 'You do not have any [Ancient Text]. Please be advised that [Ancient Text] is available for purchase at the [Power Up Store].'),
(9271, 'You have [Ancient Text] in your possession. [Ancient Text] emits magical powers that increases your chances of gaining a [Wing] with high level attributes. Would you like to use it? |# Noah is not required when [Ancient Text] is used.'),
(9272, 'You do not have enough inventory space. Come back when you have enough space for this transaction.'),
(9273, 'The exchange has been completed. I hope you got what you were looking for.'),
(9274, 'You do not have enough Noah. You need [Level x 6000 Noah] to make an exchange for a Wing.'),
(9275, 'If you make the exchange with [Noah], a Wing will be randomly selected regardless of high or low level attributes. Do you wish to continue? |# Noah cost: [Level x 6000 Noah].'),
(9276, 'You do not have a [Voucher of Oracle] in your possession. Please be advised that a [Voucher of Oracle] can be acquired through Chaos Battle.'),
(9277, 'You have selected to accept [Reward: Wing]. [Reward: Wing] can be acquired by users who have become war heroes by defeating [Gatekeeper], [Defense Squad 1 Captain] and [Defense Squad 2 Captain] during each nations battle for [King] or during [Lunar War]. Please select the menu of your choice.'),
(9278, 'You are not qualified to receive a Wing. Come back after you distinguish yourself in a War.'),
(9279, 'A wing has been given to King <selfname>. It may be used for 24 hours. After it expires, another may be acquired at the next inauguration of a King.'),
(9280, 'You already received your reward for the day. Please come back tomorrow.'),
(9281, '[Lunar War Hero Wing Reward Information]|- The following Wing Reward menu is for users who were victorious against [Gatekeeper], [Defense Squad 1 Captain] and [Defense Squad 2 Captain] in [Lunar War].|- A Wing will be rewarded after [Next Day 6 AM] to users who were victorious against [Gatekeeper], [Defense Squad 1 Captain] and [Defense Squad 2 Captain] in [Lunar War].|- It may be used for 24 hours and may only be received once a day until the next war. |- Distributed Wings attributes vary according to chance.'),
(9282, 'Its an honor to meet a hero who has slain [Gatekeeper], <selfname>. You have been rewarded for your efforts. I look forward to seeing you in action in the future.'),
(9283, 'Its an honor to meet a hero who has slain [Defense Squad 1 Captain], <selfname>. You have been rewarded for your efforts. I look forward to seeing you in action in the future.'),
(9284, 'Its an honor to meet a hero who has slain [Defense Squad 2 Captain], <selfname>. You have been rewarded for your efforts. I look forward to seeing you in action in the future.'),
(9285, 'The weapon breaker armor for levels 60~62 is being sold for 1 million Noah. The parts are [Gloves], [Boots], [Helmet], [Lower Armor], [Upper Armor], and the armor can only be bought by completing each quests.'),
(9286, 'My commision is only 1 million Noah, now which part would you like?'),
(9287, 'Hm.. You do not have enough Noah! Save up and come back for them.'),
(9288, 'Your inventory is full. Make some space and come back.'),
