(9306, 'You must spend the skill acquired from the skill box to gain another skill.'),
(9307, '[Information on Ladder Rank #1 Wing Award]|-  The following menu is available to users who have achieved [Ladder Rank #1 of the Day] by defeating enemy users in the [Underdeveloped Zone].|-  A Wing will be rewarded after [Next Day 5 AM] to users who defeated enemy users in the [Underdeveloped Area].|- It may be used for 24 hours, and may only be received once a day until the next war. |- Distributed Wings attributes vary according to chance.'),
(9308, 'You are ranked #1 in Ladder of the day! Great work! I expect you to do as well tomorrow, <selfname>!'),
(9309, '[Information on New Tier 8 Armor Set]|- This armor set is still under [Beta Test]. The armor set will be modified according to tester feedback. We look forward to a lot of user participation.|- Opinions on this armor set will be given full attention. They can be posted in the [Knight Online Home Page Survey / Discussion Forum].|- [New Tier 8 Armor Set] is being rented out from July 16, 2009 to July 30, 2009. |- Only level 75 or higher may purchase this item set.|- The price is set at 1 million Noah.|- The item is usable for 6 hours from the time of receipt and it will be deleted afterwards. |- Please be advised that this item set will be deleted from the server after July 30, 2009. |- It is sold in variations of [Vitality] and [Main Attributes in Accordance with Each Individual Class], so purchase one that suits you.'),
(9310, 'The beta test period is from July 16, 2009 to July 30, 2009. Please be advised that all items from this set will be deleted from the server after the test period.'),
(9311, 'It costs 1 million Noah to participate in this test. Upon receipt of 1 million Noah, a 5 piece armor set will be available for rent. Please select the attributes of your choice. |- Please be advised that this item set will be deleted from the server after July 30, 2009.'),
(9312, 'Only users who are Level 75 and higher can purchase this item. Please confirm your level before trying again.'),
(9313, 'One [Map of Chaos] is provided per day. However, no additional maps will be distributed for that day and it must be used within 6 hours from the time of receipt.'),
(9314, 'Would you like a [Map of Chaos]? If you receive a [Map of Chaos], it must be used within 6 hours or it will be deleted.'),
(9315, 'A [Map of Chaos Exchange Coupon] that can be exchanged for a [Map of Chaos] is available for sale until July 16th. Please be advised that all these items will be deleted after July 16th.'),
(9316, 'A [Map of Chaos Exchange Coupon] costs 1 million Noah. Would you like to make a purchase? |# This item will be deleted after July 16th.'),
(9317, 'An [Ancient Text] that induces the [Increased Chance of High Level Wing Acquisition] effect on a [Voucher of Oracle] is available for sale until July 16th. Please be advised that these items will be deleted after July 16th.'),
(9318, 'An [Ancient Text] costs 2 million Noah. Would you like to make a purchase? |# This item will be deleted after July 16th.'),
(9319, 'A [Make Over Coupon] allows users to modify exterior features and is available for sale until July 16th. Please be advised that this item will be deleted after July 16th.'),
(9320, 'A [Make Over Coupon] costs 3 million Noah. Would you like to make a purchase?'),
(9321, 'I provide information on Chaos Battles. Please select a category for further details.'),
(9322, '# What is Chaos?| When the [World of Enlightenment Fissure] occurs, people are devoured at |the Altar of Ancient Deities. The rules are simple: [Last One Standing]. To survive, everyone else must die. Everyone in this zone is an enemy. Everyone who opposes you or your Deity must be destroyed.'),
(9323, '# 1-1 Entrance| In order to enter Chaos Battle, a [Map of Chaos] must be selected from [White Shadow Commander] Sirin. Only one is available each day. This map can be used to attend 11 AM, 6 PM and 11 PM battles. The [Map of Chaos] is valid for 6 hours from time of receipt. Once used, It will be available for purchase at the [Power Up Shop].'),
(9324, '# 1-2 Start| At least 1 minute is given to prepare for battle upon entrance into Chaos Battle. The user is invincible during this minute and may use the time to configure skills and such. No damage may be inflicted by an enemy or Saw Blade Attack during this period.'),
(9325, '# 1-3 Battle| One minute after entrance into battle, a message will inform the user that the battle has begun. Basic combat is the same as with the standard Knight Online combat. Your chosen skill must be used to defeat your opponent. If the user has been defeated by an opponent, click [Confirm] to revive. The user will have 3 seconds of invincibility after reviving.'),
(9326, '# 1-4 Revive| If the user is defeated by an opponent, the battle may continue by clicking [Confirm] to revive the user. The player revives in a random location within the Temple, but not where the user has been slain. The user will have 3 seconds of invincibility after reviving.'),
(9327, '# 1-5 Victory| A user with a higher kill count will gain higher rank in Chaos. If the kill count is tied, superiority is given to the user with the lowest death count. If both kill and death counts are tied, the users will receive the same rank.'),
(9328, '# 1-6 Reward| The top 20% will receive a [Voucher of Oracle] and all participants will receive an [Emblem of Chaos]. Details on how to use the [Voucher of Oracle] and [Emblem of Chaos] can be found under [Reward Information].'),
(9329, '# 2-1 Basic Skill| Some basic skills that are available upon entry into Chaos. There are a total of 10 different skill types that may be configured per user requirements.| # 2-1-1 Spirit Sword| - This basic skill is available when beginning Chaos. It inflicts 1000 damage on the enemy.'),
(9330, '# 2-1-2 Ice Counter| -  This basic skill is available when beginning Chaos. It inflicts 1000 damage to an opponent and slows movement speed.'),
(9331, '# 2-1-3 Fire Sword| - This basic skill is available when beginning Chaos. It hurls a fire ball and instantly inflicts 3000 damage from a distance.'),
(9332, '# 2-1-4 Tears of Angel| - This basic skill is available when beginning Chaos. It immediately restores 1000 HP.'),
(9333, '# 2-1-5 Sprint| - This basic skill is available when beginning Chaos. It increases movement speed over a set period of time.'),
(9334, '# 2-1-6 Ice Sword| - This basic skill is available when beginning Chaos. It launches a ranged attack that inflicts 3000 damage over time.'),
(9335, '# 2-1-7 Stealth| - This basic skill is available when beginning Chaos. It allows users to sustain invisibility while not attacking for a duration of 80 seconds. However, stealth is broken if struck while casting or if damaged in a specified attack range.'),
(9336, '# 2-1-8  Stun Lightning| - This basic skill is available when beginning Chaos. It inflicts 2000 electrical damage. It may also disable an enemys mobility from time to time.'),
(9337, '# 2-1-9 Poison Knife| - This basic skill is available when beginning Chaos. It delivers a damage equivalent to 20% of the targets current HP.'),
(9338, '# 2-2 Gain Skill| This skill is available through the [Chaos Cube] in Chaos. Three types exist and they are issued according to rank.|# 2-2-1 Light Pit| - This skill is learned through the Chaos Cube. It temporarily boosts movement speed by 200%. Light Pit cannot be stacked and used with Sprint.'),
(9339, '# 2-2-2 Drain Restore| - This skill is learned through the Chaos Cube, restoring 1000 HP for a duration of 20 seconds.'),
(9340, '# 2-2-3 Killing Blade| - This skill is learned through the Chaos Cube, enabling the user to kill an opponent in a single strike by targeting a vital point.'),
(9341, '# Chaos Cube| The Chaos Cube converts unknown materials within the Temple to create new user skills.'),
(9342, '# 3-1 Light Pit| - This skill is learned through the Chaos Cube. It temporarily boosts movement speed by 200%. Light Pit cannot be stacked and used with Sprint.'),
(9343, '# 3-2 Drain Restore| - This skill is learned through the Chaos Cube, restoring 1000 HP for a duration of 20 seconds.'),
(9344, '# 3-3 Killing Blade| - This skill is learned through the Chaos Cube, enabling one to kill an opponent in a single strike by targeting a vital point.'),
(9345, '# Regarding Rewards| - In order to receive a reward, a user must be in the top 20% tier of all players. [For example, when 10 players participate, rewards will be given out to the top two players.]| - All participants will receive an [Emblem of Chaos].'),
(9346, '# 4-1 Voucher of Oracle| - This item is given to players who finished Chaos Battle within the top 20% tier. Go see [White Shadow Commander] Sirin and he will convert it into a [Wing] that may be used immediately.'),
(9347, '# 4-2 [Emblem of Chaos]| - This emblem is given to all who participate in Chaos Battle. If a user collects 5 of these emblems, they may be exchanged for other items such as a  [Wing].'),
(9348, 'You do not have enough [Emblem of Chaos]. Please be advised that an [Emblem of Chaos] may be acquired through Chaos Battle.'),
(9349, 'An [Emblem of Chaos] is awarded to everyone who participates in Chaos Battle. Users who did not manage to acquire a [Voucher of Oracle] can collect 5 [Emblem of Chaos] to trade for a Wing. The Wing will have an additional cost of either an [Ancient Text] or [Noah]. |# Using the [Ancient Text] will not cost any Noah. It also increases the likelihood of acquiring a high level Wing that will have better attributes. |# If you make the exchange with [Noah], a Wing will be randomly selected regardless of high or low level attributes.'),
(9350, '[Wealthy Merchants Daughter] Menissiah has commissioned you to participate in [Chaos Battle] to bring her an [Emblem of Chaos]. Complete this quest to receive experience points, contribution points and some exceptional weapons.'),
(9351, '[Wealthy Merchants Daughter] Menissiah has commissioned you to participate in [Chaos Battle] to bring her an [Emblem of Chaos]. Complete this quest to receive experience points, contribution points and some exceptional weapons.'),
(9352, '[Wealthy Merchants Daughter] Menissiah has commissioned you to participate in [Chaos Battle] to bring her an [Emblem of Chaos]. Complete this quest to receive experience points, contribution points and some exceptional weapons.'),
(9353, '[Wealthy Merchants Daughter] Menissiah has commissioned you to participate in [Chaos Battle] to bring her [Emblem of Chaos]. Complete this quest to receive experience points, contribution points and some exceptional weapons.'),
(9354, 'Hi! It has been a while. I need an item. Would you get it for me?'),
(9355, '[Chaos Battle] occurs within the World of Enlightenment. An [Emblem of Chaos] may be acquired there. Think you could get it for me?  Bring me an [Emblem of Chaos] and youll be handsomely rewarded.'),
(9356, 'You still havent got it all? An [Emblem of Chaos] can be acquired during any [Chaos Battle] at 10 AM, 12 PM, 4 PM, 6 PM, 9 PM, 10 PM, and 12 AM.'),
(9357, 'You got it! Ill start my research on this new material! Thank you. Oh, um, how about keeping this from my dad, OK?'),
(9358, '# 2-1-10 Throw Stone| - This basic skill is available when beginning Chaos. It inflicts 10 damage and can sustain multiple hits.'),
(9359, 'You already loaned weapon and armor today, please come back tomorrow.'),
(9360, 'Welcome.We let you borrow items for the masters who are back to complete the event. Please get it verified on our home page to receive [Secret Box] and come back to receive the equipments.'),
(9361, 'Since <Selfname> is a warrior (looking at the list)  </ font> <font color=@#660066@> Glaive and the <font color=@#660066@> the chitin armor set </ font> have been prepared.'),
(9362, 'Since <Selfname> is a Rogue (looking at the list)  </ font> <font color=@#660066@> Daggar of Mirazu and <font color=@#660066@> the chitin bow set </ font> have been prepared.'),
(9363, 'Since <Selfname> is a magician (looking at the list)  </ font> <font color=@#660066@> Elemental Staff and the <font color=@#660066@> Creamson armor sets </ font> have been prepared.'),
(9364, 'Since <Selfname> is a Priest (looking at the list)  </ font> <font color=@#660066@> Rikaon Iron Mace and <font color=@#660066@> the chitin armor set </ font> have been prepared.'),
(9365, 'Since <Selfname> is a warrior (looking at the list)  </ font> <font color=@#660066@> Raptor and <font color=@#660066@> The chitinshell armor set </ font> have been prepared.'),
(9366, 'Since <Selfname> is a rogue (looking at the list)  </ font> <font color=@#660066@> Iron Bow <font color=@#660066@> the Chitin Armor Set </ font> have been prepared.'),
(9367, 'We have prepared these for you.'),
(9368, 'We have prepared these for you.'),
(9369, 'We have prepared these for you.'),
(9370, 'is the log the <selfname> by looking at the list of (..) entry-<font color=@#660066@> The assassins dagger and <font color=@#660066@> Beginner Assassins Bow </ font> </ font>prepared for beginner <font color=@#660066@> the assassin armor sets </ font>.'),
(9371, 'We have prepared these for you.'),
(9372, 'We have prepared these for you.'),
(9373, 'You can start the event if you are over Lv 30.  Please train more and come back.'),
(9374, 'You dont have enough space in your inventory. You need 6 spaces to give out.'),
(9375, 'You dont have enough space in your inventory. You need 8 spaces to give out.'),
(9376, 'You dont have enough space in your inventory. You need 7 spaces to give out.'),
(9377, 'Hello. You can rent once in 24 hrs. If you want to rent it please let me know.'),
(9378, 'The euipqments will disappeared after 24 hrs. Have a great day'),
(9379, 'For masters who are back for the Comeback Event, were providing this service. If you qualify for the comeback event, please show me [Secret Box].'),
(9380, 'Masters who are coming back to Knight Online, were providing [Unlimited] service. <Selfname>, you seem to have the [Secret Box]. You must be a past knight. Which menu would you like to use?'),
(9381, 'Thank you. You can obtain the following item until the event ends, please remember that.'),
(9382, 'This isnt the [Come Back Event] period. When its the right event period the service will be provided.'),
(9383, 'Yay! Im going to go play now.'),
(9384, 'Please give the lunch box to my brother whos training to be a mercenary. I gotta go, bye!'),
(9385, 'Hey. Come here a moment.'),
(9386, 'Man, this has all gone bad! I£l going to need to throw this away! Cant you event deliver the right stuff?'),
(9387, 'Phew?Im almost 7 years old now but I still have to deliver my brother his lunch. Help me out here. With what? Of course the delivery!'),
(9388, 'Give it to my brother. Before it goes bad hurry!'),
(9389, 'My friend like to draw pictures. But he is still dreaming to approach the goal. You can find him in  Moradon Castle because he always stays in there.'),
(9390, 'What are you looking for?'),
(9391, 'My sister made me a lunch? Shes all grown up now. But why didnt she come by herself?'),
(9392, 'She went out to play! I thought she was too old for that now.'),
(9393, 'Thanks anyways. I want to reward you with [Ascend Scroll]'),
(9394, 'Ah, and I want you to give this journal to my friend. He dreams of being a painter but he doesnt have that much of a passion. I want to motivate him by letting him know that Im trying my best here getting trained and that Im thinking of him.'),
(9395, 'Your inventory is full. Make some space to get reward.'),
(9396, 'ah, she must have liked <selfname>. Instead of [Ascend Scroll] she wants to follow you around. I know it could be annoying but could you please allow her?'),
(9397, 'Where is my lunch box?'),
(9398, 'Man.. I cant think of anything?'),
(9399, 'who? Who again? Why are you calling someone whos having a hard time?!'),
(9400, 'Friend? Ah, the friend in the training. That friend wanted to deliver [Training Journal]?'),
(9401, 'Ok. Hes doing great.Im shame at myself.  Now I will work more harder.'),
(9402, 'I want a replay. I give you disguise of guardian, it is not that outstanding ability but still useful . You can use it when you want.'),
(9403, 'So, where is the [Training Journal]?'),
(9404, 'Hello. [Sailor] Jorgu. Theres the [Knight Online Anniversary] Event.'),
(9405, 'You have selected to participate in the event. You can participate in Ardream, Ronarkland areas.'),
(9406, 'Knight Online Anniversary Event'),
(9407, 'You have accumulated enough coins! The more you have the more chance to win!'),
(9408, 'It seems you dont have any suitable coins. Come on, go collect more coins.'),
(9409, 'With the two coins you can get the item. Not sure what youll get but some are really valuable.'),
(9410, 'I hope you got the item you wanted. Come back next time.'),
(9411, 'It seems you dont have enough inventory. Make enough space and come back.'),
(9412, 'Items paid will be paid after the end of the days events from July 16 to July 30'),
(9413, 'Use 10 coins to receive the item.'),
(9414, 'You want to participate this event.'),
(9415, 'So, now Im 7 years old. Its my birthday today. But my brother has gone to get training and my parents just bought a stupid present. I want to receive something special and unique.'),
(9416, 'Really? Wow. Well I like the present but.. I have another problem.'),
(9417, 'Dont think Im childish. Do you like bullying me like this??!'),
(9418, '[Anniversary Event] Free Buff during the event'),
(9419, '[You received buff]'),
(9420, '[You already received another buff]'),
(9421, 'Hi! Im glad to see you. We are rewarding the ones who participated in the [Karus] battle and received [Chaos spirit].'),
(9422, 'If its possible, get the [Chaos Spirit] and come back.'),
(9423, 'You dont have the item. Participate in the [Karus] battle.')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(9424, 'Participate in [World Championship] and receive [Hero Wings Exchange Coupon]'),
(9425, 'You dont have item. Please check and come back again.'),
(9426, 'Thank you. Because of you, we were able to win.'),
(9427, 'Event about [Attendance Event]'),
(9428, 'Thanksgiving Event'),
(9429, 'I said [10 Chestnut]. Do you need a drink to hear me right, or something?'),
(9430, 'Good you got it! Now, select the buff you want. Ill get the buff you want.'),
(9431, 'You already have the buff. Dont be so greedy now.'),
(9432, 'Hahahaha, Happy Holi..  I mean happy thanksgiving. Its short so itll pass by quickly.'),
(9433, 'How are you, sir! Everything£r fine here! <selfname>, you£qe going to be discharged after 12 . . . no, no, no. I£l dispatched to this place to collect [Chestnuts] by the [First Sergeant£r] order. But it£r very difficult to collect so many [Chestnuts]. Could you please give me if you have about [10 Chestnuts]? If you give me them, I£kl cast you a buff you want!'),
(9434, 'I need [10 HoneyChestnut]?[Quartermaster] will be mad at me. Sigh?'),
(9435, 'You got it! Thank you so much! Now please select the buff you want.'),
(9436, 'You already have the buff. Please select another buff.'),
(9437, 'Hope you have a great thanksgiving!'),
(9438, 'Hello! Im Jeros. I have been summoned by [Kingdom Election Administrative Unit]. Im here to distribute [Promotional Item] to [Candidate] for [King Election]. [King Election Candidate] should receive the item from me.'),
(9439, 'Election Promotion Item Description.'),
(9440, 'Its not the [Repay time] yet. Come back next time.'),
(9441, 'You are not candidate. We cant provide to a person who is not a candidate.'),
(9442, 'Item received. Hopefully have a good result.'),
(9443, 'Hello! Im Jayce. I have been summoned by [Kingdom Election Administrative Unit]. Im here to distribute [Promotional Item] to [Candidate] for [King Election]. [King Election Candidate] should receive the item from me.'),
(9444, 'Election Promotion Item Description.'),
(9445, 'Its not the [Repay time] yet. Come back next time.'),
(9446, 'You are not candidate. We cant provide to a person who is not a candidate.'),
(9447, 'item received. Hopefully have a good result.'),
(9448, 'Hello. Im [Kingship Aide] Halo. Im here to welcome the [Council] for the Thanskgiving.'),
(9449, 'It seemed those who were supposed to be here werent here, so we went out to welcome them and provide them with the [Homecoming Gift]. Yep, its you! <selfname. Should deliver this to them for an exchange with the experience.'),
(9450, 'Description about Thanksgiving Event'),
(9451, 'Were you able to read the guide? Where would you like to go? You can only obtain once a day.'),
(9452, 'you already finished today. Please come back next time.'),
(9453, 'You dont have enough space in your bag. Please make some room and come again.'),
(9454, 'You already have the [Homecoming Gift]. Go visit [council] now.'),
(9455, 'This event can be done by Lv 36 and up users. Level up and come back, please.'),
(9456, '[World Championship] Event Participation Description'),
(9457, '[World Championship] Event Participation Description'),
(9458, 'Currently <selfname>s nation is [Karus] and you will receive [Iron Pet transformation Scroll] Would you like to accept it?'),
(9459, 'Currently <selfname>s nation is [Elmorad] and you will receive [Crisis Pet Transporation Scroll] Would you like to accept it?'),
(9460, 'Thank you. Have a good time!'),
(9461, 'You can receive one accessory from the [Accessory Box]'),
(9462, 'You do not have the [Accessory Box]. Bring it to exchange it with the item.'),
(9463, 'You brought [Accessory Box]. You can get it randomly now. Would you like to exchange it?'),
(9464, 'What do you need?'),
(9465, 'Hi. Im the [High Priest] Scotty. Im guarding the seal of the Dark Dragon in this room [Dark Dragon Room]. But because our Castellan has passed away, what I do is meaningless.'),
(9466, 'Fortunately, a new castellan came to rule over this place, but the former castellan£r ghost is wandering around here. I need 30 [Castellan£r stamp], 1 [blooded Fantasy Cube] and 1 [Gold peels] to ease the former castellan£r grudge. Please bring me these items so that I can ease his grudge. At the same time, I£kl make you a weapon that£r covered with the ghost of the former castellan.'),
(9467, 'You corrected all. Which weapon do you want?'),
(9468, 'Please check the material you have. You need certain items I mentioned before.30 x [Castellan Seal], 1 x [Red Ringshaped Cube], 1 x [Golden Shell]'),
(9469, 'Please select the weapon you want. Remember that you can only select one.'),
(9470, 'Are you sure this weapon is what you want? Please check again.'),
(9471, 'The darkness comes from the dark dungeons of the Delian.'),
(9472, 'Im very scared. Lets get rid of the darkness roots.'),
(9473, 'You have many other duties. Complete other missions and come back.'),
(9474, 'Ah?till darkness?'),
(9475, 'Thank you. Right now darkness is gone but it will come again.'),
(9476, 'Are you want quit [Dark Dragons Room]?'),
(9477, 'Who is it? What are you looking for?'),
(9478, 'You must want to enter [Dark Dragon Room]. Then you are at the right place. If you bring what I tell you now, youll get the [Castellan Key] to enter [Unknown tombstone]'),
(9479, 'It cant be too hard to obtain the item. You want to know what it is? Its [Tarantula Tooth] x 5. Im sure its not hard to get. Right?'),
(9480, 'You dont have enough. Do better now.'),
(9481, 'You have collected them all! Do you want to receive [Castellan Key]?'),
(9482, 'You reside inside the dungeon. Would you like to get out of here?'),
(9483, 'You are <selfname>. Hello.'),
(9484, 'Not too long ago, [Tarantula]s have invated the dungeon.'),
(9485, 'There are spiders web everywhere and their horrifying looks?!  Sigh? we need to get rid of them and bring me [Tarantula Tooth] then Ill reward you with 100,000 Noah.'),
(9486, 'Are you kidding me? Where is [Tarantulas tooth]?'),
(9487, 'Good job. Ill give you 100,000 noah per one tooth.'),
(9488, '[Rules in Delos Dungeon]|? This dungeon is for the [Castellan] and the [Members of Castellan£r Clan] who occupied the [Delos Castle]|? Only users of [Castellan£r Clan] and [United Clan of Castellans] can enter this dungeon|? [Castellan£r Clan] are able to expel users of [Other Clans other than Castellan£r Clan] from the dungeon, anytime|? [Castellan] and the [Castellan£r Clan] have priority to stay in this dungeon.'),
(9489, '[whats written is unknown]'),
(9490, '[nothing happened]'),
(9491, '[The lights coming out from the monument. Would you like to move?]'),
(9492, 'Please bring the following to [High Priest] Scotty:30 x [Castellan Seal], 1 x [Red Ringshaped Cube], 1 x [Golden Shell]'),
(9493, 'Get rid of [Bloody Krowaz] and [Krowaz] of Krowaz territory and return back to [High Priest] Scotty.'),
(9494, '[Shaman] Samaran will exchange 5 x [Tarantula Tooth] with [Castallen Key].'),
(9495, '[Shaman] Maria will exchange 1 x [Tarantula Tooth] with 100,000'),
(9496, '[Next is written on the Guardian Stone] |?Only the Castellan and the Members of the Castellan£r Clan are able to use the [Guardian Stone of Delos]. |? You can move all the users in Delos Dungeon to Delos.|? Move all the users who don£s belong to the Castellan£r Clan to Delos.'),
(9497, '[You are not a member of the Castellan Clan. The Stone wont work]'),
(9498, '[The stone has dimmed light and collects Dark Energy. Would you like to dismiss other members?]'),
