(9546, 'You do not have [EXP 100% Resurrection Scroll Exchange Coupon]. Youll need to have this to proceed.'),
(9547, 'What is it? I am busy partying. Go and enjoy Christmas Party instead of bugging me!'),
(9548, 'I feel good cause I picked something pretty while I was walking. Huh? You want this? Why? Well.. It doesnt really matter to me.. But you need to get me a Christmas gift! Something pretty!'),
(9549, 'There was only one.. I have no more~'),
(9550, 'Wow! This is.. This is.. This is.. Stars! Ten of them!!'),
(9551, 'Here you go.  I love these stars!!'),
(9552, 'Hmmph... I hate this world... who the heck are you? What? Merry Christmas? What does Christmas mean in this crazy world anyway?!'),
(9553, 'Hmmm... What is this..this looks like a sock.. What? Why are you bothering me? Hmm? You want this? Well this is mine. I will trade with something that is useful to me.'),
(9554, 'I only had one that I gave you. I will let you know if I find another one.'),
(9555, 'Oh.. You got something great here.. Ten of them..'),
(9556, 'Here take it. Nothings free in this damn world.'),
(9557, 'Ahhh.. I am alone again this Christmas.. What are you looking at?!'),
(9558, 'Well.. I actually found this but this is not good enough to give to someone I have crush on.What? You want to trade this with something? Really?'),
(9559, 'Oh! You came. I appreciate your kindness. The stocking? I only had one.'),
(9560, 'oh!! This is .. stars!! Ten!! This will be the best gift ever! Thank you so much!'),
(9561, 'Take this and hand me the stars!'),
(9562, 'Life is full of new adventures! Huh? Did you say Merry Christmas?  Christmas? Christmas! I feel the vibe of a new adventure!'),
(9563, 'I got this while I was in a new adventure. Where did I get it? I found it at the Moradon Sewer! Ahahahaha!! It was a very dangerous and spectacular place! And this is what I got there!! If you want this, bring me something cool!!'),
(9564, 'Hey!! Didnt we already change what I had with yours?'),
(9565, 'Ooh! 10 stars which will lead me to new adventures!!'),
(9566, 'Come on! Lets trade!'),
(9567, 'So noisy. People should not be to relaxed just because it is Christmas..'),
(9568, 'This was on the ground when I went to training place early this morning. I thought of decorating the Christmas tree .. but since theres only one.. I didnt. I need something else that can fill the Christmas Tree. Do you have any? If so, I will trade this Sock with them.'),
(9569, 'My soldiers are very happy as well. Thank you.'),
(9570, 'Oh.. This is very nice. These are enough to decorate the trees.'),
(9571, 'Wow.. I dont know what to say.. Thank you very much.'),
(9572, 'This is so crazy. Christmas wont get us anything!'),
(9573, 'What is this? Is this some useless worthless old sock? Her you there,is? I dont mind as long as anything seems to worth some money.'),
(9574, 'You gave me something pricy! Thanks! Ah.. And please dont tell my brother. He might want to take this away from me.'),
(9575, 'Oh cool!!!'),
(9576, 'Come on. Hurry up!'),
(9577, 'Ahh, it is Christmas... I need to make some money..'),
(9578, 'Do you have some time for me? I got this thing.. And I was wondering if you were looking for this. I would love to trade with something useful if you bring it to me.'),
(9579, 'No more trading today. Please come back later.'),
(9580, 'Let me see.. Oh, you brought valuable things!'),
(9581, 'Lets trade before my Big Bro sees me!'),
(9582, 'Phew.. I always make mistakes everytime I come here... ah.. <selfname>.. What did I do? I always make mistakes!!'),
(9583, 'Well.. I lost Christmas Sock which was going to wrap the gift while preparing Christmas. I was really doing great! Can you please find me the Christmas Sock? I lost it somewhere around the Moradon area.. Please help!!'),
(9584, 'Did you find it yet? But dont push too much.. I am worried that <selfname> could get hurt or something.'),
(9585, 'Wow! You found it! Heres a little gift for you.'),
(9586, 'Thank you very much. Have a merry Christmas!!'),
(9587, 'Christmas bells is ringing all around! This is a happy day! We need to make it happier and we need.... [Shining Star] !! I will give you rewards according to number of [Shining Stars] you bring! | # Reward for 100 Shining Star : Parfait Pet Transform Scroll'),
(9588, 'You have selected [Christmas Buff Item]! If you bring 4 of [Shining Star] then you can choose 1 of [Christmas Buff Item]!'),
(9589, 'This is what the [Christmas Buff Item] does!|# Reward 4 Shining Star| - EXP Stone : Increase EXP by 10%| - DEF Stone : increase DEF by 25| - HP Stone : increase HP by 250| - Attribute Stone : increase Attribute by 4'),
(9590, 'Waw! You chose the [Christmas Pet Transform Scroll]! You have good eyes! Bring me 100 [Shining Stars] and you can get the[Christmas Pet Transform Scroll] of your choice!'),
(9591, '[Christmas Pet Transform Scroll] will transform your pet into me [Parfait].. But.. Well you said you like me.. I will follow you.. not because i like <selfname> .. so dont think that I like you or anything!'),
(9592, 'Hmm? Theres not enough [Shining Stars]. Please check again.'),
(9593, 'You have collected all! Heres the reward!'),
(9594, 'Merry Christmas! Christmas has comeback again this year! Hmm...... however... it really doesnt feel like Christmas at all. Whats the problem..? Its snowing outside.. we have the tree with perfect decorations.. whats missing..? Ah! Snowman! We dont have the Snowman!!'),
(9595, 'Hoho, You need to sacrifice to improve the Christmas atmosphere. Would you go to the towns entrance and make us a Huge Snowman? Make the huge Snowman and bring the Snowmans [Scarf] as a proof.'),
(9596, 'Wheres the [Scarf]? The [Scarf]? The [Scarf]? Not done yet? Hmm? Hmm?'),
(9597, 'Finally it feels like Christmas! Please hand me the [Scarf]!'),
(9598, 'I appreciate your help today. See you tomorrow!'),
(9599, '[Christmas Special Free Buff Event]|- Get wanted Buff for Free|- Buff types are ATK, DEF, Stamina increase and you can use more than one at a time.'),
(9600, 'Buff list for Level.1~34. |-Scream of Assault : ATK 10%|- Firm Will : DEF 100|-Endless Fortitude : Stamina 500'),
(9601, 'Buff list for Level.35~60.|-Scream of Assault : ATK 10%|-Undefeated Will : DEF 150|-INfinite Fortitude : Stamina 800'),
(9602, 'Buff list for Level.61~83.|-Scream of Assault : ATK 10%|- Invincible Will : DEF 200|-Extreme Fortitude : Stamina 1000'),
(9603, '[Christmas Special Free Buff Event]|- Get 3 types of buffs which will increase ATK, DEF, Stamina for 30 minutes.|- Buffs are different according to levels.|- 3 types of buffs can be used at the same time. You cannot get the same buff while you have the buff on you unless you cancel the buff or times up.'),
(9604, 'Please select one effect.|-Scream of Assault : ATK 10%|-Firm Will : DEF 100|-Endless Fortitude : Stamina 500'),
(9605, 'You already have a buff. You cannot get the same type.'),
(9606, 'Please select one effect.|-Scream of Assault : ATK 10%|-Undefeated Will : DEF 150|-Infinite Fortitude : Stamina 800'),
(9607, 'Please select one effect.|-Scream of Assault : ATK 10%|-Invincible Will : DEF 200|-Extreme Fortitude : Stamina 1000'),
(9608, '[Sexy Santa] Parfait help you prepare for Christmas'),
(9609, 'Wow! You selected [Snowman Exchange Scroll]! Bring me 10 [Shiny star] to receive [Snowman Exchange Scroll]!'),
(9610, 'You will be able to transform into one of my friends [Forum], [teetee], [Teo], or [NuNu]. You can only select one.'),
(9611, 'You cant enter if you are not lord of a Castellan clan.'),
(9612, 'Im the [Arena Master] in charge of this soccer field. How may I be of service today?'),
(9613, 'Youve come to enter a soccer game. I will transfer you to any team you select. The team can be composed of players from any nation. Please keep in mind that once a team has 11 players, you cannot join that team.'),
(9614, 'The maximum number of 11 players has been selected for this team. Please select the other team.'),
(9615, 'Youve already received a [Soccer Uniform] today. Please come back again tomorrow.'),
(9616, 'You need 10 [Goal Pendants]. Please confirm the number of medals in your inventory.'),
(9617, 'Youve brought 10 [Goal Pendants]. Would you like to exchange them for a [Soccer Uniform]? Please be aware that once you choose to trade for a soccer uniform, all [Goal Pendants] in your inventory will be collected.'),
(9618, 'Exchange complete. I hope you score even more goals this time!'),
(9619, 'You cant join the selected team. The difference between the two teams is more than two players at this time.'),
(9620, 'Players who purchased the [Minerva Package] will be provided with the [Voucher for a Minerva Helmet] and [Voucher for a Minerva Armor]. Vouchers can be exchanged from [Vendor] Hammers.'),
(9621, 'You purchased the [Minerva Package]. Would you like to exchange to [Voucher for a Minerva Helmet] and [Voucher for a Minerva Armor]?'),
(9622, 'You don not have the [Minerva Package]. Please come back when you have purchased the [Minerva Package].'),
(9624, 'Players who purchased the [Minerva Package] will be provided with the [Voucher for a Minerva Helmet] and [Voucher for a Minerva Armor]. Vouchers can be exchanged from [Vendor] Hammers.')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(9625, 'You purchased the [Minerva Package]. Would you like to exchange to [Voucher for a Minerva Helmet] and [Voucher for a Minerva Armor]?'),
(9626, 'You don not have the [Minerva Package]. Please come back when you have purchased the [Minerva Package].'),
(9627, 'Players who purchased the [Pathos Glove Package] will be provided with 2EA [Voucher for a Pathos Glove]. Vouchers can be exchanged from [Vendor] Kayra.'),
(9628, 'You purchased the [Pathos Glove Package]. Would you like to exchange to 2EA of [Voucher for a Pathos Glove]?'),
(9629, 'You dont have the [Pathos Glove Package]. Please come back when you have purchased the [Pathos Glove Package].'),
(9630, 'Youre not on a team. Only players that are registered for the game may announce the start of the game.'),
(9631, 'We do not have an even number of players. Please try again when we have the same number of players on each team.'),
(9632, 'The game has begun. Please try again after the current game has finished.'),
(9633, 'Please deliver [Kimchi Dumpling]s ingredients [Snow Cabbage] and [Daikon] to [Royal Chef] Yancook.'),
(9634, 'Please deliver [Gift from Homeland] acquired from [Beef Administrator] Roast from [Beef Roast].'),
(9635, 'Please deliver [Fortune Bag] rewarded from [Spinning the Top] to [Royal Chef] Yancook.'),
(9636, 'Please deliver [Kimchi Dumpling] to [Beef Administrator] Roast.'),
(9637, 'Disguise as [Valen attempting to confess her love] and deliver [Chocolate] to [Her unrequited love]. |? Thisquest can only be completed once each day. |? This item has a time limit of one hour. The quest must be completed within the hour.'),
(9638, 'Whew, its always busy around New Years. I wish someone would help me.'),
(9639, '     [New Year Event Information]|- Following event will continue from February 11 to February 25. |- Following quest is a [Repeatable] quest. However, upon the request to exchange, all [Snow Cabbage] and [Daikon] in your inventory will be [Collected] regardless of their numbers. |- Please refer to our online website for other information regarding miscellaneous events.'),
(9640, 'Whats that? You want to help? Good thing, too, cause Im swamped here. Im short on ingredients for Kimchi Dumpling. I need 10 [Snow Cabbage] and 10 [Daikon]. Would you mind using your Mattock to grab [Snow Cabbage] and [Daikon] around the [Mining Area] thats nearby?'),
(9641, 'Still not done? I cant make [Kimchi Dumpling] without [Snow Cabbage] and [Daikon]!'),
(9642, 'Oh! You brought it. Just in time. Well, hand em over. Im running low on ingredients! As a token of appreciation, Ill give you a Kimchi Dumpling!|? Upon completion of the current quest, all [Snow Cabbage] and [Daikon] will be collected in your inventory.'),
(9643, 'Im running low on ingredients, so Ill take all youve got! Thanks for your trouble!'),
(9644, 'You brought [Gift from Homeland]? So where is it?'),
(9645, 'Oh, will you exchange it for an item?'),
(9646, 'You brought [Fortune Bag]? So where is it? If youre messing with me, you wont get a fortune!'),
(9647, 'Greetings. Im [Chalet Keeper] Beef. If you bring me 20 [Kimchi Dumpling], as a reward for helping [Royal Chef] Yancook Ill send you to [Beef Roast] in return. |? Even if you enter [Beef Roast], [Kimchi Dumpling] wont be taken from your inventory.'),
(9648, 'Upon your entrance, please deliver 20 [Kimchi Dumpling] to [Beef Administrator] Roast somewhere in [Beef Roast]. Its a special request from [Beef Administrator] Roast. Well, then! Would you like to proceed to [Beef Roast]?'),
(9649, 'You dont have enough [Kimchi Dumpling] on you. To enter, please acquire 20 [Kimchi Dumpling] from [Royal Chef] Yancook by seeing to his needs.'),
(9650, 'Happy New Year. Its not every day that I see a visitor around here. So what brings you here today?'),
(9651, 'Ive already received [Kimchi Dumpling] today. Please come back again tomorrow.'),
(9652, 'Are you telling me that you brought [Kimchi Dumpling] as a favor to [Chalet Keeper] Beef?'),
(9653, 'Thats great! It just so happens Im in need of [Kimchi Dumpling]. Could I have them right now?'),
(9654, 'Hmm. You dont have enough [Kimchi Dumpling]. Please come back after you have collected 20 of them.'),
(9655, 'You have exactly 20 [Kimchi Dumpling] on you. As a token of my gratitude, Ill give you [Gift from Homeland]. Would you like to make an exchange?'),
(9656, 'Sigh? Why a sigh? Actually for this Valentines day, I want to propose to [That person]. But this time its overlapping with the new years so I have to help out at home running errands. I hope someone can help me here?'),
(9657, '[Valentines Day Event Information]|- Event Duration: February 11, 2010 - February 25, 2010|- Following events item [Chocolate of Love] must be delivered within an hour or else it will melt away.|- The chat function will be disabled upon the receipt of [Chocolate of Love].|- The designated person you have to deliver [Chocolate of Love] to changes every hour.'),
(9658, 'I appreciate your help. Thanks to you, I got to profess my love!'),
(9659, '[Chocolate of Love] has melted!? What a shame. Even so, I made quite a few, so Ill give you another one. Please do not fail this time.'),
(9660, 'Why does [Valentines Day] have to overlap with [New Year]? Im so busy helping my father out with chores at home, I dont even have enough time to deliver my chocolate.'),
(9661, 'Please help me. Ill transform you into me, so please deliver this chocolate to [That Person]. Oh yeah, I cant change your voice. Dont say anything, whatever you do!'),
(9662, 'You still didnt deliver it? Please deliver the chocolate before it melts.'),
(9663, 'Did you deliver it? Oh, is this his reply!? Thank you! Thank you!'),
(9664, 'Yes? Is there something you need from me?'),
(9665, 'I think youve got the wrong person. A lot of people look like me, so you should look again.'),
(9666, 'Your bag is full and I cant give you the reply. Please secure a free space in your inventory.'),
(9667, 'Oh my! A chocolate? This is totally unexpected! Thank you. Heres my reply. Please take it'),
(9668, 'Wheres this chocolate you mentioned? You pulling my leg?'),
(9669, 'Fight on, Korea! Greetings! Im [Victory] who ran here in hopes of a victory in [Vancouver Olympics]! Im giving away free buffs as symbols of victory for the Korean competitors in [Vancouver Olympics].'),
(9670, 'Duration: February 11, 2010 to February 25, 2010! During that time, I will offer free buffs regardless of level! Be sure to get as many as you need and please cheer on the Korean competitors! I apologize in advance that the buffs will vary depending upon the level of the requester.'),
(9671, 'You already have a buff of the same kind! Try again next time!'),
(9672, 'From February 11, 2010 to February 25, 2010, you can receive free buffs from [Vancouver Olympics] Victory at Moradon. We are off to a long-awaited vacation. Happy New Year!'),
(9673, 'From February 11, 2010 to February 25, 2010, you can receive free buffs from [Vancouver Olympics] Victory at Moradon. We are off to a long-awaited vacation. Happy New Year!'),
(9674, 'Would you like to leave Beef Roast?'),
(9675, 'You are unable to transform into me at the moment. Please be sure that you did not assume another transformation or that you are not under the influence of another buff.'),
(9676, '    Please note the following when commencing event quests|- You cannot begin a quest on the same day that you completed a task the previous week. |- Make certain you complete the task begun on the same day of the previous week before beginning another.|- e.g.)  If you began a task on Monday of the first week, you must complete it by the Monday of the second week before beginning another.'),
(9677, 'We need to collect [Bloated Fish] and [Mackeral] as [Captain] Icap wishes. |?[Fishing] is near the each nations base castles camp (Laon/Dona). |? When the quest is completed, these items will be turned in.'),
(9678, '? This quest | [Jade Solo 30 years to bring the candy ingredients to receive a basket of candy to give to his girl must be passed as a daily quest once a day can be done. Takes a one-hour time limit * item must be performed within 1 hour quest.'),
(9679, 'What? [Candy Ingredient]? Sorry I dont think I can do it. For now I have lost all the [Candy Ingrediant] into the water.'),
(9680, 'Do you want to know what happened? Okay, I£kl tell you. I was transporting massive [Candy Ingredients] for this White Day. Then, suddenly, a school of fish in the water made a hole in the bottom of my ship and swallowed all the [Candy Ingredients]! I think the sweet smell has seduced them. Can you catch 20 [Fat-bellied fishes], because they swallowed all of my candy ingredients, and bring them to me? I can£s go by myself because I need to fix the ship . . . Oh, can you please catch 20 [Mackerels], too? I think I£kl get hungry after I fix my boat. You can purchase the fishing pole at the [Sundries Store] for fishing. Fishing places are located at near the camps (Laon, Dona) of the main castle in each country.'),
(9681, 'Still no? You need to catch [Bloated Fish] and [Mackerel].'),
(9682, 'Finally! Sneaky Fish! Im going to cut your stomach to find the ingredients. |? Once the quest gets completed [Bloated Fish] and [Mackerel] will be turned in.'),
(9683, 'Ill take all of these! See you again!'),
(9684, 'What are you looking for? You have something for me?'),
(9685, 'I think you are thinking of me as someone else. People say I look a like with many other people.'),
(9686, 'You do not have enough bag space so I cant give you a reply. Come back after making sure you have enough space.'),
(9687, 'He wanted this delivered? Hes not brave! Coward! Ill reply so please deliver it.'),
(9688, 'Wheres the candy basket?'),
(9689, 'Sigh?I dont want to be single anymore.'),
(9690, 'White Day Event Information.'),
(9691, '? for 31 years Ive been single?31 years? I should have shown her my braveside?'),
(9692, 'You have lost the [Candy basket]? No!!! Ill just give you another!!'),
(9693, 'Whats wrong with me? You really dont know? Look above my head!!! It says [Single for 30 years]. Sigh? I really need to get out of this single status.'),
(9694, 'Come on, please help me. Theres a [Captain] Icap and he has all the [Candy Ingredients]. Please give me the [Candy Ingredients] and Ill turn that into a [Candy Basket]. With that, please make me not a solo for 31 years.'),
(9695, 'You havent finished with the delivery? Come up please deliver safely.'),
(9696, 'Its an answer!!!!   Th?Thank you?'),
(9697, 'You have brought me the [Candy Ingredients]. Hold on a minute. Ill make the [Candy Basket] now.'),
(9698, '[Captain] Icap has the [Candy ingredients]. Please help me.'),
(9699, 'Ah!!!! Ive been single for 31 years! No?Im single again? No way!!!'),
(9700, 'You do not have enough space. Please come back after making more enough'),
(9701, 'Damn fish! I need to fix the boat too! Ah!!!'),
(9702, 'Thank you for your help today. Please help me again tomorrow.'),
(9703, 'You want me to open something? Wheres the box I need to open?'),
(9704, 'This box?lets see. Yep, I can open it. I dont know whats gonna come out though.'),
(9705, 'Heres the [Candy Basket]. Please propose to her with this.'),
(9706, 'You can get [Seal Item]. If you have purchased the [Seal Exchange Coupon] from the Power Up Store, youll be able to receive the item.'),
(9707, 'You can get [Seal Item]. If you have purchased the [Seal Exchange Coupon] from the Power Up Store, youll be able to receive the item.'),
(9708, 'You have selected [10 Seal Exchange]. Would you like to receive the item?'),
(9709, 'You have selected [50 Seal Exchange]. Would you like to receive the item?'),
(9710, 'Follow [Guard] Cabals order and catch [Worm], [Bandikut], [Caegoon] and [Vulkan].'),
(9711, 'Follow [Guard] Cabals order and catch [Bandikut], [Caegoon], [Vulkan], [Gabolt].'),
(9712, 'Follow [Guard] Cabals order and catch  [Vulkan], [Gabolt],[Volteur], [Werewolf].'),
(9713, 'Follow [Guard] Cabals order and catch  [Vulkan], [Gabolt],[Volteur], [Werewolf].'),
(9714, 'Follow [Guard] Cabals order and catch  [Vulkan], [Gabolt],[Volteur], [Werewolf].'),
(9715, 'Follow [Guard] Cabals order and catch  [Gabolt],[Volteur], [Werewolf], [Cylan].'),
(9716, 'Follow [Guard] Cabals order and catch  [Gabolt],[Volteur], [Werewolf], [Cylan].'),
(9717, 'Follow [Guard] Cabals order and catch  [Volteur], [Werewolf], [Cylan], [Gloomwing].'),
(9718, 'Follow [Guard] Cabals order and catch  [Volteur], [Werewolf], [Cylan], [Gloomwing].'),
(9719, 'Follow [Guard] Cabals order and catch  [Werewolf], [Cylan], [Gloomwing], [Scorpion].'),
(9720, 'Follow [Guard] Cabals order and catch  [Werewolf], [Cylan], [Gloomwing], [Scorpion].'),
(9721, 'Follow [Guard] Cabals order and catch  [Cylan], [Gloomwing], [Scorpion], [Zombie].'),
(9722, 'Follow [Guard] Cabals order and catch  [Cylan], [Gloomwing], [Scorpion], [Zombie].'),
(9723, 'Follow [Guard] Cabals order and catch [Gloomwing], [Scorpion], [Zombie], [Skeleton].'),
(9724, 'Follow [Guard] Cabals order and catch [Gloomwing], [Scorpion], [Zombie], [Skeleton].'),
(9725, 'You have been brought to the jail for using [Hack Tool]. You can go back to Moradon when you have completed the punishments here.'),
(9726, 'Please come back when you have completed the punishment missions. You need the [Punishment Stick] to defeat the monsters for the missions. Take the first item'),
(9727, 'You have used the [Hack Tool] again? Why would you use it again? You dont have any respect towards the game at all? Come on!!'),
(9728, 'Please thoroughly complete the mission to leave the jail.'),
(9729, 'Mission completed. If you even come back here again, you will get harsher punishment. Keep in mind and try not to come back here ever again.'),
(9730, 'You have the [Return of the Warrior]. For the Returned hero, you can rent out the weapon for free.'),
(9731, 'You have the [Return of the Warrior]. For the returned hero, well give free buff.'),
(9732, 'You have the [Return of the Warrior]. For the returned hero, well give free buff.'),
(9733, 'You do not have the [Return of the Warrior]. You are not a participant of this event. This event is [comeback] Event'),
(9734, 'Come back Event Description'),
(9735, 'The items you can receive because you have [Return of the Warrior] can be received only once. Please remember this.'),
(9736, 'You have [Return of the Warrior]. Thank you for coming back. Would you like to receive the item?'),
(9737, 'You do not have the enough inventory space. Make at least 15 spaces.'),
(9738, 'Hello, I£l here to distribute the prize for those who has come back. Im the [Savor] Sirin.'),
(9739, 'You have already received all the item. Thank you for your return.'),
(9740, 'Oh, the [Punishment Stick]? You need to purchase the [Wing of Dragon + Stick] from the PUS. Then come and I will trade you the item.'),
(9741, 'You want to trade the [Punishment Stick]?'),
(9742, 'It seems like you do not have the voucher for the stick. Or you already have one.'),
(9743, 'You have not enough Noah. You cant buy this yet.'),
(9744, 'Here is the [Punishment Stick]. It will disappear once the quest is finished or after one month if the quest is not finished.'),
(9745, 'Collect [Small Sprout] for [Forest Guard] Dry to receive one of the followings: [EXP Scroll], [Contribution Scroll], [Life Scroll], [Defense Scroll].'),
(9746, 'Bring the [Leaf of Disguise] to [Forest Guard] Dry and receive [Tree Transformation Hat]'),
(9747, 'You must go to [Life Guardian] Naia with [Tree Seedlings of Life] after planting [Seed of Life] in the [Gigantic heap of Earth] in the middle of Arrdream, Ronark Land and stronghold of Ronark Land.|? You can receive [Seed of Life] from [Angry Spirit of Tree], which is summoned rarely from [Heap of Earth with good quality] or [Loggers] dispatched to Arrdream, Ronark Land and the stronghold of Ronark Land.'),
(9748, 'Go visit [Forest Guard] Dry with [Seed] which you can obtain from many monsters and [Fertilizer] from the merchant. |? This quest is a [chain quest].You will need to complete the whole quest to receive [Shiny Tree Soul]'),
(9749, 'You need to bring [Small Sprout] to [Forest Guard] Dry. [Small Sprout] can be obtained by giving [Good Quality Heap of Earth], some [Seed] and [Fertilizer].'),
(9750, '[Forest Guard] Dry asks for the peace of the [Mad Tree Soul]. |? This quest is a [chain quest].You will need to complete the whole quest to receive [Shiny Tree Soul]'),
(9751, 'Please deliver [Branch of the Life Tree] which can be obtained from [Good quality heap of earth] to [Forest Guard] Dry.|? This quest is a [chain quest].You will need to complete the whole quest to receive [Shiny Tree Soul]'),
(9752, 'Please deliver [Leaf of Life] which you can obtain by completing the quest [New Life for the Pioneer Area] to [Forest Guard] Dry. |? This quest is a [chain quest].You will need to complete the whole quest to receive [Shiny Tree Soul]'),
(9753, 'Please deliver [Forest Guardian Registration Form] which you can obtain by completing quest [Evidence of Seedling] to [Forest Guard] Dry. |? This quest is a [chain quest].You will need to complete the whole quest to receive [Shiny Tree Soul]'),
(9754, 'You must bring [Branch of Life], which you can obtain from [Heap of Earth with good quality], and [Leaf of Life], which you can obtain after you complete the quest [New Life in the Frontier Zone], to [Life Guardian] Naia.|? This quest is [Repeatable Quest]. If you complete the quest [Forest Guardian], you can perform this quest once a day.'),
(9755, 'Planting Tree Event Description'),
(9756, 'Todays sky seems so blue. Hello. Im Dry whos been summoned by the [Forest Guard].'),
(9757, 'This beautiful land is changing as there had been war battles and careless lumberjacks.'),
(9758, 'We are collecting [Small Sprout] to save the trees.'),
(9759, 'Please bring me [Small Sprout] then youll be able to select one of the following. Would you help me?'),
(9760, 'Hm.. Youll need some more.'),
(9761, 'Good job! You are done!'),
(9762, 'Ill keep asking you for this. Until Adonis continent becomes all green!'),
(9763, 'Oh no? No matter how hard I try to plant the seed because of [Lumberjack]s Im not able to speed up.'),
(9764, 'To trade these [Lumberjack] Im collecting [Leaf of Disguise] to make [Tree Transformation Hat]. Could you please bring me [Transformation Leaves] then Ill give you [Tree Transformation Hat].'),
(9765, 'Will you help me? | >> This quest can be done only once.'),
(9766, 'For the goal of making this continent green again, [Forest Guardian] has summoned me and [Guard of Life] Naiya.'),
(9767, 'We are trying our best to collect [Small Sprouts]. But we dont seem to have enough. This means youll need to help me!'),
(9768, 'Please go ahead and bring me [Seed] and [Fertilizer]. Ill be waiting for you. |? This quest is a [chain quest].You will need to complete the whole quest to receive [Shiny Tree Soul]'),
(9769, 'Next, I need [Small Sprout]. What does it mean? Please go ahead and come back with it again.'),
(9770, 'Thank you. With the [Seed] and [Fertilizers] you have brought to us, we were able to start on this. We have another favor to ask you now.'),
(9771, 'This time well need [Small Sprout]. We have as much as possible, but itll be great if you can contribute.'),
(9772, 'What am I saying? Im saying that you should hurry up to help us.'),
(9773, 'Because of the ruined environment [Mad Tree Souls] are attacking human. They became really upset. Could you please calm them out? Please?'),
(9774, 'Trees are disappearing from Adonis Land and the guardians protecting the tree souls are disappearing as well.'),
(9775, 'Their hatred has been intensified. Its so sad..  Because of the greed humans have, pure souls are invaded by the darkness.'),
(9776, 'Could you please help them to calm down?'),
(9777, 'It seems that the spirits have been calmed down. Now we can restore their souls into pure ones. Please bring [Branch of the life]. With this, well be able to wake them up.'),
(9778, 'Thank you. [Mad Tree Spirit] have been restored back to the nature.'),
(9779, 'Now we need to make sure that this forest grows by waking the restored spirits up.'),
(9780, 'Please bring [Branch of Life]. With this we will be able to wake them up.'),
(9781, 'They£kl wake up soon! I can feel that the energy of the spirit is getting full! Now it£r time to help those spirits in earnest. Recover [Seed of Life] from [Loggers] and plant it in the [Gigantic heap of Earth] in Arrdream, Ronark Land, and the Stronghold of Ronark Land. Then, get the [Tree Seedlings of Life] sprouted from the [Gigantic heap of Earth] and bring it to [Guardian of Life] Naia. Don£s forget that you have to bring [Leaf of Life] to me.'),
(9782, 'Spirits are feeling that their energy is getting filled!'),
(9783, 'Now its our time to help them. We should do our best. Of course with you <selfname>.'),
(9784, 'First, you have to help [Guardian of Life] Naia by getting the [Seed of Life] back from the [Loggers] who has taken them away from us. Then, go to Arrdream, Ronark Land, the Stronghold of Ronark Land, and plant those seeds in the middle of [Gigantic heap of Earth], and then bring [Tree Seedlings of Life]. If you deliver [Tree Seedlings of Life] to [Guardian of Life] Naia, you£kl get [Leaf of Life]. Please bring that [Leaf of Life] to me.'),
(9785, 'Thank you <selfname>. Due to your effort, this continent will be full of trees again. I£kl appoint you as the [Guardian of Forest] to return your favor! Bring me the [Application of Forest Guardian], which I gave to you before. You don£s understand why you should fill this form? Well, we need to do the paperwork, don£s we?'),
(9786, 'Because of you, <selfname> this continent will become green again. Thank you for helping.'),
(9787, 'Ill appoint you as a [Forest Guardian]. Whats the benefit of being the guardian? Youll find out soon.'),
(9788, 'Please bring me [Forest Guardian Registration Form], the one I gave you earlier. Ill need this to make it official.'),
(9789, 'Thats correct. Now, please bring [Sleeping Tree Spirit] to [Life Guardian] Naiya. After that, once a day, sleeping spirit will be woken up.'),
(9790, 'Hello. Im [Life Guardian] Naiya. Ive been dispatched by [Forest Guard].'),
(9791, 'You already finished today. Please come back tomorrow.'),
(9792, 'Ill take all of the [Leaf of Disguise]. Well need it.'),
(9793, 'The reason I came here is to restore new lives in these Ardream, Ronarkland area. But it seems the place is really big so its a bit difficult for me to handle it by myself'),
(9794, 'Then regain [Life Seed] from [Lumberjack], go to Ardream, Ronarkland, plant it on [Giant Heap of Earth] and come back to me with [Life Tree Seedling]. Please hurry'),
(9795, 'You are still not done? Its taking too long.'),
(9796, 'Good job. Well it did take a long time for you to get this done. But anyways, good job.'),
(9797, 'Ill ask you again tomorrow. Please dont runaway but come. We have many trees to plant.'),
(9798, 'You came to wake sleeping tree spirits. Since you are the [Forest Guardian] you can definitely do this.'),
(9799, 'In order to wake sleeping Tree Spirit, youll need [Leaf of Life] and [Branch of Life]. These two will be needed.'),
(9800, 'These are [Leaf of Life] and [Branches of Life]. You can obtain [Leaf of Life] by completing [New life to the New land] quest. [Branch of Life] can be obtained when you are planting seeds on [Good quality healp of Earth].'),
(9801, 'You have brought everything. We should wake up the spirits, now.'),
(9802, 'Finally, its been woken up. This child wants to be with you, <selfname>. Please take a good care of him.'),
(9803, 'Its the [Sleeping Tree Spirit]?Then it means that [Forest Observer] has been recognized as [Forest Guard].'),
(9804, 'Wheres the [Sleeping Tree Spirit]? Dont kid around.'),
(9805, 'Would you like to wake him up now?'),
(9806, '[You can see the traces that the seedling has started to grow. Well need to wait a day to plant it again.]'),
(9807, '[There is no seed to plant]'),
(9808, 'New Life to the New Land Quest Description'),
