(9810, 'Complete once a day [New Life to the New Land] quest and receive [Organic Tree Box]. [Organic Tree Box] has random accessories and other items.'),
(9811, 'Do you have the [Organic Tree Box]? Would you like to trade it?'),
(9812, 'You do not have [Organic Tree Box]. You will need to complete the [New Life to New Land] quest to receive the box.'),
