(9936, 'Description about [Runaway brother] Event.'),
(9937, 'Description about [Runaway brother] Event.'),
(9938, '[Yeniceri Minerva Costume] is in stock. You can get the new Minerva by exchanging with the voucher from the PowerUp Store.'),
(9939, 'Select timeline shown on the Voucher that you have purchased.'),
(9940, 'You do not have the [Yeniceri Minerva Helmet Voucher]. You can purchase the Voucher at the PowerUp Store.'),
(9941, 'Voucher confirmed. Please select the option.'),
(9942, 'You do not have the [Yeniceri Minerva Armor Voucher].  You can purchase the Voucher at the PowerUp Store.'),
(9943, 'You do not have the [Golden Pickax Voucher]. Once you purchase the [DISC Premium] you will get the [Golden Pickax Voucher].'),
(9944, 'You can exchange to a [Golden Pickax] which you can use for 30 days. Would like to exchange it now?'),
(9945, 'You do not have the [Golden Fishing Pole Voucher]. [Golden Fishing Pole Voucher] can be received if you buy either the  [EXP Premium] or the  [WAR Premium].'),
