(9954, 'Would you like to receive benefit of [War Premium]?'),
(9955, 'You do not have [War Premium].'),
(9956, 'You do not have [Mysterious Gold]. You can obtain this by digging with [Gold Pickax]'),
(9957, 'You do not have [Mysterious Gold]. You can obtain this by digging with [Gold Pickax]'),
(9958, 'Hello. I£l the ¡iuide?of [Twilight Guard], Ura, and I£l from the far desert country. I came here to eradicate the force of evil that I have sensed in my country. I£l performing my role as a guide for heroes here, as the great and generous king of Karus promised to support me. <selfname>, I£ue found that you£qe one of the great heroes. Will you help us?'),
(9959, 'You have registered for another battle. Since you are involved in the other battle, I cannot transport you.'),
(9960, 'Currently, theres [Lunar War]. How can I guide when its time like this? Please finish what you have started and talk to me again.'),
(9961, 'There are many heros helping us already. Come back next time, please.'),
(9962, 'You will help us! Great! Are you ready? Would you like me to guide you right now?'),
(9963, 'Hello. I£l the ¡iuide?of [Twilight Guard], Murr, and I£l from the desert country. I came here to eradicate the force of evil that I have sensed in my country. Under wise and noble decision of El Morad£r king, who is the guard of honor and justice, we can get help from the heroes. That£r why I£l guiding heroes, just like you, to their own countries. <selfname>, I found that you£qe one of the great heroes. Will you help us for the country?'),
(9964, 'You have registered for another battle. Since you are involved in the other battle, I cannot transport you.'),
(9965, 'Currently, theres [Lunar War]. How can I guide when its time like this? Please finish what you have started and talk to me again.'),
(9966, 'There are many heros helping us already. Come back next time, please.'),
(9967, 'You will help us? Thank you. Lets see if you are ready for this. Itll be a long journey.'),
(9968, 'I£ue heard that [Belongings of Dead Warrior] are found in many places. I£l casting a buff for the heroes who bring 3 [Belongings of Dead Warrior], by order of our great king. It£r a reward for helping us to praise the honor and appease the souls of honorable warriors.'),
(9969, '[Belongings of Dead Warrior] that you have brought to me isn£s enough. Be sure you have enough and then talk to me again.'),
(9970, 'Which buff do you want?'),
(9971, 'I£ue heard that [Belongings of Dead Warrior] are found in many places. I£l casting a buff for the heroes who bring three [Belongings of Dead Warrior], by order of our great king. It£r a reward for helping us to praise the honor and appease the souls of honorable warriors.'),
(9972, '[Belongings of Dead Warrior] that you have brought to me isn£s enough. Be sure you have enough and then talk to me again.'),
(9973, 'Which buff do you want?'),
(9974, 'Today£r mission is over. Please come back tomorrow.'),
(9975, 'There is an official request to Moradon. We are renting our weapons to the users who bring 10 [Belongings of Dead Warrior] once a day, under support of kings of Karus and El Morad. We aren£s paid with money for it but we accept [Belongings of Dead Warrior] instead.'),
(9976, '[Belongings of Dead Warrior] that you have brought to me isn£s enough. Be sure you have enough and then talk to me again.'),
(9977, '<Selfname> is a Warrior, so (looking at the list) . . . . <font color=@#660066@>Glaive</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Chitin Armor Set</font> will be provided. Will you spend your 10 [Belongings of Dead Warrior] for rental?'),
(9978, '<Selfname> is a Rogue, so (looking at the list) . . . . <font color=@#660066@>Mirage Dagger</font>, <font color=@#660066@>Chitin Bow</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Chitin Armor Set</font> will be provided. Will you spend your 10 [Belongings of Dead Warrior] for rental?'),
(9979, '<Selfname> is a Mage, so (looking at the list) . . . . <font color=@#660066@>Elemental Staff</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Crimson Armor Set</font> will be provided. Will you spend your 10 [Belongings of Dead Warrior] for rental?'),
(9980, '<Selfname> is a Priest, so (looking at the list) . . . . <font color=@#660066@>Lycaon Mace</font>, <font color=@#660066@>Defender of the Road</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Chitin Armor Set</font> will be provided. Will you spend your 10 [Belongings of Dead Warrior] for rental?'),
(9981, '<Selfname> is a Warrior, so (looking at the list) . . . . <font color=@#660066@>Raptor</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Chitin Shell Armor Set</font> will be provided. Will you spend your 10 [Belongings of Dead Warrior] for rental?'),
(9982, '<Selfname> is a Rogue, so (looking at the list) . . . . <font color=@#660066@>Shard</font>, <font color=@#660066@>Iron Bow</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Chitin Shell Armor Set</font> will be provided. Will you spend your 10 [Belongings of Dead Warrior] for rental?'),
(9983, '<Selfname> is a Mage, so (looking at the list) . . . . <font color=@#660066@>Elixir Staff</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Complete Armor Set</font> will be provided. Will you spend your 10 [Belongings of Dead Warrior] for rental?'),
(9984, '<Selfname> is a Priest, so (looking at the list) . . . . <font color=@#660066@>Holy Animal</font>, <font color=@#660066@>Defender of Piana Knight Squad</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Chitin Shell Armor Set</font> will be provided. Will you spend your 10 [Belongings of Dead Warrior] for rental?'),
(9985, '<Selfname> is a Warrior, so (looking at the list) . . . . <font color=@#660066@> Sword of Novice Mercenary</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Armor Set of Novice Mercenary</font> will be provided. Will you spend your 10 [Belongings of Dead Warrior] for rental?'),
(9986, '<Selfname> is a Rogue, so (looking at the list) . . . . <font color=@#660066@> Dagger of Novice Assassin</font>, <font color=@#660066@>Bow of Novice Assassin</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Armor Set of Novice Assassin</font> will be provided. Will you spend your 10 [Belongings of Dead Warrior] for rental?'),
(9987, '<Selfname> is a Mage, so (looking at the list) . . . . <font color=@#660066@>Staff of Novice Magic Scholar</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Armor Set of Novice Magic Scholar</font> will be provided. Will you spend your 10 [Belongings of Dead Warrior] for rental?'),
(9988, '<Selfname> is a Priest, so (looking at the list) . . . . <font color=@#660066@>Mace of Novice Paladin</font> and <font color=@#660066@>Armor Set of Novice Paladin</font> will be provided. Will you spend your 10 [Belongings of Dead Warrior] for rental?'),
(9989, 'You are the one who came here to ask [Spirit£r Help]. You need [Dryads Exchange Coupon] or [Oreads Exchange Coupon] to get help from each spirit. You can purchase each coupon at the [Powerup Store]. Then, you£kl be helped in these ways:|?Dryads: Dryads is a nymph who lives in a tree. The nymph sharply increases the acquisition rate of Noahs.|?Oreads: Oreads is a nymph who lives in a mountain. The nymph makes you to obtain items around you automatically.|?Alseids: a nymph who lives in the forest. The nymph casts you a buff of the [King£r Enchanter] for free and rents you an item from [Equipment Quartermaster] for free once a day.'),
(9990, 'Do you really want to exchange an item? Please be aware of the fact that once you exchange it, you won£s be able to cancel it or exchange to another item.'),
(9991, 'You don£s have an exchange coupon. You need [Dryads Exchange Coupon] or [Oreads Exchange Coupon]. You can purchase these coupons at the [Powerup Store].'),
(9992, 'You don£s have an exchange coupon. You need [Alseids Exchange Coupon] or [Alseids Exchange Coupon]. You can purchase these coupons at the [Powerup Store].'),
(10000, 'Cheers! For the strong warrior! Heres some good nutritious food for you. Hehehe'),
