(10020, '9th Knight Online Anniversary Event'),
(10021, 'Youll receive [Gift Box] when you are hunting the monsters at your level. If you attack [Cakie] whos in front of the town with the [Fork] which you can obtain from the merchant, youll be able to obtain [Piece of cake].'),
