(10023, 'Youll need to have the box in order for me to unlock the box.'),
(10024, 'If you have 50 [Piece of Cake] you can exchange them with a [Unique Pet Transformation Scroll]. Its hard to obtain so theres only one chance.'),
(10025, 'What type of cake do you like? With the 10 [Pieces of Cake] you can obtain buffs. [Piece of Cake] x 10 and [choco Cake] : Defense increases by 40; [Yam Cake] : HP Increase 250 ; [Cheese Cake] : Attack increase 5'),
(10026, 'If you have 10 [Pieces of Cake] youll be able to receive one of the following.'),
(10027, 'Youll need to have enough [Pieces of Cake].'),
(10028, 'Physical strength is very important for early cheering. [Buff Items for World Cup Victory] have the following effects. |? You£kl get reward for each of five [Ginsengs] and five [Sea Cucumbers], and the reward will be one of the next. | ? three-year-old ginseng: 40-point increase of Defensive Power |? three-year-old Red ginseng: 250-point increase of HP |- Sea Cucumber Soup: 5-point increase of Attack Power | - Steamed Sea Cucumber: 4-point increase of Contribution Point'),
(10029, 'Which one of the [Buff Cake] would you like?'),
(10030, 'You have received [monster stone] already.Youll need to wait for another day to obtain [Monster stone]. Please come back tomorrow'),
(10031, 'This is the [Monster stone]. Hunt the boss and good luck obtaining the item.'),
(10032, 'You have [Pieces of Cake]! Ill take them now.'),
(10033, 'This [Unique Pet Transportation Scroll] is very rare. Bring me 50 [Pieces of Cake] to exchange it with the scroll'),
