(10300, 'Hey, Listen to me. | That Mister over there is dismantling the wepon I made.'),
(10301, 'What are you doing? Are you just looking at what Im doing? Does it just look like its a piece of metal? Go tell them about my skill.')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(10302, 'Hahaha. Shojin says that? It seems like hes the person who has craftsmanship.'),
(10303, 'I get how he has the skill now.'),
(10304, 'It seems that Shojin is upset at the skill that Ive been teaching.'),
(10305, 'Hello. Im Ereya [Twilight Knight].'),
(10306, 'Do you know of [Unknown] Narki? He used to be our master craftsman. | He wasnt dismantling from the first place.'),
(10307, 'Then, one day, he started to dismantling National treasures so he was deported. | Im sure he misses the food from here. Could you please deliver the food to him?'),
(10308, 'If you dont hurry the food will go bad.'),
(10309, 'This smell! Its the smell of our kingdoms spice!'),
(10310, 'Ereya? he hasnt forgotten me. | Its so good to smell the home meal. Ill do my best. Give me all the [Middle level item] then Ill show you my skills. I dont know what Ill be making but Ill show you how its done.'),
(10311, 'It takes a long time to cook hometowns meal. Please come back tomorrow.'),
(10312, 'The item made by Shojin is special. | to prove that, well need [Master Craftmans Touch]. You can get this by mismantling items that are at least [Middle Level Item].'),
(10313, 'You seem you are quick in understanding. Bring me 20 [Master Craftmans touch] then Ill give you [Manganese] which will help combining the old accessories.'),
(10314, 'You will need at least 20 [Master Craftmans touch] to exchange it with the [Manganese]. At least 1 to exchange it with [Buff Jewel].'),
(10315, 'It seems that your pockets full. You must have at least 20 [Master Craftmans Touch].'),
(10316, 'Hm..you dont have space in your inventory.'),
(10317, 'Ireya is good at making hometown meal. | What he had made before was awesome I miss it!'),
(10318, '20 [Master Craftmans Touch] is changed to 1 [Manganese] and 1 [Master Craftmans Touch] is exchanged with 1 [Buff Jewel]. Which one would you like?'),
(10319, 'You are a student whos looking forward to take the final exam! Hope you get the score you want. Cheers!'),
(10320, 'Lets prey for all As!'),
(10321, '[Final Test] Quest'),
(10330, 'Ho, ho, ho, <selfname>!! Merry Christmas! |I can tell that Christmas is coming since the weather is getting colder.'),
(10331, 'Hmm, but I heard the monsters are attacking the main castle and ruining the vacation.'),
(10332, 'And they also took the materials that will be made into gifts. There will be some monsters that drop [Gift Material] when you punish them. |If you happen to pick them up, collect 10 of [Gift Material] and bring them to me. |Ill give you [Santas Hat] in return so you can enjoy the Christmas mood.'),
(10333, 'You havent punished the monsters yet? I guess you are short of [Gift Material] still. |Monsters will appear on certain time near the entrance of main castle. Find out when they come out, and punish those bastards.'),
(10334, 'Well, I can see that youve done your job! You have 10 or more of [Gift Material] with you.'),
(10335, 'Alright, as I promised, Ill take the [Gift Materials] and give you [Santas Hat]. Im  sure youd look good in one.'),
(10336, 'Hello, <selfname>. Merry Christmas...|Why do I seem depressed, you ask? I hid the powder used for flying and my Christmas present under the ground, but I cant find where I hid it! |I tried everywhere, but I cant find them.'),
(10337, 'I think I put them near the mining area, |but I now have no idea where it is. Everything there is dug up!|Please mine there and find [Mudskipper] and [Salmon], 10 of each.'),
(10338, 'If you get me 10 of both [Mudskipper] and [Salmon], Ill give you [Cupids Wings]. They will make you feel like you can fly.|You wont be able to use them for a long time, but thats all I could do for you. Please understand.'),
(10339, '[Mudskipper] and [Salmon] are hard to find, huh? But I need them, 10 of each!'),
(10340, 'I can tell that you found all of [Mudskipper] and [Salmon]!! Am I right?'),
(10341, 'Ill give you this for your hard work.|I can give you this any time you bring 10 [Flying Powders] and 10 [Salmons]. Thanks in advance!'),
(10342, '<selfname>!! Merry Christmas! Have you been well?|I can tell that the year is almost over now that Christmas is coming.|Why dont you give gifts to people that are close and dear to you?'),
(10343, 'Since you are a warrior, I will give you [Warriors Seal]. |Write somebody a letter and let them know that you care by giving them the seal.'),
(10344, 'Since you are a rogue, I will give you [Rogues Seal]. |Write somebody a letter and let them know that you care by giving them the seal.'),
(10345, 'Since you are a magician, I will give you [Magicians Seal]. |Write somebody a letter and let them know that you care by giving them the seal.'),
(10346, 'Since you are a priest, I will give you [Priests Seal]. |Write somebody a letter and let them know that you care by giving them the seal.'),
(10347, 'If you have been good to people, you will probably receive lots of seals.|Once you have all four kinds of seals, go visit  [OKAN].|I heard [Okan] has been collecting those seals.'),
(10348, 'Each of those seals are hand made. |That means they take long time to make! |Come back tomorrow.'),
(10349, '<selfname>!Merry Christmas!! |I dont know if you heard yet, but I am collecting [Heroes Seals].|I heard that the seals of warrior, rogue, magician, and priest form one set. |[Islant Fortuneteller] wouldnt give one to me because Im not a hero like you. |If you ever get to collect [Heroes Seals] by the set, then please give them to me.'),
(10350, '<selfname>! Merry Christmas!! |You are smiling! Does that mean you have something for me? |Isnt that [Heroes Seal] in your hands? ||Could you give that to me? ||Why dont you exchange that with something I have? Hmmm?'),
(10351, 'Oh, the seal!!|Please come back to me anytime you come across this seal!'),
(10352, 'Merry Christmas! |Im quite in a hurry. I need [Christmas Crystal] for decorating the Christmas tree. Could you get me 10 of that? Thanks! *Winks*'),
(10353, 'Ive heard that as you hunt monsters that are suited for you, you can obtain [Christmas Crystal].|If you get me 10 [Christmas Crystals], I will take something out of [Beautiful Santa]s gift bag and give it to you. *Winks*'),
(10354, 'You don£s have 10 of [Christmas Crystal] yet, it seems.|As you hunt monsters that are suited for your level, |you should be able to obtain [Christmas Crystal]. *Winks*'),
(10355, 'It looks like you have 10 or more of [Christmas Crystals]! Wanna trade with me? *Winks*'),
(10356, 'Thanks to you, <selfname>, now I can decorate my tree! |Ill give you this in return. *Winks*'),
(10360, 'There is not enough room in the bag. Please check it out.'),
(10361, 'There is not enough room in the bag. Please check it out.'),
(10362, 'There is not enough room in the bag. Please check it out.'),
(10363, 'There is not enough room in the bag. Please check it out.'),
(10364, 'There is not enough room in the bag. Please check it out.'),
