(10366, 'You dont have a [Price of Spirit Recovery Voucher].'),
(10370, 'I would like to express how respectful of you I am. | Because we have hero like yourself, our country is looking brighter than ever! | Myself [Twilight Guardian], Martin, will reward you.'),
(10371, 'It seems you dont have enough inventory space.'),
(10372, 'It seems you didnt really contribute much for this battle. But I do praise your bravery. | [Twlight Guardian] will reward you now.'),
(10373, 'Please remember that I honestly appreciate what youve done for us. | Ill see you at the next battle.'),
(10374, 'I believe Ive honestly expressed my appreciation.'),
(10375, 'You seem to have all the ability as the Twilight Knight. Ill give you a mission, complete it at once.'),
(10376, 'Please receive the order from [Twilight Guardian] Issac.'),
