(10510, 'G-Zone PC Cafe  Description'),
(10511, 'G-Zone PC Cafe  Description'),
(10512, '[Lucky Bag] has been stolen by the bad snowman. Please find my [Lucky Bag].'),
(10513, 'Snowman can cast spells but with this youll be able to see what types of spells they are casting. Please defeat the snowman and get me 5 [Lucky Bag].'),
