(10843, 'What type of [Knight Choas Day Wing] would you want?'),
(10844, 'You do not have the wing exchange coupon.'),
(10845, 'Whenever my son defeated enemy, he received [Dog Tag]. I would like to have [Luthers Tags].'),
(10846, 'You have 10 tags? | sobbing?  yes..  Thats my sons name..  Thank you so very much. | To show my appreciation Ill give you one of these.'),
(10847, 'If you keep bringing more Ill exchange them with the item you want.'),
(10848, 'Your bag is full so I cant give you the item.'),
(10849, 'We dont know what type of items will be coming out but we wish you luck.'),
(10850, 'You have [Monster Staff] Juriad Jewel Box. | You have received this item. | Here you go.'),
(10851, 'I do not think you have [Monster Staff] Juriad Jewel Box. | Check again.'),
(10852, 'You have [Monster Staff] Accessory Box. | You have thie type of time. | Here you go.'),
(10853, 'You do not have [Monster Staff] Accessory Box. | Check again.'),
