(10857, 'You do not have [Monster Staff] 7th Defense Package. | Check again.'),
(10858, 'You have [Monster Staff] Guardian Exchange Coupon. | Here you go.'),
(10859, 'You do not have [Monster Staff] Guardian Exchange Coupon. | Check again.'),
