(10869, 'You do not have the item thatll not be able to strengthen the 7th Defense equipment. Check again.'),
(10870, 'Thank you for your participation for [Knight Chaos Day]. You have {Knight Chaos Day] Chaos Guardian Exchange Coupon. Ill exchange it for you.'),
(10871, 'We are exchanging the Kaos Guardian Transformation Exchange Coupon for the ones who have joined for the [Knight Chaos Day]. | Characters who has the coupon can visit to exchange it.'),
