(10879, 'You do not have [World Championship Application].'),
(10880, 'Hello</ font> <font color=@#990000@> <selfname> Im [VIP Manager] Julianne.'),
(10881, 'Would you like to receive benefit of [Gold Premium]?'),
(10882, 'You do not have [Gold Premium].'),
(10883, 'Dear <selfname>, do you like Snowman?'),
(10884, 'Nope, Snowman isnt our friend anymore. Hes just an enemy now.'),
(10885, 'Due to the Naughty Snowman, the townspeople are all complaining. Snowman has made the ground slippery and its so dangerous for us!'),
(10886, 'Oh my, you the Knight must help us out! Please defeat the snowman and bring me 5 x snow crystals. I will reward you!'),
(10887, 'You have 5 [Snow Crystal]!'),
(10888, 'Thank you so much, Knight! Heres the gift I have prepared for you.'),
(10889, 'When will you defeat the Snowman?'),
(10890, 'Thats too bad. Im sure Snowman could have been defeated by you.'),
(10891, 'Thank you for purchasing [Chaos Wings].  Preferred Option of [Chaos Wings] is available.'),
(10892, '[Chaos Wings Voucher] can be exchanged for [Chaos Wings].  Please visit [NPC] Kayra in Moradon to exchange.'),
(10893, 'You have received Chaos Wings. Thank you for your support for Knight Online. Good Hunting!'),
(10894, 'Which [Chaos Wings] would you like to receive?'),
(10895, 'You do not have a [Chaos Wing Voucher]. Please return with the character who holds the [Chaos Wing Voucher].'),
(10896, 'Please help us tomorrow. You have already obtained enough of [Mudskipper] and [Salmon].'),
(10897, 'Ill take one [Evidence of Oracle].'),
(10898, 'You do not have [Evidence of Oracle].'),
(10899, 'You have turned in 1 [Evidence of Oracle].'),
(10900, 'You do not have the name that fits the merchanting. Would you like to change your character name?'),
(10901, 'To change the character name youll be logged out from the game. Would you like to accept?'),
(10902, 'Your character name isnt suitable for merchanting. Youll need to change your character name. If you are a king or any important advisor, you wont be able to change yhour name. Youll need to withdraw from your position to change your name.'),
(10903, 'Hello! Its the new year! For this year, hope you have a great new year! | If you offer contribution, your fortune will be told. | Arent you interested?'),
(10904, 'How much will you pay?'),
(10905, 'Congratulations. You have a great fortune for this coming year.'),
(10906, 'Ill give you reward for your great fortune.'),
(10907, 'Happy new year! *^^*| Because this years related to dragon. Were asking Black Dragon for a favor. But in order to do this well need old teeth x 10,000. I dont think we can do it by ourselves. What can we do?'),
(10908, 'Really? Thanks a lot. Could you collect old teeth and deliver it to me?'),
(10909, 'Thank you. If you help Ill repay you.'),
(10910, 'I dont think we have enough teeth. What can we do?'),
(10911, 'Wow! You brought a lot! Thank you.'),
(10912, 'Oh, hello! This is our warrior!'),
(10913, 'Hey Mr. Warrior! Please do me a favor. | I have to make sure that our babies eat rice cake soup. But theres no meat in the soup so they arent eating it. | Could you bring me 10 Turkey from infront of the town?'),
(10914, 'You still dont have the meat? My babies are hungry. T.T'),
(10915, 'You brought the meat! Thank you!'),
(10916, 'Here, have a bowl of soup!'),
(10917, 'Its the new year! Why dont you go say happy new year to the elders at Moradon? Maybe theyll give you a reward for being so well mannered. | Oh yeah, and theyll like this rice cake soup.'),
(10918, 'You havent said the greeting yet?'),
(10919, 'You are our Hero! Have a happy new year!'),
(10920, 'Thank you. Take this!'),
(10921, 'I did not not take the rice cake soup!'),
(10922, 'Oh, you are our hero! Have a great new year!'),
(10923, 'Thank you. Take this!'),
(10924, 'Since you dont have the rice cake soup. I dont want to hear you greet me.'),
(10925, 'Oh, you are our hero! Have a great new year!'),
(10926, 'Thank you, Take this!'),
(10927, 'You dont even have the rice cake soup. I dont want to hear you greet me.'),
(10928, 'Hey, Mr. Warrior. Have you seen the gourd infront of the Moradon?'),
(10929, 'To welcome the new year, Gourds are blooming. If you throw the lucky pockets and break the gourds, youll get EXP and old box.'),
(10930, 'It happens every 8 hours. Hope you are interested!'),
(10931, 'You already broke the gourd! Congrats! Ill open the old box for you.'),
(10932, 'Mr. Warrior. Somethings happened!'),
(10933, 'In the island of Mora which is on the west side of the Moradon, a gold dragon has appeared!'),
(10934, 'This gold dragon cant be defeated by normal attack.'),
(10935, 'This dragon likes lucky pockets.'),
(10936, 'Yep. Throw the poisonous lucky pockets at the dragon.'),
(10937, 'Congrats! Lucks on your way for this year.')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(10938, 'Congrats! Youll have a great new year.'),
(10939, 'Careful! It looks your fortune isnt so great for this new year. Careful with Water.'),
(10940, 'Oh! Really bad fortune?Careful now.'),
(10941, 'In order to tell your fortune, there should be spaces in your bag.'),
(10942, 'Instead of me today, greet the other elder today.'),
(10943, 'Instead of me today, greet the other elder today.'),
(10944, 'Instead of me today, greet the other elder today.'),
(10945, 'Dragon has appeared at the Mora Island. Would you like to participate in the Dragon subjugation?'),
(10946, 'Dragon has appeared at the Mora Island. Would you like to participate in the Dragon subjugation?'),
(10947, 'I only accept one greeting per day. Come back tomorrow.'),
(10948, 'I only accept one greeting per day. Come back tomorrow.'),
(10949, 'I only accept one greeting per day. Come back tomorrow.'),
(10950, 'You dont have spaces in your bag.'),
(10951, 'You dont have spaces in your bag.'),
(10952, 'You dont have spaces in your bag.'),
(10953, 'Nation Transfer System|-  <font color=@#660066@>Only Karus users can do Nation Transfer temporary.</font> |- When transferring, all the characters within the account must withdraw from the clan |- When transferring, when you submit  the  [Exile Application Form] you can exchange it with a  [National Transfer Certificate]. Accumulation starts from this point of time.'),
(10954, 'Only Karus users can do Nation Transfer temporary.'),
(11000, 'Its supposed to be a full moon but this is really unfortunate.'),
(11001, 'You know how when theres full moon you are supposed to eat nuts to have good skin? Im so busy I cant get the nuts for our kids. Could you help me?'),
(11002, 'Just pick them on on the way to monster hunting. Give me 5 of the nuts.'),
(11003, 'Knight! Thank you. If you give me chestnuts Ill give you some rice cake.'),
(11004, 'I dont think you have all 5 nuts. Check it please.'),
(11005, 'Thank you!! You must be so tired but you remembered to bring all 5 nuts.'),
(11006, 'This is to show my appreciation.'),
(11007, 'Knight. I want to take this chance during Valentines day and propose. But Im so shy. Ill need Love spirits help.'),
(11008, 'Give this letter with the chocolate to the Love Spirit who lives in the South Meadow?'),
(11009, 'Jane wanted to give this to him? Whatever!! |Chocolate wont work.'),
(11010, 'Do I have to really say it to make you understand? Its a different world now. You really need the ring.'),
(11011, 'Why are you asking? Bring the pickaxe and start digging! You might be able to find a ring.'),
(11012, 'What you havent found a ring? Go dig more!'),
(11013, 'You didnt get his message yet?'),
(11014, 'Great! Ill be back soon.'),
(11015, 'Give this letter to Jane.'),
(11016, 'ah.. I see..  There was already someone.. | Thank you. This is to show my apprecation.'),
(11017, 'Theres Full moon celebration at Moradon.'),
(11018, 'But in order to participate youll need to bring some rice straws.'),
(11019, 'Start spinning top infront of the town youll be able to find some rice straws. Bring me 10 rice straws to participate for the event.'),
(11020, 'Use the bamboo to spin the tops.'),
(11021, 'You dont have all 10.'),
(11022, 'Just in time. Well need to burn the moon house so give me all the rice straws now.'),
(11023, 'Im giving you this fire since its tradition. Make sure you be careful.'),
(11024, 'Were trying to select Warmonger to celebrate the Full Moon.'),
(11025, 'Theres no requirement. Just that anyone who defeat enemy will be able to collect Warmonger Evidence and bring 10 of these to receive gifts.'),
(11026, 'Defeat the enemy to collect Warmonger Evidence. And youll need at least 10.'),
(11027, 'We recognize you as a Warmonger. The prize is dumblings. What is this?? Its food!'),
(11028, 'How to spin the top infront of the town? Its simple. Youll need the towns people though. Get the bamboo from the merchant and use it to spin the tops.'),
(11029, 'I dont think you know. If you cooperate theres hidden bride and grom transformation coupon. Bring those and Ill give you the scroll.'),
(11030, 'You havent found the bride and groom transformation coupon.'),
(11031, 'You broug the bride and groom transformation coupon! Come on, change into these clothes and go propose to the one you love.'),
(11032, 'South Meadow is where the middle ground between the Village of Fork and Moradon are. Its located at 520, 310.'),
(11033, 'You can make Love happen! If you want to deliver your love come to me. Jane must have something she wants from me.'),
(11034, 'Moon welcoming can only be watched once a day.'),
(11035, 'The warmonger evidence is collected once a day.'),
(11036, 'You have [Monster Staff] Wing Weapon Box. | You have this type of item. | Here you go.'),
(11037, 'You do not have [Monster Staff] Wing Weapon Box. | Check again.'),
(11038, 'Pick the desired Wing from the following rewards.'),
(11039, '? She was an angel come from heaven ~ ~ very cute ~ her I loved ... whoops! Since when were you there?'),
(11040, 'My body is cold?ungry..also my sides are cold?opefully she accept my confession this time..??'),
(11041, 'I want to confess but I have no clothes. T.T hey there! Help me get some good clothes so I can confess my love. | I want to have some wedding clothes. I heard that if you spin the top infront of the town you can get the coupon to exchange for clothes?'),
(11042, 'Since Im naked do I look funny to you? | you dont have the clothes yet?'),
(11043, 'That!!!  Thats the exchange coupon for clothes!!! If I confess my love Im sure shell say yes 100%. Thank you so much! Here you must be hungry. Take this and eat it.'),
(11044, 'Dont you want to see these special items from the Eastern countries?'),
(11045, 'I found something.. But I dont need it. Arent you curious? You want it? Hey now. I cant just give it to you.'),
(11046, 'Hm.. Lets see..  If you have useful leather x 100 or ;Warmonger Evidence x 10.'),
(11047, 'Nothings free, right? | If you defeat enemy youll get the warmonger evidence and useful leather can be obtained by getting rid of your level or higher leveled monsters.'),
(11048, 'You know how to deal! Here you are~'),
(11049, 'You dont have spaces in your bag.'),
(11050, 'Hello! This is [VIP Specialist] Julian. Thank you for your interest in the Level Jumping Event. Please check out the below Event information.'),
(11051, 'Level Jumping Event|When you reach Lv 50 -59, you will become Lv 73 or Lv 75 (for Premium User). Respective weapons/armors will be distributed.(1st Job)|When you reach Lv 60 ? 64, you will become Lv 74 or Lv 76 (for Premium User). Respective weapons/armors will be distributed. (2nd Job)|When you reach Lv 65 -74, you will become Lv 75 and respective weapons/armors will be distributed (2nd jobWhen you reach Lv 65 ? 74 (with the premium), you will become Lv 77 and respective weapons and armors will be distributed (2nd job|? You must reach the required level to participate in the Level Jumping Event.'),
(11052, 'Would you like to participate in the Level Jumping Event?'),
(11053, 'Your level does not qualify to participate in the Level Jumping Event.'),
(11054, '22 Inventory Slots would be needed for Level Jumping Event. Please check your inventory space.'),
(11055, 'Your level is between the levels of 50 and 59. You will become Lv 73 and Lv 75 (with the premium)'),
(11056, 'Your level is between the levels of 60 and 64. You will become Lv 74 and Lv 76 (with the premium)'),
(11057, 'Your level is between the levels of 65 and 74 (Premium not used). Your new level will be Lv 75.'),
(11058, 'Your level is between the levels of 65 nd 76 (Premium used). Your new level will be Lv 77.'),
(11059, 'Premium isnt being used. |Premium usage will result in +2 Levels when participating in the Level Jumping Event.'),
(11060, 'You have level-jumped already by participating in the Level Jumping Event.'),
(11061, 'You do not have [Under the Castle Weapon Box]. | Check again, please.'),
(11062, 'You have the [Under the Castle Weapon Box]. | You have received this item. | Here you go.'),
(11063, 'You do not have the certificate for this item.'),
(11064, 'You are not qualified to participate in the Level Jump Event'),
(11065, 'You do not have the certificate for this item.'),
(11100, 'sobbing?   my bag?  How can I lose it there? How am I going to get to school? T.T'),
(11101, 'I lost my school supplies at the fishing area. T.T Please find it for me. 5 pencils, 1 eraser, 1 pencil box are missing. You can bring more to me.'),
(11102, 'You havent found the supplies yet? You arent even a child and youre so slow. Come on. Get me 5 pencils, 1 eraser, 1 pencil box.'),
(11103, 'Yeah! Those are mine! Thank you!'),
(11104, 'I lost my bag.. I want to have a new one. Could you get it for me from [Suspicious Eastern Merchant]? And talk to me again to get another quest.'),
(11105, 'I have enough school suppolies now. Im gonna go fishing again?:)'),
(11106, 'sigh?  sobbing?T.T  my bag?   you dont have my bag yet?'),
(11107, 'Yeah!! Thats my bag. Thank you! You are the best, <selfname>!'),
(11108, 'What? You need a bag?'),
(11109, 'I cant just give it to you. | Give me at least 5 useful leather.'),
(11110, 'Bag cant just be made from nothing.'),
(11111, 'oh you! You have some useful leather. | Give me 5 then Ill make you a bag.'),
(11112, 'I have made the bag. Here, make a good use of it.'),
(11113, 'Hey you have no space in your bag.'),
(11114, 'Are you kidding?You dont have enough Warmongers Evidence.'),
(11115, 'Are you kidding? You dont have enough useful leather.'),
(11116, 'Oh! You have the item! Will you give me the warmonger evidence or useful leather?'),
(11117, 'Theres no space in your bag.'),
(11118, 'Thank you for the school supplies. But I dont have a bag. What am I gonna do? T.T'),
(11119, 'You are the best, <selfname>. Bag can be purchased from Suspicious Eastern Merchant.'),
(11120, 'Ill give you <selfname> since I dont need this. It£r the old box. Heard that you can get random item.'),
(11121, 'You have something for me? I can only make one bag a day. | ah! You! Go visit the daydreaming girl. | She lost her bag.'),
(11122, 'Dont lose anymore stuff for today.'),
(11123, 'Did you get to see the sprout on the street? Its spring already. Go out and feel the spring air!'),
(11124, 'Please make 2 spaces in your bag.'),
(11130, 'What do you want?'),
(11131, 'Please choose what you want'),
(11132, 'I hope a good time'),
(11200, 'Veda is looking for you, master. But who is Veda??'),
(11201, 'Welcome to Islante. I appreciate your interest in our corner of the world. My name is Veda, I train in aesthetic practices here in Islante.'),
(11202, 'I called for you because with your reputation and ability, Islante is the perfect place for you to improve your skills. Youll understand if you start hunting Doom Soldiers.'),
(11203, 'Good job. Are you satisfied with that?'),
(11204, 'Master, Veda is going to start you on the second training. Go and see him~'),
(11205, 'Are you ready for the second round of training?'),
(11206, 'The second training target is our friend, the Brahman. Brahman are in a completely different class to the Esoteric Buddhist Monks. His nonstop attacks wont give you any breathing time. Its a tougher opponent than perhaps what youre used to, but for training, this can only be a good thing. What do you think?'),
(11207, 'The road of practice must be walked with patience.'),
(11208, 'Well done. Was it a hard hunt? But I can see the results of your training already. Well done. Heh.'),
(11209, 'We meet again. How goes the training?'),
(11210, 'I saw some Harpy type Monsters - Crimson Wings I think theyre called - a few days ago while I was training. Big wings, Sharp claws... its said that hundreds of people have died from their poisons in even little scratches. But, for you, theyd make for great training.'),
(11211, 'Well done. Was it a hard hunt? But I can see the results of your training already. Well done. Heh.'),
(11212, 'Master, Theres a monster with a devils shape! Ill bet Veda knows about it.'),
(11213, 'The devil-shaped monster is actually a Gargoyle.'),
(11214, 'Its a stony monster with the devils visage that owes its life to an ancient spell. After the war against Pathos, the seals were permanently removed and its been stuck here threatening humans ever since. I think itd be good to ¡—rain on these beasts next. Heh.'),
(11215, 'Well done. Was it a hard hunt? But I can see the results of your training already. Well done. Heh.'),
(11216, 'You want to keep training? You look strong enough already... How much stronger do you want to be?? Heh.'),
(11217, 'Right then, I think its time you met the Apostle of Piercing Cold. You should be able to dispatch him easily enough. Just watch out for that meddling monks Glacier Spell of Darkness. It can freeze your bones solid.'),
(11218, 'Master, Are you ready for more training?'),
(11219, 'Hmm... Did you have anything in particular in mind?'),
(11220, 'What? What are you going to do with that worm? Itll just decrease your ability. Ha Ha! This time, lets make the Apostle of Flames the target of the training. His Flame Spell of Darkness attack cannot be explained in words. So please, be careful. And wear asbestos underwear for this one!.'),
(11221, 'Master, what about hunting in Islante?'),
(11222, 'Welcome! Its been quite a while since I saw you here. Did you come here to loosen up? Haha~'),
(11223, 'Troll Berserker! Its one of the targets which many hunters and questers want to hunt. Do you accept the challenge? The quest target is 250...'),
(11224, 'Whooa...! Its not just not to loosen up!'),
(11225, 'Are you looking for another quest? I like this attitude of ceaseless effort! Find the Troll Captain.'),
(11226, 'Master, Its said that something strange is going on in Islante. Please go to [Ascetic] Veda and ask.'),
(11227, 'Nights here in Islante are getting more and more fearful. Citizens here are suffering from a monster in their dreams every night...'),
(11228, 'Given the shape of the monster, I suspect its a Buro, a monster living in the northeastern part of the forest. Theyre said to be capable of real magic, but who knows? If theyre the real cause of the nightmares, they should be removed...'),
(11229, 'Master, its said that theres a monster whos gone berserk in Islante. Please ask [Ascetic] Veda for details.'),
(11230, 'Hm~they were no more than rocks. The ancient Priest gave life to them, and employed them as servants. Theyre Stone Golems. After the war against Pathos, the Priests lost control of them, and they staged an attack against anything living.'),
(11231, 'Well, the carelessness of the ancient Priests may have caused the current problem, but everybody makes mistakes. But the power of Dark Stones is the strongest, and theyre ruthless. The outcome of one mistake seems too severe...'),
(11232, 'Fallen Spirit of Flame...  They seem like huge burning men with manes and whips of flames with many leather strings... If you see how horrible they look once, youll never want to see them again.'),
(11233, 'Its called Balog. Theyre already notorious in this region. You may be the one who can get rid of them. Dont you think so?'),
(11234, 'Veda is looking for you, master. But who is Veda??'),
(11235, 'Welcome to Islante. I appreciate your interest in our corner of the world. My name is Veda, I train in aesthetic practices here in Islante.'),
(11236, 'I called for you because with your reputation and ability, Islante is the perfect place for you to improve your skills. Youll understand if you start hunting Doom Soldiers.'),
(11237, 'Good job. Are you satisfied with that?'),
