(11264, 'Given the shape of the monster, I suspect its a Buro, a monster living in the northeastern part of the forest. Theyre said to be capable of real magic, but who knows? If theyre the real cause of the nightmares, they should be removed...'),
(11265, 'Master, its said that theres a monster whos gone berserk in Islante. Please ask [Ascetic] Veda for details.'),
(11266, 'Hm~they were no more than rocks. The ancient Priest gave life to them, and employed them as servants. Theyre Stone Golems. After the war against Pathos, the Priests lost control of them, and they staged an attack against anything living.'),
(11267, 'Well, the carelessness of the ancient Priests may have caused the current problem, but everybody makes mistakes. But the power of Dark Stones is the strongest, and theyre ruthless. The outcome of one mistake seems too severe...'),
(11268, 'Fallen Spirit of Flame...  They seem like huge burning men with manes and whips of flames with many leather strings... If you see how horrible they look once, youll never want to see them again.'),
(11269, 'Its called Balog. Theyre already notorious in this region. You may be the one who can get rid of them. Dont you think so?'),
(11336, 'You are the citizen who defeated [Ronark Monument]! Do you want to cross this river?'),
(11337, 'You have not defeated [Ronark Monument]. If you pay me 1M noah, I will let you cross this river.'),
(11338, 'You don£s have 1M noah? Bring it to cross this river.'),
(11339, 'Welcome. Did you get to see the Knight Captain outside of the town? They used to be our soldiers. After they died, they were resurrected by lich.'),
(11340, 'I hope they rest now. Could you help? Help at least 20 of them.'),
(11341, 'Dont you pity their souls?'),
(11342, 'Thank you. Because of you they can rest now.'),
(11343, 'Oh Im so glad to see you! Do you remember how you defeated the Knight captain the last time?'),
(11344, 'There are still many wandering souls. Can we use your skills once again?'),
(11345, '(Look at the eyes..  Theres so much dark circle?'),
(11346, 'Harpies are making noises so I cant sleep. Can you get rid of them?'),
(11347, 'Youre still not done? I cant sleep a good night sleep at night.'),
(11348, 'Now thanks to you. I can sleep.'),
(11349, 'Ah Im so sleepy.  Hey there! You are!!'),
(11350, 'You really dont know? Those harpies are making weird noises! Please take care of them.'),
(11351, 'Welcome. Heard that apostles are hosting a conference.'),
(11352, 'I think they are trying to call out the evil. Please go take care of them.'),
(11353, 'We dont have time.'),
(11354, 'Thanks to you. I feel so much better.'),
(11355, 'Welcome. The reason I called you is to tell you that the apostles are gathering around.'),
(11356, 'Well.. Im not sure why.. But lets catch them first.')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(11357, 'What are we going to do with trolls?'),
(11358, 'Trolls are setting something up. They are gathering around here.  I think they might be coming to invade us. Could you defeat them?'),
(11359, 'Did you find out the reason trolls are gathering around?'),
(11360, 'No!!!  That cant be?!!'),
(11361, 'Trolls have invaded the North town. Theres no survivor. Could you take revenge?'),
(11362, 'Did you take revenge?'),
(11363, 'You have done well here..  Thank you.'),
(11364, 'So many have died because of the trolls. So we organized punitive expedition.'),
(11365, 'Well takd down Harp Troll Berserker. Could you defeat 40 of them for now?'),
(11366, 'Is Harp Troll Berserker strong?'),
(11367, 'You are so awesome!'),
(11368, 'Our punitive force has been sieged by the berserkers.'),
(11369, 'Could you go help them?'),
(11370, 'Their lives at stake.'),
(11371, 'The boss has been finally appeared. Troll Captain is the one. Heard they are powerful'),
(11372, 'Yes! You have the talent.'),
(11373, 'do you have an understanding of their power now?'),
(11374, 'They werent so much different from Harp Troll Berserkers. Good job.'),
(11375, 'You know how troll captain is also a threatening being to us?'),
(11376, 'We have to prevent the danger. Please kill 40 of them.'),
(11377, 'You are still now done getting rid of them?'),
(11378, 'These days, the residents of Eslant cant go outside.'),
(11379, 'Because of Iron Claw  At night they come out to find prey.'),
(11380, 'Not yet..Not enough.'),
(11381, 'Iron Claw are still out. Could you get rid of them?'),
(11382, 'Theres no sign that the storm will be gone.'),
(11383, 'Its because of the storm apostles. Can you take care of them?'),
(11384, 'From the past week, its happening again.'),
(11385, 'Yeah. Could you take care of them?'),
(11386, 'So many are afraid these days.'),
(11387, 'A few days ago, they say that armors with no bodies were killing townspeople. Can you find out whats really happening? If its the monster, please get rid of them.'),
(11388, 'You found out of their identity?!'),
(11389, 'Doom knight? Whats happening in Eslant?'),
(11390, 'You know those doom knights you defeated? They are the armors of our soldiers.'),
(11391, 'I think thats it..  Please make sure that our soldiers armors dont do that again.'),
(11392, 'Do you know of the Order of Destruction?'),
(11393, 'You can kill the enemy instantly. Death Wizard is using that magic. Ill give you the immune so that you can go get rid of them.'),
(11394, 'Thank you for the last time.'),
(11395, 'No..  Its beacause youve done the deed. Could you get rid of the death wizards one more time?'),
(11396, 'Horse holding a pickaxe? Thats a funny monster..'),
(11397, 'Horse with pickaxes are threatening the townspeople. Cant you help?'),
(11398, 'I knew youd be the person.'),
(11399, 'Welcome. I hear that our soldiers are eating horse meat because of you.'),
(11400, 'Since those monsters can be a good food supply to use. Can you take care of them again?'),
(11401, 'Thank you. Eslant is getting full because of you now.'),
(11402, 'Because of us getting rid of trolls, magicians are mad and they are coming out.'),
(11403, 'Harp Troll Magicians are pretty powerful. Careful.'),
(11404, 'Welcome. Those harp troll magicians are gathering around now.'),
(11405, 'I think they are trying to call out the trolls evil god. Can you get rid of them and seal the magic?'),
(11406, 'Have you seen the human with wings from the South West?'),
(11407, 'They are the monsters who are with the evil. We call them Raven Harpie.They had bad characters and are just killing anyone they see. Can you go get rid of them?'),
(11408, 'Raven Harpies are invading the South west towns.'),
(11409, 'You have to help once again.'),
(11410, 'Chief of Raven Harpies are invading South west towns now.'),
(11411, 'Thank you! The name of the chief is Falcon. Please defeat him.'),
(11412, 'Thank you for what you did the last time.'),
(11413, 'However, those in retreat might come back to invade again. Can you get rid of the rest of the falcons?'),
(11414, 'Have you seen the necklace the chief was wearing?'),
(11415, 'Can you get at least 10 necklaces?'),
(11416, 'Thats the valuable necklace.'),
(11417, 'Can you sleep well these days?'),
(11418, 'What are you talking about? Harpies are crying outloud at night. Defeat them and bring me 10 harpies feathers.'),
(11419, 'If you want to earn experience bring me feathers.'),
(11420, 'Because of you I can sleep now.'),
(11421, 'Have you see the apostles?'),
(11422, 'They are carrying around the skull statue. Bring me 20 of that.'),
(11423, 'You do not have enough.'),
(11424, 'Thank you. Now Ill make a good use of them.'),
(11425, 'I heard that the trolls bones are good for disc.'),
(11426, 'Yep. Well boil that and drink the soup. Could you bring 20 bones?'),
(11427, 'Come on! Bring trolls bones.'),
(11428, 'Thank you. Because of you itll help on fixing the disc.'),
(11429, 'Did you know? Gargoyles skin is harder than the rocks.'),
(11430, 'Well need to study their skin and maybe we can improve our armors. Bring me 20 gargoyles wings.'),
(11431, 'If you bring the Gargoyle wings well be able to make improved armors.'),
(11432, 'Thank you.'),
(11433, 'Have you seen the storm apostle?'),
(11434, 'The reason that they can call out the storm is due to their magical staff. Bring me 20 Apostles Staff.'),
(11435, 'Hurry! Bring them to me.'),
(11436, 'hahahaha I can not improve my magic.'),
(11437, 'Have you seen the doom knight?'),
(11438, 'Without the soul their armors are just wandering around. I want to know why so could you bring me 20 armor pieces?'),
(11439, 'Hm.. Not yet?'),
(11440, 'I need to study more. Its amazing.'),
(11441, 'Ive figured it out! There is the soul on the armor but we just cant see it!'),
(11442, 'Could you now bring me Resentment Soul Its hard to find but if you keep defeating doom Knight youll be able to obtain them.'),
(11443, 'oh!! You got it!!!!  You are the best.'),
(11444, 'Do you know?'),
(11445, 'Heard that jewels are embeded on the Satiros horses hoofs? Could you bring 20 hoofs?'),
(11446, 'So shiny. Ill give you the reward later.'),
(11447, 'Help me!!!  I cant sleep because of those harpies.'),
