(22072, 'The second nightmare sinners are called the [Nightmare]. They are the worst of their kind. They appear in peoples dream riding a horse and guide them to the deep end of nightmare. Be careful and good luck!'),
(22073, '[The endless desire of the sinners that devour dreams...] What the?You didntleave yet?'),
(22074, 'Oh no, you completed eliminated them.'),
(22075, 'Thank you. All existing [Nightmare Sinners] all paid for their sins. However, another [Nightmare sinners] may appear once again. If such day comes, I hope you could help us again.'),
(22076, '[Chief Researcher] Gaz is in Islant. Hes doing a research on magic at the [Magic Soceity].'),
(22077, 'What do you want? Unless its urgent, leave me alone.'),
(22078, 'The leader? I see. Let me explain to you. There have been some strange movements of magical creatures in Islant. And Im here to invetigate by collecting specimen and conducting a research.g specimen.'),
(22079, 'By specimen, I mean magical creatures in whose body [Mana Piece] is already finished crystalizing. And I collect and analyze them. <selfname>, it would mean a great deal if you could collect [Mana Piece] and bring them back to me.'),
(22080, 'If you have decided to help me, please first bring me the apparatus. I need a catalyst called [Potion of Soul] and [Magicians Stone] to test its reaction to pure magic. You can get them from [Potion Merchant] and [Store] respectively. Please hurry.'),
