(22270, 'Its been a while, <selfname>. I thought you had no more business here. Hmm...[Magic Power Transmission/Diffusion Marble]? I have a pile of them here. I guess I could just give you one for old times sake. But you must keep this secret from Rage.'),
(22271, 'So you want me to make [Delicately Crafted Seal Ring]? Let see?ou got [Plain Old Ring], [Magic Power Transmission/Diffusion Marble]...Guess you got all the materials.  But its going to cost you [200,000 Noahs]. Do you still want it?'),
