(23311, 'This isnt normal..  Its very serious.'),
(23312, 'Something was leaking and was contaminating..'),
(23313, 'For now, bring this [Cracking Experiement Report] to [Associate of Magic Advisor] Marcus. And following his order, youll need to take care of something. Hurry!'),
(23314, 'Oh no! Master! It was worse than what we had imagined. Lets go meet Harrigon at [Ronarkland].'),
(23315, 'Hello~ Youre back! You seem tired.'),
(23316, '[Cracking Experiment Report]? That was the issue. But a crack?  Something must have had happened.'),
(23317, 'So where is it?'),
(23318, 'Hm?I see.. Thats why.'),
(23319, 'The answer is to get rid of the main culprit. Im asking you to do this, <selfname>. Destroy [Crack] and its main culprit. And come back.'),
(23320, 'Oh no! Master! It was worse than what we had imagined. Lets go meet Marcus at [Ronarkland].'),
(23321, 'Hello~ Youre back! You seem tired.'),
(23322, '[Cracking Experiment Report]? That was the issue. But a crack?  Something must have had happened.'),
(23323, 'So where is it?'),
(23324, 'Hm?I see.. Thats why.'),
(23325, 'The answer is to get rid of the main culprit. Im asking you to do this, <selfname>. Destroy [Crack] and its main culprit. And come back.'),
(23326, 'Huff Huff ... This must be the final battle. But we dont even know whom we need to fight! Im kinda scared. Lets visit Harrigon.'),
(23327, 'ah you are here. Were at the final stage.'),
(23328, 'The answer is to get rid of the main culprit. Im asking you to do this, <selfname>. Destroy [Crack] and its main culprit. And come back.'),
(23329, 'You havent destroyed the main culprit?'),
(23330, 'Oh you are done! [Krowaz Shadow].. Finally Krowaz has been awaken.'),
(23331, 'Good job. But now youll need to defeat Krowaz. Well do our best as well.'),
(23332, 'Huff Huff ... This must be the final battle. But we dont even know whom we need to fight! Im kinda scared. Lets visit Marcus.'),
(23333, 'ah you are here. Were at the final stage.'),
(23334, 'The answer is to get rid of the main culprit. Im asking you to do this, <selfname>. Destroy [Crack] and its main culprit. And come back.'),
(23335, 'You havent destroyed the main culprit?'),
(23336, 'Oh you are done! [Krowaz Shadow].. Finally Krowaz has been awaken.'),
(23337, 'Good job. But now youll need to defeat Krowaz. Well do our best as well.'),
(23338, 'ah.. You lost it? Ill give it to you again, so dont lose it.'),
(23339, 'What happened?'),
(23340, 'ah.. You lost it? Ill give it to you again, so dont lose it.'),
(23341, 'What happened?'),
(23342, 'You lost it..  Thats too bad. Ill give it to you again.'),
(23343, 'Welcome, What made you come here?'),
(23344, 'You lost it..  Thats too bad. Ill give it to you again.'),
(23345, 'Welcome, What made you come here?'),
(23346, 'Did you finish what you came for? Will you exit?'),
(23347, 'Im busy so stop bothering me.'),
(23348, 'Youll need to be level 55 to receive the next mission. Go find [Magic Researcher] Norker.'),
