(40632, 'Im knitting a special hat for the Winter Holiday. Red Chicken Feather would look good on this hat. Could you pleae collect 5 feathers for me?'),
(40633, 'You can prove your honor by contributing 10,000 Nation Points or 300,000,000 Noah. How do you want to prove your honor?'),
(40634, 'You dont have enough Noah. If you want to prove your honor, you need to contribute 300,000,000 Noah'),
(40635, 'Please bring me 10,000 Nation Points or 300,000,000 Noah'),
(40636, 'I remember you. You already got your Qualification of Rebirth!'),
