INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(43661, 'Oh no! Ill give it to you again.'),
(43662, 'Welcome. You want to earn my trust? Come back after clearing the next quest. |1. Worm Hunt|2. Bandicoot Hunt| 3. Kecoon Hunt |4. Bulcan Hunt |5. Wild Bulcan Hunt'),
(43663, 'You want to earn my trust? Then the quests I give you need to be cleared.'),
(43664, 'Its been too hard to come here crossing the continent. But did you see it too? Theres a guy named Jed whos so handsome!'),
(43665, 'I sell unique items from all over the world~ Would you like to take a look? |Oh, dont tell nobody I merchant here.'),
(43666, 'Black Pirates?Smugglers?Attacking Moradon?! What! Its a letter about Black Pirates stealing goods?Theres no details though.'),
(43667, 'Yes! That sounds good. Since Im busy to defeating these monsters, could you take care of this? Get the smugglers and investigate!|Those smugglers should be around Folk Village somewhere.'),
(43668, 'After decoding the secret ledger, it seems smugglers are trying to steal goods from Moradon for Pirates. Could you interrogate the pirates, please?'),
(43669, 'You havent found the smugglers? They should be around Folk Village.'),
(43670, 'Smugglers were indeed communicating with Black Pirates?'),
(43671, 'Try this~ Its a medicine to cure everything~ Would you like to buy one?'),
(43672, 'Wow! How did you?!'),
(43673, 'Im well prepared to deal with a situation like this. Guys! Come out!'),
(43674, 'Please <selfname>. Please save me this once. Ive gotten the order from the Black Pirate Captain. |Oh and I just remembered. Jed was looking for you.'),
(43675, 'Please give my regards to Jed.'),
(43676, 'Pirates are making suspicious movements? Interrogate the smugglers and find out more about the pirates.'),
(43677, 'Are you sure?! Pirates have invaded Moradon! We have no time!'),
(43678, 'Pirates have appeared at Mora Island.|Its very suspicious.|Its also dangerous, but Ill take you there if you want.'),
(43679, 'Pirates have appeared at Mora Island.|Its very suspicious.|Its also dangerous, but Ill take you there if you want.'),
(43680, 'Yes, <selfname>, what I told you is everything. Please believe me?T.T'),
(43681, '<selfname> What made you come here? Heh~ Heh~'),
(43682, 'Pirates? Hm?I havent heard anything like that.'),
(43683, 'Oh~ <selfname>. Please stop..  I get it. Ill tell you everything I know.'),
(43684, 'Mighty Warrior! Ill be a good person now.|Oh, would you like to take this new medicine that just came in?'),
(43685, 'No~~  Have a safe trip back!'),
(43686, 'There isnt a day I can rest! As you know, pirates are trying to invade Moradon. We need to do something about it.'),
(43687, 'Since we dont have enough food to get to Mora Island, we will need Apples of Moradon, and  Hm..  I think the scorpions have a habit of collecting Apples of Moradon?'),
(43688, '<selfname>, Jed is looking for you.'),
(43689, '<selfname>, Jed is looking for you.'),
(43690, 'Something seems not right. Please go get more info from the smugglers.'),
(43691, 'Oh!!! Because of you <selfname> we can do this before they attack Moradon. This is a reward to show you my appreciation.'),
(43692, 'We are running out of time. Please get Apple of Moradon. Apple of Moradon can be obtained from wolves and scorpions.'),
(43693, 'We are ready now. Please go to Mora Island and defeat the Pirates. For now, get about 20 pirates.|Oh, Mora Island is located in the south of Moradon. Go to Quayside to find Laidas or Portman.'),
(43694, 'There are still many pirates left. Please get them all.|Mora Island is on the south side of Moradon. Go to Quayside to find Laidas or Portman.'),
(43695, 'Oh! If it wasnt for you <selfname> Moradon could have been?    Thank you so very much. Here, this is the reward.'),
(43696, 'Welcome back. When you were defeating the pirates, you should have been able to see their weapons. They use Apples of Moradon to strengthen them. Steal their Apples of Moradon.|Mora Island is located on the south side of Moradon. Go to Quayside to find Laidas or Portman.'),
(43697, 'You didnt get the apples? You dont care if Moradon gets invaded? |Mora Island is located in the south of Moradon. Go to Quayside to find Laidas and Portman.'),
(43698, 'You are great! Because of you, all the townsmen can sleep without any worries now.'),
(43699, 'Hmm.. According to the Smugglers testimony, the Pirates captain has that weird potion. Once you drink it you gain tremendous power?Can you get me that potion from the captain next time you see him?'),
(43700, 'You didnt get it yet?| Mora Island is located in the south from Moradon. Go to Quayside to find Laidas or Portman.'),
(43701, 'Oh! This is a leap. What? Eat a pirate ship this chapter, these three forces, yet eventually rupture the body dead? | Hmm .. Know the leap ... youll have to investigate a little more, and I know this area well.'),
(43702, 'You know about a person who is called Sharine? Shes a wanderer of potion researcher, I asked her to search about a mysterious elixir but havent seen her since then.. Can you first find an evidence for her disappearance? You probably get an evidence if you open the Suspicious Box on the side street.'),
(43703, 'Hmm..Indeed..Cant find that easily'),
(43704, 'Finally we might find him soon, but then.. How come Amelie possessed the last piece?'),
(43705, 'Welcome in! Since Portu and Human have united together, many of them heve been immigrating to Moradon recently. With those monsters moving in there have been so many issues. Can you help?'),
(43706, 'First of all, kill 10 each of Battalion, Rotten Eyes,Wild Smilodon, and Direwolf.'),
(43707, 'There are still many monsters left.'),
(43708, 'Thanks! Many refugees can now travel comfortably because of you!'),
(43709, 'Ohh! Did you see?'),
(43710, 'A gorgeous woman among those refugees~'),
(43711, 'What?! You must be blind! How can you miss that beauty?'),
(43712, 'Hmm ..Hmm, hmm. So, I have a favor to ask of you ...'),
(43713, 'I want to confess my love to her, and having a gift would be a plus. Can you go find me something good for a gift? Im begging you. Since Im a leader of security guards, I cant go outside of Folk Village?'),
(43714, 'You didnt find one yet? Well its not easy to decide whats good for a gift.. I once heard that the king of fruits are Apples of Moradon.. I wish I could get one?'),
(43715, 'Ohh! This is an Apple of Moradon!? I really appreciate it. Just in time to eat.'),
(43716, 'Oh~ Welcome <selfname>. If you have time, do you want to get a proposal ring from Jewel for me? I will pay you.'),
(43717, 'The ring is not ready yet? My heart is racing. I cant wait to give her this ring!!(Jeds face turns red.) She will be in my arms~ah~!'),
(43718, 'Ah~ Who in the worlds going to refuse this ring? This is really beautiful! Even to guys like me!!'),
(43719, '(Jed is looking nervously)<selfname>..oh What should I do?'),
(43720, '(Holding the ring) I gotta give this to her, but I cant even move one step forward..| Perhaps if <selfname> can deliver this to her? Please! Im begging you!!'),
(43721, 'Did you go yet? Please hurry!'),
(43722, 'Oh! Thank you <selfname>. I really appreciate it.'),
(43723, '<selfname> Long time no see..(Jed is pale) Im having trouble sleeping?any reply from her yet?...Perhaps <selfname> can go and ask her?'),
(43724, 'Oh ... Amelie ...'),
(43725, 'Are you serious? She..me? Oh! Thank God! (Jed reads letter) (Jed is smiling) <selfname> really. I truly thank you.'),
(43726, 'Long time no see <selfname>. Did you hear that people of Folk village are vanishing? I havent find any clues on their whereabouts, but only people who went to the graveyard are gone..<selfname>, can you search for more evidence?'),
(43727, 'Any clue yet? We need more clues.'),
(43728, 'Oh my!... Clothing from missing people..And..This ring..what???'),
(43729, 'Hmm.. Although shes my love? cannot overlook this. <selfname> can you ask Amelie about the ring found at the graveyard?'),
(43730, 'I cant believe it. Just lost it there?'),
(43731, 'Ha?Good. She just lost it there.'),
(43732, 'I cant just sit and watch. So many people gone missing. <selfname>, you want to join me for a stakeout at the graveyard tonight? I want to find these missing people no matter what.'),
(43733, 'Find anything yet?'),
(43734, 'Amelie..How?Shocked silence)'),
(43735, '<selfname>?How could this be? She became a monster..| Please do me this favor.| <selfname> can you keep this ring with you? When you see her someday I want you to give this to her. I need to protect this village.'),
(43736, '(Jed has a serious look. Not a word spoken.)'),
(43737, 'did you come <selfname>?'),
(43738, 'Never thought she was such a monster .... He blood formed this stone could be an evidence in some way?'),
(43739, 'By the way, why she had the last chapter of the Sharines journal? Everything is riddled with doubt. First of all can you ask Sharine about this stone? Sharine seems to know something..'),
(43740, 'Have you met Sharine? The journal tells she might be at Teil village..'),
(43741, 'Amelies Spiritual Stone? Amelie got contaminated with a Spiritual Stone and that made her a monster?f purifying her contaminated body..Thank you. Im glad to see her at least..Thank you.'),
(43742, '<Sharine> O what this? Where did you get this stone?'),
(43743, 'What the..She finally?'),
(43744, 'I heard that she was kidnapped by Draki and was used for his experiment. The experiment to strengthen the Spiritual Stone?She was the only survivor who escaped from there.'),
(43745, 'She oneday came to me and ask for a cure but I didnt have any at the time.. She was left like that and I realized of my incapacity. I started to travel around the world studying more about the Spiritual Stone..'),
(43746, '<Drakis Heart> I believe you know this as well, there was species called Draki in this continent before our kind. Very strong tribe but with Gods anger, their kind almost disappeared or few survivors hid themselves somewhere deep and secret. On their chest there was a Spiritual Stone which creates a great power which was their primary energy source..'),
(43747, 'Based on my research, the pieces of Spiritual Stone are found at different places in the world. And people who are contaminated with, makes them struggle, and..become a monster.'),
(43748, 'It is not accurate yet! But, my research can be more improved. It seems to be possible from my perspective. I gotta observe more.'),
(43749, 'Arent you curious of ability of the stone? Here I will show you.'),
(43750, 'Can you get me Amelies blood sample? If you bring it to me, I will show you something cool.'),
(43751, 'You havent got Amelies blood sample yet?'),
(43752, 'Good Job youve got it. Lets see. Keke'),
(43753, 'Here. This is the Spiritual Stone and blood sample you brought. Feed this to that worm over there. Something incredible will happen Haha. Oh, make sure you put an armor on yourself just in case.'),
(43754, 'Havent feed it yet? Go head come on~Haha'),
(43755, 'Hows it? Unbelievable huh? Thats an ability of Spiritual Stone. Make even a puny thing into a monster?ope the stone doesnt spread out no more?'),
(43756, 'See what I mean? The power of Spiritual Stone ... I stay here and do more research. Oh yes. I have a favor, do you know anything about Pole of Purificaion?'),
(43757, 'Yes. It is a Pole which Spirit of Water possessed in the past. If we have it, we could probably heal the contaminated people. If you ever find it, can you please bring it to me?'),
(43758, 'Thanks! This is my written letter to Great Elder in the castle. If you take it, you will get more information about the Spiritual Stone'),
(43759, 'Go ahead. I have more researches.'),
(43760, 'Deliver Sharines letter to Great Elder.'),
(43761, 'Oh! Is it the Apple of Moradon? How beautiful it is!!'),
(43762, 'Of course! Heh heh, but nothing comes for free!  If you give me the Apple of Moradon and only 100,000 Noah Ill make a ring for her.'),
(43763, 'Good Choice! Here~ I wish you success and much love.'),
(43764, 'You dont have enough Noah...'),
(43765, 'You dont have enough Apples of Moradon?'),
(43766, 'You dont have enough Apples of Moradon?'),
(43767, 'It seems you dont find any evidence in the box. Where can the last page be at?'),
(43768, 'Now I can live happily with Jed. Im happy :D'),
(43769, 'Oh. What is this?'),
(43770, '(The ring sparkles radiantly when she opens the box) Wow?his is so beautiful?From Jed?'),
(43771, 'Oh?hank you?ut I need a man with courage. Tell him to bring this to me himself.'),
(43772, 'Excuse me. Miss Amelie ... (clears throat)'),
(43773, '(Amelies cheek turns in red) Oh. Jed!|Thank you for saving me from the monsters last time.'),
(43774, 'It was nothing. Well, I will be thankful if you accept this ring.'),
(43775, 'Why do I need to accept this ring?|(Amelie being haughty)'),
(43776, 'B?ecause. To get rid of those monsters?(Jed is bewildered)'),
(43777, 'I? lo..ve you! Since the first time I saw you.'),
(43778, 'Wh..what..(Amelie being shy)|I will accept the ring?ut first I will think about it.'),
(43779, 'Dont you need to go to Jed? *^^*'),
(43780, 'Oh. Welcome <selfname>. Jed is troubled? Haha Hes waited long enough. Here. This is my response. Can you deliver it please?'),
(43781, 'Please hurry?^?^*'),
(43782, '(Amelie appears unhealthy) Thank you for finding my ring..'),
(43783, 'What brings you here today <selfname>?'),
(43784, 'Whats the matter ^^? I will answer you to the best of my ability.'),
(43785, '(Embarrassed) R.Right. I lost it the other day, Where did you find it?'),
(43786, '!!!!! |I? probably lost it when I went there to visit my fathers grave. Thank God you found this for me..I was really sad about this.'),
(43787, '(Amelie looks suspicious?hat will do it for today)'),
(43788, 'Kyaaaak!!Kyak! Kak! (Amelie is out of control!) Yumyum.(Amelie is eating human flesh.)'),
(43789, '(Amelies senses return)..Jed..Je..Jed..No!! Dont look..Please.. Dont LooooooooooooooK~!!!'),
(43790, 'It is ordinary worm. (What is this for..)'),
(43791, 'Insert the Spiritual Stone and Amelies blood.'),
(43792, 'Kuoooooooooooooo.(Worms getting bigger)'),
(43793, 'Wonder how Great Elders doing.. Drakis move seems suspicious..'),
(43794, 'Master. Sharine is looking for you.'),
(43795, 'Master. Sharine is looking for you.'),
(43796, 'Welcome?I knew it that you will come.'),
(43797, 'Long time nosee Sharine.. So is he doing alright? (Atlas unseals the letter) Oh no! The Spiritual Stone has been spreaded out this wide?ave to find a Pole of Purification ASAP..'),
(43798, 'According to legend, a Pole of purification was divided by 3 pieces and given to 3 most sacred sprits in Temple of Water. And when the temple collapsed, it got diappeared since then..'),
(43799, 'When Temple of Water collapsed, all 3 spirits died and theres no way to find the Pole of Purification.'),
(43800, 'However according to oral tradition, the Spirit of Water reincarnate in human-being. If we find the reincarnated spirt of Water, we could find a Pole of Purification as well.'),
(43801, 'Welcome <selfname>. Come on in. Can you do me a favor by any chance?'),
(43802, 'When we Portu ran away from Draky, there were some refugees came out together as well. However among refugees, there are few still chased by monsters.'),
(43803, 'Yes. Please get rid of the Savages and Wolfdogs to guard the refugee way.'),
(43804, 'You havent finish them yet? Please protect our refugees..'),
(43805, 'Thank you for your help. The refugees got arrived to the castle safely.'),
(43806, 'Welcome. I called you because food has been scarce since the refugee population has grown. Can you find something to eat for the refugees? I heard that Shebijis Meat is delicious.'),
(43807, 'No food yet? People are starving to death.'),
(43808, 'Ohh.. This is Shebijis Meat. Thank you so much. Many refugees can survive with this.'),
(43809, 'This is a dream come true to settle down here.. I have been chased by monsters everyday..'),
(43810, 'Hello. <selfname> right? So..I need a favor.'),
(43811, 'My mothers birthday is soon and Id liked to give her a warm coat for a gift but? dont have money, nor the energy to work?'),
(43812, 'Can you get me 20 pieces of Wolfdogs Leather so I can make a coat for her? I will pay you back once I grow up..Please, I am begging you.'),
(43813, 'Mothers birthday is around the corner.. Do you have them yet??'),
(43814, 'Wow! Thank you <selfname>. Really I truly mean it!!'),
(43815, '(Cough)(Cough) Hello <selfname>. Can you deliver this gift to my mother? She is probably near the [Advisor].(Cough)(Cough)'),
(43816, '(cough) I..Im fine~ Please do me this favor.'),
(43817, 'You didnt give her the present yet? (cough)'),
(43818, '<selfname> thank you. Did my mother like it?'),
(43819, 'Thank you to <selfname>. I wanted to give a present to mother before I die..Really thank you..(Cough)..(Co?g)'),
(43820, 'Sigh? wonder how Sadi is doing?its hard to see her face because shes extremely busy working..'),
(43821, 'Hello. What is it?'),
(43822, 'Oh. Sadi..sobbing..I have done nothing to deserve this?'),
(43823, 'This is not much, but it is some extra money for Sadi.|Can you deliver this <selfname>?'),
(43824, 'Sobbing..my Sadi..Sadi died ?ontaminated by the Spiritual Stone..'),
(43825, 'Are you <selfname>? Right. Can you help me?'),
(43826, 'Refugees were caught by Apes during their exodus. | Can you get rid of those Apes before they eat the refugees?'),
(43827, 'We dont have time. Lets hurry.'),
(43828, 'Ohoh! <selfname> thank you.'),
(43829, '<selfname>, have you seen my father while rescuing the refugees? My father was kidnapped too.. Could you try one more time?'),
(43830, 'Thank you so much'),
(43831, 'You didnt find my father yet?'),
(43832, 'What? My father died? (Wailing) Father ... Father ... sobbing ....'),
(43833, '(When Leia receives the Ring of Spirit, Leia floats in the air with blue lights.)'),
(43834, 'Ah..I..I was a Spirit?ather?hank you..<selfname>. Thank you for my father?nd bring my memory back?m an envoy of King Spirit. King Spirt ordered me to purify the Spiritual Stones in worldwide.'),
(43835, 'First of all, I have to go find my sisters. I could find them if I had the Earring of Spirit and Bracelet of Spirit with me. They are?Leia concentrates on her ring) hmm..They are located northwest from here. Seems Death Knight and Ancient have them near Raiba Village.'),
(43836, 'Please find spirit of earring and bracelet.'),
(43837, 'Please find spirit of earring and bracelet.'),
(43838, 'Aahh. Finally I can meet my sisters.'),
(43839, 'Death Knights King? think the Death knights king has the earring. Be careful. When you get rid of the knight, the king will appear. Get him too and find the Earring of Spirit.'),
(43840, 'Death Knights King will appear when you kill death knights.'),
(43841, 'Ohoh! <selfname> thank you.'),
(43842, 'If Death Knights are alive, they will kill anyone. When you get the earring, please kill those Death Knights.'),
(43843, 'Please kill more Death Knights'),
(43844, 'Ahah. <selfname> thank you.'),
(43845, 'King of Ancient Trees..Probably those contaminated trees became Ashunt when Temple of Water collapsed. There is more possibility with the oldest Tree has the bracelet.'),
(43846, 'Cheer up Warrior! King of Ancient will be among the Ancients.'),
(43847, 'Ahah. <selfname> thank you. It wasnt easy to find. The continent is getting purified slowly.'),
(43848, 'Warrior. Can you ged rid of those Ashunts while you find the bracelet? The forest wont be safe as long as theyre there.'),
(43849, 'Cheer up warrior! Get rid of 20 Ashunts'),
(43850, 'Ahah. <selfname> thank you.'),
(43851, 'You finally brought them all. The location where earring and bracelet respond is inside of the local villages. Once you go there, find Pina and Sara and give them these eaaring and bracelet. | I will prepare for ceremony of Pole of Purification at Jeras temple. I will see you there with the sisters.'),
(43852, 'You havent found the Pina yet. Seems Pina is at towards Asga village'),
(43853, 'Ah..No doubt to see them again?Meet me at the temple of Jeras<selfname>'),
(43854, '(Earrings of Spirit are flashing) ...... Oh those earrings ...'),
(43855, '(Sara is shining in blue with the earring.) You came to see me..'),
(43856, 'Leia.. My sister is still alive..Thank you Warrior. Lets go see my sister.'),
(43857, '(Bracelet of Spirit is flashing) ...... Oh that bracelet ...'),
(43858, '(Pina is shining in blue with the bracelet) You came to see me..'),
(43859, 'Leia.. My sister still alive..Thank you Warrior. Lets go see my sister.'),
(43860, 'Thank you Warrior. Its all your effort for our reunion. Summon the Pole of Purification. Once we start summoning, the monsters will come and attack us. I want you to protect us against those monsters.')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(43861, 'Are you ready?'),
(43862, 'The Pole of Purification doesnt have enough holy power..'),
(43863, '(Bang!)(A bright shining staff is in the air above altar.) Its done.. Use this pole to cure those people contaminated with Spiritual Stone.'),
(43864, 'I will fill the Purification pole with souls. Warrior you must protect me. Tell me when youre ready. It wont be easy to protect me against the monsters'),
(43865, 'The Pole of Purification doesnt have enough holy power..'),
(43866, 'I have to protect the pole against the contamination. Please kill the mosters around us. Lets start then.'),
(43867, 'The Pole of Purification doesnt have enough holy power..'),
(43868, 'Saras part is not finished yet'),
(43869, 'Pinas part is not finished yet'),
(43870, 'Pinas part is not finished yet'),
(43871, 'Leias part is not finished yet'),
(43872, 'Saras part is not finished yet'),
(43873, 'Leias part is not finished yet'),
(43874, 'There gotta be some refugees who got contaminated by Spiritual Stone at Elmorad castle. Go there and heal them.'),
(43875, 'Contaminated refugees are at the castle. Please hurry.'),
(43876, 'Good job. Now those people wont die because of the Spiritual Stone.'),
(43877, 'Ah..It hurts?elp me..its like my chest is burning.'),
(43878, 'Aaah!! Help me. Ou! Ch! Ah! (Chest is dyed in dark and purification pole does not work.)'),
(43879, 'Ha.. Thought you could purify me..?'),
(43880, 'O my. Its Draiden!!..Spiritual Stone was Draidens plot'),
(43881, 'Warrior, this is dangerous here. Move to a different place first.'),
(43882, 'Shit.. I got unnecessary damage because of that stupid Spirit..Hehe. But at least I got Leia down..next time is you guys..'),
(43883, 'Draiden is an evil that lives in darkness.'),
(43884, 'Sobbing?ister???..'),
(43885, 'Sobbing?e cant keep being sad like this.. Once Draiden appears, Spiritual Stones contamination will continue.'),
(43886, 'I have to get rid of Draiden.'),
(43887, '<selfname>s ability is enough. But you just dont have good enough weapons.'),
(43888, 'As far as I know, you can make a sword that can cuts the spirits with this purified Spiritual Stone.'),
(43889, 'Yes. Draiden really doesnt have its body so you have to cut his spirit. I heard theres a great blacksmith in Adonis continent. Was it Heppa? Take this purified Spiritual Stone to him.'),
(43890, 'Have you met Heppa yet?'),
(43891, 'Draiden wait for me..'),
(43892, 'Welcome~ which weapon do you need?'),
(43893, '!!! This is Spiritual Stone? Never seen a Spiritual Stone like this, Hmm? can make it, but I cant guarantee how it will come out. In worst case, even this Spiritual Stone will become useless.'),
(43894, 'If you insist, I will try with my best. Then, can you get me those materials? I need those at least so I can make a sword with Spiritual Stone.'),
(43895, 'First, I need Great Wizard Drakis Elixir. With that I can make the stone calm down.'),
(43896, 'Secondly, I need the Trinity jewel that contained a War force. Jeweler Jewel should know the create procedure of Trinity jewel.'),
(43897, 'Third, I need a legendary mineral, Oriharcon. In fact, Spiritual stone is main material but its strength will be doubled with a coating of Oriharcon. You can obtain it from defeating Halion which is at south of Eslant.'),
(43898, 'Lastly, Spiritual researcher, Sherines recipe. Theres no one better than her. Get me the recipe.'),
(43899, 'Yes. Please take care of yourself.'),
(43900, 'Not enough material yet'),
(43901, 'Aahh.. Never knew this ever happened to me..Thank you..(Crying Heppa) I will make you the best sword I ever made!! Just wait for it!!(Heppa going into forge while holding a giant hammer)'),
(43902, 'Clattering~Rattles~Cracking~~! (The noise of hammering echoed in Moradon and after a week, Heppa brings a sword.)'),
(43903, '(Heppa was holding a sword which is the most beautiful sword I ever seen.) This is my masterpiece! Hahahaha please use it on purpose!!'),
(43904, 'Im the blacksmith Atlas. Wait! Your star is twinkling gloriously.'),
(43905, 'Master! Blacksmith is looking for you.'),
(43906, 'Master! Blacksmith is looking for you.'),
(43907, 'Wonder if Sharines doing alright..'),
(43908, 'Not enough space. Please make some space in your bag.'),
(43909, 'I can hear the sound of wind?Can you hear it as well? | What brought you here?'),
(43910, 'I can feel the force of the earth.. Can you feel it as well? | What brought you here?'),
(43911, 'I can feel the force of water... Can you feel it as well? | What brought you here?'),
(43912, '(Bones are laid between empty cells)'),
(43913, 'Please save me!!!! Those Apes are trying to eat me alive.!! Please save me..We can get a prison key if you kill those Apes!!'),
(43914, 'Help me~~!! Oh!! You have a key~ Please help me out of here.'),
(43915, 'Thank you. Thank you so much..Lets go out together.'),
(43916, '(King Aif smacks Leias father with a giant bat) Run. No.! Old man. Kill. Human. Weak?'),
(43917, 'Sigh?Look..Please deliver this letter to Leia in the castle.. Im begging you?'),
(43918, 'Old man..not delicious..you are..delicious..human.delicious.'),
(43919, 'Wait. <selfname>. Can I take a look at the ring on you?'),
(43920, '(Once the ring touches Leias hand, it starts glowing.) Ah.. This is what father said?'),
(43921, 'Its OK. Yeah. Everything is clear now..Ah?I got my memory back?hank you. <selfname>. I got it back because of you.'),
(43922, 'The memory that I was once a Spirit. Im the Spirit of Water Leia. I lost my memory somehow. First of all I have to find my sisters.'),
(43923, 'I have two sisters. If I find them, I probably get the rest of my lost memories.'),
(43924, 'This ring is a 3 piece-set accessory. They pull to each other with the power of King Spirit. It can guide us to find the other pieces.'),
(43925, 'According to fathers letter, it tells me to find a ring of Spirit from king Aif. Can you get it from King Aif?'),
(43926, 'Save me please!! I worry about my daugher.. I have to see her.'),
(43927, '(If I open this door, would king Ape appear? Should I open it?)'),
(43928, '(The bracelet starts to glow once it goes to Pina)'),
(43929, '(The earring starts to glow once it goes to Sara)'),
(43930, 'You havent found Sara yet. I think shes in one of the local villages.'),
(43931, 'See you at Jeras Temple.<selfname>'),
(43932, 'See you at Jeras Temple.<selfname>'),
(43933, 'See you at Jeras Temple.<selfname>'),
(43943, '<selfname>Welcome.| you are our great supporter <selfname>.'),
(43944, 'I dont know what to say but weve lost the Eslants treasure which are 3 God equipments.'),
(43945, 'Yes. Theyre Esperancers armor that protects against any attacks, Eclipses Spear that cut through any armors, and Jerpers guntlet that makes users hand as fast as the light. Of course they work on only chosen person but theyre important to people of Eslant as Gods possessions.'),
(43946, 'Lost to Marcil, Badin, Garlong. They were not big threats to us but someday they came up with incredible powers and attacked us. It was too sudden and Im sorry we couldn£s protect those equipments.'),
(43947, 'It is mystery to us too. For now its more important to get those 3 equipments back from them.| and there is a rumor that a strange monster showed up near ancient site in Southwest area. .|<selfname>, please bring peace to Eslant.'),
(43948, '<selfname>, are you now on the way to kill Marcil? If so, please save Eslant people over there. I heard that our people are used as servants. Please help them.'),
(43949, 'Our people not yet? The kidnapped people are captured in northwest of Marcils settlement.'),
(43950, 'You really saved kidnapped people, <selfname> thank you. This is nothing but our express of appreciation.'),
(43951, 'Are you on the way to kill Marcil? Then I have another favor. Marcils fellows invade to cilvilians village and steal foods and kidnap the kids and women in the village these days. We will appreciate if you kill those bastards.'),
(43952, 'Fellows not yet defeated? Their settlement are located  at southwest.'),
(43953, 'I heard the news. Youre awesome. That you got rid of them. Youre the true hero. The legendary Gods equipments probably belong to you.<selfname>'),
(43954, '<selfname>, are you now on the way to kill Badin? If so, please save Eslant people over there. I heard that our people are used as servants. Please help them.'),
(43955, 'Our people not yet? The kidnapped people are captured in northwest of Badins settlement.'),
(43956, 'You really saved kidnapped people, <selfname> thank you. This is nothing but our express of appreciation.'),
(43957, 'Are you on the way to kill Badin? Then I have another favor. Badins fellows invade to cilvilians village and steal foods and kidnap the kids and women in the village these days. We will appreciate if you kill those bastards.'),
(43958, 'Fellows not yet defeated? Their settlement are located  at northwest.'),
(43959, 'I heard the news. Youre awesome. That you got rid of them. Youre the true here. The legendary Gods equipments probably belong to you.<selfname>'),
(43960, '<selfname>, are you now on the way to kill Garlong? If so, please save Eslant people over there. I heard that our people are used as servants. Please help them.'),
(43961, 'Our people not yet? The kidnapped people are captured in northeast of Garlongs settlement.'),
(43962, 'You really saved kidnapped people, <selfname> thank you. This is nothing but our express of appreciation.'),
(43963, 'Are you on the way to kill Garlong? Then I have another favor. Garlongs fellows invade to cilvilians village and steal foods and kidnap the kids and women in the village these days. We will appreciate if you kill those bastards.'),
(43964, 'Fellows not yet defeated? Their settlement are located  at northeast.'),
(43965, 'I heard the news. Youre awesome. That you got rid of them. Youre the true hero. The legendary Gods equipments probably belong to you.<selfname>'),
(43966, 'Are you going to face the enemy?Dont forget about us supporting your back, <selfname>. Please bring the peace back after you defeat Marcil / Badin / Garlong.'),
(43967, 'Not easy enemies. Theyre located at southwest / northwest / northeast.'),
(43968, 'Unbelievable to defeat that strong enemy. Youre truly a hero this era.'),
(43969, 'Please find back those stolen Eslants 3 treasures from the Devils. Were all counting on you. <selfname>'),
(43970, 'Marcil, Badin and Garlong each possess the 3 treasures. Please bring them back..'),
(43971, 'Thank you. Now this equipments finally find its owner?'),
(43972, '<selfname>, have you heard of sound that a mountain collapsed in southwest?'),
(43973, 'Yes. The Southwest mountain which has ancient ruins collapsed last night. Regarding what Patrol said, a legendary monster Prisila just revived there. Why troubles keep happening.. Perhaps <selfname> can get rid of it too?'),
(43974, 'if Prisila is alive, Eslant could be exterminated anytime. Prisila would be at southwest area.'),
(43975, 'Although youve got 3 Gods equipments on you, didnt know you could still knock out a legendary monster.'),
(43976, '(Us receiving a letter) T?his!! Ancient Draki language.. Draki tribe disappeared centuries ago..'),
(43977, 'Yes. Its Drakis language. Maybe revival of Prisila is somehow related to Draki.'),
(43978, 'We should let Uranos know about this.'),
(43979, 'Hes our captain who fights in the first line of Ronalkland. Please deliver this letter to Uranos.'),
(43980, 'Please hurry.'),
(43981, 'I could hear sound of mind?hat brought you here?'),
(43982, 'What this!! They finally come here to find the Adonis continent.'),
(43983, 'LOST PAGE. Do you know every Bible exist in Adonis continent miss pg.2? |  that legendary page tells God created Draki species before Elmorad and Karuth..'),
(43984, 'Yes.. Theyre strong and smart..They promised to come back when they got kicked out to a different world.. With curses to God, comeback with the power to defeat God..They finally got here to Adonis continent.'),
(43985, 'They will need Draki gate to teleport themselves here. We have to destroy the gate before they coming through.'),
(43986, 'Theres no way to find out. If we could find rest piece of this ruined page..'),
(43987, 'They keep coming and coming.. You bastards...'),
(43988, 'From someday, the dead bodies around village arose and attack the village.'),
(43989, 'Would you? Ok. Then can you kill 20 (contaminated Karuth warrior) or (contaminated Elmorad warrior) around here?'),
(43990, 'Thanks.. Give them a rest in peace. About 20.'),
(43991, 'Seriously. Its enough to protect against warriors attacks, but what if neibor country attack at this point.. Its like somebodys behind all this. If you dont mind, can you get ride of 30 soldiers from enemy contry user?'),
(43992, 'Enemies dont stop attack us! Hurry help us quick!'),
(43993, 'Indeed! I was right! I knew you could do it. Well done!'),
(43994, 'Come Come! I found this when I was killing warriors!'),
(43995, 'Yes! Its a dark Spiritual stone. They were controled by this stone. Seems its dark force covers entire Ronalkland'),
(43996, 'Well? Draki? Draiden? No clue to find out for now. First lets give a peace to fallen warriors. I heard that you have a purification pole on you . If you use it on fallen warriors, you would get the purified spiritual stones. Please get me 10 of them.'),
(43997, 'If you have a pole of purification, you would get the purified spiritual stones from fallen warrirors'),
(43998, 'What? The pole of purification wont work?'),
(43999, 'Even the pole of purification doesnt work.. How powerful it could be if pole of purification has no effect to it...'),
(44000, 'Ah?theres any hope?t would be enough with Pole of Life..'),
(44001, 'You want to find out?'),
(44002, 'if you insist?hats what pole of purification actually looks.. Purifies no matter what kinds of darkness it is. King Spirit Rifte used in the past. King Spirit should be contained to uncover its disguise. Becoming the pole of Life.'),
(44003, 'Yes..but forget it. Do you believe in spirit nowadays?'),
(44004, 'Long time no see.<selfname>. How are you?'),
(44005, 'I could sometimes hear some of your adventure story at the castle. What brought you here today?'),
(44006, 'Lord Rifte?'),
(44007, 'it s hard to see him.  Even us to see him once in 1000 years.'),
(44008, 'We cant go see him.'),
(44009, 'Haha then we should bring him here.'),
(44010, 'If we want to recall him we need 200 spiritual souls. King spirit take good care of Spiritual souls.'),
(44011, 'Monsters at Ronalkland have all spriritual souls. Release those souls and meet a king spirit.'),
(44012, 'Not enough souls yet.'),
(44013, 'Im so exciting to see him'),
(44014, 'Are you ready? Now we will see king Spirit. Ready?'),
(44015, 'Then I will prepare for it. Are you going to hand me the souls?'),
(44016, '(Start speaking spells with collecting of bloody spirits)'),
(44017, '(By the time spells becoming a song and echos in the village, Spirits start scatter and those scattered spirits shaped themselves into a shape of human.)'),
(44018, 'Who was looking for me?'),
(44019, 'A mortal being calld me? How funny. Just wasted time |(King Spirit about to disappear)'),
(44020, '(Disappearing King spirit with ignore)'),
(44021, '(King Spirit stops) Draki? You mean son of Pathos?'),
(44022, 'This continent is about to face the end. So? What about Draki?'),
(44023, 'Haha.. So what do you want me to do?'),
(44024, 'My power? Yea? I will let you borrow. Then what do I get for?'),
(44025, 'See? Haha I like the deal. Ok. But your body cant accept my tremendous power. But Its possible if you have a pole of purification.'),
(44026, 'You have prepared for this. Very detailed. Ok. Heres my power. I will take what I want once I collect my power. Haha'),
(44027, 'Welcome. Ronalk tribes patriarches gone crazy since you were gone. Please hurry to get rid of them!'),
(44028, 'The damage grows by patriarches everyday. Help us.'),
(44029, 'You. Whats up with your power? I never seen a person like you fast and strong.'),
(44030, 'What! Perhaps thats pole of Life? Thought it was a legend.'),
(44031, 'That holy aurora light..really beautiful and powerful. That should purify the warriors. I have to ask you for one more time.'),
(44032, 'Fallen warriors dead bodies should be near the village. If you use the pole onto dead bodies, you will get purified stones. Bring 10 of them.'),
(44033, 'Yes.. O yes?What cant a pole of Life cure.. Thank you'),
(44034, 'Come in. I dont know if you heard this too but, our strongest squad in our unit lost connection with us few days ago.'),
(44035, 'Theyre unbitten squad.. Can you go find out?'),
(44036, 'Thank you. They disappeared where Dragon knight commander was. If you get rid of them you should get some evidences.'),
(44037, 'You havent found any clues yet? Hope the 1st squad is ok.. We lost a connection where Dragon knights are located.'),
(44038, 'Chaos Dragon knights commander which appeared once 1000 years ago.. Its weird.'),
(44039, 'Come! Its getting worse. 2nd squad also got disappeared just like 1st squad. Can you go find them?'),
(44040, 'Thank you. They disappeared where Fossil Guard was. If you get rid of them you should get some evidences.'),
(44041, 'You havent found any clues yet? Hope the 2nd squad is ok..'),
(44042, 'Chaos Fossil Guard!! Drakis fellos showed up.. I have to let everybody knows and add more manpower.'),
(44043, 'Welcome <selfname>. Thank you for accepting our request for help.'),
(44044, 'You probably heard this but, Oaks are kidnapping Portus on immigration.'),
(44045, 'Indeed I tried. But at the center of Oak whre people disappeared, we cant trace anything maybe its because of the sealing spell.'),
(44046, 'Yes. We have to first release its sealing spell to save people. Thats what we want <selfname> to do.'),
(44047, 'Thank you for saying to help us. First we have to stop the operation of Sealing tower located at Ardreams every corners.'),
(44048, 'There have to be Oaks around the sealing towers. Obtain a key to release the seal on the tower after defeating the Oaks.'),
(44049, 'Yes. Its tough job, it ll be hard without <selfname>. Please do it for us.'),
(44050, 'Not released the seal yet? Please hurry.'),
(44051, 'Indeed <selfname>. Youre awesome as I heard. This is nothing but a small reward for all this.'),
(44052, 'Weldome <selfname>. Were conducting a rescue operation after you destroyed the sealing towers from last time, but Oaks resistance is not easy. Can <selfname> go to them and reduce Oaks strength?'),
(44053, 'There still many resistance by Oaks. Please defeat only 20 each Oak warriors, archer, wizards.'),
(44054, 'Thank you. Youre so sexy to cut those Oaks at once. This is reward for that.'),
(44055, 'Come. Were running out of time.  Save the people while you wipe out the Oaks.'),
(44056, 'There are still many hostages captured. Their lives are hanging on the cliff. Please save them from the prison.'),
(44057, 'Indeed! <selfname>! I knew you were awesome when I first saw you. But you are more than awesome. Thank you.'),
(44058, 'Welcome. Its all because of the commander Kaisraq controls those brainless monsters blocking our attacks. If we get rid of him, those Oaks are nothing. Please get Kaisraq down.'),
(44059, 'Please cut Kaisraqs head off!'),
(44060, 'Indeed youre great! Thank you.'),
(44061, '<selfname> came? Recently the monsters around Eslant bocome stronger and more damages rise. I think its all about the red Spiritual stone effects. I want you <selfname> to defeat them. Please defeat 20 cardinals.'),
(44062, 'Not yet on cardinals? More damages appear on the Refugees immigration to Ardream'),
(44063, '<selfname> came? Recently the monsters around Eslant bocome stronger and more damages rise. I think its all about the red Spiritual stone effects. I want you <selfname> to defeat them. Please defeat 20 Trents?'),
(44064, 'Not yet on Trent? More damages appear on the Refugees immigration to Ardream'),
(44065, '<selfname> came? Recently the monsters around Eslant bocome stronger and more damages rise. I think its all about the red Spiritual stone effects. I want you <selfname> to defeat them. Please defeat 20 Barrens'),
(44066, 'Not yet on Barren? More damages appear on the Refugees immigration to Ardream'),
(44067, '<selfname> came? Recently the monsters around Eslant bocome stronger and more damages rise. I think its all about the red Spiritual stone effects. I want you <selfname> to defeat them. Please defeat 20 Ashents'),
(44068, 'Not yet on Ashents? More damages appear on the Refugees immigration to Ardream'),
(44069, 'Ardreams monsters become stronger ever with an effect of red spiritual stone. Now we can defend just with Ardreams military and its all because of <selfname>. Thank you. We got here from now on. And this red spiritual stone. Can you take this to Us at Eslant?')
INSERT INTO quest_talk (i_num, str_talk) VALUES
(44070, 'Yes. As far as I know. Best professor. Maybe he know about this red spiritual stone. Can you go find him and find more about this stone?'),
(44071, 'Thanks for everything. Be well. Anything with a red spiritual stone, go see Eslants Us'),
(44072, 'Welcome. I have heard enough about you. Supporting our unit. Thank you!'),
(44073, 'Gave them a peace. Thank you.'),
(44074, 'You dont have a pole of purification. You wont be able to accept my power..'),
(44075, 'Haha. Im not afraid of a weakling like you. You cant even beat the pirates. If you want to win, come back tomorrow! [This quest is available once per day]'),
(44076, 'She loves me!! Oh~!~! God!! Thank you.'),
(44077, 'To take both earring and bracelet of spirit with you, make two empty spaces in your bag.'),
(44078, 'Save me!! Save me!!! I could get killed anytime here..please..'),
(44079, 'Thank you. Thank you. Take us to the village please.'),
(44080, 'It is a tower with numerous Oak language on it.'),
(44081, 'Oh yea. We dont need this. Please take it with you.'),
(44082, 'Empty cell. There are some marks that people were here once..'),
(44083, 'Its a Western sealing tower. I can release the seal if I have a key. (I can hear sound of key from Oaks)'),
(44084, 'Its a Eastern sealing tower. I can release the seal if I have a key. (I can hear sound of key from Oaks)'),
(44085, 'Its a Southern sealing tower. I can release the seal if I have a key. (I can hear sound of key from Oaks)'),
(44086, 'Its a Northern sealing tower. I can release the seal if I have a key. (I can hear sound of key from Oaks)'),
(44087, 'Sealing is released already.'),
(44088, 'No key to fit in this Pole.'),
(44089, 'Welcome. As you know, 1st squad is disappeared where Fossil Guards are.'),
(44090, 'Theres something else we dont know yet. Can you find that out while you get rid of those Fossil Guards?'),
(44091, 'Thanks. Then get rid of 20 Fossil Guards.'),
(44092, 'There are still many Fossil Guards. Please keep it up.'),
(44093, 'There was a Chaos Fossil Guard? Indeed thats what is was.. Thank you..They were Drakis fellows in the past.. What brought them here again?'),
(44094, 'Shit. 2nd squad is disappeared just like the 1st squad.. So weird.. Where 2nd squad disappear is near Dragon knights location. Please find an evidence of disappearance while you defeat Dragon knights.'),
(44095, 'Any clue for their disappearance?'),
(44096, 'Really!? Chaos Dragon knights commander.. It is impossible for monsters get a power of chaos in general..'),
(44097, 'Drakis attack!! No..Ancient tribe tries to revive and attack on Adonis continent.'),
(44098, 'First thing to do is establish the military and prepare for the battle. Let everyone knows and alliance even with enemies will be necessary.'),
(44099, 'Welcome. <selfname>, heard it from sister Lea that you need a Black Onix. As you know, the guardian of Black Onix, DeathReverse is very powerful.'),
(44100, 'Death Reverse is powerful. Be ready enough and request to summon. Summon now?'),
(44101, 'Defeating the DeathReverse. Really impressive.'),
(44102, 'Havent defeated the Deathreverse yet.'),
(44103, 'because I havent got all my powers yet, Deathrevers can be summoned once per day.'),
(44104, 'Welcome. <selfname>, heard it from sister Lea that you need a Blue Onix. As you know, the guardian of Blue Onix, Sindria is very powerful.'),
(44105, 'Sindria is powerful. Be ready enough and request to summon. Summon now?'),
(44106, 'Defeating the Sindria Really impressive.'),
(44107, 'Havent defeated the Sindria yet.'),
(44108, 'because I havent got all my powers yet, Sindria can be summoned once per day.'),
(44109, 'Welcome. <selfname>, heard it from sister Lea that you need a Red Onix. As you know, the guardian of Red Onix, Horizon is very powerful.'),
(44110, 'Be ready enough and request to summon. Summon now?'),
(44111, 'Defeating the Horizon Really impressive.'),
(44112, 'Havent defeated the Horizon yet.'),
(44113, 'because I havent got all my powers yet, Horizon can be summoned once per day.'),
(44114, 'Adreams Oaks kidnap the refugees and make them as their servants. Save the people and get rid of the Oaks.'),
(44115, 'To go to central Oak village in Ardream, the sealing tower in every corners of Ardream have to be destroyed. Defeat the Oaks around the tower, get a key and release the seal.'),
(44116, 'Oaks try to use kidnapped refugees as offering to God. Get rid of those Oaks in central of Ardream.'),
(44117, 'Oaks try to use kidnapped refugees as offering to God. Save refugees from the prison in central of Ardream.'),
(44118, 'There is an Oak which is smarter than other Oaks. Kill Kaisiraq who is being a leader of Oak tribe.'),
(44119, 'Existing Monsters become more violent with an effect of red spiritual stone. Kill the 20 violent(Cardinal).'),
(44120, 'Existing Monsters become more violent with an effect of red spiritual stone. Kill the 20 violent(Trents).'),
(44121, 'Existing Monsters become more violent with an effect of red spiritual stone. Kill the 20 violent(Barrens).'),
(44122, 'Existing Monsters become more violent with an effect of red spiritual stone. Kill the 20 violent(Ashunts).'),
(44123, 'The reason Ardream monsters bocome more violent is a contamination of red spiritual stone. Other areas may have same effect too, so I have to report this to Eslant.'),
(44124, 'Eslants 3 Gods equipments were stolen by Devils. We have to bring them back from the Devils.'),
(44125, 'I have to free the people treated as servants under one of the Eslants Devils, Marcil. Have to let people escape from the Prison around Maril'),
(44126, 'Lets kill 20 fellows of Marcil.'),
(44127, 'I have to free the people treated as servants under one of the Eslants Devils, Badin. Have to let people escape from the Prison around Barin'),
(44128, 'Lets kill 20 fellows of Badin.'),
(44129, 'I have to free the people treated as servants under one of the Eslants Devils, Garlong. Have to let people escape from the Prison around Garlong.'),
(44130, 'Lets kill 20 fellows of Garlong.'),
(44131, 'Defeat Eslants 3 Devils Marcil, Badin, Garlong.'),
(44132, 'Lets get 3 Gods equipments that were stolen by Eslants 3 Devils.'),
(44133, 'An ancient monster Prisila shows up at northern Mountain from southwest of Eslant. Defeat Prisila.'),
(44134, 'Go tell in Ronarkland about Eslant issue.'),
(44135, 'Dead Warriors have resurrected and are attacking the town. Defeat them now.'),
(44136, 'Enemys attack has been getting stronger. Need to defeat and see the cause of this.'),
(44137, '(Contaminated Karus Warrior) or (Contaminated Elmorad Warrior) need to be defeated to collect improved darkness stones x 10.'),
(44138, 'Need to see how we can purify the darkness stone. Spirit Fina might know.'),
(44139, 'Find out what to do to purify darkness stone from Fina.'),
(44140, 'In order to meet Spirit King Lifte, need Soul of spirit. Soul of spirits can be found among humans. Defeat 30 enemies now.'),
(44141, 'Conversation with Spirit King Lifte'),
(44142, 'In Ronarkland, tribe chiefs are getting more violent. Defeat Tribe chiefs.'),
(44143, 'Utilize Life Pole to heal 10 fallen down soldiers.'),
(44144, 'Inspection team 1 has been disappeared at where fossil guards are. Find out the reason for this. Accrording to the recent news, Chaos Fossil guards were the ones who did this. Find Chaos Fossil Guards.'),
(44145, 'Inspection team 2 has been disappeared where Dragon Knights are located. Find out the reason for this. According to the recent news, they were defeated by the Dragon Knights. Find Chaos Dragon Knights.'),
(44146, 'In order to make Purified Pole, need Red Onyx. Leia should be able to summon Horizon who will summon Red Onyx. Defeat Horizon.'),
(44147, 'In order to make Purified Pole, need Blue Onyx. Leia should be able to summon Cindrea who can summon Blue Onyx. Defeat Cindrea.'),
(44148, 'In order to make Purified Pole, need Black Onyx. Leia should be able to summon Death Rebirth who will summon Black Onyx. Defeat Death Rebirth.'),
(44149, 'The reason for the disappearance of Inspection team 1 was because of Fossil Guards. Take revenge now. Defeat 20 fossil guards.'),
(44150, 'The reason for the disappearance of inspection team 2 was because of Dragon Knights. Defeat 20 dragon knights.'),
(44151, 'Found Drakis invasion planning document. Block Drakis invasion and let all the continents know of this.'),
(44152, 'We dont have the key for the prison. Defeat surrounding monsters to get the key.'),
(44153, 'Thank you, <selfname> for letting all three of us get together finally. I believe you said you needed Purification Pole?'),
(44154, 'In order to obtain the purification Pole, youll need Red, Blue and Black Onyx. We have these onyx.'),
(44155, 'But, these guardians of Onyx wont allow us to uses onyx that easily. Youll need to show them how strong you are in order for us to use the onyx.'),
(44156, 'Brave <selfname>. When you are ready, just tell us to unseal the onyx.'),
(44157, 'In order to obtain the purification Pole, you need 3 onyx which we, three sisters each have.'),
(44158, 'But in order to make the purification Pole, you need to defeat guardians. Defeat them now!'),
(44159, 'Heres Red Onyx. You are so brave <selfname>.'),
(44160, 'Heres Blue Onyx. You are so brave <selfname>.'),
(44161, 'Heres Red Onyx. You are so brave <selfname>.'),
(44162, 'Welcome. To support new portus castle has sent new equipment supports. For basic equipments, youll get raptor and Krowaz sets (strength) accessories and (magical, intelligent) accessories are being given out. See if you need anything.'),
(44163, 'Have fun at the war!! (When the test is over, items will be deleted)'),
(44164, 'You do not have enough inventory space. You need at least 9 spaces.'),
(44165, 'You do not have enough inventory space. You need at least 5 spaces.'),
(44166, 'You do not have enough inventory space. You need at least 6 spaces.'),
(44167, 'Youve already gotten your share of equipments.'),
(44168, '<selfname>, thank you! See you again!! ??'),
(44169, 'You are so awesome how you defeated guardians of onyx. Heres the Purification Pole.'),
(44170, 'Finally you have the Purification Pole. Congratulations. Now theres a bad news. Contaminated Refugees at the town are dying.'),
(44171, 'Bring the purification Pole and heal the refugees. Once you heal them youll be able to obtain Darkness stones. Heal 5 refugees.'),
(44172, 'Good job. Purification Pole is so awesome. Wait. Somethings coming out from the darkness stone.'),
(44173, 'Many refugees are in pain. Please go help them.'),
(44174, 'oh, hey there. Good to see you again.'),
(44175, 'You..  You are Draiden?'),
(44176, 'I was saving my power within the stones. You think you can purify me with that stupid purification Pole?'),
(44177, 'It was you all along?<selfname>, defeat Draiden with me.'),
(44178, 'You defeated Draiden! You are awesome! The town will be safe now. But Draiden isnt completely gone. He must be hidden somewhere charging his powers back.'),
(44179, 'You havent defeated Draiden. Draiden might be hiding in the Darkness Stone.'),
(44180, 'Thank you for everything. Have a good life now. To find out more regarding the red stones, go find Mas from Eslant.'),
(44181, 'Save me?my body.. My body is burning!'),
(44182, 'Th.. Thank you..  My body that was burning is all healed now. Thank you so much.'),
(44183, 'Ah..  Please.. Give me some.. Water..  Im so thirsty.'),
(44184, 'save.. Save me..  My body, my bodys burning.'),
(44185, 'Th.. Thank you..  My body that was burning is all healed now. Thank you so much.'),
(44186, 'Ah..  Please.. Give me some.. Water..  Im so thirsty.'),
(44187, 'Kill me..   Its so painful I cant handle it.'),
(44188, 'Thank you. Thank you so much! Ill be your help now.'),
(44189, 'Portu cant really change the appearance.'),
(44200, 'Actually I was looking for you. Magician organization in Moradon says that they need materials and are in a hurry. They say that theyll need skulls of Dragon Knights. Could you get them for us?'),
(44201, 'Of course youll need to kill dragon knights in order to get their skulls. Please bring back 5 skulls.'),
(44202, 'Still you dont have them yet? Come on hurry up. You know where to find them right?'),
(44203, 'Wow~~  good job.'),
(44204, 'Oh man..  Why do we keep needing stuff? This time its the weapon materials. Could you just get some weapons monsters use? Were really in a hurry so could you please start now?'),
(44205, 'Urkblade weapons will be perfect. Could you get about 20 of them?'),
(44206, 'Urkblades are stronger than you thought? I thought you would be stronger.'),
(44207, 'Oh great! I knew you could have done it.'),
(44208, 'You are here again, great! This time, the elders are trying to understand monsters life cycle. And now they are asking to get samples from me. Im just a merchant.'),
(44209, 'I need Hellhounds teeth x 15. Could you please get them?'),
(44210, 'You still dont have the teeth?'),
(44211, 'oh wow, so sharp!'),
(44212, 'Those elders are saying that they wanted to investigate. This time they want Manticores life cycle.'),
(44213, 'Thank you so much!!! Then could you get manticores leather x 5?'),
(44214, 'You? you can do this right?'),
(44215, 'Oh!! This is the manticore leather!!!'),
(44216, 'You have already resurrected 5 times. I wont help you with the next resurrection because one more might destroy your soul.'),
(44217, 'Abnormal levels must be 70 to enter the appropriate station.'),
(44218, 'If you pay 1,000 Nation points, you can get Dark Knight material [Elemental Stone] with low chances.'),
(44219, 'You have 1,000 Nation points! Good luck!'),
(44220, 'You can exchange once per day.'),
(44221, 'Do you want Flame of Dark Knight Spirit?'),
(44222, 'If you bring me 1 Gold Coin and 1 Evil Ingot,I will give you Flame of Spirit (15 days). Evil Ingot can be obtained from reverse item upgrade failure with low chances.'),
(44223, 'Well done. Flame of Spirit only lasts for 15days so please be careful with it!'),
(44224, 'If you bring me 1 Gold Coin and 1 Evil Ingot,I will give you Flame of Spirit (15 days). Evil Ingot can be obtained from reverse item upgrade failure with low chances.'),
(44225, 'Welcome. We exchange Chest of Chaos Crystal to Chaos Crystals. 2~7 Chaos Crystals will be obtained. You can create Chest of Chaos by NPC Shojin. Do you want to exchange Chest of Chaos Crystal?'),
(44226, 'You brought Chest of Chaos Crystal. I will exchange it with Chaos Crystals.'),
(44227, 'You dont have Chest of Chaos Crystal. Please bring me Chest of Chaos Crystal.'),
(44228, 'To create Dark Knight Weapon, you need special materials! What kind of materials do you want to use?'),
(44229, 'So, you brought 1 Gold Coin and 1 Evil Ingot?'),
(44230, 'Flame of Dark Knight Spirit quest only can be done once in a day. Please come back tomorrow.'),
(44231, 'Your level is between 40~50. If you are using Premium (WAR, EXP, DC) level will be jumped to 65. If you are not using Premium, level will be jumped to 60. | We encourage you to jump your level while using Premium. | Would you like to jump your level?'),
(44232, 'Your level is between 51~60. If you are using Premium (WAR, EXP, DC) level will be jumped to 65. If you are not using Premium, level will be jumped to 60. | We encourage you to jump your level while using Premium. | Would you like to jump your level?'),
(44233, 'Your level is between 61~70. If you are using Premium (WAR, EXP, DC) level will be jumped to 65. If you are not using Premium, level will be jumped to 60. | We encourage you to jump your level while using Premium. | Would you like to jump your level?'),
