(44248, 'Wild Plants can be exchanged once a day. Oh! When accumulated number of total 500 quests are done by users from server, Mutant Worm appears!'),
(44249, 'Welcome knight, I will briefly explain about the [War with Wild Plant] quest. When accumulated number of total 500 quests are done by users from server, Mutant Worm appears! Besides, we are running [Boutique Farmer] event and [Genie Limited Sale] event as well. Which event do you want to do?'),
(44250, 'You have 5 Wild Plants! Choose one from Banana-flavored Sweet Potato, Apple-flavored Tomatoe, and Orange-flavored Onion!'),
