(44337, 'Greetings Knight, Could you please help me? I need your help to prevent an inevitable disaster.'),
(44338, 'Recently, a dimensional rift was created near the castle. Drakis army will soon invade us using this rift. Could you please use the rift before them to take a look at their moves and look for the lost ones.'),
(44339, 'Do you wish to activate the [Boom Boom Power Premium]? Client will be closed.'),
(44340, 'You dont have [Boom Boom Power Premium]. Please check your inventory. Premiums can be purchased from PUS.'),
(44341, 'Thank you for saving me.'),
(44342, 'I miss my mom and dad?'),
(44343, 'Thank you! I will guide you to where other monsters are.'),
(44344, 'Greetings Knight, Could you please help me? I need your help to prevent an inevitable disaster.'),
(44345, 'Recently, a dimensional rift was created near the castle. Drakis army will soon invade us using this rift. Could you please use the rift before them to take a look at their moves and look for the lost ones.'),
(44346, 'A girls parents? Many were taken to the upper level so maybe her parents were taken to the upper level as well.'),
(44347, 'I will guide you to the upper level. Take care!'),
(44348, 'What happened to my body? Where is my daughter and wife?'),
(44349, 'Thank god my daughter is alive. I remember my wife was taken to the upper level before I became trapped in here. Please look for my wife once you get to the upper level.'),
(44350, ' I remember my wife taken to the upper level before I became trapped in here. Please look for my wife once you get to the upper level.'),
(44351, '(Cough?'),
(44352, 'I saw a monster taking a beautiful lady to the upper level. Do you want me to guide you to there?'),
(44353, 'Oh my?What has happened to me.'),
(44354, 'Is my daughter fine? Did my husband turn into monster too?'),
(44355, 'Thank god my daughter is alive. I remember a beautiful lady with pointy ears being taken to the upper level by a scorpion monster.'),
(44356, '(Cough?'),
(44357, 'Haha?you are too late. She should be transformed into a monster by now!'),
(44358, 'The Princess was taken to be used in an experiment.'),
(44359, 'Drakis turned me into a monster?It is fortunate you came before I lost my human nature.'),
(44360, 'My silky skin?is all ruined. Thanks for saving me.'),
(44361, 'You sure are a knight. Are you going to head to the upper levels? I keep hearing the howls of the dead?Maybe someone should find a way for them to rest in peace.'),
(44362, 'Are you going to head to the upper levels? I keep hearing the howls of the dead?Maybe someone should find a way for them to rest in peace.'),
(44363, 'Now they can rest in peace.'),
(44364, 'Thank you Knight. Can I ask you a favor?'),
(44365, 'We are a Knightage of old forgotten kingdom. Our kingdom has fallen from attacks of unknown monsters and they have brought us here. Our princess was also captured and I believe she is somewhere up top. Could you please rescue our princess?'),
(44366, 'I believe our princess is captured somewhere up top. Could you please rescue our princess?'),
(44367, 'You have saved me?Thank you.'),
(44368, 'Our royal family has inherited the ability to control time. We considered this ability as a blessing that helped our family to establish a kingdom but we soon found it wasnt.'),
(44369, 'Drakis teleported through the rift and destroyed our kingdom. People were taken back through Drakis Rift and had twisted experiments performed on them. You will find the high rank Drakis at the top of this tower. We dont know what their plan is but it certainly will bring disaster to the whole Adonis continent.'),
(44370, 'If you reach the top of the tower, you will be able to face the high rank Drakis who are responsible for these atrocities. Please defeat them and take revenge for us.'),
(44371, 'I cant believe this?You are just a human?'),
(44372, 'How dare an inferior human try to disrupt our master plan. We could have traveled back in time to our glorious days!'),
(44373, 'This is not the end! This is the beginning of the end! We can still go back in time to where you werent here.'),
(44374, 'They will be the stepping stone to our master plan. Farewell. Hahaha!'),
(44375, 'I see?That was what Drakis have been plotting for. If Drakis are going back in time, the only thing we can do is to defeat them over and over again until we find a solution to defeat them completely. I will ask for Gods help.'),
(44376, 'I see?That was what Drakis have been plotting for. If Drakis are going back in time, the only thing we can do is to defeat them over and over again until we find a solution to defeat them completely. I will ask for Gods help.'),
(44377, 'Even if time goes back again, we need to still rescue those captured people.'),
(44378, 'Even if time goes back again, we need to still rescue those captured people.'),
(44379, 'There must be a blind spot for time control. Lets ask [Forgotten Princess] about it.'),
(44380, 'There must be a blind spot for time control. Lets ask [Forgotten Princess] about it.'),
(44381, 'Even if we keep failing, we have to keep trying to stop Drakis from controlling time. At some point we will be successful.'),
(44382, 'Even if we keep failing, we have to keep trying to stop Drakis from controlling time. At some point we will be successful.'),
(44383, 'You need to defeat Drakis Tower Boss 3 times.'),
(44384, 'You need to defeat Drakis Tower Boss 3 times.'),
(44385, 'You havent defeated Drakis Tower Boss 3 times yet.'),
(44386, 'You havent defeated Drakis Tower Boss 3 times yet.'),
(44387, 'Available only once a day.'),
(44388, 'Available only once a day.'),
(44389, 'According to this message?a huge disaster will take over the whole Adonis continent. Please go to the other side of Drakis Rift and see if there are any survivors.'),
(44390, 'My parents were taken by monsters along with other villagers. Plesae find my parents.'),
(44391, 'Many were captured and brought here. Drakis have taken some to the top of the tower. Maybe her parents are there too.'),
(44392, 'Thank god my daughter is alive. I remember my wife was taken to the upper level before I became trapped in here. Please look for my wife once you get to the upper level.'),
(44393, 'Thank god my daughter is alive. I remember a beautiful lady with pointy ears taken to the upper level by a scorpion monster.'),
