(44395, 'My silky skin?is all ruined. Are you going to head to the upper levels? I keep hearing the howls of the dead?Maybe someone should find a way for them to rest in peace.'),
(44396, 'We are a Knightage of old forgotten kingdom. Our kingdom has fallen from attacks of unknown monsters and they have brought us here. Our princess was also captured and I believe she is somewhere up top. Could you please rescue our princess?'),
(44397, 'Our royal family has inherited the ability to control time. We considered this ability as a blessing which helped our family establish a kingdom but it brought us disaster as well. One day, Drakis teleported through the rift and destroyed our kingdom. People were taken back through Drakis Rift and had twisted experiments perfomred on them. You will find the high rank Drakis at the top of this tower. Please defeat them and bring us peace.'),
(44398, 'This is not the end! This is the beginning of the end! We can still go back in time to where you werent here. You will just become a part of our master plan!'),
