(44552, 'Im [Ascetic of Modesty] Beriel. I practice asceticism to fight against the Seven Deadly Sins. I have overthrown the Greed in myself and have found inner peace.Do you wish to learn true modesty from me?'),
(44553, 'I have taught you everything about Modesty. I hope you can find another Ascetic to learn about avoiding the Seven Deadly Sins.'),
(44554, 'Human beings needs to know how to control themselves. If not, they are no different than animals. Welcome. Im [Ascetic of Moderation] Ragel. Are you prepared for a new lesson?'),
(44555, 'Oh... you havent learned about Modesty yet? You must learn about Modestry prior to learning about Moderation.'),
(44556, 'I have taught you everything about Moderation.  I hope you can find another Ascetic to learn about avoiding the Seven Deadly Sins.'),
(44557, 'Patience is a virtue. Im [Ascetic of Patience] Barael. Welcome. Are you prepared for a new lesson?'),
(44558, 'Oh... you havent learned about Moderation yet? You must learn about Moderation prior to learning about Patience.'),
(44559, 'I have taught you everything about Patience.  I hope you can find another Ascetic to learn about avoiding the Seven Deadly Sins.'),
(44560, 'The early bird gets the worm. Welcome, Im [Ascetic of Diligence] Tron. Do you wish to talk with me?'),
