(44565, 'I have taught you everything about Purity. I hope you can find another Ascetic to learn about avoiding the Seven Deadly Sins.'),
(44566, 'If someone strikes you on the right cheek, turn to him the other also. Im [Ascetic of Kindness] Lapiel.'),
