(44568, 'I have taught you the everything about Kindness. I hope you can find another Ascetic to learn about avoiding the Seven Deadly Sins. [Ascetic of Charity] is located at 718, 190. Please dont get lost.'),
(44569, 'I respect you for overcoming the Six Deadly Sins and coming this far. Im the last Ascetic, [Ascetic of Charity] Miel. Are you ready for the last lesson?'),
