Hmm. You brought them. Time to burn my craftsman`s passion. |There you go. Hope it comes to good use.'),
(613, '[Blacksmith] Heppa will make you 16Lv weaponry for 3 Bulture horns and 5 iron bar.'),
(614, 'Master, I heard that [Blacksmith] Heppa has been awfully down lately. Let`s go see what`s getting him so down.'),
(615, 'Master, I heard that [Blacksmith] Heppa has been awfully down  lately. Let`s go see what`s getting him so down.'),
(616, 'Frankly, I`ve been concerned about weapon production methods lately. As you`re well aware, unremarkable ingredients produce stock weapons and special ingredients are so hard to come by  ...|I`m contemplating using Apples of Moradon but there aren`t many warriors in Moradon who can hunt werewolves, the only ones with  Apples of Moradon.'),
(617, 'Now it occurs to me that you may have the ability to hunt werewolf. You dont need to be modest.  My eyes, which have dealt with numerous warriors and knights for decades, are relatively correct! So I want to ask of you a favor. Can you hunt werewolf and collect 3 Apples of Moradon for me? I really need the materials as I am in a slump.'),
(618, 'Master, now werewolf is not a difficult opponent any more. You are really great. By the way, I collected 3 Apples of Moradon. Hurry, bring them to [Blacksmith] Hepa.'),
(619, 'Master, now werewolf is not a difficult opponent any more. You are really great. By the way, I collected 3 Apples of Moradon. Hurry, bring them to [Blacksmith] Hepa.'),
(620, 'I need 3 Apples of Moradon for my research on weapon production!'),
(621, 'Wow, you brought the Apples of Moradon I asked for. I feel motivated already. Shall we begin?'),
(622, 'In order to help the research on weapon production by [Blacksmith] Hepa who is in a slump, we need 3 Apples of Moradon. If you bring 3 Apples of Moradon to [Blacksmith] Hepa, you can receive experience as compensation.'),
(623, 'Master, [Blacksmith] Heppa`s technique isn`t what it used to be. He seems to be preoccupied with something...'),
(624, 'Master, [Blacksmith] Heppa`s technique isn`t what it used to be. He seems to be preoccupied with something...'),
(625, 'I guess I could tell someone like you about the Armor of Destruction. It can be made with the Amulet of Destruction which can be obtained by hunting Hell Hounds that dwell in the mainland. Armor of Destruction is made by melting and mixing the Amulet of Destruction and iron bar. It sounds savage but its performance is guaranteed.'),
(626, 'At least 7 Amulets of Destruction and 15 iron bar are needed to make the Armor of Destruction. Want to give it a shot?'),
(627, 'At least 7 Amulets of Destruction are required to make Armor of Destruction.'),
(628, 'Didn`t I tell you at least 15 iron bar are needed to make the Armor of Destruction?'),
(629, 'It requires a lot of work hence I will charge a fee of 500,000 Noahs.'),
(630, 'Here, this is the Armor of Destruction made just for you.'),
