(648, 'Didn`t I tell you at least 3 iron bar are needed to make the Body Armor of Destruction boots?'),
(649, 'It requires a lot of work hence I will charge a fee of 500,000 Noahs.'),
(650, 'Here, this is the Body Armor of Destruction made just for you.'),
(651, 'To make Body Armor of Destruction top, you must take 7 Amulets of Destruction, 15 iron bar, and 500,000 Noahs to [Blacksmith] Heppa.'),
(652, 'To make Body Armor of Destruction top, you must take 5 Amulets of Destruction, 12 iron bar, and 500,000 Noahs to [Blacksmith] Heppa.'),
(653, 'To make Body Armor of Destruction helmet, you must take 4 Amulets of Destruction, 9 iron bar, and 500,000 Noahs to [Blacksmith] Heppa.'),
(654, 'To make Body Armor of Destruction gauntlet, you must take 3 Amulets of Destruction, 6 iron bar, and 500,000 Noahs to [Blacksmith] Heppa.'),
