(656, 'Master. You ¡l earn a Wolfmans Claw if you catch Lycan here. Ask [Sentinel] Melverick.'),
(657, 'Phew! Our masters armor is too old. Theres a lot of armor in Folk Villages Mercenary Storage... You should ask  Osmond for a favor.'),
(658, 'Phew! Our masters armor is too old. Theres a lot of armor in Folk Villages Mercenary Storage... You should ask  Osmond for a favor.'),
(659, 'This is Apple of Moradon. Emm, it looks delicious, and its worth its weight in coin. Heh!'),
(660, 'This is Apple of Moradon. Emm, it looks delicious, and its worth its weight in coin. Heh!'),
(661, 'Ehh?? The way I see it, <selfname>s wearing some good armor!'),
(662, 'Thanks. Now I can finish my new fishing tool...'),
(663, 'The best Fishing Cork is made with Wolfmans Claw!! Wolfmans Claw, equals Fishing Cork. Simple! Moradon equals apple, apple equals Moradon! Ha Ha Ha!'),
(664, 'I commend your passion but don`t save your strength.'),
(665, 'You should contribute to your country if you`ve returned home after wandering for so long. I`ve got just the mission for a new recruit like you.'),
(666, 'Master, if Moradon has Mercenary Captain Cougar, we have [Captain] Polkwein. It wouldn`t hurt to say hello.'),
(667, 'Not long ago, Recons from Karus infiltrated our country, examined our land and began to draft a map. We planted a spy among them in return. And that spy submitted regular reconnaissance reports. But somehow, the soldier who went to receive the reconnaissance report didn`t come back this time.'),
(668, 'I need a favor. Go take out the hostiles and establish contact with our spy. Give him this [Orders from Captain] and return with [3 Scouting Maps] and [Reconnaissance Report]. Well, you up to it?'),
(669, 'Master, all [Reconnaissance Report] and [3 Scouting Maps] have been gathered. Hurry back to [Captain] Folkwine.'),
(670, 'Master, all [Reconnaissance Report] and [3 Scouting Maps] have been gathered. Hurry back to [Captain] Folkwine.'),
(671, 'What happened to the reconnaissance map? Don`t tell me you dropped it somewhere.'),
(672, 'Listen, I told you to bring the reconnaissance report. Just what were you doing?'),
(673, 'Good work. You`ve successfully completed your mission.'),
(674, '(whisper whisper) I`m a bogus Recon who infiltrated this house. You`d better leave before other Recons catch on.'),
(675, 'I`d better share my mission with you.'),
(676, 'This is the reconnaissance report. I hope you deliver it safely to the captain.'),
(677, 'You didn`t bring the captain`s written order? Did you come here to fool around?'),
(678, 'And you must attack the Recons around me now and confiscate the reconnaissance map from them. Without the map, the reconnaissance report is utterly useless. Mark my words.'),
(679, 'Weve got a spy among the enemy scouts. Find the scouts and establish contact with our spy to receive [Reconnaissance Report]. Also, defeat all enemy scouts and collect all [3 Scouting Maps] you can find.'),
(680, 'We have plenty of cooking ingredients but it`s not time to eat yet so just hold your horses.'),
(681, 'Don`t you think I should make a lavish dish!?'),
(682, 'Master, it`s time for the Imperial Palace Chef to start cooking. Go and see him.'),
(683, 'Oh, no, I need to make BBQ and I`m short on Tyon meat.'),
(684, 'Can you find me 2 slabs of Tyon meat from the nearby farm? I`ll give you a hefty reward and some BBQ. What do you say?'),
(685, 'Master, you`ve collected all slabs of Tyon meat. Let`s go to the Imperial Palace Chef.'),
(686, 'Tyons live to the right of the nearby farm. They`re a bit wild so be careful now.'),
(687, 'Wow! You brought them!?!? Here`s your reward.'),
(688, 'Can I ask you one more favor?!'),
(689, 'Please take this BBQ to the Lunar Gate Sentinel. I`m too busy to take it myself. I`ll give you a nice gift if you do this for me.'),
(690, 'If you`re craving something delicious, you`ve come to the right place.'),
(691, 'Today, the Imperial Palace Chef will be bringing  BBQ.  Did you see him when you were coming here?'),
(692, 'Thanks. For bringing the food, I mean.|Erm, look, Im sorry to ask you this, but could you take this Ring to my girl? Youll find her near the Islante Entrace.'),
(693, 'I`m sorry to ask you a favor but I`m hoping you, <selfname>, would do this for me. Take this ring to my love. She`ll be somewhere near the Islante entrance.'),
(694, 'I was wondering if you can take this ring to my love. I heard she`s always lingering somewhere near the Islante entrance. You should be able to spot her there.')
