(12452, 'Welcome. As you know, we need Feather of Hellfire Dragon in order to fight against Pirak. For players who donate more than 100 Feather of Hellfire Dragon, 1 of 3 titles will be given. (Hellfire Dragon , Terrae Dragon, Storm Dragon). Would you like to donate?'),
