(12454, 'Thank you. You are worthy to receive the title. Please defeat Pirak?'),
(12455, 'Knight of Hellfire Dragon, you already have the title. Please be safe.'),
(12456, 'Sir, I heard that few knights can use the power of Hellfire Dragon since Pirak was unleashed. People say that Hellfire Dragons power grants 50% increase in attack. I wish I had that kind of power.'),
(12457, 'You can use the power of the Hellfire Dragon by killing monsters of your level or obtaining Hellfire Dragon Chest which spawns at Melee arena. Hellfire Dragon Chest spawns at Melee arena at 1:00 , 7:00 everyday.'),
(12458, 'Welcome. I can exchange Hellfire Dragon Egg or Wings of Hellfire Dragon Exchange Voucher for Wings of Hellfire. Hellfire Dragon Chest spawns at the Melee Arena at 1:00, 7:00 everyday.'),
