(12484, 'Welcome. The only way to defeat Hellfire Dragon Pirak is by using the power of Dragon Stone. Would you please give your Dragon Stones to me? I will reward the top 1-20 players who donated the most Dragon Stones. (Garges Weapon, Wings of Hellfire Dragon, etc.)'),
