 Nest of the Fire Dragon is the habitat of Red Dragon, a monster incomparably powerful to previous monsters. If you are not prepared to put your life on the line as the bravest warrior of Adonis, you should not enter.

Do you want to enter Nest of the Fire Dragon?'),
(43603, 'You don`t have the [Marble of the Dragon] which grants entry into the Nest of the Fire Dragon. You can obtain the marble from the subordinates of Isiloon.'),
(43604, 'You do not have a Helmet of Wrath?'),
(43605, 'Here is the Helmet of Wrath. Good use.'),
(43606, 'Master! Mr. Potrang is looking for you.'),
(43607, 'Master! Mr. Potrang is looking for you.'),
(43608, 'We are very tired and hungry. In this state, we wont be able to last long. Get some worms to make some food. You should be able to know how to get your own food.'),
(43609, 'Worms will be near Moradon Castle. There are people who arent well. Could you get 5 more?'),
(43610, 'Good job. We will not starve now.'),
(43611, 'Can I help you? Why are you looking for me?'),
(43612, 'I have nothing to ask of you.'),
(43613, 'Its easy to get the Apple of Moradon.'),
(43614, 'Good job. This will be enough for us to not starve for a while.'),
(43615, 'Master! Mr. Potrangs looking for you.'),
(43616, 'Master! Mr. Potrangs looking for you.'),
(43617, 'Good to see you. There are people who cant even move because of what Draki has done. Could you please help them out?'),
(43618, 'We need blankets and something that they can use to wash their body, but we need to eat something first. Could you get us some Apple of Moradon? Apples of Moradon can be obtained from worms.'),
(43619, 'If you get the Apples of Moradon, others will make blankets and towels.'),
(43620, 'Good job. Thank you for what you have done.'),
(43621, 'Im sorry to ask you for another request. But could you help us one more time?'),
(43622, 'Recently, Bandicoots have increased in their population and are ruining our precious crops. Help us catch 5 Bandicoots.'),
(43623, 'I can tell how many you have, so make sure that you have enough.'),
(43624, 'You have them all. Well done.'),
(43625, 'Master! Potrang is calling again.'),
(43626, 'Master! Potrang is calling again.'),
(43627, 'Life has gotten better since we have settled in here, but now we need to get the trust of the townspeople.'),
(43628, 'You dont need every single townspersons trust, but make sure to convince the influential ones. Then, others trust will follow. Go to those with the power and obtain their tokens of trust.'),
(43629, 'I dont think you have their trust yet. Try harder.'),
(43630, 'Well done. Because of you, the townspeople will trust us.'),
(43631, 'Potrang has told me whats happened and as I observe what youve done, I can tell that you can be trustworthy. Ill give you this. This is the proof of our trust in you.'),
(43632, 'Thank you for completing my request. Ive heard that you are trying to get townspeoples trust? This will help you then. This is a token of my trust.'),
(43633, 'Seems like you are a good person. Ill give you a token of my trust for you.'),
(43634, 'Master! Mr. Bilbor is looking for you.'),
(43635, 'Master! Mr. Bilbor is looking for you.'),
(43636, 'Welcome. I have a request for you.'),
(43637, 'Looters have been showing up near Moradon harbor and bothering the townspeople. Could you please go find them and defeat them?'),
(43638, 'Im so anxiously waiting now? those Looters need to be gotten rid of ASAP!'),
(43639, 'Thank you. I heard that you are trying to get the townspeoples trust. This will help you.'),
(43640, 'Master! Kaishan is looking for you!'),
(43641, 'Master! Kaishan is looking for you!'),
(43642, 'Recently Ive heard that you are doing good deeds so Ive come to ask you a favor.'),
(43643, 'Apple of Moradon can be found by defeating monsters near Moradon. Many are looking for this so that they can see what can come out of it. <selfname> could you help us?'),
(43644, 'Still not done? Collecting 20  Apple of Moradon seem harder than I imagined.'),
(43645, 'You have collected them all! Thank you. While you were collecting the Apples of Moradon, Potrang has came by. Ill give you a certificate now.'),
(43646, 'Master! Master!! Potrang is looking for you!'),
(43647, 'Glad you are here now. The reason I called for you is because Jed from Folk Village has asked for an aid.'),
